NK064(ngu)001:1: // gu h+ya pa ti sa n+d+h+ya lam k+aa ra n+aa
NK064(ngu)001:2: ma sh+r+ai gu h+ya ga r+b+ha ta t+wa bi ni
NK064(ngu)001:3: sh+tsa ya ta n+t+ra s+ya bri t+ti bi ha ra
NK064(ngu)001:6: // dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK064(ngu)001:7: pa'i rgyud kyi 'grel pa gsang bdag dgongs rgyan zhes
NK064(ngu)001:10: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK064(ngu)001:11: pa'i rgyud kyi 'grel pa gsang bdag dgongs rgyan zhes
NK064(ngu)001:12: bya ba / dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:13: ngo bo bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la gus pas
NK064(ngu)001:14: bya ba / phyag 'tshal lo // gdod ma'i dbyings su rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:15: rnam par grol las rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun //
NK064(ngu)001:16: spro dang bsdu ba'i byed po bcom ldan 'das //
NK064(ngu)001:17: kun bzang lha yi lha la dang por 'dud //
NK064(ngu)001:18: mtha' yi rtog pas mi bskyod rdo rje'i thugs //
NK064(ngu)001:19: mtha' bral chos dbyings ngang du rtogs gyur pas //
NK064(ngu)001:20: mtha' dang dbus med rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor cher //
NK064(ngu)001:21: mtha' yas rgyud don 'chad pa'i skyes bu rgyal //
NK064(ngu)001:22: rab 'byams bde bar gshegs pa ma lus pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:23: rmad byung thugs kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i mdzod //
NK064(ngu)001:24: 'dzin mdzad rgyal sras thu bo gang lags pa //
NK064(ngu)001:25: de la dngos po kun gyis phyag bagyi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:26: chos dbyings mkha' la thabs shes mkha' lding gis //
NK064(ngu)001:27: drangs pa'i lam rgyud shing rta la bskyon nas //
NK064(ngu)001:28: rnam grol gling du bde bar 'khrid mdzad pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:29: lam mkhan rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs la 'dud //
NK064(ngu)001:30: khyad par gsang bdag drin las gsang chen gyi //
NK064(ngu)001:31: bka' babs d+r+wa ma lnga dang rgyal po dzah /
NK064(ngu)001:32: rgyud don rnam par 'grel la zla bral ba //
NK064(ngu)001:33: sgeg rdor sangs rgyas gsang ba rnam gnyis mchod //
NK064(ngu)001:34: bsil ldan mkha' la thugs rje'i rta bdun gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:35: gsang chen nyi ma 'dren mdzad pad 'byung dang //
NK064(ngu)001:36: bi ma mi tra lo chen rma gnyags zung //
NK064(ngu)001:37: bka' srol gcig 'dus gnubs chen rnams la 'dud //
NK064(ngu)001:38: gangs can ri yi sul du theg mchog gi //
NK064(ngu)001:39: 'jigs med chos sgras lta ngan ri dwags kun //
NK064(ngu)001:40: skrag mdzad phyogs las rnam rgyal mi'i seng ge //
NK064(ngu)001:41: zur gyi rigs 'khrungs mes dbon rnam gsum rgyal //
NK064(ngu)001:42: gang gi bka' srol kho nas 'dzin ma'i khyon //
NK064(ngu)001:43: khyab mdzad bshes gnyen tshogs dang de las gzhan //
NK064(ngu)001:44: legs bshad gtam gyi 'byung gnas rong zom dang //
NK064(ngu)001:45: dri med 'od zer rnams la'ang gus phyag 'tshal //
NK064(ngu)001:46: glo bur las skyes ma rig chu 'dzin gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:47: mtha' bral chos dbyings nam mkha' bsgribs gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:48: de sel mdzad po gter chen bla ma las //
NK064(ngu)001:49: gzhan du ma dmigs dad brgya'i gtsug gis mchod //
NK064(ngu)001:50: gang zhig phung khams skye mched ltar snang 'gro ba'i rtog tshogs ji snyed kun //
NK064(ngu)001:51: ye nas rnam grol rang bzhin rnam dag 'khor 'das ro mnyam dkyil 'khor cher //
NK064(ngu)001:52: mkha' ltar mi phyed thams cad bdag nyid rtag bzhugs bde ba chen po'i sku //
NK064(ngu)001:53: rang byung ye shes don dam snying po byang chub sems la gus pas 'dud //
NK064(ngu)001:54: gang yang dpal ldan snying po'i rgyud rgyal 'dir //
NK064(ngu)001:55: sngon rabs mkhas pa'i rnam bshad dpag med cing //
NK064(ngu)001:56: bdag ltas don gzhan brjod pa'ang nus min kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:57: don la mos pa 'ga' yis bskul ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:58: khyad par bdag nyid 'di na tshig gcig tsam //
NK064(ngu)001:59: smra ba gang de'ang gsung rab 'di yi mthu //
NK064(ngu)001:60: de phyir rgyud don ji bzhin mthong min kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:61: gus pa kho nas tshul 'di brjod la spro //
NK064(ngu)001:62: gang gi tshe gdod ma'i dbyings su rig pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:63: shes rnam par grol bas spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:64: byang chub chen po brnyes nas /
NK064(ngu)001:65: gtsang ma'i gnas spangs pa'i 'og min chen po'i gnas su rigs bdag drug pa'i phyag rgyar bstan te /
NK064(ngu)001:66: 'chad pa'i skyes bu de bzhin gshegs pa lnga yang mngon par snang bar mdzad nas /
NK064(ngu)001:67: rdo rje gsang ba la sogs pa rig pa khyad
NK064(ngu)001:68: par can gyi 'khor rnams la rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK064(ngu)001:69: nyid dgongs pa brda'i tshig gis dus rtag pa rgyun
NK064(ngu)001:70: gyi 'khor los bgro bar mdzad pa las rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:71: g.yo ba'i rtsol rtog mi mnga' bzhin du gdul bya
NK064(ngu)001:72: gdug pa can rnams kyi ngor 'jigs byed chen po
NK064(ngu)001:73: dpal he ru ka'i rol pa tshad med pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:74: / thun mong gi gdul bya rnams la 'dul byed
NK064(ngu)001:75: kyi ston pa thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das
NK064(ngu)001:76: drug thugs rig pa ye shes kyi byin rlabs las
NK064(ngu)001:77: spro ba sogs ji ltar 'tshams pas 'dul ba'i sgron
NK064(ngu)001:78: ma rnam par bkod de chos kyi 'khor lo bsam
NK064(ngu)001:79: gyis mi khyab pa bskor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:80: de dag gi don dang 'bras bu thams cad gang du 'du ba'i snod dang /
NK064(ngu)001:81: gang las 'phro ba'i gzhi lta bu ni dpal gsang ba'i snying po yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:83: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK064(ngu)001:84: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:85: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK064(ngu)001:86: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK064(ngu)001:87: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK064(ngu)001:88: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK064(ngu)001:89: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK064(ngu)001:92: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK064(ngu)001:93: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK064(ngu)001:95: bshad rgyud rgyas pa las kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:96: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK064(ngu)001:97: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:98: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK064(ngu)001:99: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK064(ngu)001:101: des na 'dir gang bshad par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK064(ngu)001:102: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:103: rgyud dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK064(ngu)001:104: nges pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid
NK064(ngu)001:105: yin la / de gang gis 'chad na /
NK064(ngu)001:107: bla ma dam pa rnams kyis don la rton pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:108: dgongs 'grel mdzad pa de dag la brten nas so
NK064(ngu)001:110: slob dpon chen po bi ma la'i khog gzhung gsal sgron du /
NK064(ngu)001:111: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK064(ngu)001:114: 'go smos pas go ba'i dbang po yang rab rnams la mtshan bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:115: dbang po 'bring po rnams la spyi'i don rnam par dbye bas bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:116: dbang po tha ma rnams la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas spros te bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:119: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK064(ngu)001:120: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK064(ngu)001:121: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK064(ngu)001:122: skal pa can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:123: zhes mtshan gyi rnam grangs gsum du bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:124: dang po rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang
NK064(ngu)001:125: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsum gyi mtshan thun mong du
NK064(ngu)001:126: bstan pa ni / rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:128: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:129: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:130: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:131: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:132: zhes pas rdo rje ni rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa ste shes rab stong pa nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:133: sems dpa' ni sat+wa'i sgra brtan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:135: rtogs pa gsum la skabs 'dir 'jug pas na /
NK064(ngu)001:136: thabs rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems shes rab
NK064(ngu)001:137: stong pa nyid dang ro gcig pa'i zung 'jug rang
NK064(ngu)001:138: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de rdo rje ltar
NK064(ngu)001:139: brtan pas sam / de nyid kyi phyag rgyas 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:140: 'das kyi chos thams cad la btab pas mnyam pa
NK064(ngu)001:141: nyid du bsdus pa ni gzhi 'bras gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:142: pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK064(ngu)001:143: gnas lugs kyi don de nyid sgrib gnyis zad cing
NK064(ngu)001:144: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyes bus mngon du rtogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:145: ni 'bras bu'i rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK064(ngu)001:146: gang rtogs pa'i ye shes de yang rdo rje ltar gnyis su med par gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:147: de nyid mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar snang ba dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:148: gyi gtso bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:149: mi bskyod pa la yang rdo rje sems dpa' zhes
NK064(ngu)001:150: grags so // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:152: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK064(ngu)001:153: zhes pas 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:154: ris su ma chad pa'i rgyus cir yang 'phrul pa
NK064(ngu)001:155: ni phung po lnga ste rgyu 'bras 'brel ba can
NK064(ngu)001:157: rgyu mtshan des shes rab dbyings stong pa nyid dang /
NK064(ngu)001:158: thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes gnyis zung
NK064(ngu)001:159: du 'brel ba ni nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK064(ngu)001:160: ba dang / de'i rtags lha yab yum zung du
NK064(ngu)001:161: 'brel ba ni drang don brda'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:162: ba dang / // yang na sgyu ma ni rtog tshogs //
NK064(ngu)001:164: d+r+wa ba ni rang bzhin gnyis su med par 'brel ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:166: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes la //
NK064(ngu)001:167: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK064(ngu)001:171: mang la 'brel ba d+r+wa ba'i don //
NK064(ngu)001:173: 'di nyid kyi le'u bzhi pa las ni yab la sgyu 'phrul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:174: yum la d+r+wa bar bshad cing /
NK064(ngu)001:175: gzhi dang 'bras bu la mtshan ji skad du thob
NK064(ngu)001:176: pa'i nges pas shes thob kyi bya byed dang 'brel
NK064(ngu)001:178: de mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:179: gnyis pa che ba las mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:182: so sor bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu)001:184: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK064(ngu)001:185: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:188: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi //
NK064(ngu)001:190: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:192: sngon du 'gro ba'i bdag nyid pas //
NK064(ngu)001:193: ming nyid thog mar smos pa gces //
NK064(ngu)001:194: zhes pa ltar glegs bam gyi klad du bkod pa'i mtshan te 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:196: don gyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:197: tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:201: 'bras bu yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud don /
NK064(ngu)001:203: 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:206: ston pa la sogs rab dbye bas //
NK064(ngu)001:207: phun sum tshogs pa lngar brjod do //
NK064(ngu)001:208: zhes pas gang du ston 'khor tshogs pa de'i tshe
NK064(ngu)001:209: rgyud don 'byung bar nges pa'i phyir phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:210: pa lnga ldan ni gleng gazhi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:211: ci'i phyir gleng gzhi zhes bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:212: d+aa na'i sgra las bka' yin min du rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:213: the tshom can dag la phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:214: lo rgyus brjod pas yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin
NK064(ngu)001:216: gang gleng bar bya ba rgyud kyi don 'byung ba'i rgyu'am gzhir 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:218: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:219: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:221: thabs lam dang sbyar te nang gsang ltar 'chad pa dag yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:224: rgyud 'byung ba khyad par can gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:225: zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched du bstan pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:226: sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gazhi'am /
NK064(ngu)001:227: bstan pa spyi'i gleng gzhir grags pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:228: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:230: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK064(ngu)001:231: skabs las gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK064(ngu)001:232: gnang 'dri'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:233: de des gsung la ma rag pa //
NK064(ngu)001:234: zhes pas ston 'khor dri lan gyi sbyor bas rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:235: don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par 'byung ma rag
NK064(ngu)001:236: pa'o // ci'i phyir gleng bslang zhes bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:237: gang gleng bar bya ba ni rgyud don yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:238: de nyid gleng bar bskul ba ni bslang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:239: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:241: thun mong ma yin pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:242: thun mong gi gleng bslang gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:244: ston pa yab yum gyis lhan cig pa'i 'khor la zab dbang bskur ba'i sbyor bas mdun bsus te /
NK064(ngu)001:245: thabs shes gnyis med kyi cha bzung nas gleng bslang ba gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:247: 'khor gyis gzhan don du rgyud bshad par zhus pas ston pa'i thugs rje skyes te /
NK064(ngu)001:248: dngos dang brgyud pa'i sgo nas 'chad par dgyes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:249: gsum pa 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:250: rgyud gsum gyi rnam bzhag spyir bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:251: lam cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:254: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK064(ngu)001:256: zhes pas spyir rgyun chags pa'i don gyis na rgyud ces bya la /
NK064(ngu)001:258: gang rtogs par bya ba gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:259: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa thabs sam lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:260: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud do //
NK064(ngu)001:262: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:263: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK064(ngu)001:266: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK064(ngu)001:267: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:268: ces pas gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang
NK064(ngu)001:269: rig pa byang chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:270: spyod yul dang bral bar ye nas gnas pa gang
NK064(ngu)001:271: yin pa ste / khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:272: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:274: dri bcas de bzhin nyid la sogs pa'i tha snyad gang la 'jug pa'i gazhi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:275: de nyid gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi ldog cha gang
NK064(ngu)001:276: rung dang ma bstun par spyir bzhag pa na rang
NK064(ngu)001:278: glo bur gyi dri ma sbyong ba dang bsal stobs
NK064(ngu)001:279: kyis mngon du gyur pa la ltos nas lam dang
NK064(ngu)001:281: ci'i phyir gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:282: thabs kyi rkyen gyis zin pa dang ma zin pa
NK064(ngu)001:283: las 'khor ba dang myang 'das su 'grub par byed
NK064(ngu)001:284: pas na / 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i 'byung gazhi'am rgyur gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:285: de nyid sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du
NK064(ngu)001:286: rang bzhin 'gyur ba med par rgyun chags su 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:289: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK064(ngu)001:290: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK064(ngu)001:293: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK064(ngu)001:294: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:299: dang po rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:300: ngo bo'i gzhi dang btags pa'i gzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:301: zhes pas sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK064(ngu)001:302: par dag pa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ni
NK064(ngu)001:303: dri ma sbyong ba'i gzhi nor bu rin po che
NK064(ngu)001:304: lta bu ste gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:305: dang / log pa'i zhen snang yul dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:306: ni sbyang bya'i dri ma 'dam rdzab lta bu ste
NK064(ngu)001:307: dang / / med snang glo bur ba yin pas 'khrul pa btags pa'i gzhi zhes gsungs so //
NK064(ngu)001:308: zhen snang nyid 'khor ba 'grub byed kyi rgyu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:309: rnam shes kyi 'jug pa ma zad bar rgyun chags
NK064(ngu)001:310: pa tsam yin kyang bcos ma glo bur gyi chos
NK064(ngu)001:311: yin pas 'bras bu'i nya ra len du gyur pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:313: rig pas dpyad don gyi stong nyid med dgag kyang rgyu rgyud mtshan nyid pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:314: nyer len gyi rgyu dang rgyun gyi don gnyis ka mi gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:316: rgyu rgyud de glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral
NK064(ngu)001:317: bar byed pa'i thabs shes 'jug gi byed rtsol dang
NK064(ngu)001:318: bcas pa ste / de yang ngo bo skyed byed
NK064(ngu)001:319: shes rab rnam gsum gyis bskyed bya thun mong dang
NK064(ngu)001:320: mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam skye ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:321: de ltar yang rim gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:322: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:323: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:325: ci'i phyir thabs sam lam gyi rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:326: thob bya 'bras rgyud nyid mngon du byed pa'i lhan cig byed rkyen yin pas thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:327: gang gis gang du bgrod bya'i rten yin pas lam ste /
NK064(ngu)001:328: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK064(ngu)001:329: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:330: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:331: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK064(ngu)001:334: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:336: de la'ang nye ring gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:337: rnal 'byor bla na med pa khyad par gyi lam
NK064(ngu)001:338: 'di ni nye ba'i lam mam thabs rgyud yin la
NK064(ngu)001:339: / de las gzhan pa thun mong gi lam nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:340: phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi lam rnams ni skabs 'dir ring ba'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:341: de yang gzhi 'bras gnyis dang shes thob kyi bya
NK064(ngu)001:342: byed 'brel ba can du gnas pa'i phyir thabs bar
NK064(ngu)001:343: ma chad par rgyun chags su 'byung bas na rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:344: do // khyad par gyi lam la dbye na /
NK064(ngu)001:345: thabs kyis nges pa'i lam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:346: shes rab rnam par grol ba'i lam gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:348: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:351: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK064(ngu)001:352: zhes pas gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par brtul zhugs
NK064(ngu)001:353: kyi spyod pa rmad du byung ba'i sgo nas 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:354: bu myur du 'grub par byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:355: mak+shi ka'i sbyor bas lcags khams yud tsam gyis gser du bsgyur ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:358: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK064(ngu)001:361: 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:362: bas 'khor lo bzhir bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa
NK064(ngu)001:363: la bslab pa rim gyis pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:365: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK064(ngu)001:366: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK064(ngu)001:367: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK064(ngu)001:369: 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas dbab bzung
NK064(ngu)001:370: ldog khyab kyi sbyor bas skad cig la bde stong
NK064(ngu)001:371: gnyis med kyi ye shes bskyed pa thabs lam cig
NK064(ngu)001:372: car ba ste / rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:373: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:374: gsang ba mchog gis sbyin par byed //
NK064(ngu)001:377: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK064(ngu)001:378: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:379: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK064(ngu)001:380: ces pas gtso bor shes rab rnam pa gsum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:381: sgo nas rang rgyud kyi 'ching ba chos nyid du
NK064(ngu)001:383: rin po che koostu b+ha dang lhan cig bzhag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:384: rdo'i khams rim gyis gser du 'gyur ba bzhin no
NK064(ngu)001:387: ring ba'ang rim dang cig car ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:388: zhes pas dbang po yang rab kha cig dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:389: chig chod du rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:390: yod de cig car ba zhes bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:391: yang rim gyis rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa ni rim gyis pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:395: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK064(ngu)001:396: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:397: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK064(ngu)001:398: zhes pas mtshan nyid gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:399: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK064(ngu)001:400: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK064(ngu)001:401: lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:404: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK064(ngu)001:405: zhes pas gzhal bya zhen snang nyid 'jal byed gtan
NK064(ngu)001:406: tshigs rnams kyis gtan la phab pas rtogs bya'i lta
NK064(ngu)001:407: ba rang bzhin rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don de
NK064(ngu)001:408: bzhin nyid de rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med
NK064(ngu)001:409: rang gsal du rjen par rtogs pa ni grub mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:411: rgya mtsho dang ba'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:412: sgra brten yid la byed min par //
NK064(ngu)001:413: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK064(ngu)001:414: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul bar //
NK064(ngu)001:415: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK064(ngu)001:416: thos bsam brten pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK064(ngu)001:418: gang dag sngags kyi grub mtha' ni lta ba dbu
NK064(ngu)001:419: ma las thabs khyad par du 'phags pas phye ba
NK064(ngu)001:421: bden pa dbyer med snod bcud dag mnyam chen por
NK064(ngu)001:422: gtan la 'bebs pa'i sngags kyi thun mong ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:423: pa'i lta ba la ce re long du song ba
NK064(ngu)001:424: yin no // gal te rig pa 'gyur med la
NK064(ngu)001:425: de bzhin nyid du byas pa ni nges don gyi
NK064(ngu)001:426: mdo sde zab mo rnams las kyang 'byung bas rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:427: bya'i yul la khyad par med dam snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:430: de bzhin nyid de bla na med pa'i rgyud 'dir
NK064(ngu)001:431: rgyu rgyud du 'jog pa'i tshe na lhan cig skyes
NK064(ngu)001:432: pa mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:433: du byas pa ni sngags kyi khyad chos su bzhed
NK064(ngu)001:434: pa yin te / rdo rje me long las /
NK064(ngu)001:435: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK064(ngu)001:436: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK064(ngu)001:437: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK064(ngu)001:438: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK064(ngu)001:439: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK064(ngu)001:442: des na gtso bos gang zhig 'pho med lhan skyes lus kyi bde ba sngags kyi theg par bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:445: rtag tu rang bzhin bde ba can //
NK064(ngu)001:446: 'jig rten khams ni gang du yang //
NK064(ngu)001:447: sangs rgyas gzhan du rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:448: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK064(ngu)001:449: sangs rgyas gzhan du bstan pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:451: gzhan yang gnyis snang 'khor ba'i chos 'di rnams thag khra'i sbrul ltar med snang glo bur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:452: de dag gi snang gzhi gnas lugs de bzhin nyid yin pa'i gnad kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:453: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag par gsungs pa yang /
NK064(ngu)001:454: phung sogs kyi snang gzhi de bzhin nyid kyi rtsal
NK064(ngu)001:455: gnyug ma'i ye shes kyi rtsa dang rlung sems la
NK064(ngu)001:456: sogs pa gdod nas sku gsum gyi ngo bor lhun
NK064(ngu)001:458: ye ji bzhin pa'i rigs lnga sogs lha'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa gang yin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:459: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim du /
NK064(ngu)001:460: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:461: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres gsal //
NK064(ngu)001:465: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:466: spyi'i rnam pa tsam sgom pa mos sgom dang //
NK064(ngu)001:467: lam so so'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin bar bslab pa nges rdzogs gnyis su 'dus shing /
NK064(ngu)001:470: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:471: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK064(ngu)001:472: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:473: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:474: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK064(ngu)001:475: skyes pa'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK064(ngu)001:476: zhes pas skye 'chi bar do gsum phrugs gcig sbyong ba'i lam rdzogs par ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:477: 'chi ba 'od gsal dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam stong pa chen po /
NK064(ngu)001:478: de bzhin du bar do dang snying rje sgyu ma /
NK064(ngu)001:479: skyes pa'i rim pa gsum po dang phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK064(ngu)001:481: tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste zag pa dang bcas pa'i lam gyi rnal 'byor lnga yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:482: de las kyang dang po bzhi ni zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor te /
NK064(ngu)001:484: de phyir lam bzhir zag ldog yod //
NK064(ngu)001:486: tshogs sgrub ni sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor yin pas
NK064(ngu)001:487: zag pa yod kyang ldog pa med pa'i lam ste
NK064(ngu)001:488: / spyod pa'i dus grangs nges pas zag med la
NK064(ngu)001:489: dngos su sbyor ba'i bar chad med lam yin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:490: / phyir ro // gsum pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:491: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam mthong sgom mthar lam gsum gyis bsdus pa rig 'dzin bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:492: de yang mthong lam pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:493: chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong yang blo'i nus stobs
NK064(ngu)001:494: che chung gis 'byung ba snyigs ma'i lus ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:495: kyi mes sbyong bar ma nus pa rnam smin rig
NK064(ngu)001:496: 'dzin dang / sbyong bar nus pas skye 'jig med
NK064(ngu)001:497: pa dwangs ma'i lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs
NK064(ngu)001:498: su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:500: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:501: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK064(ngu)001:504: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku can phyag chen rig 'dzin yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:506: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang gi cha lugs 'dzin pa lhun grub rig 'dzin no //
NK064(ngu)001:507: de dag kyang rnam smin rig 'dzin dang rgyu'i theg
NK064(ngu)001:508: pa'i mthong lam rab dga' la gnas pa'i sems dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:510: de las gzhan pa tshe dbang sogs gsum ni rgyu'i theg pa'i sa dang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:512: bcu pa tsam du skal ba mnyam par 'gyur mod kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:513: 'on kyang dgongs spyod kyis khyad par du gyur pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:514: rgyu'i theg pa'i sgom lam sa brgyad pa dang tshe dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:516: mi slob pa'i sa kun tu 'od dang lhun grub rig 'dzin rnams mnyam par bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:517: de ltar yang lam chung las /
NK064(ngu)001:518: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK064(ngu)001:519: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog de //
NK064(ngu)001:520: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK064(ngu)001:521: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK064(ngu)001:522: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK064(ngu)001:524: bsam gtan mig sgron gyi rang 'grel las /
NK064(ngu)001:525: kun tu 'od bsti gnas kyi sa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:526: de ni 'dir lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dngos so //
NK064(ngu)001:528: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi dngos 'bras rgya chen du nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:529: mthong lam gnyis po lam mthar chags kyi skabs su'ang rim par bgrod pa mi srid cing /
NK064(ngu)001:530: rnam smin nas thod brgal du bgrod pa yang mi 'byung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:531: gzhan du cig car ba'i rigs ma yin pa'i lam
NK064(ngu)001:532: pa blo che ba 'ga' zhig phyag rgya gcig spros
NK064(ngu)001:534: tshe dbang nas lhun grub rig 'dzin /
NK064(ngu)001:535: tshe dbang dang rgya chen gnyis nas rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK064(ngu)001:536: rgyas kyi sar lam gzhan bar nas bor la thod
NK064(ngu)001:537: brgal du sbyor ba srid pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:538: de dag la ngang gis blo che ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:539: zung 'jug gi lam bsgom pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:540: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod pa ste thod
NK064(ngu)001:541: brgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum po tshang ba'i phyir ro
NK064(ngu)001:542: // de ltar na tshogs sgrub nas kyang thod brgal 'byung ba srid dam snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:545: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:546: zhes zag med kyi lam gyi 'du sa dang dbye
NK064(ngu)001:547: sa mthong lam yin par gsungs pas lam gzhan bar
NK064(ngu)001:548: nas bor du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:550: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:552: lhun grub ji bzhin mngon byas pa'ang //
NK064(ngu)001:553: btags pa tsam ste gnyis pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:554: de phyir de la de brjod do //
NK064(ngu)001:555: zhes pas sbyang gzhi rgyu rgyud la brten pa'i sbyang
NK064(ngu)001:556: bya glo bur gyi dri ma rnams sbyong byed kyis
NK064(ngu)001:557: legs par sbyangs pas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin mngon
NK064(ngu)001:558: du gyur pa mthar thug pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:559: ci'i phyir 'bras bu'i rgyud du 'gyur zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:561: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:562: ces pas bla na med pa mchog gi 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:563: mthar thug pa don du gnyer ba rnams bsam pa
NK064(ngu)001:564: yongs su rdzogs pas na 'bras bu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:565: nam yang rgyun mi chad pas na rgyud do //
NK064(ngu)001:568: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK064(ngu)001:569: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NK064(ngu)001:570: de yang skabs kyi lnga lnga ste //
NK064(ngu)001:571: zhes pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga
NK064(ngu)001:572: re re la'ang lnga lnga ste 'bras chos nyi shu
NK064(ngu)001:576: mdzad pa phrin las gsum du 'du ba yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:579: dbyings thog tu rig pa'i ye shes grol ba zung 'jug chos kyi sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:580: de las ma g.yos bzhin du sa bcu'i sems dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:581: la mtshan dpe'i rnam par snang ba'i gzugs brnyan longs
NK064(ngu)001:582: sku dang / so skyes rnams la mos pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:583: mthun par sangs rgyas kyi gzugs brnyan ci rigs su
NK064(ngu)001:584: snang ba sprul pa'i sku ste sku gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:585: yang na sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon byang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:586: dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i sku ste gnyis po bsnan pas sku lnga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:587: gnyis pa brten pa ye shes ni /
NK064(ngu)001:588: de'i tshe tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pas ye shes lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:589: cir yang mi dmigs pa chos dbyings ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:590: gsal la rtog pa med pa me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:591: 'khor 'das kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa mnyam nyid ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:592: chos can ma lus pa mngon sum du sa ler gzigs pa sor rtog ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:593: 'gro don mdzad pa la thogs pa med pa'i phrin las 'jug pa bya grub ye shes so //
NK064(ngu)001:594: de dag kyang chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:595: phyi ma bzhi po ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes su 'du bas na ye shes gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:596: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK064(ngu)001:597: de ltar sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa mtha' dag spangs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:598: shes bya thams cad mngon sum du gzigs pa'i spangs
NK064(ngu)001:599: rtogs mthar phyin pa'i mthu las gdul bya'i skal ba
NK064(ngu)001:600: dang 'tshams pa'i phrin las dus las yol ba med
NK064(ngu)001:601: par lhun gyis grub pa nam mkha' ji srid bar
NK064(ngu)001:603: gnyis pa lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:604: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:605: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:606: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK064(ngu)001:608: de kho na nyid lta ba /
NK064(ngu)001:614: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:616: gnas su stob pa mchod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:618: dang po lta ba la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:621: thabs kyi lta spyod chen po ni //
NK064(ngu)001:622: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK064(ngu)001:623: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK064(ngu)001:624: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK064(ngu)001:625: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis //
NK064(ngu)001:626: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK064(ngu)001:627: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK064(ngu)001:628: zhes pas mtha' gang du yang ma reg pa'i sems
NK064(ngu)001:629: nyid ye nas dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun
NK064(ngu)001:630: gyis grub pa ni lhag pa don dam bden pa
NK064(ngu)001:631: dang / de nyid kyi rtsal snang snod bcud sku
NK064(ngu)001:632: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas
NK064(ngu)001:633: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du rdzogs pa ni lhag
NK064(ngu)001:634: pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:635: de gnyis kyang phyogs su lhung ba ma yin par
NK064(ngu)001:636: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par mnyam pa nyid du
NK064(ngu)001:637: gnas shing / der 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las kyang
NK064(ngu)001:638: yang dag par 'das pas na tha snyad tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:639: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK064(ngu)001:642: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK064(ngu)001:643: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa'ang //
NK064(ngu)001:644: de ming zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK064(ngu)001:645: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK064(ngu)001:647: lhag pa zhes pa'i sgra yang don dam bden ngor ma zad /
NK064(ngu)001:648: kun rdzob tu yang chos thams cad la mi gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:649: pa'i bsam spyod dang ldan pas na rgyu'i theg pa
NK064(ngu)001:650: las 'phags pa'i phyir de skad du brjod pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:652: bla med theg pa'i nang nas ni //
NK064(ngu)001:653: don dam du ni dbyer med la //
NK064(ngu)001:654: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK064(ngu)001:655: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK064(ngu)001:656: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK064(ngu)001:657: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK064(ngu)001:658: kun rdzob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK064(ngu)001:659: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:662: drish+ta'i sgra las gnas lugs kyi don la de dang
NK064(ngu)001:663: rjes su mthun pa'i shes rab kyis sgro 'dogs gcod
NK064(ngu)001:666: dbang po yang rab la gtan tshigs kyis rtogs par bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:667: dbang 'bring la rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i rtags la brten nas rtogs par bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:668: dbang rtul la brgyud de rtogs par bya ba nye ring gnyis rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:669: gnyis pa spyod pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:673: rjes mthun spyod pa gzhung bzhin spyad //
NK064(ngu)001:674: ces pas thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:675: lam pa'i sgo gsum gyi bya bar gyur pa gang
NK064(ngu)001:677: tsar+ya'i sgra las spyad bya la tshul bzhin du spyod par byed pa'i don gyis na spyod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:679: spyir lus ngag yid gsum yongs su dag par bya ba yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:681: thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:682: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa gnyis su bshad cing /
NK064(ngu)001:690: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod pa ste rim gyis pa'i spyod pa bdun dang /
NK064(ngu)001:691: blang dor med pa rmad du byung ba cig car ba'i spyod pa dang brgyad do //
NK064(ngu)001:692: gsum pa dkyil 'khor la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:695: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK064(ngu)001:696: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK064(ngu)001:697: zhes pa bkod pa lha'i 'khor lor rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:700: man+da ni snying po'am bcud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:701: la ni 'dzin pa'am len pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:702: snying po'i yon tan gyi gzhi 'dzin pas na snying po len pa zhes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:703: yang sgra gzug po zlum po'am bskor ba'i don la
NK064(ngu)001:704: 'jug pas na gang gtso bo la 'khor gyis bskor
NK064(ngu)001:708: 'grel chung las bcu gnyis su phye yang /
NK064(ngu)001:711: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK064(ngu)001:713: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:715: bzhi pa dbang la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:718: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhis yan lag bsnyad //
NK064(ngu)001:719: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK064(ngu)001:720: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:721: ces pas rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la
NK064(ngu)001:722: brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:723: las kyis thar pa'i myu gu mngon du bskyed pa'am
NK064(ngu)001:724: skye nges kyi nus rung du smin par byed pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:726: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las mngon par gtor ba'am blugs pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:727: sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud cing 'bras bu ye
NK064(ngu)001:728: shes kyi nus pa khyad par can 'jog pas na
NK064(ngu)001:731: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK064(ngu)001:732: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:734: de las kyang bum dbang la phan nus gnyis su phye bas lngar 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:736: dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:737: gnyis pa nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:738: gsum pa nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:739: bzhi pas de nyid brtan par byed //
NK064(ngu)001:740: lnga pas brtan pa nyams lon pas //
NK064(ngu)001:743: de yang zhi ba la phan dbang bcu /
NK064(ngu)001:745: zab dbang gsum ste bco brgyad /
NK064(ngu)001:747: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK064(ngu)001:748: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga ste //
NK064(ngu)001:749: zhes pa ltar phan dbang la nyer brgyad du phye bas sum cu rtsa drug go //
NK064(ngu)001:750: lnga pa dam tshig la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:753: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK064(ngu)001:754: rmi lam du yang dam tshig brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:755: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK064(ngu)001:756: ces pas bsrung bya'i don khyad par can las mi
NK064(ngu)001:757: 'da' bar sdom pa'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:759: sa ma ya'i sgra dngos su yal gam bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:760: 'i tha tshig la 'jug pas ji ltar bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:761: las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir dam
NK064(ngu)001:763: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:764: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis te bco lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:765: de dag las kyang spros na sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:766: drug pa phrin las la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:769: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:770: zhes pas tshad med pa bzhi'i rgyu las byung ba'i byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK064(ngu)001:771: shes rab chen pos zin pa'i sgo nas gtso bor
NK064(ngu)001:772: gzhan don bsgrub pa la dmigs pa'i thabs mkhas kyi
NK064(ngu)001:773: mdzad spyod do // nges tshig ni /
NK064(ngu)001:774: karma zhes pa'i sgra las sgo gsum gyi bya ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:775: mtshan nyid can ni las te byed pa po'i 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:778: zhi ba la sogs rab dbye bas //
NK064(ngu)001:779: las ni rnam pa bzhir bsdus so //
NK064(ngu)001:784: de dag kyang gang gis bya ba'i thabs kyi rim pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:789: phyag rgya'i sgo nas bya ba rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:791: bdag gzhan don grub phrin las ni //
NK064(ngu)001:792: mchod rten phyag rgya'i sgo dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:793: hom bro glu dang rdzas kyis bya //
NK064(ngu)001:795: bdun pa sgrub pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:797: rgyud phyi ma kha che 'gyur las /
NK064(ngu)001:798: 'jig rten pa yi dngos grub ni //
NK064(ngu)001:799: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas thob //
NK064(ngu)001:801: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas so //
NK064(ngu)001:802: zhes pa ltar thabs khyad par can gang gis bsgrub
NK064(ngu)001:803: bya mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub rnam pa
NK064(ngu)001:804: gnyis las gang 'dod don du gnyer ba zhig go
NK064(ngu)001:806: sid+d+hi'i sgra las dngos grub ste bsgrub bya dang /
NK064(ngu)001:807: s+aa d+ha na'i sgra las kun tu len pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:808: 'dod pa'i don len cing thob par byed pa'am sgrub pa byed pas na sgrub pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:814: ro langs tshe dang pra sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu)001:815: lha chen po dang rgyal po bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:816: gdug pa klu 'dul rgyal blon gyi //
NK064(ngu)001:817: chung ma dbang du bya ba gnyis //
NK064(ngu)001:818: yul khams ce spyang rkang mgyogs bskrad //
NK064(ngu)001:819: mi snang gzugs sgrub lha klu mo //
NK064(ngu)001:820: rgyal blon dmag dpon zhang blon sgrub //
NK064(ngu)001:825: yi ge sgyu 'phrul tshogs sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu)001:826: rdo rje sems dang sman sgrub dang //
NK064(ngu)001:827: rigs lnga sgrub dang yum lnga sems //
NK064(ngu)001:828: byin dbab sgrub pa rnam gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:830: ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:831: bye brag so so'i sgrub thabs gud du phyung ba rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:832: gtso bor ston pa ni tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:833: gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang ba'i sgo nas bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i thabs kyis sgrub pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:834: brgyad pa ting nge 'dzin la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:837: gang dang gang du gsal ba'i yid //
NK064(ngu)001:838: ma yengs pa nyid ting 'dzin te //
NK064(ngu)001:839: zhes pas bsgom bya'i don khyad par can las mi g.yo bar gnas pa'i sems rtse gcig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:841: sa ma d+h+ai'i sgra las mnyam pa'i blo ste /
NK064(ngu)001:842: sems rtse gcig tu zin pa'i don gyis na ting nge 'dzin no //
NK064(ngu)001:845: lha yi rnam pa'i sbyor ba yi //
NK064(ngu)001:846: zla ba rdo rje la sogs rim //
NK064(ngu)001:847: bskyed pa'i rim pa zhes su bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:848: rang bzhin grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK064(ngu)001:849: rdzogs pa'i rim pa zhes byar brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:854: bskyed rim la brten skye gnas te //
NK064(ngu)001:855: mnga' skyes la sogs dbye ba yis //
NK064(ngu)001:856: de yang rnam pa bzhi ru 'dod //
NK064(ngu)001:857: ces pas skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba'ang bstun te sgom tshul bzhi'am /
NK064(ngu)001:858: yang na lam rim ltar srid pa mngal skyes rdzus
NK064(ngu)001:859: skyes gnyis dang bstun te rim gyis pa dang cig
NK064(ngu)001:861: thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo la brten pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:862: grol lam zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor rim cig car
NK064(ngu)001:863: gnyis kyis bsdus pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting
NK064(ngu)001:864: nge 'dzin no // dgu pa mchod pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:867: bya byed bya ba byed 'dus pas //
NK064(ngu)001:868: dgyes tshim gyur pa'i dngos po nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:869: ces pas mchod pa'i yul du gyur pa rnams bkur zhing mchod pa'i bsam pas sgo gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:870: yo byad stob pa'i sgo nas kyang mnyes par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:872: p+au dza'i sgra las sngon du bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:873: yang dang yang du dgyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:874: bkur ba'i don gyis gnas su stob pa'i phyir mchod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:877: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:881: gsang ba sbyor sgrol zab mo'am /
NK064(ngu)001:882: zhi khro'i mchod pa bcu bzhi la sogs pa rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:883: bcu pa sngags dang phyag rgya la'ang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:886: yi ge 'dus pa grub pa bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:887: mthu can red pa gang yin pa //
NK064(ngu)001:888: bzhi rdzogs nyid las mi 'da' ba //
NK064(ngu)001:889: gang la snang ba de ngo bo //
NK064(ngu)001:891: thabs shes kyi yi ge 'dus shing byin gyis brlabs
NK064(ngu)001:892: pas nus mthu can du gyur pa ni sngags kyi
NK064(ngu)001:893: ngo bo dang / rig pa phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:894: kyi lha'i skur gsal ba las mi 'da' ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:897: man+t+ra'i sgra las yid shes bde myur du skyob pas na sngags dang /
NK064(ngu)001:898: mu dra'i sgra las 'debs shing mtshon par byed pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:899: rgyas btab pa las 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir mtshan ma'i don gyis na phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:904: bye brag tu de dag gi sgor gyur pa'i sngags la /
NK064(ngu)001:906: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK064(ngu)001:907: zhes pas rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba /
NK064(ngu)001:909: bzlas pa las kyi sngags rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:910: phyag rgya la'ang spyir rtog tshogs ye nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:912: mngon du byas pa'i gnas skabs gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:916: bye brag tu lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:918: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:919: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:921: bzhi pa rgyud kyi dgos 'brel ni //
NK064(ngu)001:923: brjod 'brel dgos pa yang dgos dang //
NK064(ngu)001:924: rgyu rkyen yan lag bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:925: zhes pas mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni brjod par bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:926: de khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud 'di ni rjod par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:927: rjod byed la brten nas brjod bya'i don shes pa ni dgos pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:928: de ltar shes pa'i don nyams su blangs pas thun
NK064(ngu)001:929: mong gi dngos grub thob pa ni nying dgos phra
NK064(ngu)001:930: mo dang / slob pa dang mi slob pa'i zung
NK064(ngu)001:931: 'jug phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub mngon
NK064(ngu)001:932: du gyur pa ni nying dgos mchog go //
NK064(ngu)001:933: de yang brjod bya dang rjod byed gnyis shes bya shes byed dang /
NK064(ngu)001:934: rjod byed dang dgos pa gnyis thabs las thabs byung dang /
NK064(ngu)001:935: dgos pa dang nying dgos gnyis de las de byung dang /
NK064(ngu)001:936: nying dgos dang brjod bya gnyis ngo bo bdag gcig gis 'brel ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:937: ci'i phyir rgyud kyi dgos 'brel zhes bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:938: thob bya mthar thug gi 'bras bu sgrub pa la
NK064(ngu)001:939: med na mi 'byung gi 'brel pa grub pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:941: grol lam dbang btsan du byas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:942: thabs lam dbang btsan du byas pa'i dgos 'brel gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:943: 'dir phyi ma btang snyoms su byas so //
NK064(ngu)001:945: bstan pa'i snying po de yongs su mi nyams shing
NK064(ngu)001:946: bsrung ba'i ched du 'khor rnams la gdams shing gtad
NK064(ngu)001:947: pa'o // ci'i phyir gdams gtad ces bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:948: rang bzhin gyi rgyud las mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'ang yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:949: lam gyi rgyud de mi nub par zungs shig ces gtad pa'ang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:953: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:954: dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad snang ba bzhir bsdus
NK064(ngu)001:956: gzhan gsum shes shing bgrod pa dang thob byar byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:957: rang bzhin gyi rgyud las mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:960: sdud pa po dang bud med dang //
NK064(ngu)001:962: zhes pas yul sdud pa po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:963: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos mig can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:964: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams la gnyer gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:965: gnyis pa tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:967: gang gis brjod bya 'chad byed pa //
NK064(ngu)001:968: de ni rjod byed du bshad do //
NK064(ngu)001:969: zhes pas brjod bya 'chad par byed pa rjod byed sgra'i rgyud dam /
NK064(ngu)001:970: yi ge'i rgyud du grags pa gang yin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:971: de yang ngo bo tshogs pa gsum ldan te /
NK064(ngu)001:972: chos gang la sgra gang zhig de nyid yin pa
NK064(ngu)001:973: lta bur btags nas brjod pa ni ming yin la
NK064(ngu)001:974: / de mang po 'dus pa ni ming gi tshogs so //
NK064(ngu)001:975: ming de nyid spyir yan du ma bcug par rnam
NK064(ngu)001:976: dbyes bye brag so sor phye nas chos de dang
NK064(ngu)001:977: de'i don gyi khyad par ston pa ni tshig yin
NK064(ngu)001:978: cing / ming tshig de dag gsal bar byed pa'i 'bru la ni yi ge zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:982: de 'dus pa las tshigs su bcad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:984: le'u la sogs pa'i rim pas glegs bam gyi bar
NK064(ngu)001:985: du rgyun chags pa las gzhung tshogs yi ge'i rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:986: dam / brjod bya don gyi rgyud mtshon par nus pa'i rjod byed sgra'i rgyud grub pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:987: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK064(ngu)001:988: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK064(ngu)001:991: ston pa'i ye shes kyi rnam par 'phrul pa las
NK064(ngu)001:992: dngos kyi 'khor rnams kyi yid la rgyud don rang
NK064(ngu)001:993: snang ba'am / de nyid ma 'ongs pa'i gdul bya
NK064(ngu)001:994: rnams kyi yid la'ang sgra spyi'i rnam par shar ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:995: ming tshig yi ge gsum tshogs pa'i rgyud gzhung ste
NK064(ngu)001:997: de dang mthun pa'i sgra brjod 'dod kyi dbang gis
NK064(ngu)001:998: gnas dang byed pa sogs 'phrad pa las ngag tu
NK064(ngu)001:999: brjod pa ni sgrar grags pa'i rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1000: de brjod pa'i rten phyi rol du yi ge'i gzugs
NK064(ngu)001:1001: brnyan glegs bam la bkod pa ni brdar gyur pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1002: rgyud gzhung ste / rjod byed kyi sgo nas phye na de tsam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:1003: ci'i phyir sgra'i rgyud ces bya zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:1004: brjod bya'i don nyid rjod byed kyi sgrar snang zhing sgrar grags pa'i don gyis na sgra dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1005: tshigs su bcad pa sogs gzhung gi tshogs rgyun chags
NK064(ngu)001:1006: pas sam gleng gzhi la sogs pa lnga rgyu rkyen
NK064(ngu)001:1007: 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel bas na rgyud do //
NK064(ngu)001:1008: gzhan du na brjod bya la rgyud kyi ming thob pas de rjod byed la'ang rgyud ces btags so //
NK064(ngu)001:1012: rtsa ba'i rgyud nyid la'ang tshig gi tshogs pa le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su bcad de gnas la /
NK064(ngu)001:1013: de yang le'u dang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1015: bco lnga pa rnams kyis rgyu gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1016: le'u gnyis pas rkyen gleng bslang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:1017: le'u gsum pa'i smad nas nyer gcig pa yan chad kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:1018: 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1019: de dag la khyab byed du rgyud kyi dgos 'brel dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1020: le'u tha mas gdams gtad rnams ston cing /
NK064(ngu)001:1021: yongs su shes par bya ba rgyud don la'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:1022: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1023: zhi khro spyi bye brag gi chos rnams le'u gang
NK064(ngu)001:1024: dang gang gis ston tshul sogs kyang spro na zhib
NK064(ngu)001:1026: gsum pa dbang po tha ma rnams la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas spros te bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:1027: rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1028: mtshan de dang ldan pa'i rgyud don dngos so //
NK064(ngu)001:1029: dang po mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1031: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1034: klad du smos pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1035: mtshan gyi don bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1038: bum pa zhes pa'i ming las bum pa'i dngos po go ba ltar /
NK064(ngu)001:1039: dbang po rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don rtogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1040: 'bring gis don gyi rnam grangs tsam brda 'phrod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1041: tha mas kyang sman snod kyi kha byang ltar glegs bam btsal sla ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK064(ngu)001:1044: rang bzhin gsang ba zhes bya ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1045: che ba zhes pa snying po'i don //
NK064(ngu)001:1046: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:1047: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1048: zhes pas mtshan bzhis rgyud kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1051: nges pa'i don rnams bstan no //
NK064(ngu)001:1052: de la gsang ba'i don ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1053: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid gdod ma nas rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:1054: nyid gdod ma nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK064(ngu)001:1055: pas 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du gnas pa ni rgyal
NK064(ngu)001:1056: ba thams cad kyi thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK064(ngu)001:1058: de nyid zab cing gting dpag dka' bas shin tu rtogs dka' ba'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1060: sgeg pa rdo rjes rang bzhin sogs gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1061: bi ma las mi bstan pa'i gsang ba bsnan te bzhir phye na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:1062: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba ni gab pa'i khongs su 'du zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:1063: mi bstan pa'i gsang ba'ang sbas pa'i nang du 'du bas 'dir rtogs dka' ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1064: rtogs su mi rung ba'i khyad par gyis gab sbas gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:1066: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1068: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par /
NK064(ngu)001:1069: sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas //
NK064(ngu)001:1071: de yang gang la gab pa'i yul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1072: gang zag 'khrul pa'i blo can rnams la'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1074: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud gnas lugs de bzhin nyid de rang la rang chas su gnas kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:1075: dbul po'i khyim na yod pa'i sa 'og gi gter
NK064(ngu)001:1076: ltar glo bur 'khrul rtog gis bsgribs nas ma mthong
NK064(ngu)001:1079: byis pa mi shes pas sgribs pas //
NK064(ngu)001:1080: tshul 'di shes par ma gyur rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:1081: sangs rgyas gzhan du 'tshol bar byed //
NK064(ngu)001:1082: 'di na gnas pa yongs ma mthong //
NK064(ngu)001:1085: bla na med pa'i dgongs spyod zab mo rnams rang stobs kyis sam /
NK064(ngu)001:1086: gzhan gyis bstan kyang ma rtogs pas gab ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1087: mig ser can la dung gi dkar snang gab pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:1090: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i lta ba phul du byung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1091: sgom spyod rmad du byung ba rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:1093: theg pa 'og ma pa rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1094: so so'i skye bo log sred can sogs snod ma smin pa'i gang zag rnams la ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1095: de dag gi spyod yul du mi rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:1097: 'di la brten nas sgro 'dogs dang skur pa mi bzad pas de dag gnas ngan du ltung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:1098: gsang sgo 'chol bas rang nyid kyang nyams par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:1100: brda la sogs pa'i tshul gyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:1102: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:1103: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK064(ngu)001:1104: gsang thub dngos grub mi yal ba //
NK064(ngu)001:1105: gsang phyir brda dag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:1107: gnyis pa snying po'i don ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1112: s+aa ra ni gcig las du ma 'phro ba'i gzhi lta bu la 'jug pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1113: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud rtogs pa dang ma
NK064(ngu)001:1114: rtogs pa las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:1115: zhing / de gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud 'di yang
NK064(ngu)001:1116: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'phro gzhir gyur pas snying
NK064(ngu)001:1117: zhing / po ste / phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1118: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK064(ngu)001:1120: hri da ya ni srog gam snying ltar gces spras su bya ba'i don la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1121: theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug bgrod
NK064(ngu)001:1122: pa gcig pa'i lam 'di las mi 'da' ba'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:1123: / thar 'dod kun gyis bsten byar gyur pas na snying po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1124: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK064(ngu)001:1125: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK064(ngu)001:1126: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK064(ngu)001:1129: gar+b+ha ni shun pa'i nang gi snying po lta bu la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1130: rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas lha'i ngo bor dag
NK064(ngu)001:1131: pas 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du gtan la phab
NK064(ngu)001:1132: pa'i don 'di ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:1133: yin pas dbus na gnas pa lta bu'am /
NK064(ngu)001:1134: bcud 'dus pa'i don gyis na snying po zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1136: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK064(ngu)001:1137: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK064(ngu)001:1140: chos rnams dbus na gnas pa'i khams //
NK064(ngu)001:1141: khyab cing spyod yul ma yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:1143: gsum pa de kho na nyid kyi don la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1144: snang stong dbyer med rang byung gi ye shes la
NK064(ngu)001:1145: sgom byed kyi blos ma bcos par 'jog pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:1146: 'bras bu byung ba la mi bslu ba'i phyir rgyu'i
NK064(ngu)001:1148: de nyid 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:1149: 'khor du rang byung ba la phyin ci log gi
NK064(ngu)001:1150: chos bsal du med pas 'bras bu'i de kho na
NK064(ngu)001:1151: nyid do // rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK064(ngu)001:1152: ye shes las shes bya dang bsgrub bya'i chos gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:1154: de la rgyu 'bras kyi dbye ba tsam yang ma
NK064(ngu)001:1155: grub pas sgro skur dang bral ba'i phyir rgyu 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:1156: ro gcig pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:1157: de dag kyang rdo rje las /
NK064(ngu)001:1158: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa la //
NK064(ngu)001:1159: de nyid ngo bo skabs kyis gsum //
NK064(ngu)001:1161: bzhi pa nges pa'i don ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1162: skal dman gyi gdul bya rnams chud mi za ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:1163: thabs drang ba'i don tsam du bstan pa lta bu
NK064(ngu)001:1164: ma yin te / 'dir skal ldan dbang rnon rnams
NK064(ngu)001:1165: la rgyal ba nyid kyi ji ltar thugs su chud
NK064(ngu)001:1166: pa'i don bstan pas na nges pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1168: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK064(ngu)001:1169: 'di la gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK064(ngu)001:1172: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa gzhi'i rgyud ni rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1173: de'i ngang la bsal bzhag med par 'jog pa'i sgo
NK064(ngu)001:1174: nas gang shar dag snang du sbyong ba'i thabs khyad
NK064(ngu)001:1175: par can ni lam gyi rgyud de bstan pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:1176: cad kyi bcud du gyur pas na snying po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1178: lam gyis de rtogs pa la mi bslu bas don
NK064(ngu)001:1179: la gnyis po phyin ci ma log pa'i phyir de
NK064(ngu)001:1181: de 'dir sgro skur dang bral bar gtan la phab pas na rnam par nges pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1183: gsang ba chos 'byung la bshad de //
NK064(ngu)001:1184: snying po'ang de yi thabs can no //
NK064(ngu)001:1185: gnyis po phyin ci ma log phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:1186: de nyid do 'dir rnam nges so //
NK064(ngu)001:1188: gzhan yang mtshan thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te nang ltar 'chad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1189: 'og sgo dang sbyar te gsang ba ltar 'chad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1190: bka' srol yod kyang 'dir ma spros pas spro na
NK064(ngu)001:1192: gsum pa rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1194: khyed kyi rgyud 'di la klad du rgya skad ma smos pas bod mar 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:1196: bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos du mar yang klad
NK064(ngu)001:1197: du rgya skad bkod pa yod de des rgya gar
NK064(ngu)001:1199: 'di yang rgya gzhung spyi'i mtshan klad du lo ts+aa bas bkod pa shas che mod kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:1200: 'di ni sdud pa pos bkod par bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1202: gu h+ya gar+b+ha ta t+wa bi nish+tsa ya /
NK064(ngu)001:1203: zhes 'byung yang lo ts+aa ba spros pa la mi
NK064(ngu)001:1204: dga' bas mtshan bod skad du bsgyur te bkod pa
NK064(ngu)001:1205: las ming gcig lan gnyis su zlos pa la dgos
NK064(ngu)001:1206: pa chung bar dgongs nas rgya skad ma smos pa
NK064(ngu)001:1207: yin no // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1208: klad kyi don ston pa la phyag btsal ba /
NK064(ngu)001:1209: gzhung gi don rgyud don dngos bshad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1210: mjug gi don rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1212: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK064(ngu)001:1214: bdud bzhi la sogs pa mi mthun pa'i phyogs ma lus pa bcom pa ni spangs pa phun tshogs /
NK064(ngu)001:1215: che ba'i yon tan thams cad rang rig pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:1216: shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan pa ni rtogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:1218: 'das pa'i sgra ni rgya skad la med de /
NK064(ngu)001:1220: 'jig rten pa'i b+ha ga w+aan las khyad par 'das zhes bla thabs su bsnan te /
NK064(ngu)001:1222: bla thabs su snon pa de skad dod dang ma
NK064(ngu)001:1223: 'brel ba zhig glo bur du dbang che'i rig pas
NK064(ngu)001:1224: bsnan pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:1226: sangs rgyas 'di la b+ha ga mnga' //
NK064(ngu)001:1227: bcom ldan 'das zhes brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:1228: b+ha ga rnam pa drug tu brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1229: dbang phyug la sogs yon tan kun //
NK064(ngu)001:1230: yang na nyon mongs la sogs bdud //
NK064(ngu)001:1232: zhes b+ha ga w+aan gyi sgra las /
NK064(ngu)001:1233: b+ha ga ni bcom pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1234: legs pa rnam pa drug po gnyis ka la 'jug pa bzhin du /
NK064(ngu)001:1235: 'dir yang yi ge bsnan pa'i sgra las /
NK064(ngu)001:1236: b+ha ni a b+ha wish+yan+ti ste 'byung bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1237: ga ni ga ti ste song ba zhes pa'i don yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1238: yang dag pa'i gnas su song zhing log pa'i gnas su mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1239: don la shes rab dang snying rje chen pos 'khor 'das gnyis kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1240: 'das zhes 'jig rten pa'i b+ha ga w+aan las khyad 'byed du byas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1241: de yang phal po che las /
NK064(ngu)001:1242: srid dang zhi las rnam grol zhing //
NK064(ngu)001:1243: yon tan rgya mtsho gnyis su med //
NK064(ngu)001:1244: spros pa kun las rab 'das pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:1245: bcom ldan 'das ni mkha' rab zhi //
NK064(ngu)001:1247: dpal ni gzhi chos dbyings shin tu dri med la rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dpal zhes grags te /
NK064(ngu)001:1248: de ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:1249: bu ni chos sku rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang
NK064(ngu)001:1250: / de nyid kyi ngang las gang la gang 'dul
NK064(ngu)001:1251: gyi gzugs sku lhun grub tu 'char ba ni thugs
NK064(ngu)001:1253: de yang chos kun gyi gnas lugs 'ching grol med
NK064(ngu)001:1254: pa'i rang bzhin thugs su chud pas spyod yul yongs
NK064(ngu)001:1255: su dag pa'i phyir kun tu bzang po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1257: rang bzhin mi g.yo lhun rdzogs shing //
NK064(ngu)001:1258: spyod yul kun tu bzang po ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1260: de la phyag 'tshal lo zhes gsang bdag gis yul
NK064(ngu)001:1261: dang 'tshal mkhan ro gcig tu rtogs pa'i sgo nas
NK064(ngu)001:1262: lta ba mjal ba'i phyag mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:1264: gzhan dag yi ge pa'i phyag tu 'dod pa ni ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:1266: sdud pa pos tshig gnyer ba de'i tshe rang gi ston pa la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1268: de ltar na lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur phyag chad par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:1270: dus 'khor bsdus rgyud kyi klad du'ang yi ge pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1271: phyag gis go bcad nas 'gyur phyag zur du ma
NK064(ngu)001:1272: bkod pa ltar 'dir yang de bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:1273: gnyis pa rgyud don dngos bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:1274: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su gnas pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:1275: le'u dang po la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:1278: dang po gzhung la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1279: thun mong ma yin pa'i sgo nas gleng gzhi mdor bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:1280: rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi'i sgo nas de rgyas par bshad /
NK064(ngu)001:1283: rgyud kyi thog mar phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i bdag nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:1285: zhes pa'i yi ge bzhi smos pas ston te /
NK064(ngu)001:1287: yi ge bzhi yis shes par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:1290: phyi grol lam ltar rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1291: nang thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud rgya mtshos bshad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1292: gsang ba 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1294: e yig shes rab kyi brda' ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1295: yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings kyi rang bzhin gnas phun sum
NK064(ngu)001:1296: tshogs pa 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang
NK064(ngu)001:1297: ngo // wa yig thabs kyi brda' ste ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rigs drug pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1298: wa yig gi thig le ni sbyor ba'i brda' ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1299: thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i don gzhi lam 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:1300: gsum dbyer mi phyed par 'brel zhing rgyun chags pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1301: rgyud rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni ston pa
NK064(ngu)001:1303: de ltar yang dang po'i sangs rgyas las /
NK064(ngu)001:1304: e yi dbus su wam yig nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:1305: sangs rgyas kun gyi bde ba'i gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1306: mkha' dbyings rdo rje sems dpa' 'di //
NK064(ngu)001:1307: sku gsung thugs su sbyor ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:1308: thig le zla ba khu ba sku //
NK064(ngu)001:1309: rnam par bcad bya rdul nyi gsung //
NK064(ngu)001:1310: a yig mun can thugs rab brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1311: mkha' khams e la rnam par gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1314: e yi cha byad bzang po gang //
NK064(ngu)001:1315: dbus su wam gis rnam par brgyan //
NK064(ngu)001:1316: bde ba thams cad kyi ni gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1317: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog /
NK064(ngu)001:1319: lha'i dbang pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:1320: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1321: bzhi stong gi ni grangs snyed kyi //
NK064(ngu)001:1322: kun gyi gzhi dang pha ma ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1323: yi ge gnyis su rab tu bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:1324: yi ge e ni mar gyur la //
NK064(ngu)001:1325: wa ni pha zhes bya bar grags //
NK064(ngu)001:1326: thig le der ni sbyor bas te //
NK064(ngu)001:1327: sbyor te shin tu rmad byung ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1329: e wam ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:1330: thabs shes ston pa nyid kyi brdar gyur pas gsung
NK064(ngu)001:1331: rab kun gyi dang por 'jog dgos par /
NK064(ngu)001:1333: e wam yig gnyis sgyu ma la //
NK064(ngu)001:1334: thams cad mkhyen pa 'dir bzhugs pas //
NK064(ngu)001:1335: dam chos ston pa'i thog mar ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1336: e wam de phyir rab tu bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:1338: ma ni ma na shes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1339: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po la sogs pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:1340: yang na spyi mdor ma ni dran pa mtshon pa'i yi ger bshad pas smri ta ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1341: dran shes kyi las kyis rgyud don mi brjed par 'dzin pas 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1342: ya ni ya d+aa'i sgra las gang tshe zhes pas dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1343: rgyud 'di bshad pa gang gi tshe zhes dus ston pa'i tshig phrad yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:1347: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1348: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK064(ngu)001:1349: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK064(ngu)001:1350: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:1351: ye shes myong bas bsdus par bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:1352: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1353: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK064(ngu)001:1354: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK064(ngu)001:1355: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1356: zhes bshad rgyud rgya mtsho las gsungs pa ltar /
NK064(ngu)001:1358: d+harma tsakra zhes pa'i snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:1359: na rtsa 'dab brgyad yod pa rtsa ba'i 'dab ma
NK064(ngu)001:1360: bzhir 'du ste / mdun na chos nyid kyi rtsa la 'od dkar po zlum po /
NK064(ngu)001:1361: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa la gru bzhi ser po /
NK064(ngu)001:1362: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa la zla gam dmar po /
NK064(ngu)001:1363: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa la gru gsum dmar nag rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:1364: e sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs mdog can ni don dam
NK064(ngu)001:1365: 'od gsal gyi bzhugs gnas yin pa'i phyir gnas so
NK064(ngu)001:1366: // wam gis mtshon pa'i ston pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1367: de lta bu'i gnas la brten pa'i dwangs ma lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:1368: dbus na bzhugs pa sems kyi dwangs ma mi shigs
NK064(ngu)001:1369: pa'i thig le wam yig gi rnam par gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:1370: ste / de nyid mar me gsal byed gzhan la
NK064(ngu)001:1371: ltos mi dgos pa ltar rang gis rang la bde
NK064(ngu)001:1372: ba gsal bar ston pas na ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1374: ma nu'i sgra las drangs na /
NK064(ngu)001:1375: ma na shes pa la'o zhes pas yid la sogs pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad de /
NK064(ngu)001:1376: chos nyid kyi rtsal kun gzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:1378: yon tan gyi rtsal nyon yid /
NK064(ngu)001:1379: rang rgyud kyi rtsal sgo lnga'i rnam shes rnams gnas pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1380: de dag brjod bral rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:1381: shes lngar gsal bar nyams su myong bas na 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:1382: ro // ya yig gis mtshon pa'i bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1383: y+aa na'i sgra las bla na med pa'i theg pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1384: de'i man ngag steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi thabs kyis
NK064(ngu)001:1385: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs
NK064(ngu)001:1387: par m+aar+tha'i sgra las dam pa'i don nam /
NK064(ngu)001:1388: don zab mo ste bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1389: rnam pa gcig tu na ya ni sa ma ya'i ming mtha' bsdus pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:1390: ya d+aa'i sgra las dus kyang mtshon te /
NK064(ngu)001:1391: bde ba'i ye shes skyes pa de'i tshe snga phyir
NK064(ngu)001:1392: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral bas dus gsum mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:1393: pa nyid de bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so
NK064(ngu)001:1396: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1397: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1398: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK064(ngu)001:1399: wam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1400: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK064(ngu)001:1401: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK064(ngu)001:1402: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK064(ngu)001:1403: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu)001:1404: y+aa na theg chen 'di yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:1405: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK064(ngu)001:1406: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1407: zhes bshad rgyud thal ba las gsungs pa ltar /
NK064(ngu)001:1408: 'di zhes pa es mtshon pa'i gnas te /
NK064(ngu)001:1409: yum gyi b+ha ga sgo gru gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:1412: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1413: e sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs can de gsang ba'i ston 'khor bzhugs pa'i gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:1414: skad ces pa wam yig gis mtshon pa'i ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1415: yab kyi rdo rje nor bu'i dbur rtsa sa ya
NK064(ngu)001:1416: phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa'i kun rdzob ye
NK064(ngu)001:1417: shes kyi thig le wam gi dbyibs can ni yab
NK064(ngu)001:1418: yum gnyis ka'i rgyud la bde ba gsal bar ston
NK064(ngu)001:1419: pa'i bdag nyid yin pas na ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1420: bshad ces pa ma yig gis mtshon pa'i 'khor te /
NK064(ngu)001:1423: byed pa sdom pa thabs dang bcas pa'i gsang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:1424: rnam shes ni ye shes nyams su myong bas na
NK064(ngu)001:1425: 'khor ro // pa'i zhes pa ya yig gis mtshon nas /
NK064(ngu)001:1426: y+aa na'i sgra las theg pa chen po zhes bsnyad pa'i bstan pa 'adi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1428: pa ra m+aar+tha zhes pas don dam pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1429: nyams su myong bya sems lnga rdzogs pa'i dga' ba
NK064(ngu)001:1430: bcu drug gi tha ma rnam thar bzhi ldan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:1431: bde ba chen po rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1432: ye shes so // dus na zhes pa ya yig gis mtshon pa'i dus te /
NK064(ngu)001:1433: de nyid nyams su myong ba'i tshe dus 'di zhes
NK064(ngu)001:1434: mtshon du med pas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1435: dus so // n+aa ma ni zhes bya ba zhes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1436: phun sum tshogs pa lnga ka'i ming de dang de mtshon pa'i mjug sdud do //
NK064(ngu)001:1437: gnyis pa rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1444: 'di skad bshad pa ni gsang ba'i snying po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1445: de yang 'di skad ces pa ni rgyud don ma lus pa mtshon pa'i tshig phrad do //
NK064(ngu)001:1446: 'o na bdag gis thos pa mi zer bar bshad pa zer ba gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:1447: rgyud gzhan rnams su bdag gis thos zhes smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1448: sdud pa po rang nyid ston pa ma yin par khas blangs nas de skad du brjod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1449: bdag nyid kyis ston pa las mngon sum du thos
NK064(ngu)001:1450: kyi gzhan las brgyud de thos pa ma yin pa
NK064(ngu)001:1451: dang / tshig thos pa tsam du zad kyi don
NK064(ngu)001:1452: rtogs pa ni ma yin no zhes mtshon par byed
NK064(ngu)001:1453: dang / pa las / 'dir ni thun mong ma yin pa'i phyogs bzung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1454: sdud pa po rang nyid ston pa dang tha mi
NK064(ngu)001:1455: dad par khas blangs nas sngar ngas 'og min du
NK064(ngu)001:1456: bshad pa nyid yang 'dir bshad par bya zhes smos
NK064(ngu)001:1457: pa'o // don 'di nyid kyis na bstan pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:1458: yang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs nges don mthar
NK064(ngu)001:1459: thug pa nyid bstan pa yin par mtshon cing /
NK064(ngu)001:1460: 'phags pa phyag na rdo rje rang nyid kyang thun
NK064(ngu)001:1461: mong gi sdud pa po gzhan las khyad par du
NK064(ngu)001:1463: de skad du'ang nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel las /
NK064(ngu)001:1464: bshad ces pas ni 'khor dang ston pa gnyis su med par bstan pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:1467: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1468: rgyud gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1470: de yang sdud pa po nyid bstan pa dang rgyud tha mi dad par /
NK064(ngu)001:1471: bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu)001:1472: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1473: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NK064(ngu)001:1476: 'chad pa po nga chos kyang nga //
NK064(ngu)001:1477: rang gi tshogs ldan nyan pa'ang nga //
NK064(ngu)001:1480: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:1481: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de //
NK064(ngu)001:1483: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1485: 'di skad bshad pa'i tshe na ston pa 'di nyid
NK064(ngu)001:1486: gnas 'dir 'khor 'di dag dang lhan cig tu bzhugs
NK064(ngu)001:1488: 'o na dus gcig na mi zer ba gang snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:1489: 'dir dus na zhes pa dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid mtshon pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1490: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni rtag pa
NK064(ngu)001:1491: rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos ston pas dus res 'ga'
NK064(ngu)001:1492: ba gcig gi nges pa las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1493: dus thun mong ma yin pa'i che ba smos pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1495: de tshe dus nyid mtha' bral phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:1496: ngo bo dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:1498: gzhan du thun mong ba ltar na //
NK064(ngu)001:1499: dus gcig gi nges pa bzung ba'i dgos pa yang /
NK064(ngu)001:1500: dus gcig gi tshe 'di thos kyi gzhan du ma thos zhes bka'i don rnyed dka' ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1501: 'dir 'di thos la gzhan du gzhan dag kyang thos
NK064(ngu)001:1502: zhes sdud pa po rang nyid thos pa che ba
NK064(ngu)001:1503: dang / dus lan gcig gis khong du chud pas
NK064(ngu)001:1504: shes rab phul du byung bar bstan pa yin no
NK064(ngu)001:1506: rgyud 'di nyid bka' yang dag pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:1507: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK064(ngu)001:1508: zhes ma smos pa'i gleng gzhi log pa'i phyir ro zer na /
NK064(ngu)001:1512: bde mchog rtsa rgyud sogs rgyud rnam dag mang po
NK064(ngu)001:1513: zhig kyang bka' yang dag pa ma yin par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:1514: bas rnam par ma brtags pa'i bla brdol lo //
NK064(ngu)001:1515: de bas na de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni rnam
NK064(ngu)001:1516: par 'phrul pa sgyu ma lta bu la mnga' brnyes
NK064(ngu)001:1517: pa'i phyir / tshu rol mthong ba'i blos phyogs gcig
NK064(ngu)001:1518: kho nar nges bzung bya ba'i yul ma yin pas
NK064(ngu)001:1519: pa'i phyir / / theg pa thun mong dang thun
NK064(ngu)001:1520: mong ma yin pa'i rnam bzhag tha dad pa gcig
NK064(ngu)001:1521: gis gcig dgag par mi bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1522: mngon rtogs rgyan gyi 'grel pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:1523: 'di ni rnam par bzhag pa gzhan kho na yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1524: theg pa gzhan gyi lugs la brten nas nam du'ang sun 'byin brjod par mi bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1526: gsum pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:1531: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:1533: de yang rgyud phyi ma las /
NK064(ngu)001:1534: gang phyir de bzhin nyid du gshegs //
NK064(ngu)001:1535: de bzhin gshegs par mngon par brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1536: ces pas sgrib byed kyi zhen pa gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:1537: dang bral ba mthar thug pas gzhi ji lta ba
NK064(ngu)001:1539: de nyid kyang rang byung gi ye shes la spang
NK064(ngu)001:1540: bya ma grub pas yang dag pa nyid kyi phyir
NK064(ngu)001:1541: / 'bras bu ma btsal bar sku dang ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:1542: kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs par rang snang ba'i bdag
NK064(ngu)001:1544: bud+d+ha'i sgra gnyid sad pa ltar sangs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1545: pad+ma kha bye ba ltar rgyas pa'i don gnyis ka la 'jug pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1546: ma rig pa'i gnyid sangs shing shes bya la blo rgyas pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1548: ma rig gnyid las sangs phyir dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1549: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:1551: de ni 'dir don ji bzhin pa mngon du byas
NK064(ngu)001:1552: pa'i stobs kyis spangs thob med pa'i yon tan mthar
NK064(ngu)001:1555: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK064(ngu)001:1556: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:1558: de lta bu'i rang bzhin ni bdud bzhi sgrib gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:1559: bag chags dang bcas pa ma lus pa bcom zhing
NK064(ngu)001:1560: / sku lnga la sogs pa che ba'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:1561: thams cad kyi bdag nyid du gnas pas na ldan
NK064(ngu)001:1562: / la / mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pas rang
NK064(ngu)001:1563: gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med pas na
NK064(ngu)001:1564: / la / 'das pa ste / rdo rje las rim las /
NK064(ngu)001:1565: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdengs kyis bcom //
NK064(ngu)001:1566: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK064(ngu)001:1567: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK064(ngu)001:1570: nyon mongs pa lnga nyid ye shes lnga'i ngo bor
NK064(ngu)001:1571: rnam par dag pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom la
NK064(ngu)001:1572: / de dag pas phung po lnga yang rigs lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:1573: ngo bor mngon du 'gyur bar gdon mi za bas
NK064(ngu)001:1574: na phung po'i bdud bcom mo //
NK064(ngu)001:1575: de ltar lha rtog dbyer med du rtogs pa la 'dod lha'i bar chad kyis mi tshugs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:1576: phung po'i bdud bcom pas phung po nying mtshams sbyor ba med la /
NK064(ngu)001:1577: de med pas sems nyid skye 'chi las grol ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:1578: phyir lha'i bu'i bdud dang 'chi bdag gi bdud kyang
NK064(ngu)001:1580: bdud bzhi tshar gcod ces bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1581: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK064(ngu)001:1582: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK064(ngu)001:1583: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK064(ngu)001:1584: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1588: 'khor gsum rnam par rtog pa gang //
NK064(ngu)001:1589: de ni shes bya'i sgrib par brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1590: ser sna la sogs rnam rtog gang //
NK064(ngu)001:1591: de ni nyon mongs sgrib par brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1592: ces pas dug lnga rang mtshan gyi rtog pa ni nyon sgrib yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:1594: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdor dus gsum yid byed la bshad de /
NK064(ngu)001:1595: don la dag byed gnyen po la zhen pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1596: bag chags ni kun 'byung phra ba'i mthar thug 'pho
NK064(ngu)001:1597: ba'i bag chags te dkar dmar rlung gsum 'grogs pas
NK064(ngu)001:1598: shes pa gnyis snang 'khor ba'i chos su shar ba
NK064(ngu)001:1599: la bzhed pas / de sbyong byed rten gyi byed
NK064(ngu)001:1600: bcings las rten dang brten pa'i 'brel chad nas dag
NK064(ngu)001:1602: 'di ni lam bden mthar thug sngags kyi theg pa
NK064(ngu)001:1603: kho nas sbyong dgos pa'i sgrib pa shin tu phra
NK064(ngu)001:1604: ba'o // sku lnga'i yon tan dang ldan pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:1605: gzhan las skal pa phun sum tshogs pa drug bshad
NK064(ngu)001:1606: pa dang dgongs pa mthun te /
NK064(ngu)001:1608: dbang phyug dang ni gzugs bzang dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1609: dpal dang grags dang ye shes dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1610: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1611: drug po de la ldan zhes brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:1612: ces pas dbang phyug ni bag chags ma lus pa
NK064(ngu)001:1613: bcom pa'i bdag nyid shin tu rnam par dag pa
NK064(ngu)001:1614: chos kyi sku dang chos dbyings ye shes yin la
NK064(ngu)001:1615: / de bzhin du gzugs bzang ba ni yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:1616: thams cad kyi 'byung gnas mngon byang dang me long
NK064(ngu)001:1617: / lta bu / dpal dang grags pa ni 'gro
NK064(ngu)001:1618: la yon tan ster ba las mi g.yo ba longs
NK064(ngu)001:1620: ye shes ni chos kun dbyer mi phyed par dus
NK064(ngu)001:1621: gcig tu mkhyen pas rdo rje'i sku dang sor rtog
NK064(ngu)001:1622: / brtson 'grus ni phrin las tshad med par snang
NK064(ngu)001:1623: bas sprul pa'i sku dang bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:1624: / shes so // 'khor 'das gnyis kyi chos la
NK064(ngu)001:1625: rdzogs par longs spyod kyang thams cad ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:1626: rol par lhun gyis grub pas blang dor gyi spyod
NK064(ngu)001:1627: yul las 'das pa'i phyir gzhan las 'phags pas na
NK064(ngu)001:1628: / shes so // chen po'o // de yang steng 'og phyogs mtshams brgyad de phyogs bcu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1629: 'das ma 'ongs da lta 'byung bar ma nges pa
NK064(ngu)001:1630: ste dus bzhi'i dbyings na bzhugs shing 'gro don mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:1631: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi che ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:1632: yon tan gyi rten byed pas sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1633: gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'i chos brda sprod pas gsung dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1634: shes bya ma lus pa mkhyen cing sgrib pa gsum las rnam par grol bas thugs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1635: de dag gi zlas drangs te /
NK064(ngu)001:1636: dgos 'dod ma lus pa 'byung bas yon tan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1637: gzhan don mdzad pa la nus mthu thogs pa med pas phrin las te /
