NK064(ngu)001:1638: re re yang lnga lngar phye bas 'bras chos nyi shu rtsa lngar 'gyur la /
NK064(ngu)001:1639: de dag thams cad kyang rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1640: mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang bral ba /
NK064(ngu)001:1641: ngo bo 'dus ma byas pas rdo rje'i bdag nyid du ro gcig pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1642: rgyal ba drug pa la rigs thams cad kyi bdag po'am /
NK064(ngu)001:1643: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs can zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1644: de ltar na sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK064(ngu)001:1645: kho nar nges pas 'khor ba'i chos rnams 'dor ram
NK064(ngu)001:1647: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dang dbyer mi phyed
NK064(ngu)001:1648: pa'i rang bzhin du bzhugs so zhes ston pa la
NK064(ngu)001:1649: / sngar 'das pa'i 'khor 'das ma lus pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1651: ma 'ongs pa'i 'khor 'das lus pa med pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:1652: cad dang rgyud kyi bdag po rigs drug pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:1653: kun rdzob tu rig pa sgyu ma'i snang brnyan yin
NK064(ngu)001:1655: don dam par ma skyes pas tha mi dad /
NK064(ngu)001:1656: bden pa gnyis ka'i tha snyad las kyang 'das pas dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:1659: rgyal ba drug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa yang mdor bdun du 'du ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1660: zhes pas gzhung tshan bdun pos rim bzhin /
NK064(ngu)001:1661: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1662: yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1663: ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1664: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan du med pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1665: mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1666: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1667: gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen por dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin rnams yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:1669: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan //
NK064(ngu)001:1670: zhes pas yang dag pa'i rang bzhin dang rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin gnyis so sor phye ste brgyad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1671: 'grel chung du bcom ldan 'das zhes pa yan chad gcig tu bsdoms nas bzhir bshad de /
NK064(ngu)001:1673: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1674: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1675: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1676: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1678: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1679: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa nas /
NK064(ngu)001:1682: ston pa ni ye shes kyi sku can yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1683: de'i sku la mdun dang rgyab kho nar ris su
NK064(ngu)001:1684: chad pa med pas phyogs thams cad du sgrib pa
NK064(ngu)001:1685: med par zhal gyi dkyil 'khor thal le bar gsal
NK064(ngu)001:1686: ba ste kun tu zhal gyi rang bzhin du bzhugs
NK064(ngu)001:1687: shing / skyes bu chen po'i mtshan dang dpe byad
NK064(ngu)001:1688: bzang po gsal zhing so sor 'byed pa dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:1689: pas sku la rnam par spras pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1694: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1696: phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK064(ngu)001:1697: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1698: phyag ni zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK064(ngu)001:1699: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1700: sor mo ring dang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK064(ngu)001:1701: zhabs 'bur mi mngon spu ni gyen du phyogs /
NK064(ngu)001:1702: byin pa e n+ya ya'i 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK064(ngu)001:1703: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:1704: lpags pa gser mdog lpags pa srab pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1705: spu ni re re nas kyang g.yas legs 'khrungs //
NK064(ngu)001:1706: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge 'dra //
NK064(ngu)001:1707: 'di yi dpung pa'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK064(ngu)001:1708: 'di la ro mi zhim pa ro mchog snang //
NK064(ngu)001:1709: sku ni nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK064(ngu)001:1710: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1711: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge 'dra dang tshems //
NK064(ngu)001:1712: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thags bzang dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1713: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1714: spyan ni mthon mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi //
NK064(ngu)001:1715: 'dra ba 'di dag sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK064(ngu)001:1717: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1719: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1720: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:1721: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1722: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:1723: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1724: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1725: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1726: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khrul bag chags //
NK064(ngu)001:1728: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK064(ngu)001:1729: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1730: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK064(ngu)001:1731: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1732: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1733: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1734: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1735: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1736: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1737: dku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1738: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1739: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1740: kun nas blta na sdug pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1741: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1742: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1743: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1744: phyag ris mdangs yod zab ring dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1745: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1746: mchu ni bim+ba ltar dmar dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1747: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1748: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1749: gsung mnyen 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK064(ngu)001:1750: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1751: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1752: mchog tu dag pa dag dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1753: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /
NK064(ngu)001:1755: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1756: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1757: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1758: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1759: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1760: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1761: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1763: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK064(ngu)001:1764: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1765: dpal gyi be'u bkra shis ni //
NK064(ngu)001:1766: g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1767: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK064(ngu)001:1770: me long lta bu la sogs pa ye shes bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:1771: re re'ang bzhi bzhir phye ba'i ye shes bcu drug
NK064(ngu)001:1772: gi rtsal sems dpa' bcu drug /
NK064(ngu)001:1773: de'i yul chos dbyings bcu drug gi rtsal sems ma
NK064(ngu)001:1774: bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mtshan bzang
NK064(ngu)001:1775: po yin la / sems dpa' bcu drug la ye
NK064(ngu)001:1776: shes lnga'i rtags rigs kyi lha lnga lngas dbu brgyan
NK064(ngu)001:1777: pa'i lha brgyad cu ni dpe byad de /
NK064(ngu)001:1779: mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bus spras pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1780: sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas brgyan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1782: 'o na sems ma bcu drug la dbu rgyan med dam zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:1784: chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:1785: de yang phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan sogs thun mong
NK064(ngu)001:1786: du grags pa las khyad par du gyur pa ye
NK064(ngu)001:1787: shes chen po'i rtags kyi mtshan mar snang bas na
NK064(ngu)001:1788: thun mong ma yin pa zhes bya la /
NK064(ngu)001:1789: de dag mtshan dper 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK064(ngu)001:1790: 'khor dang 'khor gyi rgyan phun sum tshogs pas gtso
NK064(ngu)001:1791: bo'i rang bzhin yang bkod pas mdzes par byed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1792: phyir te / sor gdub dang sor gdub kyi phras
NK064(ngu)001:1793: skyes bu'i lag pa mdzes par byed pa bzhin no
NK064(ngu)001:1794: phyir te / // de lta bu'i sku las mi
NK064(ngu)001:1795: g.yo bzhin du zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK064(ngu)001:1796: thams cad du gang la gang 'dul gyi sku'i bkod
NK064(ngu)001:1797: phyir te / // pa dang / sgra skad mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:1798: yas pas theg pa ma lus pa ston pa'i gsung
NK064(ngu)001:1799: phyir te / // pa dang / dang / spangs
NK064(ngu)001:1800: rtogs kyis bsdus pa'i yon tan thugs mkhyen pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:1802: gdul bya dag ma dag gi snang ba dang mthun
NK064(ngu)001:1803: pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa sna tshogs par kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:1804: snang bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad de /
NK064(ngu)001:1806: nam mkhas ji snyed khyab gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1807: sku yis kyang ni de snyed khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:1808: sku yis ji snyed khyab gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1809: 'od kyis kyang ni de snyed khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:1810: 'od kyis ji snyed khyab gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1811: gsung gis kyang ni de snyed khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:1812: gsung gis ji snyed khyab gyur pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1813: thugs kyis kyang ni de snyed khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:1815: 'dis sprul pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su bstan
NK064(ngu)001:1816: pas thub pa drug kyang shugs kyis bstan par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:1817: zhing / gong ma rnams gzhung tshan gsum po de
NK064(ngu)001:1818: ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid yin par so
NK064(ngu)001:1819: sor sbyor bar mdzad pa'ang mi 'gal lo //
NK064(ngu)001:1820: 'o na ston pa'i rnam 'gyur ji lta bu snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:1821: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa
NK064(ngu)001:1822: nyid kyi ye shes kyis srid zhi'i mtha' la mi
NK064(ngu)001:1823: gnas pa'i brdar zhabs gnyis yab mnyam pa'i skyil krung
NK064(ngu)001:1824: dang / yum brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung dang mtshungs par bzhugs nas snyoms par 'jug pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1825: 'dir yum gyi bzhugs tshul bshad pas kun tu bzang mo bstan pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:1826: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug gi don mtshon byed phyag drug dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1827: ye shes de dag gi gdul bya'i re ba yid
NK064(ngu)001:1828: bzhin du skong ba'i rtags rin po che las grub
NK064(ngu)001:1829: pa'i rigs lnga ye shes lnga dang chos dbyings kyi
NK064(ngu)001:1830: phyag rgya rdo rje la sogs pa 'od 'bar ba
NK064(ngu)001:1832: sgyu 'phrul rol pa chen po las /
NK064(ngu)001:1833: ye shes drug gi bdag nyid kyi //
NK064(ngu)001:1834: phyag rgya rin chen 'bar ba'i mtshan //
NK064(ngu)001:1835: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK064(ngu)001:1839: gsung mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1840: thugs smon pa med pa gsum ni blo'i yul las 'das pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:1841: de'i rtags su dbu gsum dang ldan pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1842: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing gar snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1843: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:1848: de la spyir 'og min ni bla na gzhan med pa'i don yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:1850: chos dbyings don gyi 'og min dang /
NK064(ngu)001:1853: gtsang ris kyi lha lnga'i nang tshan 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min rnams las /
NK064(ngu)001:1854: 'dir 'og min chen po zhes bya ba longs spyod
NK064(ngu)001:1855: rdzogs pa sku'i sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas gtsang ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:1856: gnas las spags pa gang yin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1858: gtsang ma'i ris dag rnam spangs pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:1859: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK064(ngu)001:1863: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa na //
NK064(ngu)001:1864: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK064(ngu)001:1865: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang //
NK064(ngu)001:1867: de yang rgyu'i byang sems kyis sa dang po'i bden pa mthong ba'i gnas gtsang ma'i 'og min las /
NK064(ngu)001:1868: nges don du 'tshang rgya ba'i zhing khams 'og min
NK064(ngu)001:1869: chen po nyis 'gyur gyis 'phags par gsungs pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:1870: / tshogs lam gyi sna zin nas mthong lam thob
NK064(ngu)001:1871: pa la yun ji tsam thogs pa'i nyis 'gyur sa
NK064(ngu)001:1872: dang po nas sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar du dgos
NK064(ngu)001:1873: pa la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK064(ngu)001:1874: gtsang ma'i gnas de'i ya rol na yod pa'i nges pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:1875: sangs rgyas kyi zhing ni rang gang na bzhugs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1876: rang snang yin pas ma dag pa'i zhing spangs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:1877: pha rol na dag pa'i zhing gzhan zhig blos btsal
NK064(ngu)001:1879: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:1880: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK064(ngu)001:1881: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK064(ngu)001:1882: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK064(ngu)001:1883: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:1885: rdul phra rab gcig gi steng na'ang sangs rgyas kyi
NK064(ngu)001:1886: zhing tshad med pa ma 'gags par snang bas bsam
NK064(ngu)001:1887: gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas te /
NK064(ngu)001:1889: spu yi rtse mo gcig la yang //
NK064(ngu)001:1890: zhing rnams bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:1891: sna tshogs dbyibs kyang tha dad de //
NK064(ngu)001:1892: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:1895: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:1897: don la nam mkhas gar khyab tu sangs rgyas kyi sku dang phrin las kyis khyab pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1898: sangs rgyas kyi zhing la phyogs dang ris su chad pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:1899: sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing 'di nyid kyang dag pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:1900: ma dag pa'i zhing khams so so bar mthong na
NK064(ngu)001:1901: / rang gi blo snang tsam las dag pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:1902: ma dag pa'i zhi nga rang mtshan pa zhig logs
NK064(ngu)001:1903: na yod pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:1904: de yang 'di ltar dri ma med par grags pa'i mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:1905: btsun pa sh+aa ri'i bus smras pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1906: bdag gis sa chen po 'di mtho dman dang g.yang
NK064(ngu)001:1907: sa dang ljan ljin gyis gang bar mthong ngo zhes
NK064(ngu)001:1908: zer ro // sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i zhing
NK064(ngu)001:1909: nas 'ongs pa'i tshangs pa ral pa can gyis smras
NK064(ngu)001:1910: zer ro // pa / bdag gis ni bcom ldan
NK064(ngu)001:1911: 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i zhing 'di nyid gzhan 'phrul dbang
NK064(ngu)001:1912: byed kyi lha'i gnas kyi bkod pa phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:1913: pa bzhin du yongs su dag par mthong ngo zhes
NK064(ngu)001:1914: zer ro // pa / zer ro // de nas
NK064(ngu)001:1915: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rnams la
NK064(ngu)001:1916: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di'i rang bzhin bstan par mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:1917: zer ro // pa / zer ro // pas /
NK064(ngu)001:1918: thams cad kyis shar phyogs kyi sangs rgyas rin po
NK064(ngu)001:1919: che'i rgyan bkod pa'i zhing khams bzhin yongs su dag
NK064(ngu)001:1920: par mthong bar gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK064(ngu)001:1921: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK064(ngu)001:1922: nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di ni rtag tu 'di 'dra ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1923: khyed rnams kyis mi mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:1925: des na longs sku'i gnas de'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1926: chos kyi dbyings shin tu rnam par dag pa yin
NK064(ngu)001:1927: pas mtha' dang dbus la sogs pa gang gi yang
NK064(ngu)001:1928: ris su chad pa med pas nam mkha' ltar bsam
NK064(ngu)001:1931: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK064(ngu)001:1932: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK064(ngu)001:1935: de lta bu'i gnas na yon tan gyi khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:1936: rang snang ba'i pho brang gi bkod pa ji lta
NK064(ngu)001:1937: bu snyam na / de 'chad pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:1939: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK064(ngu)001:1940: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1941: rgyan dang sgo khyud rta babs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:1942: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:1943: zhes don bcu gcig tu gsungs pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:1945: gzhi tshad med ces sogs te 'og gzhi'i rgya khyon
NK064(ngu)001:1946: blos tshad dmigs su med par brdal ba'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:1947: ye shes lnga mtshon byed kyi rtags rnam pa 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:1948: lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa ma 'dres
NK064(ngu)001:1949: par gsal ba'i steng la ste /
NK064(ngu)001:1951: 'khor lo chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NK064(ngu)001:1952: khang pa gru bzhi rnam par brjid //
NK064(ngu)001:1955: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i zhes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:1956: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:1957: bas gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su rin
NK064(ngu)001:1958: po che 'od 'bar ba las grub pa'i gzhal yas
NK064(ngu)001:1959: khang chen po'o // gsum pa rgya tshad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1960: rgya phyogs bcur zhes sogs te chos kyi dbyings la
NK064(ngu)001:1961: rgya tshad med pa'i rtags su gzhal yas khang de'i
NK064(ngu)001:1962: tshad phyogs bcu thams cad du rgya yongs su ma
NK064(ngu)001:1963: chad pa'o // bzhi pa dbyibs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1965: de ltar rgya ma chad pas phyal bar 'gyur ram snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:1967: rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1968: de'i rtags kyi phyag rgya dbyibs gru bzhi par gyur pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1971: ye shes re re yang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:1972: bzhi dang ldan pa'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su
NK064(ngu)001:1973: gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba'i rin po che'i glo
NK064(ngu)001:1974: 'bur rigs bzhi'i kha dog can gyis mdzes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:1975: drug pa rtse mo'i don ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1977: gzhal yas khang de'i rtse mo bum pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:1978: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid phyogs bcu dus
NK064(ngu)001:1979: bzhi'i sangs rgyas kun gyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK064(ngu)001:1980: thams cad bar rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:1981: rang bzhin so so ma yin zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:1982: ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes spros pa kun
NK064(ngu)001:1983: dang bral ba'i klong du 'khyil ba mtshon pa'i rtags
NK064(ngu)001:1986: bklubs pa zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:1987: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal ma 'gags
NK064(ngu)001:1988: pa las ye shes lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK064(ngu)001:1989: sogs pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga'
NK064(ngu)001:1990: ba'i rtags su ye shes rang snang ba'i rgyan rin
NK064(ngu)001:1991: po che las grub pa'i dbyibs dang kha dog la
NK064(ngu)001:1992: sogs pa rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye brag tshad
NK064(ngu)001:1993: med pa dang ldan pas gzhal yas khang gzhan las
NK064(ngu)001:1994: khyad par du gyur pa'i bkod pa phun sum tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:1995: pas brgyan pa / theg pa dang sa lam gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:1996: las 'di nyid 'phags pa'i rtags su sgo dang khyams
NK064(ngu)001:1997: sogs nas lte ba'i bar rdo rje 'greng bu res
NK064(ngu)001:1999: chos kyi dbyings la mtha' thug pa med pa'i rtags
NK064(ngu)001:2000: su pho brang gi rtse mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2001: gtsug tor ltar mtho dam'i tshad 'di zhes dpag tu
NK064(ngu)001:2002: med pa / ye shes kyi rtsal snang rin po
NK064(ngu)001:2003: che sna tshogs las grub pa'i rgyan gyi khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:2004: med pa / yang / thugs rje dang sprul pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2005: phrin las rgyun mi chad pa'i rtags su phreng ba
NK064(ngu)001:2006: med pa / yang / dang / bden gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa'i rtags su chun 'phyang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2007: thabs sna tshogs pa ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su shar bu'i rgyan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2008: gzhan yang 'dod yon thams cad ma spangs rnam dag
NK064(ngu)001:2009: rol pa'i rgyan dang shar ba'i rtags su yid du
NK064(ngu)001:2014: reg bya sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2015: de dag thogs pa'i rdo rje'i lha mo rnams kyis
NK064(ngu)001:2016: phyogs bcur sprin phung ltar 'khrigs pa ni 'bad rtsol
NK064(ngu)001:2018: de dag thams cad kyang phan tshun gcig gis gcig
NK064(ngu)001:2019: mi sgrib par phyi nang zang thal du gsal ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2020: rgyan gyi bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bkod
NK064(ngu)001:2021: pas mdzes par brgyan cing bklubs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2023: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i zhes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2024: dngos po dang mtshan 'dzin gyi sgrib pa las rnam par thar pa'i sgo thun mong ba gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2025: thun mong ma yin pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal
NK064(ngu)001:2026: ba ste bzhi'i sgo nas byang chub chen por lhun
NK064(ngu)001:2027: gyis 'jug pa'i rtags su sgo bzhi sgo khyud kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2028: zlas drangs pa'i 'gram logs dang ya phubs can gyis
NK064(ngu)001:2032: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK064(ngu)001:2035: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi zhes sogs te //
NK064(ngu)001:2037: lam brgyad rim par bgrod pa yis //
NK064(ngu)001:2038: 'bras bu'i yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK064(ngu)001:2039: rta babs rgyu 'bras bcu drug bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:2040: zhes pas rgyu dang 'bras bu'i rta babs brgyad brgyad de bcu drug las /
NK064(ngu)001:2042: mtshon sgo rnam thar bzhi'i sgo nas mtshon bya byang chub chen por 'jug pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2043: 'khor ba las rnam par thar pa theg pa brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:2044: bgrod nas 'jug pa'i rtags su sgo phugs kyi phyi
NK064(ngu)001:2045: nang gnyis na them skas bzhi bzhi ste babs zhon
NK064(ngu)001:2046: gyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2048: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK064(ngu)001:2049: rta babs brgyad du 'gyur ba yin //
NK064(ngu)001:2052: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan zlo //
NK064(ngu)001:2055: theg brgyad kyi grub mtha'i yon tan brgyad rdzogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2056: rtags su sgo khang gi steng na rgyan gyi rta
NK064(ngu)001:2057: babs brgyad dang ldan pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2058: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:2059: de yi grub pa'i mtha' rdzogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:2060: yon tan brgyad phyir rta rkang dang //
NK064(ngu)001:2061: chu skyes sgrom dang za ra tshags //
NK064(ngu)001:2063: khyung mgo mdzes pas rim par 'khrigs //
NK064(ngu)001:2065: bcu pa gnas kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2066: phyi dang nang med pa zhes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2067: gzhal yas khang de'i phyi dang nang med pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:2068: cad rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang 'ba'
NK064(ngu)001:2069: zhig tu gyur pa'i phyir kun tu yang nang du
NK064(ngu)001:2071: bcu gcig pa gdan khri ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2073: rin po che'i gdan la zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2074: gsang ba'i theg pa 'di ni theg pa 'og ma rnams la nyam mi nga ba'i phyir ram /
NK064(ngu)001:2075: rgyal ba'i thugs la mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:2076: grub pa mtshon byed dbus su seng ge'i khri dang
NK064(ngu)001:2077: / theg pa 'og mar mi chud pa'i don 'dir
NK064(ngu)001:2078: shong zhing theg pas sam sku stobs bcu dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:2079: pa'i rtags su shar du glang po che'i khri dang
NK064(ngu)001:2080: / / 'dis gdul bya rnams myur du sgrol zhing
NK064(ngu)001:2081: yon tan rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:2082: pa'i rtags su lhor rta'i khri dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2083: 'dis las nyon ma spangs par dbang du byed cing
NK064(ngu)001:2084: gsung dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su nub tu
NK064(ngu)001:2086: phrin las 'gro ba sgrol ba la chags pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:2087: thogs pa med pa'i rtags su byang du nam mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:2088: lding ste shang shang gi khri dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2089: theg pa brgyad bgrod nas 'bras bu'i yon tan thugs
NK064(ngu)001:2090: su chud pa'i rtags su seng ge la sogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2091: de dag re re yang brgyad brgyad de mjug ma
NK064(ngu)001:2092: nang du bsnol nas rin po che'i khri rkang 'degs
NK064(ngu)001:2093: pa'o // de yang dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK064(ngu)001:2094: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK064(ngu)001:2095: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2096: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK064(ngu)001:2097: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2098: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK064(ngu)001:2099: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2100: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i gsung //
NK064(ngu)001:2101: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2102: las ni phrin las bzhi yis 'gro ba sgrol //
NK064(ngu)001:2103: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2105: thugs rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas 'od gsal
NK064(ngu)001:2106: zhing thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i rtags su nyi
NK064(ngu)001:2108: nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i rtags su pad+ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2109: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i rtags su rin po che'i gdan te /
NK064(ngu)001:2110: de yang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:2111: grub pa'i rtags su ka bas btegs pa'i khri rkang
NK064(ngu)001:2113: de ltar gdan lnga brtsegs de dag gtso bo dang rigs lnga'i gdan te /
NK064(ngu)001:2114: 'khor gzhan rnams la ni so so'i gnas su ji ltar 'os pa'i gdan /
NK064(ngu)001:2115: sems dpa' la ni sum brtsegs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2116: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK064(ngu)001:2118: kun bzang yab yum ni dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe bzhi brtsegs su bshad kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:2119: gleng gzhi'i skabs 'dir pho brang gi lte bar bzhugs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2121: gdan yang lnga brtsegs su gsungs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2122: 'o na 'dir mi bskyod pa gang du bzhugs snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:2123: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga las thugs kyi sgyu
NK064(ngu)001:2124: 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir rdo rje mi bskyod pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:2125: ston pa rigs drug pa'i mdun na bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2128: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK064(ngu)001:2129: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:2130: brjod pa med bzhin go bar mdzod //
NK064(ngu)001:2134: bdag po kun bzang 'khor rnams la //
NK064(ngu)001:2136: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:2138: lnga pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2139: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2140: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2145: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK064(ngu)001:2147: de yang spangs rtogs kyi yon tan mthar phyin cing
NK064(ngu)001:2148: mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pas bcom ldan 'das dang
NK064(ngu)001:2149: / ye ji bzhin pa'i dbyings su gshegs pas de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2150: mtshan gnyis po de ston pa rigs drug pa dang thun mong ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2152: mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni sngar thal te /
NK064(ngu)001:2154: des mtshon nas ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun po rigs
NK064(ngu)001:2155: lnga'i rang bzhin du'ang 'gyur bas rang bzhin gnyis su
NK064(ngu)001:2157: rnam par shes pa ni yul rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs brgyad do //
NK064(ngu)001:2158: gzugs ni gzugs su rung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi rgyu'i gzugs bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:2159: 'bras gzugs bcu gcig ste bco lnga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2160: tshor ba ni nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi chos bde ba /
NK064(ngu)001:2162: btang snyoms gsum gyis bsdus pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2163: 'du shes ni mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi chos mtshan ma med pa /
NK064(ngu)001:2168: 'du byed ni mngon par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2170: yul so sor nges pa lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:2172: rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug /
NK064(ngu)001:2173: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu /
NK064(ngu)001:2174: gzhan 'gyur bzhi ste sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig
NK064(ngu)001:2175: las tshor ba dang 'du shes gnyis logs su bgrangs
NK064(ngu)001:2176: pa'i lhag ma bzhi bcu rtsa dagu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2177: gzhung lugs phal mo cher phung po lnga'i 'go gzugs phung nas brtsams te ston na /
NK064(ngu)001:2179: 'dir rnam shes dang por smos zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:2180: gzugs la sogs pa'i chos rnams kyang sems kyi rol rtsal tsam las gzhan ma yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:2181: sems nyid gtso bo'i dbang du mdzad nas rnam shes dang por smos shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2182: lha'i dus na'ang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo mi bskyod pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2183: lha dang rtog pa'i chos mthun brtsi ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2184: rnam shes thugs kyi bdag nyid yin pas thugs kyi rigs mi bskyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2185: gzugs ni sku dang dngos su mthun pas na sku'i rigs rnam snang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2186: tshor ba ni yul la longs spyod du lta ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2187: gzhi yin pas yon tan gyi rigs rin chen 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:2188: gnas dang / 'du shes ni mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2189: bdag nyid phyi nang gi chos rnams la tha snyad
NK064(ngu)001:2190: du 'dogs pa'i las kyis brda' sprod pas gsung gi
NK064(ngu)001:2192: 'du byed ni bya ba byed pa las kyi bdag
NK064(ngu)001:2193: nyid yin pas phrin las kyi rigs don yod grub
NK064(ngu)001:2195: gzugs ni rnam par snang mdzad nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:2196: tshor ba rin chen 'byung ldan la //
NK064(ngu)001:2197: 'du shes snang ba mtha' yas te //
NK064(ngu)001:2198: 'du byed don yod grub pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:2199: rnam par shes pa mi bskyod pa //
NK064(ngu)001:2200: zhes ye shes grub pa'i rgyud du gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2201: gang dag de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2202: rgyal po rnam snang du bzhed pa ni ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:2203: te / rdo rje las rim las /
NK064(ngu)001:2204: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:2205: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK064(ngu)001:2206: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK064(ngu)001:2207: zhes pas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2208: yan lag brgyad cu dang ldan pa'i phung po lnga
NK064(ngu)001:2209: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i chos ltar snang ba 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2210: kho na rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yin nam snyam na
NK064(ngu)001:2212: ma dag pa'i phung sogs rtog tshogs 'di dag sbyang
NK064(ngu)001:2213: bya'i chos med snang glo bur ba yin pas rigs
NK064(ngu)001:2214: lnga'i sangs rgyas su mi rung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2215: dper na mig nad can gyis dung ser por mthong ba'i tshe /
NK064(ngu)001:2216: ser po de dung gi kha dog gi gnas lugs ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:2217: de bas na rtogs pa dang lha gnyis chos mthun
NK064(ngu)001:2218: brtsi ba'ang dngos po la mngon par zhen pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:2219: lha rtog dbyer med kyi shes rab skye ba la
NK064(ngu)001:2220: kha drang ba'i thabs tsam du gsungs pa yin no
NK064(ngu)001:2221: // 'o na phung sogs ma dag pa'i rtog tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:2222: las rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas gzhan du grub pa zhig
NK064(ngu)001:2223: // gam snyam na / de yang ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:2224: de dag gi snang gzhi rang bzhin nam gnyug ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:2225: phung po lnga ye nas rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su
NK064(ngu)001:2226: rnam par dag pa de nyid lam rkyen gyis mngon
NK064(ngu)001:2227: du gyur pa la 'bras bur rnam par bzhag pas
NK064(ngu)001:2228: na rtog tshogs las gzhan du'ang brjod du med pa
NK064(ngu)001:2229: ste / mig gi nad sman gyis sbyangs pas dag
NK064(ngu)001:2230: pa'i tshe na sngar ser por mthong ba'i dung de
NK064(ngu)001:2231: ka dkar por snang ba las /
NK064(ngu)001:2232: dkar po'i kha dog gzhan zhig logs nas btsal du med pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:2233: rigs lnga ka'i mtshan la rgyal po zhes smos pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2234: dper na rgyal po rnams rang gi rgyal srid la dbang sgyur zhing longs spyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2235: gzhan gyi dpung pham pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2236: rang gi dpung rgyal bar byed pa bzhin du /
NK064(ngu)001:2237: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtog tshogs la dbang sgyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2238: zag pa med pa'i chos la mnga' brnyes pas bde
NK064(ngu)001:2239: ba chen po'i longs spyod la rol bar mdzad cing
NK064(ngu)001:2240: / chos kyi rgyal srid bskyangs pas gdul bya'i rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:2241: kyi sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa'i dpung ma
NK064(ngu)001:2243: tshogs gnyis la sogs pa'i yon tan gyi dpung rgyal bar mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2244: mi bskyod pa la sogs pa so so'i mtshan gyi rgyu mtshan yang /
NK064(ngu)001:2245: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:2246: ni phyi nang gi rkyen gang gis kyang bskyod par
NK064(ngu)001:2247: mi nus pas mi 'gyur ba rdo rje'i rigs mi
NK064(ngu)001:2248: bskyod pa dang / sku ni de bzhin nyid las
NK064(ngu)001:2249: ma g.yos bzhin du rnam pa sna tshogs par snang
NK064(ngu)001:2250: bas de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs rnam snang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2251: yon tan ni don gnyis 'grub pa'i gnas su gyur
NK064(ngu)001:2252: pas rin po che'i rigs rin chen 'byung gnas dang
NK064(ngu)001:2253: / gsung ni chags pa med pa'i sgo nas 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:2254: rten du chos kyi snang ba chen po rgyas par
NK064(ngu)001:2255: mdzad pas pad+ma'i rigs snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2256: phrin las ni 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par mdzad pas las kyi rigs don yod grub pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2258: sku ni ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:2259: thugs ni mi 'gyur rdo rje'i rigs //
NK064(ngu)001:2260: yon tan kun 'byung rin chen rigs //
NK064(ngu)001:2261: gsung ni chags med pad+ma'i rigs //
NK064(ngu)001:2262: don grub spyod pa las kyi rigs //
NK064(ngu)001:2264: de yang 'bras chos lnga la mtshan ji skad du thob pa'i nges pas /
NK064(ngu)001:2265: de nyid 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs kyi phyag rgyar
NK064(ngu)001:2266: 'phrul pa 'chang ba'i skyes bu lnga la'ang de ltar
NK064(ngu)001:2267: du grags so // rigs lnga po de dag kun
NK064(ngu)001:2268: gyi rigs kyi mtshan mar gyur pa'i kha dog kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2269: du grags so // / chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2270: brdar chos dbyings ye shes dang rdo rje'i rigs mthing
NK064(ngu)001:2271: du grags so // / ga dang / nyes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2272: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i brdar me long lta bu'i
NK064(ngu)001:2273: ye shes dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dkar po
NK064(ngu)001:2274: du grags so // / ga dang / dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2275: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i brdar mnyam nyid ye
NK064(ngu)001:2276: shes dang rin chen rigs ser po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2277: gdul bya'i don la rjes su chags pa'i brdar sor
NK064(ngu)001:2278: rtog ye shes dang pad+ma'i rigs le brgan te dmar
NK064(ngu)001:2279: po dang / sems can gyi don sna tshogs mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:2280: pa'i phrin las lhun gyis grub pa'i brdar bya grub
NK064(ngu)001:2281: ye shes dang las kyi rigs rnams ljang gu ste
NK064(ngu)001:2282: po dang / / thams cad kyang so so'i mdog tu gsal zhing bkrag mdangs 'tsher ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2287: rtog pa'i dus na 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:2288: lha'i dus na rigs kyi yab lngas longs spyod par bya ba'i yul lam /
NK064(ngu)001:2289: sras bskyed pa'i yum du gyur pas na btsun mo /
NK064(ngu)001:2290: yon tan gyi khyad par gzhan las 'phags pas na dam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2291: gang gis go phye bas dngos po thams cad snang
NK064(ngu)001:2292: bar byed pa nam mkha' ni chos kyi khams rnam
NK064(ngu)001:2294: de gnas su dag pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu)001:2295: thugs rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2296: sra ba sa'i khams ni brtan cing rten du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:2297: pas na sku'i rigs kyi yum sangs rgyas spyan ma
NK064(ngu)001:2298: dang / mnyen pa chu'i khams ni rgyud brlan cing
NK064(ngu)001:2299: yon tan sdud par byed pa rin chen rigs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2301: dro ba me'i khams ni mtshan 'dzin gyi spu ris
NK064(ngu)001:2302: gsal bar byed cing shes rab kyi mes dag par
NK064(ngu)001:2303: byed pa'i bdag nyid pad+ma rigs kyi yum gos dkar
NK064(ngu)001:2304: mo dang / bskyod pa rlung gi khams ni gdul
NK064(ngu)001:2305: bya sgrol ba la thogs pa med pa las kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2306: rigs kyi yum dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2307: de yang 'byung lnga'i khams ye nas yum lnga'i dbyings su dag pas sam /
NK064(ngu)001:2308: sras dang bde ba'i ye shes kyi 'byung khungs su
NK064(ngu)001:2309: gyur pas na thams cad la dbyings kyi sgras smos
NK064(ngu)001:2310: so // de dag la sogs pa rigs kyi btsun mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2311: don rang bzhin gnyis su med cing /
NK064(ngu)001:2312: rtags yab yum 'khril bas mnyam par sbyor ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2314: khyab byed chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab bya shes bya'i
NK064(ngu)001:2315: dkyil 'khor thams cad la khyab pas nam mkha'i mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:2316: klas pa kun tu ston pa'i mdzad spyod kyi rol
NK064(ngu)001:2317: mo mtha' yas par snang bas khyab pa ni 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2318: lta ste / dper na til gyi gang bu kha
NK064(ngu)001:2319: phye ba bzhin du go mtshams med par gang nas
NK064(ngu)001:2320: kun tu khyab par bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2321: gnyis pa rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2328: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba nas //
NK064(ngu)001:2329: myong bar bya ba'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2331: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga bshad pa'i rjes de nas zhes 'brel sbyar la /
NK064(ngu)001:2332: mig shes la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs rnams ye nas chos nyid byang chub kyi sems te /
NK064(ngu)001:2333: de nyid mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni spangs rtogs mthar phyin pas byang chub kyang yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2334: sar gnas kyi sems dpa' las 'phags pas chen po'ang yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:2335: 'dir bstan gyi 'khor thams cad ston pa'i thugs rig
NK064(ngu)001:2336: pa rang snang gi sprul pa ba yin pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:2338: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK064(ngu)001:2339: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:2341: rdo rje ni rtog tshogs su snang yang rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:2342: lha'i dkyil 'khor du nges pas dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2344: bye brag tu mig dbang la brten nas mig shes
NK064(ngu)001:2345: kyi yul gzugs mthong bas na mig gi rnam shes
NK064(ngu)001:2346: la mthong ba zhes brjod la /
NK064(ngu)001:2347: de gnas su dag pa sa'i snying po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2348: de bzhin du thos pa rna ba'i rnam shes te phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2349: snom pa sna'i rnam shes te nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2350: myong ba lce'i rnam shes te spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2352: yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed par byed cing rnam shes kyis spyad byar gyur pas na btsun mo /
NK064(ngu)001:2353: mig shes kyis mthong bya'i yul yin pas mthong bar bya ba gzugs te rdo rje sgeg mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2354: de bzhin du mnyan par bya ba sgra ste glu dbyangs ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2355: bsnam par bya ba dri ste phreng ba ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2356: myong bar bya ba ro ste gar sgyur ma'i tshogs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2357: yab yum 'di rnams 'dir go rim bzhin yul shes
NK064(ngu)001:2358: sbyor ba dang man ngag las spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2360: phyag rdor gyi yum gar mar mdzad pa gnyis mi 'gal lam snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:2361: 'dir ni rtog pa'i yul yul can gtso bor byas la /
NK064(ngu)001:2362: man ngag las ni rigs gtso bo'i dbang du byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:2363: glu ma gsung gi rigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2364: gar ma las rigs su bsdus pa yin pas 'gal ba med do //
NK064(ngu)001:2366: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed nas /
NK064(ngu)001:2367: ma byon pa'i tshogs dang zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2368: 'dir yang byang chub chen po rdo rje ni spyi'i mtshan yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2369: bye brag tu mig shes kyis gzugs mthong bar byed pa'i bdag rkyen mig gi dbang pos byed pas /
NK064(ngu)001:2370: mthong byed ni mig dbang ste byams pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2371: de bzhin du thos byed rna ba'i dbang po ste sgrib sel dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2372: snom byed sna'i dbang po ste kun tu bzang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2373: myong byed lce'i dbang po ste 'jam dpal dbyangs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2375: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi bskyed pas na btsun mo /
NK064(ngu)001:2376: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa 'das pa'i dus te bdug spos ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2377: rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa da ltar ba ste me tog ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2378: rgyu 'bras tshogs la ma spyad pa 'byung ba ni ma 'ongs pa ste mar me ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2379: rgyu 'bras yod la ma tshogs pas 'das ma 'ongs
NK064(ngu)001:2380: gang du'ang ma nges pa ni ma byon pa'i dus
NK064(ngu)001:2381: te dri chab ma'i tshogs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2382: de yang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rgyal
NK064(ngu)001:2383: ba rnams kyi dag pa'i dbang po me long lta
NK064(ngu)001:2384: bu'i nang du chags thogs med par sal ler gsal
NK064(ngu)001:2385: bas kyang yab yum du 'brel te /
NK064(ngu)001:2388: ji snyed ji bzhin mngon du gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:2390: gnyis pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2392: gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2394: gdug pa can 'joms pa'i brtul zhugs chen pos thams cad 'joms shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2395: phas kyi rgol bas tshur mi tshugs pas na rdo rje ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2397: rdo rje'i rang bzhin sgrib pa kun //
NK064(ngu)001:2398: 'joms shing cis kyang mi tshugs la //
NK064(ngu)001:2399: rang byung ye shes lha yi lha //
NK064(ngu)001:2400: thams cad kun la 'big par byed //
NK064(ngu)001:2402: bye brag tu lus kyi yul dbang rnam shes gsum
NK064(ngu)001:2403: 'dus pa'i reg pa ste bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang
NK064(ngu)001:2404: / reg byed lus kyi dbang po ste rta mgrin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2405: reg bya yul te stobs po che dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2406: reg shes lus kyi rnam par shes pa ste gshin rje gshed dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2407: gdug pa can 'joms byed kyi gnyen po yang rtag
NK064(ngu)001:2408: chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i chos nyid yum
NK064(ngu)001:2409: gyi ngo bo des bskyed pa'i phyir ram /
NK064(ngu)001:2410: chos nyid de yang ye shes kyis dmigs shing spyad byar gyur pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2411: tshad med pa bzhi yang spyad bya'i yul yin pas na btsun mo /
NK064(ngu)001:2412: chos thams cad rtag par 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid rang ga mar snang ba ltar ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:2413: de gnas su dag pa'i lha byams pas sdud cing
NK064(ngu)001:2414: 'dren par byed pa'i bdag nyid lcags kyu ma dang
NK064(ngu)001:2415: / de bzhin du chad par 'dzin pa ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:2416: pa ste snying rjes gzhan sdud cing 'ching bar byed
NK064(ngu)001:2417: pa'i las can zhags pa ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2418: bdag tu 'dzin pa ma yin pa ste dga' bas
NK064(ngu)001:2419: sdud cing sdom pa'i las can lcags sgrog ma dang
NK064(ngu)001:2420: / mtshan mar 'dzin pa ma yin pa ste btang
NK064(ngu)001:2421: snyoms kyis sdud cing mnyes par byed pa'i las can
NK064(ngu)001:2422: dril bu ma la sogs pa de lta bu thugs
NK064(ngu)001:2423: ye shes rang snang gi 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2424: gzhan yang rgyud mas sbyangs kyi tshogs dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:2425: brjod kyis mi lang ba rnams dang rang bzhin gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:2427: ji skad smos pa'i ston 'khor gyi rnam par snang
NK064(ngu)001:2428: ba de thams cad ston pa rigs drug pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2429: kyi ye shes kyi rol pa gcig gi ngang du
NK064(ngu)001:2430: 'du zhing / 'gro ba'i phung khams skye mched ji
NK064(ngu)001:2431: snyed pa thams cad kyang lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:2432: 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir te /
NK064(ngu)001:2434: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK064(ngu)001:2435: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK064(ngu)001:2436: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK064(ngu)001:2438: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK064(ngu)001:2439: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK064(ngu)001:2440: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:2443: nga yis 'di kun khyab pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:2444: 'gro ba'i rang bzhin gzhan ma mthong //
NK064(ngu)001:2446: gsum pa bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2447: gsungs pa lo rgyus su barjooda pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2449: bka' gsang sngags mtshon byed kyi tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:2451: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2452: gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:2453: gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang dgongs
NK064(ngu)001:2454: pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo rtogs dka' ba
NK064(ngu)001:2455: gsang ba'i ye shes rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2456: dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi don gzhan gyi spyod
NK064(ngu)001:2457: yul las 'das pa'i gsang ba chen po 'di nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2458: ston pa rigs drug pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK064(ngu)001:2459: dang yon tan dang phrin las lnga'i ngo bo 'chad
NK064(ngu)001:2460: pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK064(ngu)001:2461: rje'i ngang de las mngon par snang bas na phyung
NK064(ngu)001:2465: de bzhin nyid ces sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste //
NK064(ngu)001:2466: e e ma e ma'o zhes zlos te brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2468: e zhes bya ba ngam pa'i tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:2469: e ma zhes pa rab tu ngam //
NK064(ngu)001:2470: e ma'o zhes pa shin tu ngam /
NK064(ngu)001:2471: zhes pas shin tu ngo mtshar bar ston pa'i tshig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2473: kye ma sangs rgyas kye sangs rgyas //
NK064(ngu)001:2474: kye ma sangs rgyas mdzad pa legs //
NK064(ngu)001:2476: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces par gnas kyi rang bzhin dang mtshan nyid bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2477: de yang sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2478: rang snang ba nyid ces par /
NK064(ngu)001:2479: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK064(ngu)001:2480: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK064(ngu)001:2481: rgyan dang zhes pa yan chad bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2482: rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid la 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:2483: thams cad rdzogs pa'i rtsal pho brang gi gzhi la
NK064(ngu)001:2484: sogs pa rnam 'phrul sna tshogs par rang snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:2485: nyid do // ting 'dzin zhes par sgo'i don bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2486: rnam thar bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug pa'i brdar sgo bzhir snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2487: gzugs brnyan zhes par rta babs kyi don bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2488: theg pa brgyad nas bsgrod pa'i rgyu 'bras mtshon byed rta babs kyi gzugs brnyan du rang snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2489: sgyu ma rnam dag gsal ba zhes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2490: yid bzhin rin po zhes par gdan gyi don bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2491: mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs mtshon byed rtogs pa'i rig
NK064(ngu)001:2492: pa nyid sgyu ma ltar sems can lnga'i gdan dang
NK064(ngu)001:2493: / nyes skyon gyis ma gos pas rnam par dag pa pad+ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2495: re ba yid bzhin du skong ba rin po che'i gdan rnams su snang ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:2496: dbang sgyur ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang zhes par ston pa'i don bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2497: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings la mnga' mdzad cing dbang
NK064(ngu)001:2498: sgyur ba'i ye shes nyid ston pa'i ngo bor snang
NK064(ngu)001:2499: la / rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:2500: dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing de nyid chos can 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:2501: 'das kyi chos thams cad dang chos nyid tha mi
NK064(ngu)001:2502: dad par gnas pa thugs rje'i ngang ste ston pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2503: la / rang bzhin no // sku gsung thugs dang
NK064(ngu)001:2504: yon tan phrin las zhes par rang bzhin gnyis su
NK064(ngu)001:2505: med pa'i 'khor rigs lnga yab yum bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2506: ston pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:2507: dang phrin las lnga las phung khams rnam par dag
NK064(ngu)001:2508: pa 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga yab yum du
NK064(ngu)001:2509: snang ba'o // sel med ces par khyab pa'i tshad chos kyi dbyings kun tu zhes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2510: mang ba'i tshad de lta bu'i tshogs zhes sogs bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2511: chos thams cad la sku dang ye shes kyis khyab
NK064(ngu)001:2512: pas nyes skyon cung zad tsam gyi yang sel med
NK064(ngu)001:2513: pa'o // yon tan zhes par sku mdog gi don
NK064(ngu)001:2514: bsdu ste rigs kyi sku mdog dang 'od zer la
NK064(ngu)001:2515: sogs par snang bas 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs ma
NK064(ngu)001:2516: 'dres par gsal ba'i yon tan mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2517: mi zad par ldan rgyan gyi 'khor lo zhes par rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2518: ston pa nyid kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK064(ngu)001:2519: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i khyad par las rang snang ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:2520: // rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do zhes par dus dang chos phun sum tshogs pa bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2521: rdo rje theg pas rgyud mchog tu gyur pa ni bstan pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2522: de 'byung ba'i gnas ni ston 'khor gnas gsum tshogs pa'i dus nyid do zhes pa'i tha tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:2524: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2526: rdo rje gsang ba ni rdo rje'i theg pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2527: de mtshon par byed pa'i tshig tu bsdus pa'o zhes sam /
NK064(ngu)001:2528: yang na rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2529: de ltar na rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa drug
NK064(ngu)001:2530: pa nyid kyi thugs las phyung bar bshad pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:2532: 'dir sdud pa po nyid ston pa dang dgongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2533: tha mi dad par sngar bshad pa bzhin yin pas
NK064(ngu)001:2534: skyon med do // gnyis pa le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2536: de ltar bshad pa de dag gis gsang ba'i snying
NK064(ngu)001:2537: po de kho na nyid nges pa rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:2538: 'di la nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las
NK064(ngu)001:2539: / 'dis rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu phun sum tshogs pa lnga bstan pas na gleng gzhi zhes bya la /
NK064(ngu)001:2540: le'u ni pa ta la'i sgra las ris su bcad pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:2541: yang na pa ta ni gos kyi don te skyob pa'i mtshan nyid can /
NK064(ngu)001:2542: la ni 'dzin pa'i don la 'jug pas mtshan gyis
NK064(ngu)001:2543: gzhung khebs shing gzhung dum bur bcad pas don tshan
NK064(ngu)001:2544: 'dres pa las nye bar skyob pa'i phyir le'u zhes
NK064(ngu)001:2545: bya ste / yas nas bgrangs pa'i thog ma yin pas na dang po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2547: // le'u gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2550: dang po gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2551: thun mong ma yin par gleng bslang ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2552: thun mong du gleng bslang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2554: yab yum gnyis kyis gleng bslang ba'i sgo nas gsang dbang bskur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2555: dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2557: gsang dbang bskur ba'i ched du yab yum snyoms par zhugs tshul /
NK064(ngu)001:2558: nyams su bstar ba'i don las rdzas kyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:2560: dbang thob pa'i yon tan nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2562: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje yid ces sogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2563: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:2564: bzang mos zhes sogs 'og nas blangs te gzhung tshan
NK064(ngu)001:2566: de yang gleng gzhi tshogs pa de nas zhes 'brel sbyar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2567: spyir yid ni rtogs pa'i dus na rang rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:2568: rang byung gi ye shes zhes grags pa gnyug ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:2569: yid de 'das pa'i byed pa po yin mod kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2570: / de nyid ma rtogs pa'i dus na rtog bcas
NK064(ngu)001:2571: 'khrul pa'i yid ces glo bur ba med snang 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:2572: ba'i byed pa por 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:2574: chos bya ba zhes pa ni dbang po gzugs can
NK064(ngu)001:2575: lngas spyad byar ma gyur pa'i yul 'dus byas dang
NK064(ngu)001:2576: 'dus ma byas kyi chos kyi khams te /
NK064(ngu)001:2577: yid kyis gtan la dbab par bya ba'i yul kyang yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2578: des yid skyed par byed pas na skyed byed du'ang 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2579: de bas na 'dir ni bcom ldan 'das rgyud dang
NK064(ngu)001:2580: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi byed pa po 'khor 'das
NK064(ngu)001:2581: rdo rje ltar dbyer mi phyed par thugs su chud
NK064(ngu)001:2582: pa'i yid rang rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:2583: te / spyod yul yongs su dag pas kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:2584: bzang po 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma lus
NK064(ngu)001:2585: pa'i rang bzhin bdag nyid kyi tshul du ro gcig
NK064(ngu)001:2586: cing dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rjes /
NK064(ngu)001:2587: btsun mo ste yul gtan la dbab par bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:2588: mo 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:2589: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings kyi phyag rgya yum kun
NK064(ngu)001:2590: tu bzang mo la snyoms par 'jug par gyur cing
NK064(ngu)001:2591: / de'i tshe btsun mo bya ba mo chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2592: dbyings kun tu bzang mo yang bcom ldan 'das yid
NK064(ngu)001:2593: kun tu bzang po dang thabs shes gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:2594: par snyoms par 'jug par gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:2595: de ltar thabs shes gnyis phan tshun snyoms par zhugs
NK064(ngu)001:2596: pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:2597: lus pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa dbyings dang ye
NK064(ngu)001:2598: shes zung 'jug gcig gi rang bzhin du dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:2599: par mkhyen pas nyid las gzhan pa'i gdul bya ma
NK064(ngu)001:2600: gzigs nas ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa yab yum
NK064(ngu)001:2601: nyid lhan cig pa'i 'khor rang bzhin gyi de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:2602: gshegs pa nyid la thabs dang shes rab kyi gsang
NK064(ngu)001:2603: dbang bskur ba'i phyir rang gis nyams su bstar ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2604: dgongs pa 'og nas 'byung ba nyid bstan par bzhed
NK064(ngu)001:2605: nas ched du brjod pa'i tshul thabs shes kyi gleng
NK064(ngu)001:2606: bslang gnyis po 'di brjod par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:2608: dang po yab kyis nyams su bstar ba'i don thabs kyi cha bzung nas brjod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2609: e ma'o rdo rje phung po nas /
NK064(ngu)001:2610: mnyes par gyur to zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2611: rtog tshogs thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du rtogs pa la e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2613: srid dang rnam par grol ba'i chos thams cad rang
NK064(ngu)001:2614: rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin du dbyer mi
NK064(ngu)001:2616: phung po ni du ma spungs pa'i don yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2617: de'i yan lag gi dbye ba ni rnam shes sogs lnga'i bye brag rtog pa brgyad cu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2618: de dag rnam shes kyi phung po mi bskyod par
NK064(ngu)001:2619: grub pa sogs phung po lnga rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:2621: de bzhin du dbang yul las rnam shes drug skye
NK064(ngu)001:2622: zhing skad cig phyi mar rgyun mched par byed pas
NK064(ngu)001:2623: dang / rnam shes yul dbang gi khams drug drug
NK064(ngu)001:2624: ste bco brgyad po rnams kyi rtog pa'i bye brag
NK064(ngu)001:2625: mang po kun kyang byang chub sems dpa' yab yum
NK064(ngu)001:2626: sogs 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du gnas te /
NK064(ngu)001:2627: shees yul dbang gsum re re yang drug drug gi snga ma bzhi bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2628: dbang po'i go 'byed dus rnams ni rim pa ji
NK064(ngu)001:2629: lta bar nang sems yab yum dang phyi sems yab
NK064(ngu)001:2630: yum / de gsum gyi lnga pa lus kyi dbang shes reg bya gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2631: gsum 'dus kyi reg pa rnams kyi 'joms pa bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:2632: yid kyi dbang shes kun tu bzang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2633: yul chos ni bzang mo yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:2634: sgo ma bzhi'i rtog pa'ang de'i bye brag ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2635: rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i chos nyid kyang der 'du ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:2636: 'byung ba lnga ni rigs kyi yum lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2637: sa dang chu ni sangs rgyas spyan ma dang m+aa ma k+ai'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2638: me dang rlung ni gos dkar mo dang dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2639: nam mkha' ni yum dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2640: de ltar na srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2641: sku dang zhing khams su rnam par dag pas 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:2643: 'das pa'i chos ma lus pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2644: snang zhing srid pa'i chos so cog thams cad rang
NK064(ngu)001:2645: bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing 'od gsal bas sku
NK064(ngu)001:2646: dang ye shes su sangs rgyas pa nyid las gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:2647: ma yin te / sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan du
NK064(ngu)001:2648: gyur pa'i chos 'di zhes rang mtshan du grub pa
NK064(ngu)001:2649: zhig sangs rgyas nyid kyis btsal kyang don la med
NK064(ngu)001:2650: pas mi brnyes so ste rnyed pa ma yin no
NK064(ngu)001:2651: ma yin te / // de ltar yang phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:2652: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK064(ngu)001:2653: byang chub nam mkha'i mtshan nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:2655: de ltar rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:2656: pa'o zhes ston pa yab kyis brjod pas yum dang
NK064(ngu)001:2657: 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par
NK064(ngu)001:2658: gyur to // gnyis pa yum gyis nyams su bstar
NK064(ngu)001:2659: ba'i don shes rab kyi cha bzung nas dbyings kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2661: kye ma'o phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2662: rang gis rtogs pa'i don gzhan la ston par bzhed nas kye ma'o zhes bod cing /
NK064(ngu)001:2663: 'di 'dra'i ngo mtshar ba bstan du yod ces ngam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2664: de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:2665: zhing 'dis mtshon te phyogs bcu'i stong khams kyi 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:2666: rten du snang ba thams cad log rtog gis brtags
NK064(ngu)001:2667: pa las ye nas rang bzhin gyis dben la /
NK064(ngu)001:2668: de'i rgyu mtshan gyis srid pa gsum nyid rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:2669: dag pa sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi zhing khams dang
NK064(ngu)001:2671: nyon mongs dus tshe lta ba sems can nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:2672: ces gsungs pa'i snyigs ma lnga nyid ma spangs par bde ldan gyi gnas su rtogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2673: nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i snyigs ma lnga po rim bzhin dwangs ma ye shes lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2675: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i tshe dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2676: ye nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2677: srid zhi mnyam nyid du ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2679: lta ba'i snyigs ma'i dod du las kyi snyigs ma bshad pa ltar na /
NK064(ngu)001:2680: ci byed yang dag pa'i mdzad spyod du rtogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2681: 'gro ba'i phung po lnga nyid rang bzhin gyis mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pas na /
NK064(ngu)001:2682: chos thams cad gnas lugs la mchog gi 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:2683: bsgrub bya'i gzhi bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste
NK064(ngu)001:2684: / gnyug ma rang bzhin rnam dag gi sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:2685: de las gzhan du rgyal ba'i chos shig yod dam snyam nas btsal bar mi bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2686: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan du gyur pa ma dag
NK064(ngu)001:2687: pa 'di zhes bya ba'i chos shig gud nas btsal
NK064(ngu)001:2688: kyang / gzigs pa rnam par dag pa rgyal ba nyid kyis kyang mi brnyes so ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2689: don la med nges yin pa'i phyir mi rnyed do //
NK064(ngu)001:2691: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs pa log pa ni thams
NK064(ngu)001:2692: cad du med par go bar byed pa kho na
NK064(ngu)001:2695: zhes brjod pas thams cad ces sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2696: de yang ston pa'i thugs rang rig pa nyid gdul
NK064(ngu)001:2697: bya'i ngo la ye shes sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:2698: rlung thig le'i rnam par snang bas yab yum snyoms
NK064(ngu)001:2699: par zhugs te / de las byung ba'i nyi zlas rgyu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2700: nyams su bstar ba'i don rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas lha'i phyag rgya dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2701: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pa'o zhes rtogs pa brjod pas rkyen byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:2702: lhag pa kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa
NK064(ngu)001:2703: mthong ste rtog tshogs thams cad ye gdod ma nas
NK064(ngu)001:2704: sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa ston pa yab
NK064(ngu)001:2705: yum nyid dang dgongs pa tha mi dad pa'i 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:2706: rnams kyis mkhyen to zhes 'dir gzhan rnam par bcad
NK064(ngu)001:2707: pa'i tshig gis gsang dbang gi nges tshig kyang grub
NK064(ngu)001:2708: ste / 'khor thun mong ba rnams kyis dbang thob
NK064(ngu)001:2709: pas don dam rtog med kyi ye shes rgyud la
NK064(ngu)001:2710: skyes kyang ston pa'i dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ye
NK064(ngu)001:2711: shes chen po da dung ma myong ba'i phyir spyod
NK064(ngu)001:2712: yul ma yin pas na gsang ba'i dbang zhes bya'o
NK064(ngu)001:2713: ste / // gnyis pa dbang gnyis kyi las la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2715: sems bskyed cing ji ltar bskur ba'i rim pa dngos dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2718: de nas gnyis su med pa'i zhes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:2719: gsang dbang bskur ba de nas don dgongs pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:2720: rtags yab yum gyi nyi zla byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu)001:2721: gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid bde ba chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:2722: rang bzhin gyis 'khor rnams la chos thams cad ye
NK064(ngu)001:2723: nas sangs rgyas pa'i don sems nyid ye shes lngar
NK064(ngu)001:2724: dngos su bskyed pa 'di gsungs so //
NK064(ngu)001:2726: e ma'o ngo mtshar sogs tshigs bcad lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2727: 'di la gsum gzhi rang bzhin gyi /
NK064(ngu)001:2729: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed do //
NK064(ngu)001:2731: e ma'o zhes pa ngo mtshar ba'i tshig ste //
NK064(ngu)001:2733: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rang bzhin ye shes lngar
NK064(ngu)001:2734: dag pa'i gnas lugs ngo mtshar zhing gzhan las rmad
NK064(ngu)001:2735: du byung ba'i chos nyid 'di ni rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK064(ngu)001:2736: rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba zab mo ste
NK064(ngu)001:2737: / phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2739: sems nyid gdod nas skye ba med pa las 'khrul
NK064(ngu)001:2740: ngor rtog bcas kyi sems thams cad rgyu rkyen las
NK064(ngu)001:2742: de ltar skyes par snang tsam nyid na don la
NK064(ngu)001:2743: de lta bur skye ba grub pa med pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2744: ni kun gzhi nyid chos dbyings ye shes su bskyed
NK064(ngu)001:2745: pa'o // de bzhin du snang ba thams cad 'gag
NK064(ngu)001:2746: pa nyid na don la 'gag pa med pa'i zung
NK064(ngu)001:2747: 'jug rtog med rang gsal ba 'di ni kun gzhi'i
NK064(ngu)001:2748: rnam shes me long lta bu'i ye shes su'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2749: rten gang la gnas pa ltar snang tsam nyid na
NK064(ngu)001:2750: don la gnas pa med pa'i zung 'jug dngos po'i
NK064(ngu)001:2751: gshis tha dad dang phyogs ris bral ba 'di ni
NK064(ngu)001:2752: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2753: ye shes su'o // yul tha dad du dmigs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2754: nyid na don la dmigs pa med pa'i zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:2755: yul yul can gnyis med gsal la ma 'dres pa
NK064(ngu)001:2756: ni yid so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2757: gang du 'gro ba dang 'ong ba ltar snang tsam
NK064(ngu)001:2758: nyid na don la 'gro 'ong med pa'i zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:2759: sems nyid ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa ni sgo
NK064(ngu)001:2760: lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su bskyed pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:2765: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:2766: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i chos nyid rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:2767: pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:2768: 'di lta ste / don dam par skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong med pa'i ngang las /
NK064(ngu)001:2769: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad skye 'gag la sogs par snang la /
NK064(ngu)001:2770: de ltar skyes pa la sogs par snang dus nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2771: na don dam par skye ba la sogs pa med
NK064(ngu)001:2772: pa'i ngo bo lhag pa bden pa dbyer med du
NK064(ngu)001:2773: la bzla ba lnga po 'di ni ye shes lnga
NK064(ngu)001:2774: dang sbyar na stong pa nyid la sogs pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:2775: / de ltar rtogs pa'i blo ni ye shes so //
NK064(ngu)001:2776: de dag sems lnga dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK064(ngu)001:2777: chos thams cad thog mar skye ba med na mthar 'gag pa dang bar du gnas pa med la /
NK064(ngu)001:2778: de med pas rang spyi'i mtshan nyid du dmigs pa med cing /
NK064(ngu)001:2779: gnas dmigs med pas 'gro 'ong kyang med mod kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:2781: de'i ngang las rig pa sgyu ma tsam du thams
NK064(ngu)001:2782: cad skye 'gag la sogs pa ltar snang bas bden
NK064(ngu)001:2783: gnyis mtshon tshul gyi ldog cha nas tha dad kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2784: ngo bo dbyer med pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2785: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med pa ni bden
NK064(ngu)001:2786: pa dbyer med kyi don la sems dang por 'go
NK064(ngu)001:2787: ldang ba g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK064(ngu)001:2788: de bzhin du 'khrugs sdebs kyi rim pas dmigs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2789: sogs don de khong du chud par smon pa byang
NK064(ngu)001:2791: 'gag pa sogs dbyer med kyi don la 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2792: gnas pa sogs dbyer med kyi don la gnas pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2793: 'gro 'ong sogs dbyer med kyi don mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK064(ngu)001:2794: de yang lam pa'i blo khyad kyis dbyer med kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2795: bden pa la sems lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2797: rim par bskyed pa rim gyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2799: e ma'o zhes pa ngam pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2801: 'dod chags chen po'i spyod pa 'di ni spyad kyang mi 'ching bas ngo mtshar zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:2802: des bla na med pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byed
NK064(ngu)001:2803: pa'i myur lam gzhan las ches rmad du byung ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2804: chos rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi brnag
NK064(ngu)001:2806: khe nyen dang bcas pa'i thabs kyi lam yin pa'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2808: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa rten med kyi ye
NK064(ngu)001:2809: shes la skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong med pa
NK064(ngu)001:2810: las yab yum gnyis su med par rol pa'i sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:2811: bas dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2812: lam nyams su blangs pa'i tshe rtsa gnas thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:2813: nas thig le g.yos pas bde ba 'go ldang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2814: tshul du skyes pa ni g.yo ldang byang chub kyi
NK064(ngu)001:2815: sems so // bde ba phyi ma 'jug pa'i tshe
NK064(ngu)001:2816: snga ma 'jig cing mthar thams cad 'gag pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:2818: rten can gyi bde ba rang sa na gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:2819: med pa'i tshul gyis thams cad gnas pa ni gnas
NK064(ngu)001:2820: pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK064(ngu)001:2821: snga ma'i bde bas mtshon nas phyi ma'i bde ba
NK064(ngu)001:2822: thams cad la dmigs shing 'dun pa ni smon pa
NK064(ngu)001:2824: de dag ni dbang gnyis kyi sngon 'gro thun mong ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2826: nyi zla byang chub kyi sems rdo rje dang pad+ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:2827: rtser dga' ba bcu drug lugs 'byung du 'gro bas
NK064(ngu)001:2828: phrad tsam na thabs kyis 'dzag pa bkag ste bzung
NK064(ngu)001:2829: bas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob cing /
NK064(ngu)001:2830: thun mong gi sa bcu dang lam lnga rdzogs nas
NK064(ngu)001:2831: don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes rgyud la skyes
NK064(ngu)001:2832: pa'o // de nyid slar ldog pa'i thabs kyis rang
NK064(ngu)001:2833: gnas su 'ong ba mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu
NK064(ngu)001:2834: drug gi mthar dkar dmar gyi cha steng 'og tu
NK064(ngu)001:2835: thim pa'i skad cig gnyis par rlung yang 'gags pas
NK064(ngu)001:2836: de gsum gyi 'gyur ba myong ba'i shes rig kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2837: rgyun chad de bde ba chen po'i dbang thob cing
NK064(ngu)001:2838: pa'o // / khyad par gyi sa lam rdzogs nas
NK064(ngu)001:2839: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK064(ngu)001:2840: ba'i ye shes mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po
NK064(ngu)001:2841: mngon du byas pa ni mthar phyin pa byang chub
NK064(ngu)001:2842: pa'o // / kyi sems te / de dag kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2843: skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang dus nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2844: na don la skye ba la sogs pa med pas
NK064(ngu)001:2845: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la bden
NK064(ngu)001:2846: pa dbyer med du la bzla ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2847: de ltar dbang rdzogs pas lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams
NK064(ngu)001:2848: kyis rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don khong du
NK064(ngu)001:2849: chud de ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:2850: nas gzhan don du rgyud zhu ba'i spobs pa skyes
NK064(ngu)001:2851: pa'i phyir / sngon byung gi zab dbang gsum po
NK064(ngu)001:2852: 'di go phye ba'i 'khor la ltos te rgyud 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:2853: ba'i rkyen gleng bslang du 'gyur na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:2854: lhan cig pa'i 'khor la ltos na rgyud tshar gcig dus der rdzogs pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:2855: sngon byung du gleng bslang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:2857: rgyud don rtogs pa gsum ngo bo gcig la ldog
NK064(ngu)001:2858: pa so sor snang ba tsam yin pa'i phyir ro
NK064(ngu)001:2860: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos zab
NK064(ngu)001:2861: dbang gsum thob pas lhan cig pa rnams rang don
NK064(ngu)001:2862: du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga po kun gyi
NK064(ngu)001:2863: bdag nyid du sangs rgyas te /
NK064(ngu)001:2864: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2865: ni 'khor thun mong ba'i spyod yul ma yin pas
NK064(ngu)001:2866: gsang ba ste / skye ba med las zhes sogs kyis dbyings ye zung 'jug chos kyi sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2867: 'gag pa sogs kyis sku gsum dbyer med gsal stong zung 'jug mngon byang gi sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2868: gnas pa sogs kyis dag pa'i gdul bya la gzugs
NK064(ngu)001:2869: sku'i rnam par snang yang mtha' la mi gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2870: zung 'jug longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2871: dmigs pa sogs kyis sku gsum so sor snang yang
NK064(ngu)001:2872: mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su dbyer mi phyed pa rdo
NK064(ngu)001:2873: rje'i sku dang / 'gro 'ong sogs kyis skal pa
NK064(ngu)001:2874: dang 'tshams par 'char nub tu ston kyang don la
NK064(ngu)001:2878: sems bskyed cing dbang bskur ba'i rim pa de skad
NK064(ngu)001:2879: ces brjod pas lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:2880: gshegs pa yab thams cad dang yum btsun mo'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:2881: thams cad kyang don dam 'od gsal dang dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:2882: kyi dgongs pa nyams su myong ste ston 'khor dgongs
NK064(ngu)001:2883: pa khyad med du gyur pa la mnyes pas khyab
NK064(ngu)001:2884: par gyur to // gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:2888: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK064(ngu)001:2889: shin tu gsang zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2890: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ba de nas
NK064(ngu)001:2891: 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad rang rang
NK064(ngu)001:2892: gi btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas go phye ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2893: 'khor gyi ched du ston pa'i thugs rje bskul ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:2896: ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba la skyo ba'i tshul gyis e ma'o zhes ngam ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2897: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid la 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:2898: de'i don thog ma nyid nas ma rtogs pas ye nas gsang ba'i chos so //
NK064(ngu)001:2899: de nyid sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:2900: kyang 'bras bu mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor
NK064(ngu)001:2901: gnas pa la phyin ci log gi shes pas bslad
NK064(ngu)001:2902: nas rang gi rang bzhin ma rtogs pa ni rang
NK064(ngu)001:2904: gnas lugs de yang yul sems dang rgyu 'bras la
NK064(ngu)001:2905: sogs pa gnyis chos thams cad las ngo bo nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2906: kyis grol te yul du byar med kyang ma rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:2907: pas de ltar lta ba ni rab tu gsang ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:2908: // de yang sems nyid las gzhan zhig gud du
NK064(ngu)001:2909: yod pa min kyang sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:2910: pas bsgribs te rang la gnas pa gzhan las 'tshol
NK064(ngu)001:2911: ba ni shin tu gsang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2912: de ltar gsang ba bzhis chod nas ma rtogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:2913: gdul bya rnams thugs rjes bzung bar rigs zhes zhus
NK064(ngu)001:2914: pa'o // gnyis pa lan stsal ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2915: zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang nas /
NK064(ngu)001:2916: ched du gleng ngo zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:2917: 'khor gyis gsang ba bzhi'i don de skad ces brjod de zhus pas ston pa'i thugs rjes skyes te /
NK064(ngu)001:2919: dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba thams cad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2920: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i chos phyi nang snod bcud
NK064(ngu)001:2921: du snang ba thams cad rtogs rung ma rtogs rung
NK064(ngu)001:2923: byed pa po med par ye nas rang bzhin lhun
NK064(ngu)001:2924: grub kyi sangs rgyas bden pa dbyer med pa'i ngo
NK064(ngu)001:2925: bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:2926: mi phyed pa'i phyi ra thugs rje skyes nas don
NK064(ngu)001:2927: byar med na'ang / 'gro ba rang rang gi rnam
NK064(ngu)001:2928: par rtog pa bskyed pa'i rtsa ba ma rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:2929: byar med na'ang / gnyis las / 'bras bu lha
NK064(ngu)001:2930: ma yin stod ris lha dang smad ris dud 'gror
NK064(ngu)001:2931: bsdus pas 'gro ba rgyud lnga'i sdug bsngal nang rigs
NK064(ngu)001:2932: mi mthun pa bsam gyis mi khyab par smin pa
NK064(ngu)001:2933: byar med na'ang / gnyis las / la / thabs dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje chen po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2934: shes rab sangs rgyas kyi thugs ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2935: de nyid kyi ngang nas ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:2936: shes mi 'gag pas gdul bya'i ngo la thugs rje
NK064(ngu)001:2937: skyes nas don mdzad par dgongs te ched du brjod
NK064(ngu)001:2938: pa 'di brjod do zhes sprul pa spro bar zhal
NK064(ngu)001:2939: gyis bzhes pa'o // gang gi phyir spro na /
NK064(ngu)001:2940: ma rtogs pa la brtse ba'i rang bzhin gyis e ma'o zhes ngam ste /
NK064(ngu)001:2941: sems nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa ni bde gshegs snying po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2942: de ltar yin pa las rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo ma shes shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2943: rkyen sems can rang rang gi phyin ci log gi
NK064(ngu)001:2944: rnam par rtog pa kun brtags kyis nyon mongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:2945: skyes nas las sna tshogs la skyes nas las sna
NK064(ngu)001:2946: tshogs la spyad pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i chos 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2947: rnams thag khra la sbrul mthong ltar med snang glo
NK064(ngu)001:2949: de las bde 'gro dang ngan 'gro sogs sna tshogs pa'i lus dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2950: rang rang gi 'dod pa'i yul gzugs sgra dri ro sogs longs spyod dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2951: mtho dman sna tshogs pa'i gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2952: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal la sogs pa sna tshogs par snang ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:2953: lus can rnams kyi nga'o zhes bdag dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2954: nga'i 'di dang 'di zhes bdag gir byed pas so
NK064(ngu)001:2955: sor bzung ba dang 'dzin pas bcings te nyam thag
NK064(ngu)001:2956: go // de yang 'khrul ngor snang ba tsam du zad kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:2957: don dam par 'gro ba 'di kun 'ching byed kyi mkhan po sus kyang ma bcings shing /
NK064(ngu)001:2958: dngos po gang gis kyang bcings pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:2959: gang bcing bar bya ba rang yang yod pa ma yin kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:2960: kun rdzob tu bcings pa ltar snang ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2961: rang gi rnam rtoog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis bcings pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:2962: 'ching byed gzhan med kyang blo 'khrul ngor snang ba tsam du zad de /
NK064(ngu)001:2963: dper na rab rib can gyis nan gyis brtags kyang
NK064(ngu)001:2964: mkha' las skra shad 'dzag pa med bzhin du 'dzag
NK064(ngu)001:2965: par mthong nas / de la mdud pa 'dor ba'i 'khrul snang byung ba ltar /
NK064(ngu)001:2966: chos nyid ris med la dgag sgrub gzung 'dzin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:2967: phyogs ris su bcad pas 'khrul pa las don la
NK064(ngu)001:2968: 'khor ba tshad mas grub pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:2969: de yang bcings pa yod na de ltos kyi grol ba'ang srid pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:2970: ltos gzhi bcings pa med pas de la ltos pa'i chos rnams par grol ba'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:2971: 'gro ba mtha' dag ye nas bcings grol med pa'i gnas lugs sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2972: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub cing
NK064(ngu)001:2973: yongs su rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pas
NK064(ngu)001:2974: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du la bzla ba'i chos
NK064(ngu)001:2975: te / de nyid mtshon par byed pa'i rgyud 'di
NK064(ngu)001:2976: gdul bya khyad par can gyi ched du dngos su
NK064(ngu)001:2977: te / bstan cing / gdul bya thun mong ba
NK064(ngu)001:2978: rnams la brgyud nas bstan par bya ba'i phyir bsam
NK064(ngu)001:2979: gyis mi khyab pa'i sprul pa thub pa drug spro
NK064(ngu)001:2980: ba sogs 'gag med thugs rjee chen po'i rol pa
NK064(ngu)001:2981: rnam pa sna tshogs pa ston par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:2982: zhes ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid lhan cig
NK064(ngu)001:2983: pa'i 'khor dbang rdzogs pas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:2984: du gyur pa la go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched
NK064(ngu)001:2985: du gleng ngo // gnyis pa le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:2987: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:2988: 'dis don dam par spros pa nye bar zhi ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:2989: kun rdzob tu de nyid ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis
NK064(ngu)001:2990: 'khor ba la don mdzad tshul gnyis so sor bstan
NK064(ngu)001:2991: kyang / don la gnyis ka byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu)001:2992: 'ching grol med pa'i ngo bor dbyer mi phyed pas
NK064(ngu)001:2993: na 'khor 'das ye nas dbyer med du gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:2994: la gnas par shes pa'i bdag nyid du sems bskyed
NK064(ngu)001:2995: par bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:2997: // le'u gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3004: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3005: yongs su shes par bya ba lta ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3010: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK064(ngu)001:3012: gang gi ched du spro bar zhal gyis bzhes pa de nas /
NK064(ngu)001:3016: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las dmigs med kun
NK064(ngu)001:3017: khyab rang byung gi thugs rje chen por rang shar
NK064(ngu)001:3018: ba'i byin gyis brlabs pa dus su 'byung ba zhes
NK064(ngu)001:3019: bya ba thugs rig pa'i ye shes las rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:3020: 'phrul pas na rig pa'i skyes bu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3021: las nyon gyi dpung bcom pas na thub pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3022: gdul bya'i dbang gis rnam pa drug go //
NK064(ngu)001:3023: gang las na ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK064(ngu)001:3024: drug pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed
NK064(ngu)001:3027: tshangs pa rang gi gnas las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:3028: lha gnas gzhan thams cad du rang gzugs kyi snang
NK064(ngu)001:3029: ba ston pa ltar gdul bya'i ngo la rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:3032: ji ltar tshangs pa tshangs pa yi //
NK064(ngu)001:3033: gnas nas 'pho ba med bzhin du //
NK064(ngu)001:3034: lha yi gnas ni thams cad du //
NK064(ngu)001:3035: snang ba 'bad med ston pa ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:3036: de bzhin thub pa chos sku las //
NK064(ngu)001:3037: bskyod pa med par khams kun tu //
NK064(ngu)001:3038: skal ldan rnams la 'bad med par //
NK064(ngu)001:3039: sprul pa dag ni ston par mdzad //
NK064(ngu)001:3041: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3046: don mdzad de zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3047: de ltar thub pa drug 'thon nas kyang don mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:3048: pa'i yul ngan song gsum dang lha mi ste 'gro
NK064(ngu)001:3049: ba rgyud lnga'am / theg pa lnga'i rigs can gyi 'gro ba lnga'i don mdzad de /
NK064(ngu)001:3051: don bya ba'i zhing gdul bya'i las kyi bye brag
NK064(ngu)001:3052: tha dad pa'i dbang gis mgo 'phred la bstan nas
NK064(ngu)001:3054: gyen mthur du bstan nas 'gro ba yan man gyi
NK064(ngu)001:3055: 'jig rten snod kyi bye brag zlum po sogs bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:3056: dang gzhi phyal ba dang steng g.yogs med pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:3057: rnam pa mi 'dra ba drug gi rang bzhin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:3058: phyogs bcur khyab cing tshad bzung du med pas mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:3059: yas mu med pa'i zhing khams nam mkha'i dbyings ltar
NK064(ngu)001:3060: snang ba las / de'i khongs su tshud pa dum
NK064(ngu)001:3061: bu'i 'jig rten chu dkyil nas bsam gtan dang po
NK064(ngu)001:3062: man chad kyis bsdus pa gling bzhi pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3063: de stong la stong spyi phud /
NK064(ngu)001:3064: de stong la stong gnyis pa bar ma /
NK064(ngu)001:3065: de stong la stong gsum gyi stong chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3066: de re rer gang gis don mdzad pa po thub
NK064(ngu)001:3067: pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re rer snang nas
NK064(ngu)001:3068: ji ltar don mdzad pa'i tshul 'og nas 'byung ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:3069: sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba sogs 'dul ba
NK064(ngu)001:3070: rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas so //
NK064(ngu)001:3074: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK064(ngu)001:3080: 'dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya re rer 'dul byed
NK064(ngu)001:3081: mchog gi sprul sku yang de snyed 'byung ba thams
NK064(ngu)001:3082: cad mdzad pa'i tshul mthun par ston pas na gcig
NK064(ngu)001:3083: gi mdzad tshul smos pas thams cad kyi mdzad pa
NK064(ngu)001:3085: 'o skol gyi ston pa 'di nyid kyi sgo nas brjod de /
NK064(ngu)001:3086: dga' ldan gyi gnas su dam pa tog dkar por skye ba bzhes te /
NK064(ngu)001:3088: sa mo lug gi lo chu stod zla ba'i nya
NK064(ngu)001:3089: la glang po che'i rnam pas yum sgyu 'phrul ma
NK064(ngu)001:3090: gso sbyong la gnas pa'i lhums su zhugs te /
