NK064(ngu)001:3091: zla ba bcu phal cher rdzogs pa lcags sprel sa
NK064(ngu)001:3092: ga'i tshes bdun rgyu skar rgyal la babs pa'i tshe
NK064(ngu)001:3093: lum+bi ni'i tshal du yum gyi rtsib logs g.yas pa
NK064(ngu)001:3094: nas mngal gyi dri ma med par sku bltams te
NK064(ngu)001:3095: / yi ge sogs slob pa ltar mdzad nas bzo'i gnas la byang bar gyur cing /
NK064(ngu)001:3096: sh+aakya rnams sgyu rtsal gyis pham par mdzad de /
NK064(ngu)001:3097: sa 'tsho ma btsun mo'i 'khor brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK064(ngu)001:3098: dang bcas pa bdag gir bzhes nas lo nyi shu
NK064(ngu)001:3099: rtsa dgu'i bar khab tu bzhugs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3100: de nas khyim spangs te mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rab tu byung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3101: de nas chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du lo
NK064(ngu)001:3102: drug gi bar dka' thub mdzad pas sku shin tu
NK064(ngu)001:3103: rid pa la grong pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas
NK064(ngu)001:3104: ba stong gi 'o ma nying khur byas pa sbrang
NK064(ngu)001:3105: rtsi dang sbyar ba drangs pa gsol ba'i mod la
NK064(ngu)001:3106: sku gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:3107: dang / de nas rdo rje gdan du skyes bu
NK064(ngu)001:3108: chen po'i stabs kyis gshegs shing r+ts+wa 'tshong bkra shis
NK064(ngu)001:3109: las rtsa bslang ba la stan mdzad nas /
NK064(ngu)001:3110: byang chub kyi shing drung du skyil mo krung gis bzhugs te /
NK064(ngu)001:3111: dgung lo so lnga pa shing rta sa ga'i nya'i
NK064(ngu)001:3112: tho rengs bsam gtan bzhi pa la brten nas sgrib
NK064(ngu)001:3113: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa ma lus pa spangs
NK064(ngu)001:3114: shing / shes bya thams cad thugs su chud de mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3115: de'i snga logs nya de'i srod kyi dus su smin
NK064(ngu)001:3116: mtshams nas 'od zer bkye ba la sogs pa'i sgo
NK064(ngu)001:3117: na sa bdud btul ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3118: sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun gyi bar du chos ma gsungs pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:3119: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis bskul te w+aa ra
NK064(ngu)001:3120: n+aa s+air lnga sde las brtsams nas bka' dang po
NK064(ngu)001:3122: bya rgod phung po'i ri bo la sogs par bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3123: yangs pa can la sogs par bka' tha ma don
NK064(ngu)001:3124: dam rnam par nges pa ste chos kyi 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:3125: rnam pa gsum bskor ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3126: mnyan yod du mu stegs rnams 'dul ba dang sangs
NK064(ngu)001:3127: rgyas ma thag shing t+aa la bdun srid du 'phags
NK064(ngu)001:3128: pa sogs cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3129: mthar dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa gcig pa lcags 'brug
NK064(ngu)001:3130: sa ga'i nya la gyad yul r+ts+wa can gyi gnas
NK064(ngu)001:3131: shing s+aa la zung gi rtsa bar rdo rje lta
NK064(ngu)001:3132: bu'i sku bshig nas mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:3133: dang sku gdung ring bsrel la sogs pa rnam 'phrul
NK064(ngu)001:3134: mtha' yas par ston pa'i thub pa gang gi sku'i
NK064(ngu)001:3135: mdzad pa de dag ni bsod nams thun mong ma
NK064(ngu)001:3136: yin pa gzhan las 'phags par bstan pas na sku
NK064(ngu)001:3140: drug dang zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3141: sngon gnas dran pa dang phyi ma'i gnas mkhyen pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3142: mngon shes kyis 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:3143: kun tu sgrib pa med par sal ler mkhyen pa
NK064(ngu)001:3144: dang / pha rol gyi sems mkhyen pa'i mngon shes
NK064(ngu)001:3145: kyis gzhan thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kyi 'gyu
NK064(ngu)001:3146: ba sna tshogs pa kun tu ma sgribs par mkhyen
NK064(ngu)001:3147: dang / pa dang / sgrib pa med pa rdzu
NK064(ngu)001:3148: 'phrul gyi lha'i spyan gyis nye ring med pa'i gzugs
NK064(ngu)001:3149: dang 'chi 'pho skye ba sogs thams cad kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:3150: dang / pa dang / gzigs pa dang / lha'i
NK064(ngu)001:3151: snyan gyis sgra che chung thams cad nye ring med
NK064(ngu)001:3152: par kun tu gsan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3153: cho ga ste bya ba grub pa'i mngon shes kyis
NK064(ngu)001:3154: gang 'dul gyi mos pa dang mthun par sprul sgyur
NK064(ngu)001:3155: sogs sna tshogs ston pas kun tu sems can gyi
NK064(ngu)001:3157: sgrib pa dag pa'i ye shes zag pa med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3158: mngon shes kyis ji ltar spyad kyang mi gos pa
NK064(ngu)001:3159: rnam pa kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:3161: de lta bu'i mngon par shes pa chen po drug
NK064(ngu)001:3162: ka thugs kyi rjes su 'gro zhing mkhyen nas shes
NK064(ngu)001:3163: bya thams cad la mngon sum du dbang sgyur ba
NK064(ngu)001:3164: dang ldan pas don mdzad pa'i phyir thugs mngon sum
NK064(ngu)001:3166: kun tu sku nas snang bar gyur to zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3167: gdul bya'i zhing kun tu rang rang gi snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:3168: dang mthun par lha mi'i rgyal po la sogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3169: sku dang / rgyud kun tu mos pa dang mthun par 'jug pa'i thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3170: sku re re la'ang 'gro ba'i mos pa tha dad
NK064(ngu)001:3171: pa'i spyod yul kun tu de dang mthun pa'i zhal
NK064(ngu)001:3172: gyi dkyil 'khor zhi khro dang phra men la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:3173: pa dang / gdul bya'i skal ba ji ltar yod
NK064(ngu)001:3174: pa kun tu so so'i skad dang mthun par chos
NK064(ngu)001:3175: ston pa'i gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:3176: pa dang / pa ste / de ltar rnam 'phrul
NK064(ngu)001:3177: bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas par 'phro bas
NK064(ngu)001:3178: grangs med pa dag phyogs bcu'i zhing kun tu snang
NK064(ngu)001:3185: theg pas zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3186: de la spyir theg pa'i sgra don dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3188: phye ba so so'i don bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:3190: y+aa na'i sgra las 'degs pa'i don gyis na theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3191: de'ang 'dis 'degs pas na theg pa ste bzhon pa bzang po lta bu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3192: 'di 'degs pas na theg pa ste de la brten nas 'gro ba'i gang zag go //
NK064(ngu)001:3193: 'dir 'degs pas na theg pa ste rang rang gi 'dod bya'i 'bras bu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3195: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te //
NK064(ngu)001:3196: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:3197: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan 'da' //
NK064(ngu)001:3200: bka' spyi gzhung du grags pa ltar na /
NK064(ngu)001:3201: theg pa'i grangs 'di kho na zhes phyogs gcig tu bzung du med de /
NK064(ngu)001:3202: gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK064(ngu)001:3203: rjes chos gang la gang 'dul du bstan pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:3205: bla med theg pa bsam yas gsungs pa yang //
NK064(ngu)001:3206: so so rang gi blo la snang bar zad //
NK064(ngu)001:3209: sems can rnams ni yongs drang phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:3210: theg pa mtha' dag ngas bshad de //
NK064(ngu)001:3211: 'di zhes dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK064(ngu)001:3213: de yang re zhig bsdu na /
NK064(ngu)001:3215: theg pa gcig ste theg pa gsum du med //
NK064(ngu)001:3216: ces pa lta bu 'bras bu la dgongs te mthar thug theg pa gcig tu bsgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3217: yang theg pa chung ngu dang chen po'am /
NK064(ngu)001:3218: rgyu 'bras kyi dbye bas gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3219: nyan rang byang sems gsum mam /
NK064(ngu)001:3222: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa ste gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3223: rgyu'i theg pa gsum 'bras theg dang bcas pas bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3226: nang rgyud sde gsum ste theg pa dgu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3228: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK064(ngu)001:3229: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:3230: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK064(ngu)001:3231: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK064(ngu)001:3232: ces pas ji srid blo'i rim pa ma zad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:3233: bar du theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med pas
NK064(ngu)001:3234: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3235: gang la brten nas 'gro ba'i lam dang gang gis
NK064(ngu)001:3236: 'gro ba la sogs pa blo ngo bo nyid kyis
NK064(ngu)001:3237: dag pa'i don theg pa zhes pa'ang dmigs su med
NK064(ngu)001:3239: bye brag rgyud gzhung 'di nyid du grags pa ltar na /
NK064(ngu)001:3240: sprul sku'i gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa de dag thams cad kyang bsdu na 'di lta ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3241: rigs can lnga'i gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis theg pa'i bye brag lngar phye nas bstan to //
NK064(ngu)001:3242: phye ba so so'i don ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3243: de wa'i sgra las bde ba la rol pa'i don gyis lha dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3244: ma nu sh+ya'i sgra las yid shas che bas na
NK064(ngu)001:3245: mi ste bsod nams kyi bye brag las rten bzang
NK064(ngu)001:3246: por gyur pa'o // de'i theg pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3247: 'jig rten pha rol dang las 'bras la yid ches
NK064(ngu)001:3248: kyi lta bas zin pa'i sgo nas dge bcu'i las
NK064(ngu)001:3249: lam la spyad pas ngan song las thar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3250: dge ba'i las stobs che chung gis mi dang 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:3251: lha'i bde ba mthar thug gi bar bgrod pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:3252: / dge bcu spyod pa gzhir bzhag gi steng du
NK064(ngu)001:3253: tshad med pa bzhi dang mi g.yo ba'i ting nge
NK064(ngu)001:3254: 'dzin bsam gzugs kyi snyoms 'jug brgyad bsgoms pas khams
NK064(ngu)001:3255: gong ma gnyis kyi lha'i go 'phang bgrod par byed
NK064(ngu)001:3256: de lang gshegs su snga ma la gtso bo'i sgras
NK064(ngu)001:3257: bstan nas lha'i theg pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3258: phyi ma la 'dod nyon gyis gtsang zhing dag pas tshangs pa'i theg pa zhes bshad do //
NK064(ngu)001:3260: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa //
NK064(ngu)001:3261: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK064(ngu)001:3262: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK064(ngu)001:3263: tshangs gnas la sogs skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:3265: sh+ra ba ka'i sgra nyan pa dang thos sgrogs la 'jug pas ston pa las chos nyan cing /
NK064(ngu)001:3266: rang gis thos pa'i 'bras bu gzhan la sgrog cing thos pas na nyan thos te /
NK064(ngu)001:3267: de nyid kyi theg pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3268: dngos po bzung yul rags pa dang 'dzin pa sems
NK064(ngu)001:3269: kyi rgyun 'di kun rdzob tu snang ba tsam las
NK064(ngu)001:3270: rang bzhin med pas gang zag gi bdag med rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:3271: kyang / chos kyi bdag bzung ba rdul phran bye
NK064(ngu)001:3272: mdo gnyis kyis bskor ba bar bcas bar med dang
NK064(ngu)001:3273: kyang / / gnyis kas 'dzin sems skad cig ma don dam bden par gtan la phab nas /
NK064(ngu)001:3274: las 'bras la blang dor ma nor bar spyod cing /
NK064(ngu)001:3275: sems las su rung ba'i zhi gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3276: bden bzhi'i rnam pa bcu drug bsgom pa'i lhag mthong
NK064(ngu)001:3277: gis mthong bas spang ba sogs ye shes bcu drug
NK064(ngu)001:3279: mthong lam thob pa'i rjes la sgom lam gyis 'dod nyon dgu'i bzhi man chad tsam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3280: drug nas brgyad kyi bar dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3281: dgu pa spangs pa'i rim pas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rgyun zhugs lan cig phyir 'ong /
NK064(ngu)001:3282: phyir mi 'ong ba gsum bgrod nas mthar thug khams
NK064(ngu)001:3283: gsum gyi nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs pa dgra
NK064(ngu)001:3284: bcom pa nyid kyi 'bras bu mngon du byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:3286: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spong ba yi //
NK064(ngu)001:3287: ye shes bcu drug cha sbyangs rab zhi ba //
NK064(ngu)001:3288: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim pas sbyangs nas ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3289: nyon mongs dgra rnams zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK064(ngu)001:3291: pra t+ye ka bud+d+ha'i sgra las slob dpon la ma
NK064(ngu)001:3292: brten par rang gi byang chub rang gis rtogs pas
NK064(ngu)001:3294: de nyid kyi theg pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3296: bzung ba rang bzhin med par rtogs kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:3297: shes pa skad cig ma don dam du blta zhing
NK064(ngu)001:3298: 'khor 'das rten 'brel rgyu 'bras su shes nas lugs
NK064(ngu)001:3299: ldog stong pa bcu gnyis khrigs chags su bsgoms pas
NK064(ngu)001:3301: sgra med lus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis chos ston cing /
NK064(ngu)001:3302: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sar mya ngan las 'da' bar byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3304: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes shing //
NK064(ngu)001:3305: dngos po'i gzugs la thogs med rab tu 'jug /
NK064(ngu)001:3306: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs //
NK064(ngu)001:3307: byang chub sar bgrod yid bzhin bde ba mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:3309: bo d+hi sat+wa'i sgra las bla na med pa'i byang
NK064(ngu)001:3310: chub bsgrub pa la sems stobs che bas na byang
NK064(ngu)001:3313: sems tsam pas don dam par gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa rang rig rang gsal dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3314: dbu ma pas don dam par chos thams cad spros pa dang bral bar gtan la phab ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3315: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du smon pa dang 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:3316: pa'i sems kyis zin pa'i sgo nas pha rol tu
NK064(ngu)001:3317: phyin pa bcus don gnyis rgya chen po spyod cing
NK064(ngu)001:3318: / slob pa'i lam bzhir byang chub kyi chos sum
NK064(ngu)001:3319: cu rtsa bdun bsgoms pas bskal pa grangs med gsum
NK064(ngu)001:3320: na mi slob pa'i lam kun tu 'od kyi sa
NK064(ngu)001:3323: bdag med gnyis rtogs pha rol phyin rdzogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:3324: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK064(ngu)001:3325: sangs rgyas sa bgrod go 'phang thob pa'i lam //
NK064(ngu)001:3326: bden pa gnyis kyis rab tu thob par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:3328: gsang ba sngags kyi theg pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3330: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3331: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:3332: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK064(ngu)001:3333: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK064(ngu)001:3334: zhes pas kun rdzob tu yang chos thams cad la
NK064(ngu)001:3335: mi gnyis pa'i bsam spyod dang ldan pas bden gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:3336: la bzang ngan blang dor du blta ba rgyu'i theg
NK064(ngu)001:3338: de dag thams cad 'dir rdzogs pas na bla na med pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3341: nang pa thabs rgyud gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:3342: phyi ni kri yog sde gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3343: de yang don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:3344: dag par rtogs pas kun rdzob tu lha dang bdag
NK064(ngu)001:3345: rje khol gyi tshul du bltas nas dngos grub zhu
NK064(ngu)001:3346: zhing / gtsang sbra dang dka' spyad sogs phyi'i bya
NK064(ngu)001:3347: ba la gtso bor brten te bsgrubs pas mi tshe
NK064(ngu)001:3348: bdun na rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob
NK064(ngu)001:3349: par 'dod pa kri ya ste bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3350: lta sgom rnal 'byor rgyud dang spyod pa bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:3351: ltar spyad pas mi tshe lnga na rigs bzhi rdo
NK064(ngu)001:3352: rje 'chang gi sa thob par 'dod pa'i phyir u
NK064(ngu)001:3353: pa ya ste gnyis ka'am spyod pa zhes bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:3354: dang / don dam par mtshan ma med pa'i chos
NK064(ngu)001:3355: nyid kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK064(ngu)001:3356: dkyil 'khor du gtan la phab ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3357: bdag dam tshig pa dang lha ye shes pa gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:3358: bzang ngan med par bltas nas rnal 'byor la gtso
NK064(ngu)001:3359: bor brten cing bsgrubs pas mi tshe gsum na rigs
NK064(ngu)001:3360: lnga stug po bkod pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa
NK064(ngu)001:3361: yo ga ste rnal 'byor gyi theg pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3362: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud du chos thams cad sems
NK064(ngu)001:3363: nyid snang stong dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen
NK064(ngu)001:3364: por gtan la phab pa'i don yul med rang gsal
NK064(ngu)001:3365: du sgom zhing / de'i ngang la blang dor med
NK064(ngu)001:3366: par spyad pas tshe 'di nyid la grol bar 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:3367: du sgom zhing / ro // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3368: gnyen po la dgongs te dbye ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3369: de'ang dbang po'i bye brag gis bsdu ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3371: ma rig pa nas gsung bar 'gyur ro zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3372: 'gro ba rnams lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3373: dbang gis phyin ci log gi rnam par rtog pas
NK064(ngu)001:3374: bskyed pa'i nyon mongs pa dug gsum dang cha mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:3375: pa nyi khri chig stong re ste bsdoms pas stong
NK064(ngu)001:3376: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhir spyod pa'i gnyen por chos
NK064(ngu)001:3377: kyi sgo yang sde snod gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3378: cha mnyam rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod de bzhis
NK064(ngu)001:3379: bsdus pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi sngar gsungs
NK064(ngu)001:3381: ma 'ongs pa na'ang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:3382: de skad du'ang kun byed las /
NK064(ngu)001:3383: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3384: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:3385: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3386: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:3387: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3388: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:3389: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3390: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:3393: spyod pa rnams kyi gnyen por ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3394: chos kyi phung po mthun par gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:3397: de dag nas mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3398: chos kyi sgo de dag thams cad kyang dbang po'i bye brag gis lngar 'du ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3399: de yang las dge sdig dang mi g.yo ba'i las
NK064(ngu)001:3400: kyi 'bras bu thams cad chud mi za bar so
NK064(ngu)001:3401: sor smin par yid ches pas blang dor ma nor
NK064(ngu)001:3402: bar spyod kyang 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ma
NK064(ngu)001:3403: nus pa lha mi'i theg pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3404: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pas 'khor ba las
NK064(ngu)001:3405: nges par byung yang chos kyi bdag gzung ba rdul
NK064(ngu)001:3406: phran dang 'dzin pa skad cig ma don dam du
NK064(ngu)001:3407: 'dod pa nyan thos kyi theg pa la nyon mongs
NK064(ngu)001:3409: shes pa skad cig ma don dam du 'dod pas
NK064(ngu)001:3410: phyi'i rten 'brel sa bon nas 'bras bu'i bar dang
NK064(ngu)001:3411: / nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ma
NK064(ngu)001:3412: rig pa nas rga shi'i bar du 'khor bar 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:3413: pas rang rgyal gyi theg pa la nyon mongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:3415: de gsum ni bden pa gnyis ka rdzas yod du
NK064(ngu)001:3416: bltas nas blang dor byed pas spong ba'i lam du
NK064(ngu)001:3417: gcig go // chos thams cad bdag gnyis kyis stong
NK064(ngu)001:3418: par rtogs pas gzung ba'i yul yang 'dzin pa'i shes
NK064(ngu)001:3419: pa rkyen gyis 'khrul pa'i las kyis yul du sgro
NK064(ngu)001:3421: don la don med sgyu ma lta bur shes kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:3422: thabs kyis zin pa dang ma zin pa las phan
NK064(ngu)001:3423: gnod kyi bya ba yang byed par shes nas kun
NK064(ngu)001:3424: rdzob rdzas yod du bltas te blang dor byed pas
NK064(ngu)001:3425: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la nyon mongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:3426: chos nyid du sbyong ba'i thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3427: yang kun rdzob rdzas yod du mi 'dod kyang btags
NK064(ngu)001:3428: pa'i yod pa mi 'gog pas 'di ltar las dang
NK064(ngu)001:3429: las kyi 'bras bu rnams med ces skur pa gdab
NK064(ngu)001:3431: 'on kyang nyon mongs pa lha dang ye shes su
NK064(ngu)001:3432: sgyur ba'i thabs la brten na de dag gis mi
NK064(ngu)001:3433: gos so zhes ston pa kri yog sde gsum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:3434: theg pa dang / kun rdzob tu btags pa'i yod
NK064(ngu)001:3435: par 'dzin pa'ang cher zad de las dang las kyi
NK064(ngu)001:3436: 'bras bu bdag nyid chen po'i rol par rtogs pas
NK064(ngu)001:3437: nyon mongs pa lnga nyid ye shes lnga'i rang mdangs
NK064(ngu)001:3438: su shes te spang gnyen gnyis med pas na gos
NK064(ngu)001:3440: ji ltar spyad kyang yon tan du 'char ba sngags
NK064(ngu)001:3441: nang pa gnyis la nyon mongs pa dbang du byed
NK064(ngu)001:3442: pa'i thabs dang / chos dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK064(ngu)001:3443: par dag pa rang byung gi ye shes rang shar
NK064(ngu)001:3444: bas spong sbyong bsgyur ba dbang du byed pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:3445: cad dngos zhen gyi lta ba las byung bar rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:3446: pa'i thabs dang / nas / gang yang mi 'gog
NK064(ngu)001:3447: cing gang du'ang mi rtsol bas spang gnyen gyi tha
NK064(ngu)001:3448: snyad thams cad las grol nas las dang las kyi
NK064(ngu)001:3449: 'bras bus gos su med par ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3450: theg pa thams cad kyi grub pa'i mtha' gsang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:3451: snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud gzhung
NK064(ngu)001:3453: gnyis pa yongs su shes par bya ba lta ba la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3454: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3455: gtan la dbab pa dngos so //
NK064(ngu)001:3457: de nas de bzhin sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:3458: bstan pa'i spyi'i gleng gzhi bshad pa de nas ston
NK064(ngu)001:3459: pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po
NK064(ngu)001:3460: nyid kyis go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du dgongs
NK064(ngu)001:3461: pa brda'i gsung gis brjod pa dang 'dra bar brda
NK064(ngu)001:3462: sprod pa 'di brjod pas go bar mdzad do zhes
NK064(ngu)001:3463: sdud pa pos lo rgyus brjod de 'brel sbyar ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:3465: brtag gzhi 'khor ba'i chos rang bzhin med par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3466: 'das pa'i chos brjod med du gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3470: grub mtha' rdo rje theg par bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3472: ji snyed sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3473: phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos po ji snyed pas
NK064(ngu)001:3474: bsdus pa'i 'jig rten 'di dag de ma yin pa
NK064(ngu)001:3475: la der 'dzin gyis sgro btags pas rmi lam ltar
NK064(ngu)001:3477: rtsa ba lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3478: bdag gnyis su rtog pa'i kun brtags gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:3479: snang gi shes pas phyi'i rten 'brel sa bon gyi
NK064(ngu)001:3480: rgyu dang 'brel ba myu gu nas 'bras bu'i bar
NK064(ngu)001:3481: gyis bsdus pa / rkyen dang 'brel ba'i chos 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:3482: lnga dus kyi 'gyur ba dang bcas pas bskyed pa
NK064(ngu)001:3483: gyis bsdus pa / lta bu dang / nang gi
NK064(ngu)001:3484: rten 'brel ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar gyis
NK064(ngu)001:3485: bsdus pa lta bur phyi nang gnyis su bar med
NK064(ngu)001:3486: pa shing rta'i 'khor lo ltar 'khor te las mi
NK064(ngu)001:3487: mthun pa'i dbang gis bde sdug sna tshogs myong bas
NK064(ngu)001:3489: de ltar snang dus nyid na de'i rang bzhin chos
NK064(ngu)001:3490: nyid las nyams pa med pas 'khor 'das gnyis de
NK064(ngu)001:3491: nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med mod kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:3492: so sor zhen pa sgro btags kyi blo de nyid skabs 'dir brtag gazhi'am gzhal bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3494: btags pa'i spyod yul gnyis la gzhal //
NK064(ngu)001:3501: thun mong ma yin pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:3502: dang po thun mong ba bden pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3503: yang dag sgyu ma'i sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3504: 'khor bar snang tsam nyid nas yang dag par ma grub pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3505: sgyu ma lta bur ma 'gags par snang ba kun rdzob ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3506: de ltar mtshan nyid theg pa bas chos thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3507: bden pa gnyis su 'byed pa'i 'dod pa dang tshul
NK064(ngu)001:3508: mthun par 'dir yang gnyis su smra ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3509: 'di ltar bdag tu 'dzin pa'i shes pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3510: bdag gi bar rtog pa phung po lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3511: 'byung ba lnga la gzhan du sgro btags te yul
NK064(ngu)001:3512: du 'dzin pa 'di dag snang tsam nyid nas de
NK064(ngu)001:3514: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du tshul gcig par mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:3515: de yang bdag gsum po de don dam bden ngor grub pa med pas skye med du mnyam la /
NK064(ngu)001:3516: kun rdzob bden ngor mi bslu bas /
NK064(ngu)001:3517: sgyu ma tsam du mnyam pa ni thun mong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3518: lhag pa bden pa gnyis kyis gtan la phab na /
NK064(ngu)001:3519: bdag gsum po de rim pa ji lta bar ye shes lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3521: yum lngar dag pas don dam bden pa'i dbang du ye shes /
NK064(ngu)001:3523: rang bzhin don dam gsum ste dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub par mnyam la /
NK064(ngu)001:3524: kun rdzob bden pa'i dbang du ye shes /
NK064(ngu)001:3526: dngos po sgyu ma gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3527: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas
NK064(ngu)001:3528: rdzogs par mnyam pa ni thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3531: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu)001:3533: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni sogs rkang pa gcig dang bcas pa'i tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3534: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan zhes tha dad du snang
NK064(ngu)001:3535: ba 'di rnams ni ma rig pa'i dbang gis log
NK064(ngu)001:3536: par rtog pa'i 'khrul snang tsam nyid las gzhan du
NK064(ngu)001:3537: ma mthong bas phra zhing phra ba ste rdul phran
NK064(ngu)001:3538: dang / ma rtogs pas zab pa ste shes pa
NK064(ngu)001:3539: skad cig ma yang logs na yod pa ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:3540: dang / kyang / 'di ltar snang ba ni log
NK064(ngu)001:3541: rtog gi rgyun snga ma nyid la phyi ma nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3542: spyod pa rmi lam gyi snang ba ltar 'khrul par
NK064(ngu)001:3543: zad pas na 'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur nam mkha'i ngang
NK064(ngu)001:3544: las ma g.yos pa bzhin du don la chos nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3545: las gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:3546: rgyu gcig pa'i rtags kyi bsgrub bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3547: sgrub tshul ni tha snyad pa'i shes ngor snang yang
NK064(ngu)001:3548: rnam par dpyad na log rtog tsam yang yod pa
NK064(ngu)001:3549: ma yin te / de'i rgyu ma rig pa'i bdag dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3551: zhen pa'i rgyun rnam shes su snang ba nyid kyang
NK064(ngu)001:3552: brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba ye nas
NK064(ngu)001:3554: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su log rtog
NK064(ngu)001:3555: skad cig ma'i rgyun tsam yang ma grub pas chos
NK064(ngu)001:3556: thams cad sems kyi chos nyid du rgyu gcig par
NK064(ngu)001:3558: de ltar log rtog gi rgyun rnam par dag pas
NK064(ngu)001:3559: chos thams cad mnyam pa'i dbyings su rgyu gcig pa
NK064(ngu)001:3560: nyid rtags yig 'bru'i tshul gyis ma 'gags par rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:3561: te / de yang skye med mtshon pa a'i tshul te gsung gi rang bzhin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3562: de nyid la cir yang mi 'gags pas dbang sgyur
NK064(ngu)001:3563: ba mtshon pa u'i tshul te sku'i rang bzhin dang
NK064(ngu)001:3564: / yi ge gnyis mtshams sbyar la thig les brgyan
NK064(ngu)001:3565: pas gnyis med du rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid ye
NK064(ngu)001:3566: shes lngar gsal ba mtshon byed gyi tshul du rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:3567: pa thugs kyi rang bzhin du yig 'bru'i tshul lo
NK064(ngu)001:3568: / // de ltar rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i
NK064(ngu)001:3569: tshul du rtogs pa'i mthus bden pa dbyer med du
NK064(ngu)001:3570: ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs
NK064(ngu)001:3571: / // la 'byung zhing / rang rig mngon sum
NK064(ngu)001:3572: gyis nyid la nyid spyod pa ltar yul med rang
NK064(ngu)001:3573: gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs
NK064(ngu)001:3574: / // la 'byung zhing / so // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3575: bdag dang gzhan dang sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3578: rtog pa'i rgyun rnam shes te phyi nang gi chos
NK064(ngu)001:3579: 'di dag rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin
NK064(ngu)001:3580: te / bdag gsum po de rim pa ji lta bar rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3582: ye shes lngar dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:3584: gtan tshigs de dag gis gzhal ba'i 'bras bu sngar /
NK064(ngu)001:3585: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:3586: ces pas chos thams cad rang bzhin bden pa dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:3587: med spyod yul dang bral ba'i chos nyid du gtan
NK064(ngu)001:3589: bla na med pa rdo rje'i theg pa 'di'i grub mtha' ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3590: mtshan nyid dang phyi rgyud kyi theg pa las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir mchog go //
NK064(ngu)001:3591: gnyis pa 'das pa'i chos brjod med du gtan la dbab pa la lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3592: theg pa bzhis nges par 'byung ba'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i theg par bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3593: chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa'i cho 'phrul du bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3594: sangs rgyas dang chos la 'pho 'gyur med kyang gdul bya'i don du de ltar bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3595: rgyud kyi che ba bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3596: de thams cad btags pa tsam ste rang bzhin brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3598: theg pa bzhi sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3600: byang sems kyi theg pa bzhi yis rang rang gi mi mthun phyogs ngan 'gro dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3602: mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung la /
NK064(ngu)001:3603: de ltar nges par byung ba'i mthar bla na med pa'i theg pa gcig pu 'di kho na ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3604: de dag gi bsgrub bya dang 'di las bgrod cing
NK064(ngu)001:3605: sbyang du med pas 'bras bur nges shing gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3608: yang dag rtogs pas sogs rkang pa gnyis te //
NK064(ngu)001:3609: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis
NK064(ngu)001:3610: rab tu brtags shing dpyad na chos thams cad rang
NK064(ngu)001:3611: bzhin cir yang grub pa med pa'i ngang las rten
NK064(ngu)001:3612: 'brel tsam du rol pa cir yang ma 'gags par
NK064(ngu)001:3613: 'char bas thabs rnams kyang gdul bya'i blo dang mthun
NK064(ngu)001:3614: par chud mi za bar 'grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:3616: sangs rgyas sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3617: yang dag par na sku gsum dbyer med pas sangs
NK064(ngu)001:3618: rgyas sprul pa'i sku'ang mya ngan las yongs su mi
NK064(ngu)001:3619: 'da' zhing / des gsungs pa'i chos kyang 'khor ba ma stongs bar nub par mi 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:3620: sems can thams cad sgrol bar bzhed pa'i snying rje chen po mthar phyin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:3621: 'on kyang 'pho 'gyur yod pa ltar snang ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3622: gnas lugs ma rig pa'i sems can rnams smin par mdzad pa dang 'dul bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:3623: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du dang po byung ba nas
NK064(ngu)001:3624: mtha' mya ngan las 'da' ba'i bar gyi mdzad pa
NK064(ngu)001:3625: dang / bstan pa dar nub kyi tshul ston pa
NK064(ngu)001:3626: thams cad sprul pa tsam las rang rgyud pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:3627: dang / yin te / spyi mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:3628: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK064(ngu)001:3634: sangs rgyas bcom ldan bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:3635: de bzhin gshegs pa rtag pa'i sku //
NK064(ngu)001:3636: sems can rnams la phan pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:3637: bkod pa rnam pa sna tshogs ston //
NK064(ngu)001:3640: 'dul ba sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3641: gang du lhag pa tshul khrims dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3643: shes rab kyi bslab pa gsum gtso bor ston pas bzhag pa 'dul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:3645: chos mngon pa ste sde snod gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3646: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs 'da' bar dka' ba'i dam tshig gis bcings pa bya rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3647: kri yog gnyis ka la brten nas sgrub pa spyod rgyud dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3648: lus ngag gi spyod pa grogs tsam las gtso bor
NK064(ngu)001:3649: rnal 'byor pa brten pas don grub par byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:3650: yo ga dang / cho ga gsum bskyed sogs bskyed rim dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3651: rdzogs rim gsal stong gtso bor ston pa sku'i rgyud pha bla med dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3652: bskyed rim rdzogs tshul dang rdzogs rim bde stong gtso
NK064(ngu)001:3653: bor ston pa gsung gi rgyud ma bla med dang
NK064(ngu)001:3654: / bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing 'od gsal ye
NK064(ngu)001:3655: shes chen po'i rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa thugs
NK064(ngu)001:3656: kyi rgyud gnyis su med pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3657: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rnams su snod ldan la rab
NK064(ngu)001:3658: tu grags pa'i mdo rgyud thams cad gsang ba'i snying
NK064(ngu)001:3660: de bas na ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3661: kyis rgyas 'debs pa'i rang bzhin gyis gsang ba'i snying
NK064(ngu)001:3662: po 'di ni 'khor ba ji srid pa de srid
NK064(ngu)001:3663: du sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi 'byung gnas
NK064(ngu)001:3664: te phyi mo lta bur 'gyur zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:3665: de thams cad gtan la'ang 'dis nges par 'bebs pas
NK064(ngu)001:3666: na mdo rgyud kun gyi spyi 'grel lta bu'ang yin
NK064(ngu)001:3668: chos rnams nas brjod do zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3669: de ltar bstan pa'i chos rnams thams cad ming tha
NK064(ngu)001:3670: dad du btags pa tsam las don la grub pa
NK064(ngu)001:3671: med kyang / ston pas tha snyad la brten nas
NK064(ngu)001:3672: yang dag pa'i don la rim gyis dkri ba'i cheed
NK064(ngu)001:3673: du re zhig gdul bya'i blo dang mthun phyogs su
NK064(ngu)001:3674: ming dang tshig tu sgro btags nas chos bstan pa
NK064(ngu)001:3675: med kyang / tsam las / de ltar ston pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3676: dus nyid nas ming tshig la don gyi dngos po
NK064(ngu)001:3677: cung zad kyang grub pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:3679: ji ltar la la zhig la bu btsas nas //
NK064(ngu)001:3680: de yi ming ni tha dad der btags kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:3681: nang dang phyi rol kun tu btsal na med //
NK064(ngu)001:3682: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:3684: de ltar chos thams cad brjod dra med pa'o zhes brjod par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:3685: gnyis pa bsdu ba la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3686: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3688: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:3692: rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:3693: yab yum dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:3694: gyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi don spyod yul
NK064(ngu)001:3695: las 'das pa'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston pa'i sku
NK064(ngu)001:3696: la sogs pa lnga'i ngo bo rigs lnga dbyer mi
NK064(ngu)001:3697: phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:3699: a hoh srid rtsa'i sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3700: a hohzhesa pa ni 'khor 'das gnyis med du gtan la phebs pa la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3701: de yang tshigs su bcad pa dang po'i nang du
NK064(ngu)001:3702: ji snyed 'jig rten zhes sogs gzhal bya ston pa
NK064(ngu)001:3704: 'di ltar srid pa 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3705: bskyed pa'i rtsa ba ni nga dang bdag tu rtog
NK064(ngu)001:3707: de las 'phros pa las dang nyon mongs pa'i 'du
NK064(ngu)001:3708: byed kyi bag chags smin pa'i dbang gis mngon par
NK064(ngu)001:3709: grub pa rgyud drug gi sems can so so'i snang
NK064(ngu)001:3715: 'chi 'pho ltung ba la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal gyi
NK064(ngu)001:3716: 'khrul 'khor bar med du 'khor ba la sogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:3717: ste / de dag kyang log rtog nyid de ltar
NK064(ngu)001:3718: snang ba tsam las don gzhan du grub pa ci
NK064(ngu)001:3719: ste / yang med de / dran pa nyer bzhag las /
NK064(ngu)001:3720: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK064(ngu)001:3721: bde sdug nyid du snang ba ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3722: sems kyis sprul zhing sems kyis byas //
NK064(ngu)001:3723: sems las gzhan du cung zad med //
NK064(ngu)001:3724: dper na rmi lam ji bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:3726: rkang pa lnga pa'i phyed snga mar gtan tshigs gsum grub mtha' dang bcas pa bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3727: bden rtog dag pa'i gtan tshigs gsum gyi sgo nas
NK064(ngu)001:3728: gzhal bya'i chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:3729: dag pa'i stong nyid bdag med pa'i don gtan la
NK064(ngu)001:3730: phebs pa'o // phyed phyi mar yang dag rtogs pas sogs rkang pa drug bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3731: stong nyid bdag med pa'i don ye nas mkhyen pa
NK064(ngu)001:3732: so so rang gis rig pa'i ye shes thugs su
NK064(ngu)001:3733: chud pa na chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3734: cho 'phrul du gzigs shing ston pa dang bstan pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3735: 'pho 'gyur yang 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:3737: rkang pa drug bar theg pa'i khyad par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3739: rang bzhin brjod med du bstan pa'i don gsum bsdu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3740: dmigs bya gzung ba'i yul dang dmigs byed 'dzin sems
NK064(ngu)001:3741: kyi rtog pa gnyis ngang gis med par dran snang
NK064(ngu)001:3742: ye shes su dbang sgyur ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3743: ye shes nyid la nyid 'dod dgur spyod pas bzhis
NK064(ngu)001:3744: nges par byung ba'i 'bras bu theg pa 'dir bstan
NK064(ngu)001:3745: pa dang / 'di las bstan pa thams cad 'phros shing thams cad 'dis 'grel pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3746: dbab bya'i yul dang 'bebs byed kyi theg pa thams cad brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3747: de rnams ni bsdu ba'i stod du le'u'i smad bsdu ba zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3748: de nas rkang pa bdun pa dang brgyad pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:3749: bsdu ba'i smad du le'u'i stod bstan pa 'byung ba
NK064(ngu)001:3751: gnas lugs rtogs pas chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur
NK064(ngu)001:3752: ba'i 'bras bu mngon du byas pas yon tan lhun
NK064(ngu)001:3753: gyis grub pa la ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa gleng
NK064(ngu)001:3755: sku bsod nams chen po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3757: yon tan nyid mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul du shar nas don mdzad pa thugs mngon sum pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3758: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3759: ji ltar spro ba'i mdzad pa 'dul ba bzhis gang
NK064(ngu)001:3760: du 'dul ba'i zhing khams mtha' yas par snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:3761: de thams cad kyang sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:3762: rang snang ba las gzhan logs na rang mtshan du
NK064(ngu)001:3764: ye shes de nyid gdul bya'i snang ba la de ltar snang ba yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:3766: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes zhing khams dang //
NK064(ngu)001:3767: ye shes yon tan phrin las ji snyed pa //
NK064(ngu)001:3768: ye shes de nyid de ltar snang ba yin //
NK064(ngu)001:3769: gzhan nas ma yin de ltar lhun gyis grub //
NK064(ngu)001:3773: de ltar chos thams cad snang ba gnyis las ma
NK064(ngu)001:3774: 'das so zhes rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag
NK064(ngu)001:3777: zhes brjod pas thub pa sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:3778: de skad ces brjod pas ston pa'i thugs rje las
NK064(ngu)001:3779: thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa spros
NK064(ngu)001:3780: nas 'dul ba'i dbang gis chos kyi sgo du ma
NK064(ngu)001:3781: bstan pa dang / gdod nas grub pa'i de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:3782: gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs pa dang brda la
NK064(ngu)001:3783: sogs pa'i sgo nas gsungs pa yang chos thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3784: sems dang ye shes rang snang bar bstan pa de
NK064(ngu)001:3785: dag tsam du 'dus par ston pa de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:3786: pa rigs drug pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK064(ngu)001:3789: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod
NK064(ngu)001:3790: pa las 'dis 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems
NK064(ngu)001:3791: dang ye shes nyid de ltar snang ba tsam dang
NK064(ngu)001:3792: / de thams cad kyang mthar rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK064(ngu)001:3793: par dag pa'i chos nyid du gtan la phab nas
NK064(ngu)001:3794: bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3796: // le'u bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3797: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3801: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad nas rdo rje las phyung ngo zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3802: chos thams cad gtan la phab pa de'ang mtshon byed yi ge la brten nas 'bebs dgos pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:3803: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:3804: thams cad dgongs pa tha dad med de gcig tu
NK064(ngu)001:3805: gyur nas srid zhi mnyam pa chen po'i tshul du
NK064(ngu)001:3806: dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i dbyings su 'khor 'das
NK064(ngu)001:3807: kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye nas rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:3808: dag pas sangs rgyas par gyur pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:3809: las dgongs pa gzhan du mi g.yo bar bzhugs pas
NK064(ngu)001:3810: chos thams cad ngo bo med pa ming tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:3811: gnas pa'i don mtshon par byed pa yi ge phreng
NK064(ngu)001:3812: ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba 'di ston pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3813: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3819: yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul /
NK064(ngu)001:3821: lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:3825: ka kha nas o oo zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:3827: dbyings las a byung a las ni //
NK064(ngu)001:3828: yi ge'i tshogs rnams ma lus 'phro //
NK064(ngu)001:3829: zhes pas yi ge 'khor lo'i 'phro gazhi'am rtsa ba a yig ni khong nas rang byung ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3831: sku gsung thugs kyi klong nas a byung ste //
NK064(ngu)001:3832: a ni khong nas 'byung ba skye ba med //
NK064(ngu)001:3834: yi ge gzhan rnams sngon byung ston pa'i thugs rje
NK064(ngu)001:3835: rang snang ba'i tshe 'phro ba'i gnas ni a'i 'od
NK064(ngu)001:3836: zer sku'i gnas so sor 'khyil ba de dang de
NK064(ngu)001:3839: a las 'od zer mgur gyi bum par 'khyil //
NK064(ngu)001:3840: 'od 'phros ka la sogs pa 'bru lnga shar //
NK064(ngu)001:3842: mgur gyi gnas las ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK064(ngu)001:3843: de bzhin du ljags las tsa sde /
NK064(ngu)001:3844: ljags kyi rtse mo las ta sde dang ta sde gnyis /
NK064(ngu)001:3846: sku'i cha nyi shu las ya sogs bcu bdun dang khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum rnams 'thon to //
NK064(ngu)001:3847: de la sku'i cha nyi shu ni 'grel chung gi bzhed pa ltar sdoms su byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:3848: byin pa sta zur dku skabs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:3849: dpung las ya ra wa la byung //
NK064(ngu)001:3850: phyag mthil thugs ka mdzod spu dang //
NK064(ngu)001:3851: zhabs mthil gsang gnas las rim bzhin //
NK064(ngu)001:3852: sha sha sa ha k+sha rnams 'phros //
NK064(ngu)001:3853: spyan snyan tshems shangs rnam bzhi las //
NK064(ngu)001:3856: spyi gtsug lte ba mtshog ma yi //
NK064(ngu)001:3857: gnas las mgo shad tig gsum 'thon //
NK064(ngu)001:3859: rjes 'jug lam pa'i sems nyid rang snang ba'i yi ge 'byung ba'i gnas ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3861: khog pa mgrin pa rkan dang lce //
NK064(ngu)001:3862: sna dang spyi bo so dang mchu //
NK064(ngu)001:3863: zhes pas a ku ha rnams mgrin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:3864: i tsu ya sha e rnams rkan /
NK064(ngu)001:3865: ri tu ra sha spyi bo /
NK064(ngu)001:3868: rjes su nga ro sna ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3869: mgrin pa rkan spyi bo so bzhi'i byed pa ni rim bzhin lce'i rtsa ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3872: rtse mo rnams rkan dang 'phrad pa las so //
NK064(ngu)001:3875: am ahrnamasa ma byung ba ni lha dang sbyor ba'i dbang gis bsdus pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3878: ri li bzhi ra dang la /
NK064(ngu)001:3879: am ni o yig la sbyar nas /
NK064(ngu)001:3880: zhes bsdus par rje rong zom bzhed /
NK064(ngu)001:3881: thar lo'i phyi 'gyur las ni yi ge lnga bcu tshang bar byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:3882: 'og tu so so'i don 'chad pa'i dus su'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:3883: +aa ni thog mtha' stong pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:3884: am ni nyer skyes dag pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:3885: ahni zas sogs dag pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:3886: ri ni dngos dang dngos med stong //
NK064(ngu)001:3887: r+ai ni srid dang srid med stong //
NK064(ngu)001:3888: li ni shes dang shes bya stong //
NK064(ngu)001:3889: l+ai ni stong dang snying rje'i bdag /
NK064(ngu)001:3891: sngar gyi dpe phal che bar /
NK064(ngu)001:3892: ni thams cad zhig pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:3893: zhes rong t+ai ka gi bsdus bshad ltar oo la du 'don na'ang rgya dper /
NK064(ngu)001:3894: oo sarba b+ai n+aa shi t+aa /
NK064(ngu)001:3895: zhes snang bas oo nyid du bton pa legs so //
NK064(ngu)001:3897: 'di dag phyung bas shes sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:3898: yi ge 'di dag phyung ba tsam gyi mthus 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:3899: rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3900: shar nub dang mtha' dbus sogs phan tshun mtho dam'i
NK064(ngu)001:3903: ches cher kun tu g.yos pas dngos po'i 'khrul pa
NK064(ngu)001:3904: zhig nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ming du
NK064(ngu)001:3905: btags pa las don gyi ngo bo ma grub pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:3906: mtshan nyid tsam du gyur pa la mnyes pas hohzhesa
NK064(ngu)001:3907: bya'o // de ltar yang spyi mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:3908: gang skye ba med pa mtshon par byed pa'i yi
NK064(ngu)001:3909: ge la ni a zhes bla dwags su btags so
NK064(ngu)001:3910: // bya ba mtshon par byed pa'i yi ge la ni ka zhes bla dwags su btags so //
NK064(ngu)001:3911: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:3912: gsum pa lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3914: yi ge gzhan la sbyang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:3915: de ye shes kyi rgyur bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3918: rab tu brtan gyur sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3919: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:3920: a yig dkar po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang
NK064(ngu)001:3926: cir yang bsgyur du rung ba ste rab tu brtan
NK064(ngu)001:3927: par gyur pa'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa'i a dkar
NK064(ngu)001:3931: lhang nge ba ste gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa la rtse gcig tu blo gnas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3932: spyod yul gyi snang zhen sbyong phyir de las shin
NK064(ngu)001:3933: tu phra ba'i a grangs med pa rnams spro bar
NK064(ngu)001:3934: bya'o // de ltar spros pas phyogs bcu thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:3935: as gang bar snang ba ting nge 'dzin gyi yul
NK064(ngu)001:3936: du gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3937: de nas 'phro gzhi'i a de la bsdus kyang gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:3938: dang mkha' khyab kyi a'i rang bzhin la 'phel ba'am
NK064(ngu)001:3940: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par gsal zhing brtan pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:3942: de las sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3943: a yig de las ming gi gzhi dang nga ro
NK064(ngu)001:3944: rnams gsal bar byed pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:3945: gnyis kyi tshogs kha dog gsal zhing 'od 'bar ba
NK064(ngu)001:3946: phyogs kun khyab par spro zhing bsdu ba'i tshul gyis
NK064(ngu)001:3947: sbyong ba'ang sngar a la ji ltar sbyangs pa de
NK064(ngu)001:3949: 'di ni sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:3950: de ltar yi ge la sems sbyong ba'i thabs 'di
NK064(ngu)001:3951: la 'bad pas ni rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:3952: thams cad kyi rgyu ting nge 'dzin brtan pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3953: 'byung ste / des 'bras bu ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyu byed pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:3954: bzhi pa yi ge'i don bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3960: yi ge la sems sbyang ba bstan pa'i rjes de
NK064(ngu)001:3961: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3962: ston pas yi ge'i don bshad kyi ched du brjod
NK064(ngu)001:3965: yi ge spyi'i don bshad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3966: bye brag bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i don bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3973: yi ge sku gsum gyi bdag nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:3974: de dag gi rdo rje gsum mtshon byed du bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:3976: dmigs med chos skur bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3977: a ni stong dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3978: yi ge a ni stong pa dang mi stong pa gnyis kyi mtha' dang bral bar ma zad /
NK064(ngu)001:3979: zung 'jug dbu ma tsam du'ang dmigs su yod pa
NK064(ngu)001:3980: ma yin pas spros pa thams cad dang bral ba
NK064(ngu)001:3982: snang dang mi snang la sogs pa //
NK064(ngu)001:3983: gnyis su rtog pa thams cad mtha' //
NK064(ngu)001:3984: kun mkhyen rnams ni dbus la'ang min //
NK064(ngu)001:3986: de ltar gtan la phebs pas chos thams cad ming
NK064(ngu)001:3987: du btags pa tsam las don bsam brjod kyi yul
NK064(ngu)001:3988: las 'das pa ni sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:3990: de'i rang gdangs yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo nyid
NK064(ngu)001:3991: kyang chos sku'i ngang la gnas pa las gzhan du
NK064(ngu)001:3992: ma g.yos so // gnyis pa dbang sgyur longs skur bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:3993: a nyid sna tshogs sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:3994: yi ge thams cad kyi 'byung khungs a nyid kyis
NK064(ngu)001:3995: go phye bas sna tshogs bar snang ba'i tshul ni
NK064(ngu)001:3996: dag gi 'du byed kyi dbang las ka la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:3997: pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba'ang sgra'i nga
NK064(ngu)001:3998: ro dbyangs dang ming gzhi gsal byed kyi yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:3999: ji snyed pa thams cad 'dir de snyed du bsdus
NK064(ngu)001:4000: pa ste / de'ang sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:4001: su mngon par rdzogs par mnga' mdzad pa'i rgyal po
NK064(ngu)001:4002: de kho na nyid longs sku'i ngo bor nges pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:4003: pa ste / // gsum pa rol pa sna tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:4004: par snang ba sprul skur bstan pa la gsum las
NK064(ngu)001:4005: pa ste / // / dang po sprul sku'i gsung du bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4006: e ma ho ngo mtshar sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4007: e ma ho zhes yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:4008: ni shin tu ngo mtshar zhing ches ya mtshan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4010: cho 'phrul chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga'
NK064(ngu)001:4011: ba'i yi ge zhe gnyis kyi steng du khyab byed
NK064(ngu)001:4012: kyi yi ge gsum bsnan pas bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:4014: don gyi ngo bo tsam ston pa ming dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4015: don gyi khyad par ston pa'i tshig rnams byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4016: de 'dus pa las ngag gi rnam pa ma lus pa 'dzin pa'i gnas su gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:4017: gang 'dul sprul sku'i gsung rgya che ba theg pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4018: zab pa brjod bya'i don chen po gdul bya'i snang ngor smra zhing gzhan la ston pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4019: gnyis pa sprul sku'i thugs su bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4020: dngos med sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4021: yi ger snang dus nyid nas bden pa'i dngos po med de /
NK064(ngu)001:4022: ci'i phyir na yi ge'i rang bzhin sems nyid yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:4023: sems kyi rang bzhin ji lta ba bzhin du yi
NK064(ngu)001:4024: ge'i rang bzhin yang bdag gnyis med cing spros pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4025: mtha' thams cad dang bral bas blo'i yul du cir
NK064(ngu)001:4026: yang mi dmigs pa ni thugs kyi gsang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4027: gsum pa sprul sku'i skur bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4028: dbyibs dang sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4029: yi ge'i rang bzhin dmigs pa med kyang rol pa ma 'gags pa tsam du /
NK064(ngu)001:4031: a seng ge glal ba lta bu zhes sogs gsungs
NK064(ngu)001:4032: pa ltar brdar btags pa yi ge'i gzugs dbyibs dang
NK064(ngu)001:4033: / de dag gi kha dog kyang tha dad pa
NK064(ngu)001:4034: la brten nas ngo bo ming tshig sna tshogs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4035: rnam par 'phrul pa'i sprin las lha bskyed pa'i sa
NK064(ngu)001:4036: / bon dang / glegs bam gyi snang brnyan sogs
NK064(ngu)001:4037: thugs rje'i rol pa cir yang snang bas sprul sku'i
NK064(ngu)001:4038: mdzad pa sgrub cing ston pa'i phrin las can no
NK064(ngu)001:4039: / bon dang / // gnyis pa de dag gi rdo rje gsum mtshon byed du bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4040: phyogs bcu dus bzhir sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4041: phyogs bcu dus bzhir 'gro don la gshegs shing bzhugs
NK064(ngu)001:4042: pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyang ye shes sems dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:4043: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhe gnyis su 'dus pa
NK064(ngu)001:4044: khyab byar byas pa'i de re re la khyab byed
NK064(ngu)001:4045: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:4046: zhe gnyis khyab byed gsum dang bcas te bzhi bcu
NK064(ngu)001:4047: rtsa lnga'i bdag nyid du 'dus shing de dag kyang
NK064(ngu)001:4048: yi ge mgo shad tig ste khyab byed gsum dang
NK064(ngu)001:4049: / ka nas k+sha'i bar gsal byed so bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:4050: i dang oo'i bar dbyangs brgyad dril bas khyab bya'i yi ge zhe gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4051: mdor na a'i cho 'phrul yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:4052: lnga la 'dus shing rdzogs pa'i chos sku'i rol pa
NK064(ngu)001:4053: gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4054: rtsa ba mtshon par byed pa ni yi ge'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4055: gnyis pa yi ge'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4056: sems kyi sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4057: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba nyid yi ger rang snang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4058: de las gzhan du yi ge zhes dngos por grub pa cung zad kyang yod pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4060: rab 'byor yi ge ni don dam par ma skyes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4062: a'i ngo bo nyid gang yin pa de ni sems kyi rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:4063: dngos po dang dngos po med pa thams cad las yang dag par 'dus pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4066: dmigs med de nyid sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4067: cir yang dmigs med kyi yi ge de nyid kyang
NK064(ngu)001:4068: rol pa sna tshogs par rang snang ba'i yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:4069: sku gsung thugs dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chen por
NK064(ngu)001:4071: des ye nas sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub
NK064(ngu)001:4072: pa ni ngo mtshar gyi gnas ya mtshan zhing cho
NK064(ngu)001:4073: 'phrul chen por snang ba'i dngos grub nyid rang rig
NK064(ngu)001:4074: pa'i mngon sum du rab tu 'gugs shing 'dren par
NK064(ngu)001:4077: dbyings la sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4078: yul chos kyi dbyings la yul can mtshan med shes
NK064(ngu)001:4079: rab kyi dbyings kyis bya rtsol med pa'i bris pa
NK064(ngu)001:4080: ste / de'i phyir ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4081: yi ge'i sprin 'gyur ba med cing rnam pa brjod
NK064(ngu)001:4082: bya thams cad gsal ba'i nus pa dang ldan pas
NK064(ngu)001:4083: yi ge zhes pa'i ming ni tha snyad tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:4084: ste / brjod pa ste / yi ge'i skad dod
NK064(ngu)001:4085: ak+sha ra'i sgra las drangs na mi 'gyur ba dang
NK064(ngu)001:4086: ste / brjod pa ste / / byany+dza na gsal byed /
NK064(ngu)001:4087: war+na nus pa dang ldan par 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4088: gnyis pa bye brag gi don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4090: khyab bya zhe gnyis kyi don bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4092: mgo ni sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4093: mtshon byed yi ge mgo ni ber ka ris te /
NK064(ngu)001:4094: mtshon bya'i don zung 'jug ma nor ba gnyis med ye shes kyi rang bzhin thugs rdo rje mtshon /
NK064(ngu)001:4095: byed las ni yi ge thams cad kyi 'go 'dren
NK064(ngu)001:4096: cing 'jug pa'i sgor gyur pas lam dang 'dra ba
NK064(ngu)001:4097: yin te / dpal byin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK064(ngu)001:4098: mgo ni thog mar mtshon pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:4099: dang la gzugs su gang gsal ba //
NK064(ngu)001:4100: de ni yi ge'i mgo yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:4101: ber ka ris la mgo zhes bya //
NK064(ngu)001:4103: yi ge tig ni tsheg ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4104: don shes rab brjod med kyi rang bzhin gsung rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:4105: byed las yi ge rnams 'dus pa dbyangs kyis bcings
NK064(ngu)001:4106: pas dngos po so so'i ming du grub pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:4108: yo ga rgyan dam pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:4109: sdud pa'i phyir na tsheg ni tig /
NK064(ngu)001:4110: 'thor ba bsdus nas ming du smra //
NK064(ngu)001:4112: 'dir kha cig rgya gar gyi dpe la tsheg med pas bod ma'o zer ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4114: gug bkyed klad kor tsheg rnams ma nyams par //
NK064(ngu)001:4115: zhes pa ma mthong bar zad do //
NK064(ngu)001:4116: yi ge shad ni don thabs snying rje chen pos 'dul ba'i rang bzhin sku rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:4117: byed las rkang pa sdebs nas tshigs su gcod par byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4119: gcod pa mtshon par byed pa'i yi ge la ni ming dbyug pa zhes bla dwags su btags so //
NK064(ngu)001:4122: dang po bzang mo dang rigs lnga yab yum gyi yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4123: a ni skye med sogs rkang pas dman pa'i tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4124: yi ge a ni chos thams cad skye med de
NK064(ngu)001:4125: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings bya ba mo kun tu bzang
NK064(ngu)001:4126: mo ste / yum bar ma las /
NK064(ngu)001:4127: a zhes bya ba ni gdod ma nas ma skyes pa'i phyir chos thams cad kyi sgo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4130: a ni stong pa ye nas stong //
NK064(ngu)001:4131: stong pa nyid na stong pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:4132: yi ge kun gyi gazhi'am rgyu //
NK064(ngu)001:4133: yin pa'i phyir na mgo bor bzhag /
NK064(ngu)001:4134: ces yi ge kun gyi 'byung khungs yin pas thog mar smos so //
NK064(ngu)001:4135: tha yig ni sgyu ma lta bu'i rnam shes chos
NK064(ngu)001:4136: dbyings ye shes su dag pa'i phyag rgyar 'phrul pa
NK064(ngu)001:4137: rdo rje mi bskyod pa nyid de /
NK064(ngu)001:4138: 'dir yab lnga la sgyu 'phrul gyi sgras ston pa'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:4139: phung po lnga sgyu ma'i snang ba ltar med pa gsal snang tsam du 'char ba ma 'gags kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:4140: 'char gzhi gnyug ma rang rig pa'i ye shes su
NK064(ngu)001:4141: rnam par dag pa ni ye shes lnga yin la
NK064(ngu)001:4142: / de nyid thabs kyi phyag rgyar 'phrul pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa yab lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4144: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes la //
NK064(ngu)001:4145: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK064(ngu)001:4147: de ltar spyi'i mtshan sgyu 'phrul 'grel ba las so so'i khyad chos la /
NK064(ngu)001:4148: ta ni me long ye shes kyi phyag rgyar snang ba'i lha rnam snang /
NK064(ngu)001:4149: da ni mnyam nyid ye shes kyis re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i phyag rgya rin 'byung /
NK064(ngu)001:4150: d+ha ni chos kun so sor ma 'dres pa'i gzigs
NK064(ngu)001:4151: pa rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK064(ngu)001:4152: snang mtha' / na ni gdul bya'i don kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:4153: mthar phyin par mdzad pa'i ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK064(ngu)001:4155: tha ni d+r+wa bas te yum rnams dbyings kyi phyag
NK064(ngu)001:4156: rgya yin pas chos can thams cad dang 'brel zhing
NK064(ngu)001:4157: / rnam pa'ang yab dang phan tshun thabs shes zung
NK064(ngu)001:4158: 'brel du bzhugs pas sam yum gyi mkha' d+r+wa ba
NK064(ngu)001:4159: dang chos mthun pas kyang d+r+wa ba zhes pa'i sgras
NK064(ngu)001:4160: / bstan no // so so'i khyad par ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4161: tha ni chos nyid kyi mkha' la chos can thams
NK064(ngu)001:4162: cad mngon par rdzogs pa'i phyag rgya dbyings phyug ma
NK064(ngu)001:4163: nyid do // ta ni sra brtan sa'i khams yon tan gyi rten du gyur pa spyan ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4164: da ni lhag mthong gi me lham mer gsal ba gos dkar /
NK064(ngu)001:4165: d+ha ni mnyen cing 'khril ba chus yon tan sdud pa m+aa ma k+ai /
NK064(ngu)001:4166: na ni kun tu g.yo zhing 'gyur bas gdul bya sgrol ba dam tshig sgrol ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4167: gnyis pa nang sems bzhi shar sgo'i khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4168: ka ni spyan gyi sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4169: yul so sor rig pa sgo lnga'i rnam shes la 'dir thugs kyi sgras bstan te /
NK064(ngu)001:4170: ka ni spyan gyi rnam shes dag pas thugs kyi mchog sa snying /
NK064(ngu)001:4171: kha ni snyan gyi rnam shes dag pa phyag rdor /
NK064(ngu)001:4172: ga ni shangs kyi rnam shes dag pa nam snying /
NK064(ngu)001:4173: g+ha ni ljags kyi rnam shes dag pa spyan ras gzigs /
NK064(ngu)001:4174: nga ni lus shes kyi mthar thug gsang ba'i rnam
NK064(ngu)001:4175: shes kyis bde ba myong dus mig shes la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:4176: pa'i rtog pa 'gag pas thugs kyang 'jig par byed
NK064(ngu)001:4178: gsum pa nang gi sems ma bzhi lho sgo'i khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4179: tsa ni spyan gyi sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4180: sgo lnga'i rnam shes skye ba'i rten byed pas na yul lnga la sku'i sgras bstan te /
NK064(ngu)001:4181: tsa ni spyan gyi yul gzugs rnam par dag pas sku'i mchog sgeg mo /
NK064(ngu)001:4182: tsha ni snyan gyi yul sgra dag pa glu ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4183: dza ni shangs kyi yul dri dag pa phreng ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4184: dz+ha ni ljags kyi yul ro dag pa gar ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4185: nya ni yul reg bya'i mthar thug gsang ba'i pad+ma
NK064(ngu)001:4186: dang 'phrad pa'i dus yul gzhan gyi rtog pa 'gag
NK064(ngu)001:4187: pas sku yang 'jig par byed pa stobs chen no
NK064(ngu)001:4188: // bzhi pa phyi sems bzhi nub sgo'i khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4189: pa ni spyan gyi sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4190: yul dang shes pa gnyis phyi nang du brda sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:4191: byed pas na dbang po lnga la gsung gi sgras
NK064(ngu)001:4192: bstan te / pa ni spyan gyi dag pas gsung gi mchog byams pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4193: pha ni snyan gyi dbang po dag pa sgrib sel /
NK064(ngu)001:4194: ba ni shangs kyi dbang po dag pa kun bzang /
NK064(ngu)001:4195: b+ha ni ljags kyi dbang po dag pa 'jam dpal /
NK064(ngu)001:4196: ma ni reg byed lus dbang gi mthar thug gsang
NK064(ngu)001:4197: ba'i dbang pos yul bzhir 'dzin pa'ang mi gnas pas
NK064(ngu)001:4198: gsung yang 'jig par byed pa rta mgrin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4199: lnga pa phyi'i sems ma bzhi sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4200: ya ni skye ba sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4201: ya ni da ltar ba skye ba'i go 'byed byed 'das pa'i dus rnam par dag pa spos ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4202: wa ni gnas bzhin pa da ltar ba'i dus dag pa me tog ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4203: ra ni da ltar ba 'di 'jig pa ma 'ongs pa'i dus dag pa ste mar me ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4204: la ni dus gsum gang du'ang tha snyad gdags rung
NK064(ngu)001:4205: gis stong pa ma nges pa'i dus dag pa dri
NK064(ngu)001:4206: chab ma'o // sha ni chos la rtag pa med par 'dzin pa dag pa ste lcags kyu ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4207: sha ni chad par 'dzin pa'ang yod pa ma yin pa ste zhags pa ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4208: sa ni bdag gnyis su 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang bral bas bdag med pa ste lcags sgrog ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4209: ha ni mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid du 'dzin pa'ang dag pa dril bu ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4210: drug pa kun bzang thub drug dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4211: k+sha ni ye shes sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:4212: k+sha ni rnam shes ye shes su dag pa thugs
NK064(ngu)001:4213: kyi bdag nyid rang byung ye shes kyi thugs rigs
NK064(ngu)001:4214: drug pa kun tu bzang po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4215: 'dir thugs kyi sgra zlos te bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4216: yid kyi rnam shes kyis rang yul chos dang sgo
NK064(ngu)001:4217: lnga'i yul gnyis ka gcod par byed pa'i phyir ro
NK064(ngu)001:4218: // i ni rgya mtsho chen po'i rdul phra rab
NK064(ngu)001:4219: ji snyed pa de snyed kyi lha rnams kyi gnas
NK064(ngu)001:4220: su 'dul byed rigs mthun gyi gzugs su snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:4221: lha'i thub pa brgya byin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4222: +ai ni rdul snyed lha min gyi thub pa thag bzang ris /
NK064(ngu)001:4223: u ni rdul snyed mi rnams kyi gnas su sh+aaka thub /
NK064(ngu)001:4224: +au ni rdul snyed byol song rnams kyi thub pa seng ge rab brtan /
NK064(ngu)001:4225: e ni rdul snyed yi dwags rnams kyi gnas su kha 'bar de ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4226: ee ni rdul snyed dmyal ba'i thub pa chos kyi rgyal po rnams su bstan nas 'dul ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4227: yi ge drug po k+sha yig gi rjes su 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:4228: ba'ang byed pa po kun bzang gi thugs rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:4229: ye shes kyi byin rlabs las 'gro 'dul gyi sprul
NK064(ngu)001:4231: bdun pa byang sgo'i khro bo'i yi ge ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4232: o ni sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4233: o ni yul dbang shes gsum 'dus pa reg pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4234: mthar thug gsang ba'i khams gsum gyi rtog pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:4235: cad bde ba'i ngang du 'jig par byed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:4236: oo ni bde ba'ang stong par grol bas rtog pa
NK064(ngu)001:4237: thams cad mi gnas par zhig pa yin te rgyu
NK064(ngu)001:4238: 'bras ro gcig pas yi ge gnyis po de bdud
NK064(ngu)001:4240: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4241: yi ge nas a hoh'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:4242: de ltar na gsung yi ge 'khor lo'i tshogs chen
NK064(ngu)001:4243: 'di rnams kyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK064(ngu)001:4244: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i phreng ba
NK064(ngu)001:4245: rnams ma lus par bsdus pa'o zhes ched du brjod
NK064(ngu)001:4246: do // de ltar gsung yi ge'i 'khor lo gtan
NK064(ngu)001:4247: la phab pa la dgyes pas a hohzhesa ngo mtshar
NK064(ngu)001:4248: do // bar bstan pa'o // gnyis pa bsdus te bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4249: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4255: rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:4256: yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:4257: pa'i rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4258: don rtogs dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4259: sku sogs rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:4260: las phyung ngo // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4261: a hoh thabs dang nas a hoh'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:4262: a skye ba med pa shes rab dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4263: hohdagyesa pa thabs te zung 'jug yi ge'i 'khor lo la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4264: de yang thabs snang ba dang shes rab stong pa nyid dbyer med spros bral gyi ye shes te /
NK064(ngu)001:4265: der yi ge dmigs med chos skur bstan pa'i tshigs bcad gcig bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4266: sems nyid snang stong gnyis med du sbyor ba'i dgyes
NK064(ngu)001:4267: rol las spyod yul thams cad a'i sprin chen por
NK064(ngu)001:4269: a yig la sems sbyang ba bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4270: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin a las yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:4271: zhe gnyis kyi tshogs kyang spro zhing bsdu ba ste
NK064(ngu)001:4272: / yi ge gzhan la sems sbyang ba bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4273: ston pa'i thugs rje dang lam pas yi ge la
NK064(ngu)001:4274: sems sbyong ba'i thabs ni yi ge 'khor lo dang
NK064(ngu)001:4275: 'bras bu ye shes kyi rgyur nges pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4277: yi ge'i don bshad gnyis kyi gsungs pa lo rgyus dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4278: 'di ni sogs ye shes kyi rgyur bstan pa rnams bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4279: gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo yi ge'i
NK064(ngu)001:4280: sprin ni ston pa'i thugs rje las rang snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:4281: ste / a ka kha sogs yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4282: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum gyi phyag
NK064(ngu)001:4283: rgya rmad du byung ba'i 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:4284: bcu rtsa gnyis su smin pas don gnyis grub pa
NK064(ngu)001:4285: ste / de dag gi rdo rje gsum mtshon byed du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4286: 'go ni ma nor sogs bye brag yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i don bshad pa bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4287: yi ge'i sgo nas zab pa dang rgya che ba'i don ston pa la ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4288: yi ge sprul sku'i gsung du bstan pa bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4289: chos thams cad ming gi tshogs pa tsam las ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4290: yi ge 'byung ba'i mthu bshad pa bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4291: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni rgyal ba zhe
NK064(ngu)001:4292: gnyis kyi rang bzhin du mngon par grub pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:4293: / yi ge dbang sgyur longs skur bstan pa bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4294: yi ge de dag kyang rgyu rkyen gyis gsar du
NK064(ngu)001:4295: 'du ma byas pa sems kyi chos nyid dmigs pa
NK064(ngu)001:4297: yi ge sprul sku'i thugs su bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4299: yi ge'i nges tshig rnams bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4300: de lta na'ang lam pa'i ngor yi ge de dag
NK064(ngu)001:4301: 'dus byas pa ltar dbyibs kha dog sogs kyi rol
NK064(ngu)001:4302: pa ma 'gags pa snang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4303: yi ge'i sprul sku'i skur bstan pa bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4304: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum dbyer mi
NK064(ngu)001:4305: phyed pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa gsung yi ge'i
NK064(ngu)001:4306: 'khor los mngon du 'byin pa las mi 'da' ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:4307: dam tshig ste / yi ge 'khor lo sogs mjug bsdu'i rkang pa gnyis bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4308: de ltar rdo rje gsum gyi dkyil 'khor snang bar
NK064(ngu)001:4309: mdzad pa'i dam tshig las 'da' bar mi mdzad pas
NK064(ngu)001:4310: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyis bsdus pa'i dngos
NK064(ngu)001:4311: grub mi 'grub pa'i dbang med de /
NK064(ngu)001:4312: 'grub byed kyi rgyu lta ba dang rkyen bsgom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4313: ting nge 'dzin tshogs pa'i mthu chen po las 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:4314: bu mngon du thob pa chos nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:4315: te / dmigs med de nyid sogs yi ge'i byed las bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4316: de ltar bsdus pa la a hohzhesa ngo mtshar bas mnyes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4317: gzhan yang thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo gnyis dang sbyar nas 'chad pa'i bka' srol kyang yod de /
NK064(ngu)001:4318: spro zhing nus na 'chad pa pos bsnyad par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4321: yi ge 'khor lo bkod pa'i don rnams rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:4322: 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:4325: chos thams cad ming tsam du gnas pa'i yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:4326: phreng ba'i 'khor lo'i don thams cad de tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:4327: 'dus so zhes ched du brjod pas gzhi 'bras kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4328: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:4329: phreng ba'i 'khor lo dang rang bzhin gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:4330: par gyur to // gsum pa le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4332: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod
NK064(ngu)001:4333: pa las 'dis chos thams cad ming tsam las don
NK064(ngu)001:4334: la ma grub pa mtshon byed yi ge phreng ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:4335: 'khor lo ston pa'i thugs rje dang gdul bya'i sems
NK064(ngu)001:4336: nyid las rang snang bar bkod cing bstan pa'i le'u
NK064(ngu)001:4338: le'u lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4339: gsung pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4343: de nas yi ge sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:4344: gsung yi ge'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas bshad
NK064(ngu)001:4345: ma thag gi yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin bkod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4346: mthu las thabs shes zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul lha'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:4347: 'khor dang / las dang dngos grub sgrub pa'i rim
NK064(ngu)001:4348: pa rnam par 'phro ba 'di ched du brjod do
NK064(ngu)001:4349: 'khor dang / // gnyis pa gzhung dngos la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4350: gang gis sgrub pa rten gyi gang zag /
NK064(ngu)001:4351: rtogs goms kyi thabs kyis ji ltar 'grub tshul /
NK064(ngu)001:4352: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:4354: ston pa mchod brtson sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4355: thar lam ston pa po bla ma rdo rje slob
NK064(ngu)001:4356: dpon mchod pa la brtson zhing phan nus zab mo'i
NK064(ngu)001:4357: dbang gsum thob pas rgyud smin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4358: lta ba lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi gnas lugs rtogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4359: rtogs don sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4360: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams ma nyams pas rnam par dag pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4361: rgyu rkyen las kyi sngags gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4362: dam tshig las chos rgya bzhi'i phyag rgya rnams legs par shes shing /
NK064(ngu)001:4364: dam tshig lta ba ting 'dzin dang //
NK064(ngu)001:4365: byang chub sems dang snying rje ste //
NK064(ngu)001:4366: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs bya //
NK064(ngu)001:4367: zhes pa ltar lam dus kyi yo byad lnga'am //
NK064(ngu)001:4368: yang na bza' dang btung ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4372: +aa li k+ai li ste sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo
NK064(ngu)001:4373: byad lnga dang ldan pas bsgrubs na 'grub par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4374: la / chos de dag dang mi ldan pas ni bsgrubs kyang don med par ma zad /
NK064(ngu)001:4375: sgrub pa po rang nyid brlag par 'gyur ro zhes /
NK064(ngu)001:4376: khe nyen dang bcas te bstan no //
NK064(ngu)001:4378: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4380: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:4382: rtogs pa'i thabs la gdams pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4383: rtogs bya lta ba'i ngo bo bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4385: gang gis dmigs med sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4386: gang zag gang gis sems nyid gang du'ang dmigs su
NK064(ngu)001:4387: med pa'i don mi shes pa de yis chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4388: dbyings rnam par dag pa mtha' bral gyi gnas lugs
NK064(ngu)001:4390: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir phyi nang gi grub mtha' dngos por lta ba rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4391: dngos po med par 'dzin pa de thams cad cir
NK064(ngu)001:4392: yang ma grub cing gang du'ang ma 'gags pa'i sems
NK064(ngu)001:4393: nyid mtha' bral gyi ngang der 'jig pa'i tshul rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:4394: pas chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin dmigs med bsam
NK064(ngu)001:4395: brjod dang bral ba'i don de nyid shes par gyis
NK064(ngu)001:4398: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:4399: brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid gnyug ma'i rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4400: 'di zhes cir yang gdags su med de /
NK064(ngu)001:4401: pho dang mo dang ma ning gsum yang min la /
NK064(ngu)001:4402: de las gzhan du mtshan med dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4405: rigs so so'i rgyud sogs gang yang ma yin zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4406: dkar dmar sogs kha dog dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4407: gru bzhi zlum po sogs dbyibs su grub pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4408: brten bya'i gnas dang rten byed kyi rdzas sogs dngos
NK064(ngu)001:4409: po dang dngos med kyi chos su grub pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:4410: yin te / mdor na gang yang yin par mi
NK064(ngu)001:4411: 'gyur bas mtha' cir yang grub pa min pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:4412: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings rnam par dag
NK064(ngu)001:4413: pa rang byung gi ye shes te /
NK064(ngu)001:4414: de nyid gzhi mngon du byed pa las mi 'da' ba thabs kyi phyag rgya lam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4415: rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor 'das su snang ba kun gyi gazhi'am rgyu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4417: sems kyi chos nyid las gzhan du gyur pa'i chos 'ga' yang med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4418: de yang le'u lnga pa 'di nyid brgyud pa'i bka'
NK064(ngu)001:4419: srol la mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas 'chad pas
NK064(ngu)001:4420: na / rtogs pa'i thabs dang rtogs bya'i ngo bo
NK064(ngu)001:4421: bshad pa'i gzhung tshan gnyis po 'di rgyu shes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4423: de yang man ngag lam rim dang sbyar na /
NK064(ngu)001:4425: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK064(ngu)001:4427: bar chad med sgrub rnam par smin //
NK064(ngu)001:4428: dbang sgyur phyag rgya lhun grub lam //
NK064(ngu)001:4429: mngon byas rim pa brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:4430: zhes pa ltar mtshan nyid gsum yang le'u dgur phye ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4431: dang por rtogs bya ye shes rang gnas gzhi'i le'u /
NK064(ngu)001:4432: gnyis par rang gnas mthong ba lta ba'i le'u /
NK064(ngu)001:4433: gsum pa nas drug pa'i bar le'u bzhis /
NK064(ngu)001:4436: phyag rgya gcig spros te tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:4437: bdun pa sbyor lam tshogs sgrub /
NK064(ngu)001:4438: brgyad pas lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:4439: dgu pas gzhi ji lta ba mngon byas mthar thug gi 'bras bu rnams bstan pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:4440: rtogs bya lta ba'i ngo bo 'di lam rim gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4441: gzhi ye shes rang gnas kyi le'u dang sbyar nas
NK064(ngu)001:4442: / rtogs pa'i thabs la gdams pa rang gnas mthong
NK064(ngu)001:4443: ba dang sbyar du rung bar rgyal ba g.yung bzhed
NK064(ngu)001:4444: / cing / sngar rten gyi gang zag bshad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4445: gzhung de le'u bdun pa bar chad med pa'i lam
NK064(ngu)001:4446: tshogs sgrub dang sbyor ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4447: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4448: ci'i phyir bsgom pa'i dgos ched /
NK064(ngu)001:4450: de nyid thams cad du rang snang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4451: de las dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4452: de nyid kar dag pas blang dor dang bral bar dpes bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4453: de la 'dris par bslabs pas 'bras bu la mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4455: dngos rnams sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4456: 'di ltar dngos po sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos
NK064(ngu)001:4457: rnams snang dus nyid na dngos por grub pa rdul
NK064(ngu)001:4458: tsam yang med par rtogs pa'i don la rang dbang
NK064(ngu)001:4459: sgyur ba'i thabs ni ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4461: gang gis glang chen sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4462: sgom pa po gang gis ma dul ba'i glang chen
NK064(ngu)001:4463: chang gis myos pa dang 'dra ba'i sems 'khrul rtog
NK064(ngu)001:4464: sna tshogs kyis myos pas las su mi rung ba
NK064(ngu)001:4465: 'di nyid / ji ltar glang rdzi mkhas pas lcags
NK064(ngu)001:4466: kyu la sogs pa'i thabs kyis glang po btul na
NK064(ngu)001:4467: 'di nyid / thub pa ltar / gdams ngag gam
NK064(ngu)001:4468: shes rab kyi stobs kyis mnyam par 'jog thabs gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:4469: po gang rung la brten nas rtogs don gnas lugs
NK064(ngu)001:4470: kyi ngang la yul med rang gsal du bzhag pas
NK064(ngu)001:4471: btul ba na dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4472: 'khrul rtog thams cad zhi nas gzhi ji lta ba
NK064(ngu)001:4473: bzhin klungs su phebs pa ni thul ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4474: de ltar dgos ched dang sgom thabs gnyis po 'di
NK064(ngu)001:4475: ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin stong pa chen
NK064(ngu)001:4477: lam rim le'u gsum pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4479: rtsa ba med pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4480: gzhi dang rtsa ba gang du'ang grub pa med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4481: sems kyi chos nyid ni cir yang ma 'gags pas
NK064(ngu)001:4482: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin
NK064(ngu)001:4484: rang gnas kyi ye shes ma rtogs pas sgyu ma
NK064(ngu)001:4485: lta bu'i 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can la dmigs
NK064(ngu)001:4486: med kyi snying rje chen po bsgom pa ni kun
NK064(ngu)001:4487: snang gi ting nge 'dzin snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal
NK064(ngu)001:4488: 'byor te / lam rim le'u bzhi pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4489: de ltar skye 'gag gnyis su med pa'i sems nyid
NK064(ngu)001:4490: thams cad du rang snang ba las 'dir yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:4491: a'i rang bzhin du bsgom ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4492: yi ge de las a phra mo dang ka la
NK064(ngu)001:4493: sogs pa'i 'phro 'du la sems sbyong ba ni ji
NK064(ngu)001:4494: ltar yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i char 'dod rgur 'bebs
NK064(ngu)001:4495: pa la rin chen gyi khams las grub pa'i sprin
NK064(ngu)001:4496: dgos pa bzhin du dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams
NK064(ngu)001:4497: cad spro ba'i rgyur yi ge la sems sbyong dgos
NK064(ngu)001:4498: te / rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin nam phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4500: thabs las sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4501: rtsa ba'i thabs rang rig yi ger snang ba las /
NK064(ngu)001:4502: rten gyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba gzhi'i thabs byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4503: der brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bkod de sgom pa ni thabs bsam yas pa zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4504: de dag ni rags pa lha sku la bslab pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4506: sngar gyi phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4507: 'chad 'gyur gyi de la 'dris par bslab pa gsum
NK064(ngu)001:4508: ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor yin pas lam
NK064(ngu)001:4509: rim le'u lnga pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4510: de ltar thabs gsum dang ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4511: 'khor lo thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4512: cho 'phrul du snang bas bzang ngan tha dad par
NK064(ngu)001:4514: rnam pa gtso bo las tha dad pa'i 'khor sogs
NK064(ngu)001:4515: nang brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor dang nang gi phyi
NK064(ngu)001:4517: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor zhi ba la tshom bu stong dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4519: khro bo la stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4520: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu /
NK064(ngu)001:4521: gnyis ka la bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:4522: sogs phyag rgya spros pa mkha' khyab bsam yas kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4523: dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa de thams cad kyang rang
NK064(ngu)001:4524: rig ye shes kyi rol par shar bas 'khor ba
NK064(ngu)001:4525: tshogs lam gyi g.yang sar 'jigs pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:4526: spyod yul yongs dag kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog des ma btab pa ci yang med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4528: de nyid ye shes sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4529: bshad ma thag gi thabs gsum po de nyid rang
NK064(ngu)001:4530: rig pa'i ye shes las rang snang ba'i phyir na
NK064(ngu)001:4531: yi ge dang ming tshig gis bsdus pa'i lha'i sa
NK064(ngu)001:4532: bon dang bskyed sngags las gzugs kyi cha shas yongs
NK064(ngu)001:4533: su rdzogs pa'i skur bsgom pa sogs yid la ji
NK064(ngu)001:4534: ltar 'dod pa bzhin ting nge 'dzin la 'dod rgur
NK064(ngu)001:4535: byar yod pa'i yon tan gyi dpe ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4536: mun nag la sgron me bteg pas snang ba byung
NK064(ngu)001:4537: ba ji lta ba de bzhin du rtog tshogs gar
NK064(ngu)001:4538: yang ma spangs par brten pa lha'i snang bar grol
NK064(ngu)001:4539: zhing / lcags yud tsam gyis gser du 'gyur ba
NK064(ngu)001:4540: gser 'gyur gyi rtsis thebs pa ltar 'byung lnga ma
NK064(ngu)001:4541: spangs par yum lnga'i rang bzhin rten gzhal yas khang
NK064(ngu)001:4542: gi snang bar grol ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4543: bcud len gyi rtsis dug sman gyi rang bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:4544: 'gyur ba'i tshul dang 'dra bar rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:4545: dam dug lnga ye shes lngar grol ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4546: de'ang rnam par grol ba tsam las ma dag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4547: chos rnams med snang yin pas dag pa'i ngo bor
NK064(ngu)001:4548: gsar du bsgyur dgos par ni mi bsam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:4550: sngags dang sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4551: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su sngags kyi yan
NK064(ngu)001:4552: lag lnga dang ldan pa'i lha sku phyag rgya chen
NK064(ngu)001:4553: po'i ting nge 'dzin la 'dris par bslabs pa'i rkyen
NK064(ngu)001:4554: gyis mi 'phrog pa'i gsal snang la rab tu brtan
