NK064(ngu)001:4555: cing goms pa na 'og nas 'byung ba'i dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:4556: ya mtshan chen po rnams thob par 'gyur ba yin
NK064(ngu)001:4557: no // gsum pa mngon 'gyur 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4561: lam thabs grol gnyis kyi dbang du phyi nang gi bshad tshul gnyis mdzad pa'i bka' srol snang na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:4562: 'dir re zhig phyi bshad grol lam ltar 'chad do //
NK064(ngu)001:4564: yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub drug /
NK064(ngu)001:4568: bdud rtsir sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4569: rgyud 'grel pa dang sgrub thabs kyis 'chad pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:4570: yi ge'i 'phro 'du la brten nas bsgrub ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4571: bsgyur gzhi zas dug can la yi ge a bkod
NK064(ngu)001:4572: de 'ju 'dul gyi las kyis sman mchog bdud rtsir
NK064(ngu)001:4573: 'gyur ba zos pa tsam gyis 'dod bya 'grub pa
NK064(ngu)001:4574: dang / nad zhi ba sogs yon tan lhag ma lnga po thams cad 'grub cing /
NK064(ngu)001:4575: de lnga so sor bsgrub na /
NK064(ngu)001:4576: yi ge'i 'phro 'dus 'dod bya gzhan dmigs pa ltar 'byung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4577: nad pa'i lus la yi ge bkod pa'i 'phro 'dus rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa'i nad bzhi'am /
NK064(ngu)001:4578: yang na kun brtags don gyi /
NK064(ngu)001:4581: rang bzhin sngon las kyi nad bzhi po re re
NK064(ngu)001:4582: la'ang brgya rtsa gcig pa re sbyar ba bzhi brgya
NK064(ngu)001:4583: rtsa bzhi'i nad thams cad sel zhing bde bar 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4584: ro // tram las rin po che'i gter du bsam pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:4585: yi ge'i 'phro 'dus mchod pas longs spyod ci 'dod 'byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4586: 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum gyi 'phro 'dus ngan song du skye ba'i sgrib pa sbyong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4587: gang dang cir snang ba'i chos kyi rnam pa yang
NK064(ngu)001:4588: de dang mi mthun pa'i snang ba gzhan skam sa
NK064(ngu)001:4589: las chu dang / sol ba las ljon shing /
NK064(ngu)001:4590: bye ba las gser du 'gyur ba sogs 'grub pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4591: de dag bshad rgyud rgyas pa dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK064(ngu)001:4592: rkang pa dang po gnyis ni le'u bzhi bcu pa mchog gi bdud rtsi sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4593: bdun cu pa thun mong gi bdud rtsi ro langs sgrub pas bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4594: longs spyod 'byung ba ni zhe gcig pa'i blon po nor mang sgrub pa sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4595: ngan song sbyong ba ni zhe gcig pa'i rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:4596: rigs kyi sgrub pa las a la sems sbyangs nas
NK064(ngu)001:4597: h+aum du bsgom te bdag lus sbyong ba sogs kyis
NK064(ngu)001:4598: bstan / ci yang gzhan du 'gyur ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4599: so brgyad pa nas rkang mgyogs dang mi snang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4601: re lnga pa nas pra sgrub sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4603: nam mkha' sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4605: nam mkha' la h+aum zhes rdo rje'i skas bsams na sra ba'i skas 'byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4606: lag mthil du ram bkod pas 'bar ba'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:4607: kyi mer gyur nas tha mal gyi me yang tshig
NK064(ngu)001:4609: de bzhin du kham bkod pa ye shes kyi chur
NK064(ngu)001:4610: 'gyur bas tha mal gyi chur 'bab pa'ang dag par
NK064(ngu)001:4611: byed pa dang / yam bkod pa rlung du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4612: nas 'jig rten gyi khams ni gzhan du 'degs shing
NK064(ngu)001:4614: yi ge e bkod de 'phro 'dus 'jig rten gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4615: khams thams cad stongs par byed cing steng 'og tu
NK064(ngu)001:4616: 'phen pa dang ltung bar 'gyur ba sogs 'grub bo
NK064(ngu)001:4617: // bshad rgyud dang sbyar na 'byung ba la thogs
NK064(ngu)001:4618: pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul ston par nus pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:4619: // / rgyas pa'i so brgyad pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:4620: mi gnas nam mkha'i mtha' klas par //
NK064(ngu)001:4622: chu la sa bzhin 'gro ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:4623: bsreg bya 'bar ba'i dbus gnas dang //
NK064(ngu)001:4624: tshangs pa'i rlung gis btegs nas kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:4625: phyogs bcu kun tu phyin par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:4628: dgug dang sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4629: 'grel sgrub ltar na ting nge 'dzin gyis gzungs ma
NK064(ngu)001:4630: dang dgra bgegs sogs bsgrub bya gang yin dgug pa
NK064(ngu)001:4631: dang / yul gzhan du btang ba ste bskrad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4632: dgra rkun sogs g.yo med du bcing ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4633: byad gdon gyis bcings pa sogs dgrol ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4634: nad pa dang sri'u la sogs pa gso ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4636: gzhan sde pham par bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4637: rang sde rgyal bar bya ba'i las rnams ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:4638: de dag bshad rgyud dang sbyar na /
NK064(ngu)001:4639: dgug pa dang bcing ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4640: rgyas pa'i so brgyad par yul khams dbang du bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4641: zhe gnyis dang zhe gsum gnyis nas 'das pa'i gzungs ma rigs lnga'i yum dang sems ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4642: zhe lnga par 'jig rten pa'i gzungs ma rgyal po dang lha chen gzhan gyi chung ma dgug pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4643: nga drug pa nas dgra bgegs dgug pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4644: re lnga par pra se na /
NK064(ngu)001:4645: re drug par lha chen dang rgyal po dgug cing bcing ba sogs kyis bstan no //
NK064(ngu)001:4646: btang ba ni so brgyad par dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du bskrad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4647: zhe drug par rang gnas kyi klu bskrad pa sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4648: dgrol ba dang gsol ba ni le'u de las gzungs
NK064(ngu)001:4649: ma klu'i byad du bcug pa dgrol thabs dang 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:4650: klu nad kyis zin pa gso ba /
NK064(ngu)001:4651: zhe bdun par mthar byed bzhi'i sgo nas ro langs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4652: bdun cu par zhing chen sgrub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4653: re bzhi par tshe gso ba sogs kyis gso ba bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4654: bsad pa ni nga drug par dgra bgegs bsad pa sogs kyis bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:4656: zhe gcig par dmag mang mthu chen dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4657: re drug par lha chen dang rgyal po sde bzhi sgrub pa sogs dang sbyar bar bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4658: las dang thun mong gi dngos grub de rnam thams
NK064(ngu)001:4659: cad phyag rgya gcig spros kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di
NK064(ngu)001:4660: la brtan pa thob pa yis byed nus par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4661: zhing / de ltar thun mong gi dngos grub bstan pa 'di dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4662: sngar bshad dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4663: de nyid kar dag pas blang dor dang bral bar
NK064(ngu)001:4664: dpes bstan pa gsum gyis phyag rgya spros bcas kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4666: lam rim le'u drug pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4667: gnyis pa mchog gi dngos grub la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:4670: rtog tshogs sgyu 'phrul lha'i dkyil 'khor rgyal ba bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:4671: bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba rnams thabs shes zung
NK064(ngu)001:4672: 'brel d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor rang rig mngon sum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4673: yul du rdzogs par gsal ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:4674: bsgrub bya phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba ma lus
NK064(ngu)001:4675: pa'i yon tan rdzogs pas gcig dang du ma'i mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:4676: las grol ba'i phyir rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK064(ngu)001:4677: gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad yongs su 'grub par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4678: ro // 'di ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4679: lam rim le'u dgu pa dang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4681: dus gsum sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4682: snang spyod thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4683: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4684: de dag gis thugs su chud pa'i don yang yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:4685: rnal 'byor pa'i lta ba'ang yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:4686: thun mong gi grub pa las khyad par du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:4687: pa dngos grub mchog ces brjod pa gang gi bsgrub
NK064(ngu)001:4688: bya'i snying po 'di mngon du gyur pa'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:4689: ni ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:4690: thob nas zad pa'i dus med pas yid bzhin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:4691: nor bu'i mdzod ltar 'phel 'grib kyi 'gyur ba med
NK064(ngu)001:4693: don dam par dngos po'am mtshan mar grub pa med
NK064(ngu)001:4694: pa'i ngang las gdul bya'i ngor dngos po ltar snang
NK064(ngu)001:4695: ba'i sprin gyi rol pa lha dang dkyil 'khor la
NK064(ngu)001:4696: sogs pa dngos grub sna tshogs pa'i rnam par 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:4697: zhing / don mdzad pa'i phrin las cir yang 'gyur ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4698: 'di ni gnas skabs lam gyur gyi 'bras bu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4699: lam rim le'u brgyad pa dang sbyor zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:4700: de'ang gzhung tshan gnyis po 'di mdo rgyas su 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4701: mchog dngos spyi la sbyor ba'i tshe gzhung snga mar rang don phun tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4702: phyi mar don gnyis phun tshogs gtso bor bstan pas phyi ma brjod bya rgyas par bzhed la /
NK064(ngu)001:4703: yang gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi mchog dngos so
NK064(ngu)001:4704: sor sbyor ba na gzhung tshig mang nyung gis mdo
NK064(ngu)001:4705: rgyas su song ba yin gsungs so //
NK064(ngu)001:4706: gsum pa gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4708: de ltar sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sgrub pa'i rim pa'ang
NK064(ngu)001:4709: shes 'jug mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid gsum po der
NK064(ngu)001:4710: 'dus so zhes ched du brjod pas 'khor gyi de
NK064(ngu)001:4711: bzhin gshegs pa nyid ting nge 'dzin las dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:4712: sna tshogs yul med rang gsal du shar ba'i gzigs
NK064(ngu)001:4716: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:4717: 'dis zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dngos grub thams
NK064(ngu)001:4718: cad sgrub pa'i thabs ting nge 'dzin bstan pa'i le'u
NK064(ngu)001:4720: le'u drug pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4725: de nas de bzhin sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:4726: snga mar thabs gsum mdor bstan pa de nas gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:4727: dang bsam mi khyab kyi thabs gnyis las zhi ba
NK064(ngu)001:4728: lhag ting dang 'bras bu rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:4729: gnyis rgyas par ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:4730: thams cad kyi rang bzhin gcig dang du ma med
NK064(ngu)001:4731: pas ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK064(ngu)001:4732: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs ston pas
NK064(ngu)001:4733: gdul bar bya ba'i yul 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:4734: bcu thams cad la rnam par gzigs te /
NK064(ngu)001:4735: 'dul byed ston pa nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:4736: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par dbyung bar
NK064(ngu)001:4737: bzhed nas 'khor gyi ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK064(ngu)001:4738: do // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:4743: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4744: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin sku'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4746: ye shes phyogs sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4747: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin la phyogs ris ma grub kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:4748: yon tan gyi ldog cha nas mtshon bya ye shes lngar snang ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:4749: mtshon byed phyogs bzhi dang dbus lnga'i tha snyad brtags te /
NK064(ngu)001:4750: de ltar ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor de nyid dmigs med bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das shing /
NK064(ngu)001:4751: mtha' yas pa'i chos thams cad kyi khyab byed du
NK064(ngu)001:4752: ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa ni rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:4753: gsang ba'i snying por ye nas rdzogs pa'i gnas lugs
NK064(ngu)001:4754: chos nyid rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor chen po ste
NK064(ngu)001:4755: / de rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas chos kun 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:4756: ba'i gzhi rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor chen po de
NK064(ngu)001:4757: nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi yul du byas te goms
NK064(ngu)001:4758: shing 'dris par bslab pa'i phyir bsgom pa'i bya bas
NK064(ngu)001:4759: / spyod cig pa'o // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4762: dkyil 'khor gyi che ba bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4764: 'khor lo sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4765: 'og gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i
NK064(ngu)001:4766: lte ba la rdzogs pa'i ye shes rin po che'i
NK064(ngu)001:4767: gzhal yas khang bsgom pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4768: de'ang ye shes lngas ma rig pa gcod pa'i rtags
NK064(ngu)001:4769: su nang gi gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi
NK064(ngu)001:4771: de nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid du
NK064(ngu)001:4772: zlum pas rdo rje ra ba'i mu khyud dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:4773: pa / de'i phyir bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhis brgyan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4774: bden gnyis dbyer med mtshon pa'i bar khyams 'khor yug tu 'khor ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4775: che ba'i yon tan kun tu rgyas pa'i rtags su dbyibs gru bzhi pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4776: rnam thar bzhi mtshon pa'i sgo bzhi sgo khyud can
NK064(ngu)001:4777: rgyu 'bras kyi rta babs la sogs pa'i rgyan dang
NK064(ngu)001:4778: ldan pa gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal
NK064(ngu)001:4779: snang ma 'gags pa'i rol mo rtsig pa lnga sbrag
NK064(ngu)001:4780: gi steng na mu tig gi d+r+wa ba dpyangs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:4781: seng mgos btegs pa'i rin po che'i pha gu dang
NK064(ngu)001:4782: / bre phul gyi snam bur rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa phyed /
NK064(ngu)001:4783: bya 'dab las dpyangs pa'i shar bu /
NK064(ngu)001:4784: steng ngos su pu shus mdzes pa /
NK064(ngu)001:4785: gdugs 'phan rgyal mtshan sogs rgyan sna tshogs pas kun tu 'khrigs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:4786: 'dod yon ma spangs rgyan du shar bas gzugs rdo
NK064(ngu)001:4787: rjee ma sogs mchod rdzas thogs pa'i lha mo sprin
NK064(ngu)001:4789: chos dbyings ye shes mtha' thug pa med pa'i brdar
NK064(ngu)001:4790: dbus phyur bur bum pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil
NK064(ngu)001:4791: ba'i rtser rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes
NK064(ngu)001:4792: pa / ye shes lhag ma bzhi mtshon pa'i glo
NK064(ngu)001:4793: 'bur bzhi gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba sogs le'u
NK064(ngu)001:4794: dang por bshad pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4795: gnyis pa la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:4798: gzhal yas khang de nyid mdzes byed bdag po'i rgyan
NK064(ngu)001:4799: lha'i dkyil 'khor rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis
NK064(ngu)001:4801: khang pa mdzes byed khyim bdag bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4803: gdan gang la ji ltar bzhugs tshul /
NK064(ngu)001:4806: sku mdog zhi tshul 'od dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4808: seng ge sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4809: gdan gyi khyad par mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs mtshon
NK064(ngu)001:4810: byed dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir
NK064(ngu)001:4811: seng ge dang / glang chen dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4814: nam mkha' lding ste shang shang rnams re re yang brgyad brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri chen po la /
NK064(ngu)001:4815: thabs shes rnam dag nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:4816: de dag kyang 'dod rgu 'byung ba rin po che'i khri rkang mdzod mig bdun pas btegs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4817: snang mtha' la 'dir khyung dang gleng gzhir rma bya
NK064(ngu)001:4818: 'byung ba ni dbang gi khrir don rtags mtshungs pas
NK064(ngu)001:4819: 'dam kha ste / rma byas dug dbang du byed
NK064(ngu)001:4820: pa ltar khyung gis kyang klu'i dug dbang du byed
NK064(ngu)001:4821: 'dam kha ste / pa'i phyir ro // de ltar
NK064(ngu)001:4822: rigs lnga la srog chags dang rin po che'i khri
NK064(ngu)001:4825: des gzhan rnams kyang mtshon dgos te /
NK064(ngu)001:4827: nyi zla chu skyes sum brtsegs sems //
NK064(ngu)001:4828: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK064(ngu)001:4829: bya byed kun bzang yab yum la //
NK064(ngu)001:4830: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen rgyas //
NK064(ngu)001:4832: so so'i gdan de dag la bzhugs tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:4833: rigs lnga yab lnga ni don gnyis kyi mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4834: yum lnga ni rang don brtul nas gzhan don la
NK064(ngu)001:4835: zhugs pa'i phyir yab yum bcu po rgyal po'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:4836: ltar de dang de'i skyil krung du bzhugs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:4837: sems dpa' rnams ni gzhan don gyi mdzad pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:4838: rdzogs pas yab rnams g.yas dang yum rnams g.yon cung
NK064(ngu)001:4839: zad brkyang ba'i phyed skyil te blon po'i tshul dang
NK064(ngu)001:4840: / kun bzang yab yum ni mdzad pa rdzogs shing
NK064(ngu)001:4841: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bya byed thabs shes mtshon
NK064(ngu)001:4844: mthar byed yab yum ni dmag dpon gyi tshul ltar
NK064(ngu)001:4845: gdug pa can tshar gcod pas zhal phyir gzigs nas
NK064(ngu)001:4847: thub drug ni skad cig kyang mi gnas par 'gro don la gshegs pas bzhengs stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4849: 'khor lo rgyal po sogs rkang pas dman pa'i tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4850: dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi la
NK064(ngu)001:4851: rgyal po rigs lnga po rgyal mo yum lnga dang
NK064(ngu)001:4852: bcas pa'o // gtso bo zhal shar gzigs kyi g.yas
NK064(ngu)001:4853: nas brtsams te mdun rgyab kyi g.yas g.yon du rim
NK064(ngu)001:4858: nub byang bzhi'i rtsibs mchan la rim pa ji lta bar /
NK064(ngu)001:4862: myong ba spyan ras gzigs dang bzhi btsun mo'ang rim par sgeg mo /
NK064(ngu)001:4865: glu ma'i tshogs su bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4866: de bzhin du gru chad bzhi la ni shar lho nas g.yas bskor gyis rim par /
NK064(ngu)001:4870: myong byed 'jam dpal rnams btsun mo spos ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4873: dri chab ma'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:4876: shar lho lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK064(ngu)001:4877: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK064(ngu)001:4878: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK064(ngu)001:4879: zhes pa'i rim pa ltar thub pa drug dang //
NK064(ngu)001:4880: gzhan yang bar khyams de'i shar dang nub ste gtso
NK064(ngu)001:4881: bo zhal shar gzigs kyi mdun dang rgyab kyi phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:4882: dag tu byed pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4883: bya ba bzang mo dag ni gnas par bstan te /
NK064(ngu)001:4884: de gnyis dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bya byed du mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4885: yongs grags khams lugs pa rnams dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bzhugs par bzhed pa ni mi rigs te /
NK064(ngu)001:4887: khyams kyi mdun dang rgyab tu ni //
NK064(ngu)001:4888: kun bzang yab yum nam mkha'i mdog /
NK064(ngu)001:4889: ces gsungs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:4890: sgo khyud bzhi la gdug pa can 'joms par byed pa'i khro bo shar sgor gshin rje gshed /
NK064(ngu)001:4893: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams ni rang rang gi btsun mo lcags kyu /
NK064(ngu)001:4896: dril bu ma bzhi'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:4898: ston pa kun bzang khyams la bkod pas gtso 'khor log pa'i skyon yod ces smra ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4899: rang gi rang bzhin gsal bar ston pa'i smre sngags shor ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4900: rgyud 'chad pa po kho nas dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor byed par ma nges pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:4901: dper na 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK064(ngu)001:4902: bor ston pa sh+aaka thub mi 'byung ba bzhin no
NK064(ngu)001:4904: rdo rje sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4905: ye shes lnga mtshon pa rigs lnga'i rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4906: mtha'i rtog pas mi phyed pa'i brdar mi bskyod pa'i rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:4907: kun la dbang sgyur bas rnam snang gi 'khor lo /
NK064(ngu)001:4908: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyis grub pas rin 'byung gi rin po che /
NK064(ngu)001:4909: gsal la ma chags par gzigs pas snang mtha'i pad+ma /
NK064(ngu)001:4910: phrin las bzhis 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa gcod pas don grub kyi ral gri /
NK064(ngu)001:4911: ye shes kyi yul dbyings kyi phyag rgya dril bu ste thams cad kyang 'od 'bar ba can no //
NK064(ngu)001:4912: de yang yab lnga g.yas rang rtags thugs ka dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4913: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud cing /
NK064(ngu)001:4914: yum lnga po de las ldog ste g.yas dril bus
NK064(ngu)001:4915: yab kyi dku g.yas nas 'khyud cing g.yon rang rtags
NK064(ngu)001:4917: sems dpa' rnams kyi phyag mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:4918: 'jam dpal ni nyon mongs dag pas blo rgyas pa'i phyir ut+pala /
NK064(ngu)001:4919: byams pa ni gdung ba skyob pas klu shing 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:4920: pa la sogs pas mtshon nas gzhan rnams kyang rang
NK064(ngu)001:4923: sa snying ni ye shes bskyed pa'i rin chen myu gu /
NK064(ngu)001:4924: nam snying ni nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i ral gri /
NK064(ngu)001:4925: spyan ras gzigs ni skyon gyis ma gos pas pad dkar /
NK064(ngu)001:4926: phyag rdor ni nyon mongs pa 'joms pas rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:4927: sgrib sel ni nyon mongs pa chos nyid du mkhyen pas 'khor lo /
NK064(ngu)001:4928: kun bzang ni re ba skong bas rin chen snye ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4929: 'dir phyi sems kyi mtha' thog nas brtsams te phyag mtshan sogs khongs smos pa gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:4930: gzhan drug po'i phyag mtshan rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan du 'dus pa'i dbang du mdzad pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4931: g.yon pa'i dril bu bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:4932: sems ma brgyad ni mdzes pa'i mchor sgeg gi tshul
NK064(ngu)001:4933: dang bcas te mnyes par byed pa'i mchod rdzas gzugs
NK064(ngu)001:4935: dri rgyun mi chad pa'i phreng ba sogs rang rang
NK064(ngu)001:4936: gi ming dang mthun pa'i yo byad 'dzin pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:4937: / sems dpa' brgyad po g.yon dril bu dkur brten
NK064(ngu)001:4938: cing yab yum phan tshun 'khyud tshul kyang sngar rigs
NK064(ngu)001:4941: byams pas zhe sdang tshar gcod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4942: snying rjes sdug bsngal 'joms pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4943: dga' bas 'gro ba'i don mi gtong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4944: btang snyoms kyis 'gro don mthar phyin par mdzad pas
NK064(ngu)001:4945: phyag mtshan n+ri mgo gdengs pa la sogs pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:4946: / yum rnams tshad med pa bzhis 'gro ba rnams thugs rjes 'dzin pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:4949: nyon mongs pa thal bar rlog pas dga' bar mdzad pa'i phyir lcags kyu la sogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4950: kun bzang yab yum ni byed pas 'khor 'das mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:4951: nyid du mkhyen cing bya ba mos kun la khyab
NK064(ngu)001:4952: par gnas pas phyag mnyam bzhag go //
NK064(ngu)001:4954: sdom bzhis chos sgras nga rgyal 'joms par mdzad pas lha'i thub pa pi wam /
NK064(ngu)001:4955: bzod pas phrag dog sbyong mdzad lha min gyi thub pa go cha /
NK064(ngu)001:4956: chags bral gyi lam gyis 'dod chags dag par mdzad pas mi'i thub pa gseg par /
NK064(ngu)001:4957: gti mug sel phyir chos ston pas byol song gi thub pa pusti /
NK064(ngu)001:4958: bkres skom sel bas ser sna dag byed yi dwags kyi thub pa rin chen sgrom bu /
NK064(ngu)001:4959: tsha grang gi nyes dmigs bstan nas zhe sdang dag
NK064(ngu)001:4960: par mdzad pa dmyal ba'i thub pa me chu bsnams
NK064(ngu)001:4961: pa'o // zhal phyag spros pa'i skabs 'dir rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:4962: rgyas pa ni yum rnams dang thub drug ma gtogs
NK064(ngu)001:4963: thams cad zhal gsum phyag drug par bshad rgyud rdo
NK064(ngu)001:4964: rjer bshad cing / de las gzhan du rigs lnga'am
NK064(ngu)001:4965: gtso bo tsam zhal gsum phyag drug par mdzad pa
NK064(ngu)001:4966: 'bring po thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis par mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:4968: 'dir bla ma rnams 'bring po rigs lnga zhal gsum phyag drug pa la phyag len mdzad pas /
NK064(ngu)001:4969: de'i dbang du rdo rje las /
NK064(ngu)001:4971: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK064(ngu)001:4973: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes //
NK064(ngu)001:4974: dang po thugs dang g.yon 'khyud pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4975: zhes pas mi bskyod pa'i phyag mtshan rdzogs par bstan
NK064(ngu)001:4976: nas rigs gzhan bzhi la g.yas dang por rang rtags
NK064(ngu)001:4977: kyi phyag mtshan song ba'i shul du rdo rje spo
NK064(ngu)001:4980: mthing ga sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4981: de yang sku mdog la rigs dang rigs 'dres pa kha dog gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:4982: dang po rigs kyi sku mdog ni nyer gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:4983: le'u dang por bshad pa ltar rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i mtshon tshul nges par byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:4986: phyag rdor rnams so so'i yum bcas /
NK064(ngu)001:4987: lha min gyi thub pa dang bdun ni mthing ga /
NK064(ngu)001:4990: lha'i thub pa dang lnga ni dkar po /
NK064(ngu)001:4991: rin 'byung dang nam snying yum bcas /
NK064(ngu)001:4992: mi'i thub pa dang lnga ni ser po /
NK064(ngu)001:4993: snang mtha' dang spyan ras gzigs yum bcas bzhi ni le brgan te dmar po /
NK064(ngu)001:4994: don grub yab yum gnyis ni ljang khu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:4995: gnyis pa de la sogs pa'i khongs nas rigs gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:4996: 'dres sna tshogs pa'i sku mdog ni bcu dgu ste
NK064(ngu)001:4997: / byams pa dkar ser yin pa sogs gru chad
NK064(ngu)001:4998: kyi phyi sems bzhi yab yum phye bas brgyad ni
NK064(ngu)001:4999: phyogs gnyis 'dres kyi kha dog dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5000: shar sgo la sogs pa'i 'joms pa yab yum brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:5001: ni smug ser dmar ljang bzhi'i kha dog nag po
NK064(ngu)001:5003: thub pa drug las byol song dmar nag /
NK064(ngu)001:5007: lha de dag kyang nga rgyal gnas su dag pas sku sha mnyen pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5008: zhe sdang dag pas yan lag lcug pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:5010: 'dod chags dag pas thabs shes phan tshun 'khril ba'am
NK064(ngu)001:5011: 'khril bag chags pas sku lhod por ma gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:5012: / phrag dog dag pas sku drang zhing ldem pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5013: gti mug dag pas sku gzhon sha chags pa'i ngang tshul can /
NK064(ngu)001:5014: ma rig pa spangs pas sku gtsang zhing gsal ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5015: ye shes rgyas pas bkrag cing 'tsher ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5016: mtshan dpe rdzogs pas brjid cing yid du 'ong bas lhun sdug pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5017: che ba'i yon tan gyis thams cad zil gyis gnon pas gzi byin chen po dang ldan pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5018: snga ma lnga ngo bo'i yon tan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5019: phyi ma bzhi rnam pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:5020: sku de dag las 'od ji ltar 'phro ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5021: zhi ba rnams kyi ba spu'i bu ga re re
NK064(ngu)001:5022: nas kyang gsal zhing dag pa'i 'od zer dkar ser
NK064(ngu)001:5023: dmar sngo btsod kha dngul mdog dang drug po re
NK064(ngu)001:5024: re las kyang bye ba phrag drug drug phyogs bcur
NK064(ngu)001:5025: 'phro ba'i tshogs chen po'i snang bas khyab par byed
NK064(ngu)001:5026: cing / khro bo rnams la me ltar 'bar zhing
NK064(ngu)001:5027: rno ba'i 'od zer gyi phreng bas kun tu 'khrigs
NK064(ngu)001:5028: pa'i klong na bzhugs pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5029: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5030: 'phros don rgyan gyi khyad par la /
NK064(ngu)001:5034: gdul bya'i nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i brdar
NK064(ngu)001:5035: lha rdzas las grub pa'i dar gyi chas gos lnga
NK064(ngu)001:5036: dang / 'dod yon ma spangs rgyan du rdzogs pas
NK064(ngu)001:5037: 'gro ba'i re ba skong ba'i brdar rin po che'i
NK064(ngu)001:5038: dang / rgyan brgyad de / rgyan chas bcu gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:5039: thub drug ni gang 'dul gyi gzugs su rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:5040: ston kyang 'khor ba'i chags pas ma gos pa'i brdar
NK064(ngu)001:5041: tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5042: khro bo yab yum ni dpa' rtags kyi rgyan dur khrod kyi chas brgyad do //
NK064(ngu)001:5043: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi che ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5044: mtha' dbus sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:5045: mtha' dang dbus 'di zhes dmigs su med par chos
NK064(ngu)001:5046: thams cad la khyab pa'i chos nyid gzhi rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:5047: gyi dkyil 'khor bsam brjod las 'das pa'i mtha' yas
NK064(ngu)001:5048: pa'i gnas lugs de nyid rtogs don sgom pa'i thabs
NK064(ngu)001:5049: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la goms
NK064(ngu)001:5050: par bslabs pa'i mthus 'bras bu rang bzhin lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:5052: gsum pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin sku'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5056: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:5058: sku'i phyag rgya sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:5059: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan gyi rten byed pas na sku ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5060: de yang mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga lhun
NK064(ngu)001:5061: gyis grub pa las mi 'da' zhing gzhan las khyad
NK064(ngu)001:5062: par du gyur pa'i phyag rgya ches che ba'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:5063: ni rigs drug pa rgyal ba spyi'i gzugs can nyid
NK064(ngu)001:5064: yin la / sku gcig po de las sku lngar snang ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5065: gzhi chos dbyings de bzhin nyid zung 'jug spros bral
NK064(ngu)001:5066: gyi ye shes las ma g.yos pa'i ldog pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:5067: chos kyi sku'o // de ltar ma g.yos kyang sgrib
NK064(ngu)001:5068: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa las yang dag par
NK064(ngu)001:5069: thar pa'i gzugs sku dag pa'i gdul bya la thun
NK064(ngu)001:5070: mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpes brgyan
NK064(ngu)001:5071: par snang zhing dngos po gnyis la rdzogs par longs
NK064(ngu)001:5072: spyod pa'i ldog pa ni longs sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5073: gdul bya'i 'gro ba ma lus pa dngos brgyud ci rigs par 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:5074: de dag gi bsam pa dang mthun par byas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5075: sku'i bkod pa ni gcig tu ma nges par sna
NK064(ngu)001:5076: tshogs su ston pa'i ldog pa ni sprul pa'i sku'o
NK064(ngu)001:5077: // de ltar ston pa nyid kyang dpe sgyu ma'am
NK064(ngu)001:5078: mig yor gyi tshul dang 'dra bar gzugs sku gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:5079: su snang ba'i tshul de nyid kyang dbyings chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5080: sku las g.yos pa med pas sku gsum dbyer mi
NK064(ngu)001:5081: phyed pa'i ldog pa ni rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5082: de ltar chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin du gdul
NK064(ngu)001:5083: bya'i las dang mthun par sku sna tshogs su snang
NK064(ngu)001:5084: bas sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres par go 'byed
NK064(ngu)001:5085: pa'i ldog pa ni mngon byang gi sku'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5086: gnyis pa sku'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:5087: sku ji ltar snang ba'i tshul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5090: de tshe mi mthun sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5091: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa de'i tshe gdul bya'i
NK064(ngu)001:5092: skal pa mi mthun pa sna tshogs la 'dul byed
NK064(ngu)001:5093: kyi sku so so'i rigs dang 'dra bar snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:5094: ni de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las rtsol bas ma
NK064(ngu)001:5095: bcos kyang gdul bya rang rang gi skal ba dang
NK064(ngu)001:5096: sngon gyi las 'phro'i dbang gis sku so sor snang
NK064(ngu)001:5097: ba ste / dper na gzugs gcig nyid me long du ma'i nang du so sor 'char ba'am /
NK064(ngu)001:5098: chu snod du mar zla gzugs gcig nyid so sor 'char ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:5099: de ltar yang phal po che las /
NK064(ngu)001:5100: zla ba dbyings las ma 'phos kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:5101: chu yi snod du snang ba ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:5102: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par //
NK064(ngu)001:5103: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:5105: gnyis pa sku'i mdzad pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5106: de tshe 'gro drug sogs rkang pa bcu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5107: sku de ltar snang nas don mdzad pa de'i tshe
NK064(ngu)001:5108: lha dang mi sogs 'gro drug gi sems can tha
NK064(ngu)001:5109: mal pa thams cad la 'dul byed sdig spong gi
NK064(ngu)001:5110: gzugs brgya byin dang 'khor los sgyur rgyal sogs su
NK064(ngu)001:5111: rnam par bstan nas don mdzad cing /
NK064(ngu)001:5112: de bzhin du dge tshul gyis mtshon pa'i nyan thos
NK064(ngu)001:5113: kyi rigs can rnams la nyan thos dgra bcom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5114: gzugs dang / rang rgyal gyi rigs can rnams la
NK064(ngu)001:5115: bse ru lta bu rigs mthun pa'i tshul du bstan
NK064(ngu)001:5117: de las gzhan yang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa
NK064(ngu)001:5118: mchog gi rigs can rnams la sh+aakya thub pa sogs
NK064(ngu)001:5119: 'dul byed kyi ston pa'ang gdul bya'i dbang po'i rim
NK064(ngu)001:5120: pa bzhin du bstan nas 'dul ba ni sprul sku'i
NK064(ngu)001:5121: mdzad pa'o // longs sku'i mdzad pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5122: gnas nges pa 'og min bla na med pa'i gnas gzugs khams las 'phags pa'i mchog tu /
NK064(ngu)001:5123: ston pa nges pa longs sku rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i tshul gyis /
NK064(ngu)001:5124: 'khor nges pa sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' ste 'phags pa'i 'khor rnams la /
NK064(ngu)001:5125: dus nges pa rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos ston te /
NK064(ngu)001:5126: de'i tshul ni sprul sku bzhin du chos rnams gsung mchog tshig tu mi smra ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5127: 'o na ji ltar ston na sku'i brda yis chos
NK064(ngu)001:5128: nges pa theg pa chen po nyid 'khor rnams kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5130: gsum pa 'bras bu thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:5132: gsang sngags kyi thob tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:5134: sgrib pa sbyangs pas grol tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5135: me long bstan pa'i sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:5136: ji ltar me long bstan pa'i nang du byad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5137: dri ma snang ba'i tshul gyis byad dngos kyi mdog
NK064(ngu)001:5138: bzang po ngan par bsgyur ba'i dri ma thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:5139: ngos zin nas / gdod sel bar byed pa de
NK064(ngu)001:5140: bzhin du 'khor sa bcu'i byang sems rnams kyis ston
NK064(ngu)001:5141: pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi skur bltas
NK064(ngu)001:5142: ngos zin nas / pa na / bla na med
NK064(ngu)001:5143: pa'i byang chub la sgrib par byed pa'i dri ma
NK064(ngu)001:5144: gting dpag med pa rnams me long la snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:5145: bzhin du ston pa'i sku la snang bas rang rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:5146: kyi sbyang bya'i dri ma ngos zin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5147: de yang thog mar tshogs lam gsum du tshogs bsags
NK064(ngu)001:5148: pas gtso bor thos bsam la brten pa'i shes rab
NK064(ngu)001:5149: kyis bdag med gnyis don spyi'i tshul du rtogs shing
NK064(ngu)001:5150: / tshogs lam chen po thob nas sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku las gdams ngag nyan /
NK064(ngu)001:5151: sbyor lam bzhir 'jig rten pa'i sgom byung gi ye
NK064(ngu)001:5152: shes la dngos su zhugs pas gzung 'dzin gyi rnam
NK064(ngu)001:5153: rtog rags pa rnams rim par bcom nas /
NK064(ngu)001:5154: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes sngar ma mthong
NK064(ngu)001:5155: ba gsar du mthong bas sgro btags kyi sgrib pa
NK064(ngu)001:5156: ma lus pa sangs pa na /
NK064(ngu)001:5158: byung ba'i mun pa sangs nas rdzogs longs spyod pa mngon du snang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5159: zhes pas longs sku'i zhal mthong ste sgrib pa ngos zin pa de nas brtsams te /
NK064(ngu)001:5160: mthong zin goms par byed pa sgom lam sa dgur
NK064(ngu)001:5161: lhan skyes kyi sgrib pa je srab tu gyur pas
NK064(ngu)001:5162: sa bcu'i mi mthun phyogs rnams phar phyin bcu dang
NK064(ngu)001:5163: sa'i yongs su spyod pas rim gyis 'byang ba ste
NK064(ngu)001:5164: dag pas / sa dang por yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5165: de nyid sa gnyis par stong 'gyur /
NK064(ngu)001:5168: lnga par khrag khrig phrag stong /
NK064(ngu)001:5169: drug par khrag khrig phrag brgya stong /
NK064(ngu)001:5170: bdun par bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong /
NK064(ngu)001:5171: brgyad par stong gsum brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul snyed /
NK064(ngu)001:5172: dgu par sangs rgyas kyi zhing grangs med pa brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul snyed /
NK064(ngu)001:5173: bcu par sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa
NK064(ngu)001:5174: bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul snyed
NK064(ngu)001:5175: kyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhal blta
NK064(ngu)001:5176: ba dang / chos nyan pa sogs skad cig re re la ston par nus pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:5177: de ltar sa bcu rgyun gyi tha mar mdo sde rgyan las /
NK064(ngu)001:5178: sgom pa tha ma thob nas ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5179: 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:5180: zhes pa ltar 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur bas
NK064(ngu)001:5181: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin thob ste shes
NK064(ngu)001:5182: sgrib phra ba bag la nyal gyi dri ma bcom
NK064(ngu)001:5183: nas bla na med pa'i byang chub kun tu 'od
NK064(ngu)001:5184: kyi sa yang dag par thob bo //
NK064(ngu)001:5185: gnyis pa de ltar thob pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsum ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5186: chos sku sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5187: dag pa gnyis ldan chos kyi sku ni blos dpag
NK064(ngu)001:5188: tu med cing ngag gis brjod du med de nam
NK064(ngu)001:5189: mkha' lta bu'o // de'i ngang las longs spyod rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:5190: pa'i sku ni rtag tu zad pa med pa nor
NK064(ngu)001:5191: bu rin chen gyi gter dang 'dra bar bzhugs pa
NK064(ngu)001:5192: mkha' lta bu'o // dang / sprul ba'i sku ni
NK064(ngu)001:5193: gang la gang 'dul gyi sku'i bkod pa bye ba
NK064(ngu)001:5194: phrag brgya sogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa sna tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:5195: par bstan nas don mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:5196: gnyis pa sngags kyi thob tshul la'ang gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:5197: mthar thug gi sa'i khyad par ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5198: mtshan dang dpe byad sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5199: sngags kyi thabs khyad par can la brten nas 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:5200: ba de'i bag chags ches phra ba'ang rnam par dag
NK064(ngu)001:5201: pas mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po
NK064(ngu)001:5202: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid du 'tshang
NK064(ngu)001:5203: rgya ba'i sangs rgyas kyi sa gcig gi ngo bo
NK064(ngu)001:5204: la / sku gsum gyi ldog pas phye na /
NK064(ngu)001:5205: sgrib bral gyi dgongs pa shes rab spros bral gyi
NK064(ngu)001:5206: ye shes ni thun mong ma yin pa'i kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:5208: de'i ngang las thabs 'gag pa med pa chos sku
NK064(ngu)001:5209: dang ngo bo gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:5210: rab 'byams su 'char yang dmigs pa dang bral bas
NK064(ngu)001:5211: gos pa med pa'i ye shes ni pad+ma can longs
NK064(ngu)001:5212: sku'i sa dang / thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:5213: spyod yul kun tu ye shes rang snang bde ba chen po'i man+dala zhes dkyil 'khor te /
NK064(ngu)001:5214: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang la
NK064(ngu)001:5215: ma zhen par shar ba'i phyir tshogs chen gnyis kyang
NK064(ngu)001:5216: ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pas gdul bya gzhan snang
NK064(ngu)001:5217: du rnam par rol pa'i sprul pa ston par nus
NK064(ngu)001:5218: pa'i ye shes ni 'khor lo tshogs chen sprul sku'i
NK064(ngu)001:5219: sa'o // de la sogs te sa'i grangs dang yon
NK064(ngu)001:5220: tan bsam yas pa'i mchog rdzogs pa mthar thug gi
NK064(ngu)001:5221: sa gsum po de rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od
NK064(ngu)001:5222: las khyad par du gyur pas na sa'i mchog ces
NK064(ngu)001:5223: sa'o // bya'o // gang dag kun tu 'od sprul sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5224: yi ge 'khor lo chos sku'i sar bsdus pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:5225: mkhas pa'i gsung yin kyang 'thad par mi sems te
NK064(ngu)001:5227: dbyings la ye shes shar ba kun tu 'od //
NK064(ngu)001:5228: pad+ma'i spyan 'dra mi 'gag longs spyod rdzogs //
NK064(ngu)001:5229: yi ge 'khor lor gdul byar sprul pa 'gyed //
NK064(ngu)001:5230: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sa zhes bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5231: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:5232: gnyis pa 'bras bu sku lngar bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5233: skye shi sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:5234: skye shi sogs spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral
NK064(ngu)001:5235: ba'i ye shes 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub rtag
NK064(ngu)001:5236: brtan g.yung drung gi sku ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5237: 'gro ba nyon mongs pa can kun gyi bsod nams
NK064(ngu)001:5238: kyi zhing du gnas pa sprul pa'i sku'i snang brnyan
NK064(ngu)001:5239: gdul bya'i blo dang mthun par zad mi shes par
NK064(ngu)001:5240: 'byung ba'i gter du gyur pa ni longs spyod rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:5241: pa'i sku'o // sku gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK064(ngu)001:5242: rje rang rig pa'i ngang du 'du 'bral med par
NK064(ngu)001:5243: 'dzin pa'i sku ni rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5244: chos thams cad rig pa'i ye shes su dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:5245: pas mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa'i phyir sku gsum
NK064(ngu)001:5246: snang cha ma 'dres par snang ba'i sku ni mngon
NK064(ngu)001:5247: byang ngo // chos can ji snyed pa thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:5248: ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya'i
NK064(ngu)001:5249: mos ngor brtan g.yo sna tshogs pa'i rnam par ston
NK064(ngu)001:5250: pa'i sku ni sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5251: mthar thug thun mong ma yin pa'i sa thob pa
NK064(ngu)001:5252: de'i tshe sku lnga po de dag kun kyang rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:5253: par thob pas snga phyi med de /
NK064(ngu)001:5254: sgrib bral mi 'gyur ba'i ye shes nyid yon tan gyi rten byed pa'i ldog pa nas sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5256: mi slob pa'i lam zhes sam /
NK064(ngu)001:5257: rang byung gi rig par gnas pa'i cha nas ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5258: des don mdzad pa'i cha nas phrin las zhes so
NK064(ngu)001:5259: sor btags na'ang ngo bo tha mi dad par gcig
NK064(ngu)001:5260: pa'i phyir ro // bzhi pa gsungs pa'i yon tan ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5261: zhes brjod pas sogs te rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:5262: gyi don de skad ces brjod pas gdul bya'i yul
NK064(ngu)001:5263: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i zhing mtha' yas mu
NK064(ngu)001:5264: med pa thams cad du 'dul byed sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:5265: gyi rnam par rol pa brjod kyis mi lang ba
NK064(ngu)001:5266: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul snyed rang
NK064(ngu)001:5267: rig pa'i yul du gsal zhing snang bar gyur to
NK064(ngu)001:5268: // gnyis pa bsdus te bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5271: gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:5274: rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:5275: yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:5276: pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi rang bzhin rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:5277: dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston pa'i sku sogs
NK064(ngu)001:5278: rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung
NK064(ngu)001:5280: a hoh dmigs bya sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5281: rang bzhin ma skyes pa las rol pa 'gag med
NK064(ngu)001:5282: lam dang 'bras bu sku'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba
NK064(ngu)001:5283: la a hohzhesa ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5284: de'ang dmigs bya dbyings dang dmigs byed rang rig gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:5285: dbyer med kyi ye shes tsam du'ang mi dmigs pas
NK064(ngu)001:5286: blos dpag med bsam gyis mi khyab par rtogs nas
NK064(ngu)001:5287: bsgom pa ste / der ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i tshigs bcad gcig bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5288: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la rang rig pas
NK064(ngu)001:5289: dbang sgyur ba'i rtsal snang lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:5290: gyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa rnam
NK064(ngu)001:5291: pa sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang bar snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:5292: ste / gsungs pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5293: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i tshigs bcad brgyad bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5294: gdul bya dag pa chos mnyam nyid du rtogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5295: mi mnyam par tha dad du 'dzin pa ma dag pa'i gdul bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5296: de dag kun la rgyal ba drug pa'i phrin las kyis khyab par don mdzad pa'i dus na /
NK064(ngu)001:5297: gdul bya'i yul de dag chos nyid las gzhan du
NK064(ngu)001:5298: ma gyur pa'i phyir khyab bya khyab byed med pas
NK064(ngu)001:5300: snang stong tha mi dad pa'i dbyings rnam par dag pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5301: sku'i mtshan nyid dang phrin las /
NK064(ngu)001:5303: sngags kyi mthar thug sa'i khyad par bstan pa rnams bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5304: ye nas sku lnga po kun kyang bde ba chen
NK064(ngu)001:5305: po'i sku las ma 'gags par rang gsal ba'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:5306: 'khor rnam par spros pa tsam nyid nas spros pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5308: sngags kyi 'bras bu sku lnga bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5309: de gsungs pa'i yon tan gnyis bsdu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5310: de ltar bsdus pa'i don la hohzhesa mnyes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5313: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don de skad ces rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:5314: 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:5317: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:5318: 'dis ting 'dzin lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5319: 'bras bu rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor spros nas bstan pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5321: // le'u bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5326: de nas de bzhin sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5327: sku'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas lhag ting dang
NK064(ngu)001:5328: 'bras bu rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor gnyis ston
NK064(ngu)001:5329: pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun
NK064(ngu)001:5330: mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad kyi sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:5331: gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las
NK064(ngu)001:5332: gsung gsang sngags kyi gsang ba 'di dag phyung ngo
NK064(ngu)001:5333: // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:5334: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5335: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:5336: dang po lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:5337: 'khor 'chad pa'i skabs 'dir zhi ba'i phrin las sgom
NK064(ngu)001:5338: rim gyi sdebs cung zad brjod par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5341: rjes kyi rim pa dang gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:5343: dang po gral phyag dang tshul phyag bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5344: gnyis pa yan lag brgyad pas rgyud sbyang ba //
NK064(ngu)001:5345: gsum pa mtshon cha dam tshig las rgyal po lnga'i phyag rgyas mtshams bcad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5346: bzhi pa brjod med kyi bshags pa bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5347: lnga pa pun+da ri ka'i rgyud las gsungs pa ltar dam bca' nyi shu pa bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5348: drug pa bab drug 'das bzhi'i dgongs pas bdag gnas yo byad rnams la byin dbab pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5349: bdun pa phyi nang gi mchod pa rnams byin gyis rlob pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5350: sgrub thabs kyi las byang ltar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5351: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:5352: dang po khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5353: bdag dang mtha' yas sogs kyis kun rdzob dang //
NK064(ngu)001:5354: le'u gnyis pa'i e ma mtshar lngas don dam pa'i sems bskyed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5355: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5356: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5357: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5358: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK064(ngu)001:5359: dang po snang stong so so tha dad kyi zhen
NK064(ngu)001:5360: rtog sbyong byed le'u lnga par gsungs pa'i ting nge
NK064(ngu)001:5361: 'dzin gsum tshig rin chen d+r+wa ba ltar dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5362: brtan pa'i yan lag tu rgyu'i a las yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:5363: phra mo'i spro bsdu la sems sbyang ba le'u bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:5364: pa ltar ro // gnyis pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:5365: 'byung lnga'i zhen rtog sbyang phyir sgrub thabs ltar yum
NK064(ngu)001:5366: lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:5367: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5368: ma dag pa'i snod bcud kyi snang zhen sbyong phyir sa bon b+h+r+aum las rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5369: le'u bzhi pa ltar yi ge zhe gnyis spros pa
NK064(ngu)001:5370: las cho ga gsum gyis brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:5371: te / 'dir bshad pa'i bskyed sngags kyis bskyed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:5372: le'u drug pa ltar tshig gis gsal gdab /
NK064(ngu)001:5373: rigs mthun gyi las la dbang bsgyur ba dang sgo
NK064(ngu)001:5374: gsum gyi stobs 'phel ba'i zhen rtog sbyang phyir dbang
NK064(ngu)001:5375: bskur byin rlabs 'di nas bshad pa ltar bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:5376: rnams so // gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la drug las /
NK064(ngu)001:5377: dang po 'khor 'das tha dad kyi zhen pa sbyang
NK064(ngu)001:5378: phyir ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la snyan gsan dbab
NK064(ngu)001:5379: cing / spyan drangs pa la rig pa'i me tog
NK064(ngu)001:5380: dor nas dbyer med du bstim pa rnams 'di nas
NK064(ngu)001:5382: gnyis pas phyag dang mchod pa bcu gsum 'bul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5383: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5384: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5386: drug pa 'dzab khang phye nas dam ye 'phro 'du
NK064(ngu)001:5387: gsum gsal bas ngag gi zhen pa sbyong ba dang
NK064(ngu)001:5388: lha'i thugs dam bskul ba'i phyir 'dzab bzla zhing skabs
NK064(ngu)001:5389: kyi mjug bsdu ba rnams sgrub thabs ltar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:5390: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5391: dang po bsod nams spel phyir tshogs kyi mchod sbyin /
NK064(ngu)001:5392: gnyis pa las 'chol phyir brtan ma skyong ba //
NK064(ngu)001:5393: gsum pa rtag chad kyi mtha' bsal phyir dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing thun mtshams kyi lhar ldang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5394: bzhi pa bar chad kyi rgyun gcod phyir go bgo lus bsrung /
NK064(ngu)001:5395: lnga pa spyod pa rnam par dag pa'i phyir spyod
NK064(ngu)001:5396: lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bskyang pa rnams kyang sgrub
NK064(ngu)001:5397: thabs ltar ro // da ni dkyus nyid la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5398: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:5399: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags /
NK064(ngu)001:5400: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dgug bstim gyi sngags /
NK064(ngu)001:5403: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i /
NK064(ngu)001:5405: dbang bskur byin gyis rlob pa'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5408: zhes pa'i b+h+r+aum ni rigs lnga 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang gi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5410: bi shud+d+he rnam par dag pa na zhes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5411: 'byung lnga'i rtog pa sna tshogs yum lnga'i mkha' dbyings
NK064(ngu)001:5412: su rnam par dag pa gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5414: b+h+r+aum dbyings b+ha gar sna tshogs 'dus //
NK064(ngu)001:5415: las dang ngo bo dag pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:5416: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog /
NK064(ngu)001:5417: byin rlabs skyob phyir sngags su brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:5427: rigs kyi yab lnga'i sngags kyi 'go 'dren h+aum s+w+aa
NK064(ngu)001:5428: +aam h+aam rnams ni thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa
NK064(ngu)001:5429: sogs kyi rigs kyi sa bon te /
NK064(ngu)001:5430: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5433: rnam shes dag pa byang chub kyi sems zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:5434: dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa mi bskyod
NK064(ngu)001:5435: pa ste / de'i bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5436: sa bon dang bskyed sngags sbrel ba ni bzlas pa
NK064(ngu)001:5437: las kyi sngags te thams cad la 'gre shes par
NK064(ngu)001:5438: bya'o // dzi na dzika rgyal ba rgyal te /
NK064(ngu)001:5439: dbyings spros bral ni mi dge ba'i chos las rgyal zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:5440: de las shar ba'i 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur gyi gzugs kyang rgyal ba'i skur dag pa ste rnam snang /
NK064(ngu)001:5441: rat+na d+h+rika rin chen 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5442: bsam pa thams cad rdzogs par byed pas sems yon
NK064(ngu)001:5443: tan rin po che'i 'byung gnas de nyid nyams su
NK064(ngu)001:5444: myong bas 'dzin par byed pa tshor phung dag pa
NK064(ngu)001:5445: rin 'byung / +aa ro lika chags chen mtshon te /
NK064(ngu)001:5446: sems 'dod cing rtsen pa'i mtshan nyid mtshon byed mtshan mar 'dzin pa 'du shes dag pa snang mtha' /
NK064(ngu)001:5447: pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika shes rab 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5448: rnam shes don la phyin ci ma log par 'jug pa'i blo ni shes rab /
NK064(ngu)001:5449: de 'dzin par byed pa 'du byed dag pa don grub kyi bskyed sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5451: rdo rje 'dzin dang rgyal ba'i rgyal //
NK064(ngu)001:5452: rin chen 'dzin dang chags chen mtshon //
NK064(ngu)001:5453: shes rab 'dzin pa zhes bya ste //
NK064(ngu)001:5455: nang ltar na snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa lngas rigs lnga'i thig le'i bcud 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5457: tsit+ta khams lnga'i shi ra la //
NK064(ngu)001:5458: rdo rje rgyal ba rin chen chos //
NK064(ngu)001:5459: shes rab rigs ldan bcud kyi gzugs //
NK064(ngu)001:5460: nges par 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK064(ngu)001:5462: rigs lnga'i yum gyi sngags kyi 'go 'dren /
NK064(ngu)001:5463: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam ste sa bon rnams ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5464: mok+sha thar pa ste rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa'i dbyings mtshon par byed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5468: t+aa ra sgrol ma lnga'i ming yig dang po thig
NK064(ngu)001:5469: les brgyan pa ste byang chub kyi sems dkar cha
NK064(ngu)001:5470: thabs dang ma bral ba mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5471: d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai ni dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma ste gtso yum /
NK064(ngu)001:5475: badz+ra rdo rje ste phrag dog /
NK064(ngu)001:5476: de bzhin rnam par dag pa rigs kyi yab rnams
NK064(ngu)001:5477: mnyes par byed pas na ra ti zhes dga' ma
NK064(ngu)001:5479: gti mug zhe sdang 'dod chags dang //
NK064(ngu)001:5480: rdo rje rtag tu dga' mar sbyar //
NK064(ngu)001:5482: nang ltar snying ga'i thig le'i yul cha phra ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:5483: dwangs ma lngas dug lnga dbyings su skyob par byed
NK064(ngu)001:5485: de nyid dwangs ma'i ye shes lnga //
NK064(ngu)001:5486: ma rig gnyis sogs bzhi po dang //
NK064(ngu)001:5487: mi phyed phrag dog rdo rje'i sngags //
NK064(ngu)001:5488: dbyings su skyob pa dga' mar brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:5491: dang po nang sems yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5492: k+shim hi r+aa dza sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5493: k+shim ti zhes sa'i ming gi dang po ste sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5494: hi r+aa dza ya ngo mtshar rgyal po ste sa snying /
NK064(ngu)001:5495: tram rin chen rigs kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5497: gar+b+ha ya snying po ste nam snying /
NK064(ngu)001:5498: h+r+aim ha h+aum pad+ma rigs kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5499: pad+ma pa da ma pad+ma'i phyag ste spyan ras gzigs /
NK064(ngu)001:5501: ku ru p+aa na dang sbrel bas rgyal mdzad phyag ste phyag rdor /
NK064(ngu)001:5502: yum bzhi'i h+aum t+r+aam h+r+ai +aam bzhi ni rigs kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5510: bskyod par gyur pa'i ming ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5511: so so'i mthar snyoms 'jug gi brda bzhi sbyor te /
NK064(ngu)001:5512: sa ma ya s+t+wam dus la bab ces yum gyis bskul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5513: sa ma ya hohdusa yin no zhes lan byin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5514: r+aa go&a ham bdag chags so zhes bskul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:5515: r+aa ga ya mi chags par bagyi'o zhes lan byin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5517: las kyi bde bas sgeg pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5518: chags pa'i dam tshig dus yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:5519: slar yang lan gyis 'brel ba ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5520: gnyis ka dgyes pa'i mchog tu bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:5521: ha dang si yi bde sgra dag /
NK064(ngu)001:5522: bdag gi chags pa thob pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5523: shin tu bskyod pa'i bde ba nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:5524: kun nas bskyod pas rlung zhes bya //
NK064(ngu)001:5526: gnyis pa phyi sems yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5527: mee d+h+aa ra ne sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5528: mee ni mee tri byams pa'i ming gi dang po sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5529: d+h+aa ra ni gzungs la zhes pa ste byams pas rjes su 'dzin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5530: th+l+him sgrib sel gyi bsdus pa'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5531: nis+sa ram b+ha ya dang sbrel bas sgrib pa bsal ba'i ched du /
NK064(ngu)001:5532: h+aum byang chub sems kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5533: sa r+aa dza ya'i sa ni sa man+ta ste kun nas rgyal po'i ched du zhes kun bzang /
NK064(ngu)001:5534: mum ni muk+ta ste rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5537: r+aa ga ya chags pa'i ched du ste 'jam dpal /
NK064(ngu)001:5538: bzhi ka'i mthar s+w+aa h+aa ni yon tan khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:5539: can las dang sbyar ba'i ming so so de dang
NK064(ngu)001:5540: de'i ched du gzhi 'dzugs pa'i legs par byin zhes
NK064(ngu)001:5541: pa'o // yum bzhi'i sa bon dzahh+aum bam hohbzhi ni
NK064(ngu)001:5542: bzung 'khyud sdom mnyes te phyag rgya bzhi'i sa bon
NK064(ngu)001:5543: pa'o // / d+h+au pe bdug spos ma /
NK064(ngu)001:5546: gan+d+he dri chab ma zhes so so'i ming dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5547: mthar snyoms 'jug gi sbyor tshad bzhi rim par sbyor te /
NK064(ngu)001:5548: pra be sha rab tu zhugs pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5550: su gi r+ai bde ba ma /
NK064(ngu)001:5551: tsit+ta thugs te sems tshim pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5554: de nyid phye ba las byung ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5555: me tog bsdus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:5556: bdag po'i zhal du thim par bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:5557: shin tu bsdam pa'i rim las byung //
NK064(ngu)001:5558: gsal ba'i ye shes bde ba che //
NK064(ngu)001:5559: kun gsal brjod dang 'dra ba'i sgra //
NK064(ngu)001:5560: gnyis med thugs su shes par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:5563: h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5564: khro bo bzhi'i 'go 'dren h+aum bzhi ni spyi'i rigs
NK064(ngu)001:5565: kyis khyab bya'i rigs bzhi la zhugs pa'i sa bon
NK064(ngu)001:5570: so so'i mthar an+ta krita te mthar byed ces sbyar ba ming dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5571: phata bkas pa'i don te bkas par gyis shes las la sbyar ba'i bskul tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:5572: yum bzhi'i 'go 'dren bzhi ni rab basngagasa te spyi'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5574: badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma bzhi ni rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las /
NK064(ngu)001:5577: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai khro mo'i dbang phyug ma /
NK064(ngu)001:5578: dz+wa l+ai ni 'bar ba ma ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5579: rdo rje rin chen sogs 'chang chen po'i zhes pa thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5580: khro mo chen mo 'bar ba'i dbang phyug ma zhes pa shes rab kyi ming so so'i mthar /
NK064(ngu)001:5581: h+aum bzhi khyab byed zhugs pa'i rigs kyi snying po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5585: h+aum gsum ni kun gzhi sgo lnga yid kyi rnam shes gsum 'das pa ye shes kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5587: thabs kyi snying po ste byed pa po kun bzang /
NK064(ngu)001:5588: a gsum ni shes pa gsum gyi yul chos kyi dbyings kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5589: badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta rdo rje kun tu bzang mo /
NK064(ngu)001:5590: a ni shes rab kyi snying po ste bya ba mo'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5592: rnam shes gsum 'das rdo rje ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5593: ye shes lnga rdzogs thugs nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:5594: dbyings gsum rnam dag 'dus ma byas //
NK064(ngu)001:5595: kun tu de bzhin gnas byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5599: rnams ni rab basngagasa te phyag 'tshal ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5600: mu ne rnams ni thub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5601: k+r+aem ni byed pa ste 'dod yon gyi byed pas lhag pa lha'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5602: h+aum t+r+aum ni go cha bkod pa ste lha min gyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5603: srum ni sa ra 'khyil ba ste blo dkyil che ba mi'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5604: pram ni pra ho ste 'dud pa'i don gyis dud 'gro'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5605: k+sham ni k+sha ra ste dngos snang 'gyur bas gdung ba yi dwags kyi sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5606: ye ni gang yang rung bar khrid pas dmad pa'i gnas su gyur pa ste dmyal ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:5607: s+w+aa h+aa ni 'gro ba'i rigs de dang de'i bag
NK064(ngu)001:5608: chags zhi ba'i ched du gzhi 'dzugs pa'i don no
NK064(ngu)001:5609: // nang ltar na snying gar rigs drug gi sa
NK064(ngu)001:5610: bon zung gsum gnas pa bde ba chen pos rang
NK064(ngu)001:5611: rig pa'i ye shes su gsal ba na ma rig
NK064(ngu)001:5612: pa gnyis las byung ba'i 'khor ba'i bag chags thul
NK064(ngu)001:5614: sa bon zung gsum de bde ba //
NK064(ngu)001:5615: nges skyes rang rig gyur ba yis //
NK064(ngu)001:5616: gnyis byung 'dul bas thub par gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:5618: gsum pa dbang bskur byin gyis rlob pa'i sngags la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5623: de nas bcom ldan 'das nas phyung ngo zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:5624: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dbang
NK064(ngu)001:5625: bskur ba'i byed pa po phyogs dus bde gshegs thams
NK064(ngu)001:5626: cad dang mi phyed pa'i rdo rje rigs kyi yab
NK064(ngu)001:5627: lnga dang / spyad bya'i yul bya ba mo rdo
NK064(ngu)001:5628: rje yum lnga'i rnam par rang gi thugs ka'i dwangs
NK064(ngu)001:5629: ma'i srog h+aum yig gi 'od kyis spyan drangs pa
NK064(ngu)001:5630: rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i rjes chags kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5631: mes zhu ba ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:5632: gyi lha thams cad kyi dbu'i gnas lnga la thim
NK064(ngu)001:5633: lnga dang / par mdzad do // de ltar dbang
NK064(ngu)001:5634: bskur bas nyon mongs pa lnga sbyangs nas chu lud
NK064(ngu)001:5635: pa dbang gnas su 'khyil ba las phyogs bcu dus
NK064(ngu)001:5636: bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag
NK064(ngu)001:5637: nyid chen po rang rigs bdag por gyur pa'i rigs
NK064(ngu)001:5638: lnga sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan cing
NK064(ngu)001:5639: lnga dang / par mdzad do // / phung lnga
NK064(ngu)001:5640: bdag nyid chen po'i rang bzhin du dag pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:5641: shes kyi ngo bo rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su nga
NK064(ngu)001:5645: mi bskyod byed po yum dang bcas //
NK064(ngu)001:5646: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgyar bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:5647: byams pa sa snying de bzhin nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:5648: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgyas te //
NK064(ngu)001:5649: gshin rje gshed la rtag par bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:5651: zhes pas mi bskyod pa yab yum rdo rje'i rigs yin pa'i shugs kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:5655: don grub las rigs yin par mtshon cing /
NK064(ngu)001:5656: de bzhin du bya byed dang thub drug kyang rdo rje'i rigs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5657: rkang pa dang po gnyis dang drug pa'i don no //
NK064(ngu)001:5658: sa snying dang byams pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs yin pa'i shugs kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:5659: nam snying dang sgrib sel rin chen /
NK064(ngu)001:5660: spyan ras gzigs dang kun bzang pad+ma /
NK064(ngu)001:5661: phyag rdor dang 'jam dpal las rigs yin pas mtshon te /
NK064(ngu)001:5662: rkang pa gsum pa'i don no //
NK064(ngu)001:5663: gshin rje gshed rtag pa rnam snang gi rigs yin pa'i shugs kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:5667: rkang pa lnga pa'i don dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5668: rkang pa bzhi pas ni mtshon byed dngos su smos
NK064(ngu)001:5669: pa'i shugs las mtshon bya gzhan rnams mtshon pa'i tshig
NK064(ngu)001:5670: go // mdor na rigs gang yin gyi lha la
NK064(ngu)001:5671: rang rigs kyi bdag po dbus su song ba'i shul
NK064(ngu)001:5672: du rdo rje'i rigs 'gro ba'ang shes par bya ste
NK064(ngu)001:5673: go // / de dag ni dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5674: yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi 'bras chos lnga'i byin bsdu ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5675: spyi bo dung khang du zla ba la dkar po /
NK064(ngu)001:5676: mgrin par pad+ma la +aam dmar po /
NK064(ngu)001:5677: thugs kar tsit+ta'i mdun du nyi ma la h+aum sngon po /
NK064(ngu)001:5678: lte ba'i g.yas g.yon du zla ba la s+w+aa sngon
NK064(ngu)001:5679: po dang h+aa ljang khu rnams las 'phros pa'i 'od
NK064(ngu)001:5680: kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:5681: bskul / rdo rje lnga'i lha'i rnam par spyan drangs
NK064(ngu)001:5682: pa yi ge so so la thim pas sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:5683: thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK064(ngu)001:5684: dang gnyis su med par byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags
NK064(ngu)001:5685: yi ge lnga yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang
NK064(ngu)001:5686: dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pa sogs de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:5687: pa lngas rgyas btab par bsam pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5689: gnas gsum khyab 'jug yi ge las //
NK064(ngu)001:5691: khams gsum byin rlabs gzi byin bsdu //
NK064(ngu)001:5692: rang bzhin rdo rje gsum gnas pa //
NK064(ngu)001:5693: rgyu gnyis tshul gyis rang snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5694: lte ba rnam gnyis zla ba la //
NK064(ngu)001:5695: sngo ljang yi ge s+w+aa h+aa gnyis //
NK064(ngu)001:5696: rjes mthun 'od kyis yon tan las //
NK064(ngu)001:5697: yan lag rdzogs pa'i gzi byin ldan //
NK064(ngu)001:5699: de ltar dbang dang byin bsdu ba zhes bya ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:5700: gsang sngags 'di dag ston pa'i sku dang gsung dang
NK064(ngu)001:5701: thugs mi phyed pa'i rdo rje thabs shes zung 'brel
NK064(ngu)001:5702: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las phyung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5705: byin gyis rlob pa'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5707: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5710: sh+au nya t+aa stong pa nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:5712: sa ma t+aa mnyam pa nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:5713: pra t+ya bek+sha na so sor rtog pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5714: krit+y+aa nush+tha na bya ba grub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5715: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra ye shes rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:5716: swa b+h+aa wa rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:5719: mtshams sbyar bas +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes 'byung bas /
NK064(ngu)001:5720: rab basngagasa stong pa nyid sogs kyi ye shes chen
NK064(ngu)001:5721: po rdo rje'i ngo bo nyid kyi bdag nyid nga'o
NK064(ngu)001:5723: le'u brgyad par gsungs pa ltar gung mo rdo rje'i rigs yin pa sogs nges par byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:5724: rdo rje bsdams pa las rang rigs kyi sor mo
NK064(ngu)001:5725: gnyis sbyar nas brkyang pa spyi bo sogs mgo bo'i
NK064(ngu)001:5727: de'ang rang rigs kyi phyag rgya dbus su gang song
NK064(ngu)001:5728: gi shul du rdo rje'i rigs kyi dbang rgya 'gro
NK064(ngu)001:5731: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5734: ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5739: a nu r+aa ga na rjes su chags pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5742: swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham sngar bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:5743: rab basngagasa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:5744: sogs rdo rje chen po'i ngo bo nyid kyi bdag
NK064(ngu)001:5746: 'dir byin gyis rlob pa'i rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5747: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas de dang der gtug pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5748: de ltar dbang dang byin rlabs kyi lha lnga lnga
NK064(ngu)001:5749: ste bcu'i steng du snying dbus srog gi gor rang
NK064(ngu)001:5750: 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs
NK064(ngu)001:5751: pa re re bsgom pa rtsis pas yan lag gi
NK064(ngu)001:5752: lha bcu gcig tu 'gyur na'ang don la byin rlabs
NK064(ngu)001:5753: kyi yon tan dang phrin las gnyis rdo rje gsum
NK064(ngu)001:5754: gyi zhar byung tsam yin pas lam bsgoms pa'i dbang
NK064(ngu)001:5755: du / sa chu gnyis dang me rlung gnyis kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5756: dwangs ma ro gcig tu 'jug pas rin 'byung rnam
NK064(ngu)001:5757: snang la bsdus pa sku rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:5758: don grub mtha' yas la bsdus pa gsung rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:5759: de'i rig pas sems kyi dwangs ma don dam pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5760: nam mkha' dang ro gcig pa nyid kyis khyab byed
NK064(ngu)001:5761: drug pa dang khyab bya mi bskyod pa gnyis 'dres
NK064(ngu)001:5762: thugs rdo rjer byas pas byin rlabs kyi lha gsum
NK064(ngu)001:5763: ste / yan lag gi lha dgur gsungs pa'i gnad kyang shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5766: dbang dang byin bsdu ba'i sngags de skad ces brjod
NK064(ngu)001:5767: pas ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun spyi bo nas thim
NK064(ngu)001:5768: par gyur pas dbu'i gnas lngar dbang lha rigs lnga
NK064(ngu)001:5769: gsal bar gyur / gnas gsum du rdo rje gsum gyi lha rnams 'bar bar gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:5770: gnyis pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dgug bstim gyi sngags la bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:5771: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5773: ye shes kyi snying po ste 'go 'dren /
NK064(ngu)001:5774: e h+ye hi tshur spyon tshur spyon /
NK064(ngu)001:5776: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:5778: sa ma ya s+t+wam dus la bab bo zhes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5779: dam tshig pa'i thugs srog h+aum gi 'od kyis bskul
NK064(ngu)001:5780: bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad chos kyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:5781: las gzugs kyi sku ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i rnam
NK064(ngu)001:5782: pa can du sad par bsam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5783: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa'i sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5785: thugs ka nas spros pa'i phyag rgya'i lha mo bzhis
NK064(ngu)001:5786: dgug bcings bsdams la dgyes pa bskyed pas ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:5787: kyi 'khor lo rten dang brten par bcas pa spyan
NK064(ngu)001:5788: drangs te / dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5789: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5791: +aam h+aum s+w+aa h+aa zhes pa'i yi ge re re thog mthar sbyar ba'i bar du /
NK064(ngu)001:5792: badz+ra sa ma ya zhes yi ge re re btus te sdebs pa'i sngags tshan lngas /
NK064(ngu)001:5793: bdag dam tshig pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK064(ngu)001:5794: las rnams rdo rje ltar mi phyed pa'i dam tshig
NK064(ngu)001:5795: gis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'bras chos
NK064(ngu)001:5796: lnga dang gnyis med du rtags par byed pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:5797: / rig pa'i me tog dor ba zhes kyang bya /
NK064(ngu)001:5798: so so ma yin par rig pa 'dun pa'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:5799: gam rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:5801: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul te bstim pa'i sngags ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5803: ni dngos grub gsol ba'i glu'i 'go 'dren no //
NK064(ngu)001:5804: rang rig pa'i ye shes la mnga' mdzad pa'i rgyal po zhes bos te /
NK064(ngu)001:5805: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK064(ngu)001:5806: yon tan phrin las gzhan las ches rmad po che
NK064(ngu)001:5807: de nyid dus phyir ma lus par da lta nyid
NK064(ngu)001:5808: du 'dir ni dbyer med mnyam par sbyor bas ye
NK064(ngu)001:5809: shes lha'i rdo rjee gsum gyi phyag rgya chen por
NK064(ngu)001:5810: bdag gi sgo gsum sbyor bar mdzod cig ces bskul
NK064(ngu)001:5811: bas lha rnams dngos grub stsol ba la phyogs par
NK064(ngu)001:5812: gyur pa dang / badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum zhes
NK064(ngu)001:5813: pa'i h+aum thugs bskul ba'i sa bon du byas te
NK064(ngu)001:5814: gyur pa dang / / rab basngagasa rdo rje mnyam par mdzod /
NK064(ngu)001:5815: ces pas ye shes pa dam tshig pa la bstim ste gnyis med du gyur /
NK064(ngu)001:5816: badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes pas nam mkha'i lha'i
NK064(ngu)001:5817: 'khor lor grub par ma gyur gyi bar du brtan
NK064(ngu)001:5818: par bzhugs pa'i rdo rje'i dam tshig khyod ces so
NK064(ngu)001:5819: // badz+ra sa ma ya hohmachoga ster rdo rje'i dam
NK064(ngu)001:5820: tshig gis mnyes par mdzod ces bskul bas shin tu
NK064(ngu)001:5821: dbang du gyur te dgyes pa chen pos rjes su
NK064(ngu)001:5822: // chags par bya'o // dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa phyag rgya bzhis shin tu brtan cing gsal bar byas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5825: de skad ces brjod pas lhag ting gsung gsang sngags
NK064(ngu)001:5826: kyi dkyil 'khor 'di dag gis yul 'jig rten drug
NK064(ngu)001:5827: gi phyogs bcu thams cad kyi gdul bya'i ngag la
NK064(ngu)001:5829: de lam rkyen gyis sngags sgrar rab tu /
NK064(ngu)001:5830: des 'gag med gsung rdo rjer grol bas kun tu grags so //
NK064(ngu)001:5831: gnyis pa rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5836: dang po skye med don gyi gsung ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5837: e ma hohngo mtshar sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5838: e ma hoh zhes brjod med las don go bas ngo mtshar zhing ches rmad kyi chos te /
NK064(ngu)001:5839: ji ltar na rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi khyab
NK064(ngu)001:5840: byed chos kyi sku'i gsung ni grags pa'i sgra dang
NK064(ngu)001:5842: brjod pa'i tshig sogs kun las 'das pa'i brjod med
NK064(ngu)001:5843: kyi gsung des go phye bas sna tshogs pa'i sgra
NK064(ngu)001:5844: rnams gsal bar 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5845: gnyis pa brjod pa tshig gi gsung ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5846: gsung gcig sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5847: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi gsang ba gcig la
NK064(ngu)001:5848: yang gsung gi dkyil 'khor yan lag drug cu la
NK064(ngu)001:5850: mdo chen por gsungs pa'i don sdoms su byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:5851: tshangs dbyangs sil snyan glu gar dang //
NK064(ngu)001:5853: sgra brnyan lta bu'i rnam grangs drug /
NK064(ngu)001:5854: re re la yang yan lag ni //
NK064(ngu)001:5856: rnam rig mnyan 'os mi mthun med //
NK064(ngu)001:5857: shin tu zab dang rjes su 'byung //
NK064(ngu)001:5858: mi tshugs rnar snyan ma 'khrugs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:5859: shin tu gsang ste drug cu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5860: de dag kyang gdul bya rigs drug gi gnas kyis
NK064(ngu)001:5861: phye bas sum brgya drug cu sogs bsam gyis mi
NK064(ngu)001:5862: khyab pas zhing khams kun tu khyab cing rang rang
NK064(ngu)001:5863: gi skad du brda sprod pa'i sgra dang ming tshig
NK064(ngu)001:5865: grags pa de thams cad kyang zab pa dang rgya
NK064(ngu)001:5866: che ba'i gsung gi phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:5868: gsum pa rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5869: rgyud mchog sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5870: rgyud thams cad kyi mchog thabs shes zung 'brel sgyu
NK064(ngu)001:5871: 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud las 'bras bu bde ba chen
NK064(ngu)001:5872: po dang ldan pa rang rig pa ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5873: gsung gi don 'byung ba'ang ji ltar zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:5874: 'khor 'das kyi sgra thams cad gzung 'dzin gyis gos
NK064(ngu)001:5875: pa med pa pad+ma lta bu'i ngang du gyur pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5876: phyir na / rnam par grol ba 'das pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5877: thar par bgrod byed lam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5878: bcings pa 'khor ba'i sgra skad kyi rnam pa ji
NK064(ngu)001:5879: skad brjod pa thams cad kyang mtshan mas ma gos
NK064(ngu)001:5881: cir yang mi 'gag par rang rig la snang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:5882: phyir rig pa'i gsung ngam bde ba chen po'i gsung
NK064(ngu)001:5883: zhes kyang bya'o // bzhi pa dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5884: theg pa mtho dman sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5885: rnam par grol ba'i theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5886: phyin ci log mu stegs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5887: 'gro ba rigs drug gis bsdus pa'i sems can ma
NK064(ngu)001:5888: lus thams cad kyi sgra skad kun kyang don la
NK064(ngu)001:5889: grags stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor ye nas
NK064(ngu)001:5890: byang chub pa rdo rje'i gsung du bsdus shing /
NK064(ngu)001:5891: bsdus tsam nyid na'ang de las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:5892: phyogs bcu rnam par grags shing go bar mdzad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:5893: sgra nyid ji ltar pad+ma la chus mis gos pa
NK064(ngu)001:5894: ltar ma chags 'dzin med kyi ngang du gsungs pas
NK064(ngu)001:5895: mtha' gnyis las grol ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:5896: ma 'gags par gsungs pa'i dus nyid na ma dmigs pas brjod du med pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5897: lnga pa tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5898: brjod med de nyid sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5899: brjod med don gyi gsung de nyid brjod pa sna
NK064(ngu)001:5900: tshogs pa'i sgra'i 'byung gnas su snang bas gdul bya
NK064(ngu)001:5901: kun la tshig gcig mthun par grags shing /
NK064(ngu)001:5902: de las don so sor 'jal zhing go bar byed de /
NK064(ngu)001:5903: dper na tshul de bzhin du thub pa'i dbang pos
NK064(ngu)001:5904: sbrid pa sangs pa la nad pa sman pa khyim
NK064(ngu)001:5905: bdag mo gsum gyis don so sor go ba bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:5906: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gcig gi sgra yis so
NK064(ngu)001:5907: so'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'i chos thams cad go
NK064(ngu)001:5908: ba de ni gsung gcig gis kun la khyab pas
NK064(ngu)001:5909: gsung mchog rgyal po ste tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung
NK064(ngu)001:5910: yin no // de ltar yang dkon brtsegs las /
NK064(ngu)001:5911: rgyal ba'i gsung dbyangs gcig snang ba //
NK064(ngu)001:5912: mos pa'i dbang gis so sor thos //
NK064(ngu)001:5914: 'dir longs sku brda'i gsung ma byung bas chad la /
NK064(ngu)001:5915: sprul sku'i gsung gnyis byung bas lhag go zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:5916: longs sku'i gsung ni sngar le'u drug par /
NK064(ngu)001:5917: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK064(ngu)001:5918: sku yis chos rnams 'jal bar ston //
NK064(ngu)001:5919: zhes bstan zin pas 'dir ma smos la /
NK064(ngu)001:5921: tshig gi gsung ni tshig res don re mtshon pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:5922: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ni tshig res don du
NK064(ngu)001:5923: ma mtshon pa yin pas lhag pa'i skyon med ces
NK064(ngu)001:5924: gsungs so // gnyis pa gsung gi byed las ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5925: theg pa mtho dman sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5926: gdul bya'i snang bar theg pa mtho dman bsam yas
NK064(ngu)001:5927: gsungs pa ltar snang yang bcom ldan 'das kyis de
NK064(ngu)001:5928: bzhin nyid la 'bab pa kho na las gzhan ma
NK064(ngu)001:5929: gsungs te / gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs su chos
NK064(ngu)001:5930: kyi rnam grangs so sor thos pa tsam du zad
NK064(ngu)001:5931: gsungs te / do // de ltar yang ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK064(ngu)001:5933: ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid 'ba' zhig gsungs na /
NK064(ngu)001:5934: la las ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK064(ngu)001:5935: la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK064(ngu)001:5936: la las ni gzugs bde zhes bya bar thos /
NK064(ngu)001:5937: la las ni gzugs sdug bsngal zhes bya bar thos /
NK064(ngu)001:5939: gsum pa gsung gi rnam grangs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:5940: ji ltar gsung rab sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5941: ji ltar gsung rab kyi don kun tshig tu brjod
NK064(ngu)001:5942: kyang don chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyis gzhal na
NK064(ngu)001:5943: brjod du med pa'i phyir cung zad kyang gsungs pa
NK064(ngu)001:5944: med de / chos sku skye med don gyi gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5945: don gyi gsung de nyid mtshon byed kyi yi ger
NK064(ngu)001:5946: grub pa med pa dang sgrar brjod du med pas
NK064(ngu)001:5947: ljags kyi rtse mor sgra tshig tu ma byung yang
NK064(ngu)001:5948: sku'i brdas 'khor gyi blo la don 'jal bar ston
NK064(ngu)001:5949: pas na longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5950: rig pa ye shes kyi gsung de nyid kun khyab
NK064(ngu)001:5951: kyi thugs rje dang sgra thams cad chos nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5952: ngang du lhun gyis grub pa'i gsung gi byin rlabs
NK064(ngu)001:5953: cir yang mi 'gags pa'i stobs kyis don mdzad pa
NK064(ngu)001:5954: ni mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ngo
NK064(ngu)001:5955: // 'gro ba gang la gang 'dul gyi mos pa
NK064(ngu)001:5956: dang mthun pa'i sgra don sna tshogs tshig gcig gis
NK064(ngu)001:5957: so sor gsal zhing thos pas brda sprod pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:5958: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5959: de ltar gsal ba nyid na'ang mi dmigs pas gsung
NK064(ngu)001:5960: gi rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pas rdo rje'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:5961: ste dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:5962: tshul de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi sgo
NK064(ngu)001:5963: nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa rnams ni brjod med
NK064(ngu)001:5964: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las gzhan du ma g.yos
NK064(ngu)001:5965: kyang rgyal ba'i thugs rje dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5966: gdul bya'i mos pa las rang snang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5967: dper na brag cha'i sgra nyid kyang brjod 'dod dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5969: rtsol ba gang yang med bzhin du rkyen gyis sgra'i rnam pa 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:5971: ji ltar sgra brnyan gyi ni sgra //
NK064(ngu)001:5972: gzhan gyi rnam rig las byung ba //
NK064(ngu)001:5973: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung //
NK064(ngu)001:5974: phyi dang nang na'ang gnas ma yin //
NK064(ngu)001:5978: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:5979: 'dis rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa gsung lngar bsdus pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5980: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor gsang sngags kyi don bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:5982: // le'u brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5987: de nas de bzhin sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:5988: gsung gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:5989: dang lta ba dang lhag ting ste thugs phyag rgya'i
NK064(ngu)001:5990: dkyil 'khor gsum ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:5991: thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid kyis lus dang rtog
NK064(ngu)001:5992: pa'i yan lag thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:5993: dkyil 'khor du ye shes lhun gyis grub pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:5994: rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas mthar phyin par byin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:5995: rlob pa zhes bya ba'i phyag rgya'i rim pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:5997: gnyis pa gzhung la lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:5998: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK064(ngu)001:5999: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6001: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6002: phyag rgya'i rnam grangs kyi sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6004: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6005: chos thams cad zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:6006: 'khor du ye nas rang bzhin gyis mngon par rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:6007: par sangs rgyas pa'i phyir rtog tshogs thams cad la
NK064(ngu)001:6008: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po
NK064(ngu)001:6009: mchog gi phyag rgyas btab pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6010: de nyid gnas rtogs mngon du byas pa'i gnas skabs gsum la /
NK064(ngu)001:6014: de ltar rtogs dka' ba'i gsang ba de kho na
NK064(ngu)001:6015: nyid du nges pa'i don chos nyid snying po'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:6016: rgyas btab pa ni rgyal po'i bka' rtags ltar 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:6021: de las byung ba rigs lnga spyi'i dam rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6022: de las 'phros pa lha so so'i phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6024: mi bskyod sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6026: dbu ni bde gshegs rigs nyid de //
NK064(ngu)001:6027: lag g.yas rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
NK064(ngu)001:6028: lag g.yon rin chen sems dpa'i rigs //
NK064(ngu)001:6029: rkang g.yon chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK064(ngu)001:6030: rkang g.yas las kyi sems dapa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6031: zhes lus kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6032: nying lag gi gung mo rdo rje //
NK064(ngu)001:6037: yan lag dang nying lag thams cad rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
