NK064(ngu)001:6038: mi bskyod pa'i rigs lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i
NK064(ngu)001:6039: bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lnga'i steng
NK064(ngu)001:6040: du thabs rigs lnga'i yi ge h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa
NK064(ngu)001:6041: / rin chen rigs lag pa g.yon gyi sor mo
NK064(ngu)001:6042: lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor lnga'i steng du shes
NK064(ngu)001:6043: rab yum lnga'i yi ge m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam
NK064(ngu)001:6044: rnams sor mo'i rigs gang yin ltar ma 'khrul bar
NK064(ngu)001:6045: / bkod rjes / sor mo lnga phrag gnyis po
NK064(ngu)001:6046: zung du sprad pa'i las kyis thal mo mnyam par
NK064(ngu)001:6047: sbyar bas lha so so'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyur
NK064(ngu)001:6048: / bkod rjes / 'gyur ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6049: dang m+au gnyis sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6050: g.yas kyi mdzub mo'i dang g.yon gyi gung mo'i m+aum
NK064(ngu)001:6051: gnyis rtse sbyar te lhag ma rigs bzhi'i yi ge
NK064(ngu)001:6052: 'bru brgyad kyang / g.yas kyi gung mo'i h+aum dang g.yon gyi mdzub mo'i l+aam /
NK064(ngu)001:6053: de bzhin du mthe bong dang mathe'u chung g.yas g.yon gyi h+aa dang p+aam /
NK064(ngu)001:6054: +aam dang t+aam rnams phan tshun so sor bsnol nas
NK064(ngu)001:6055: rtse sprad pa las srin lag gi s+w+aa m+aam gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:6056: mathe'u chung nang du bkug pa'i rgyab tu sbyar nas
NK064(ngu)001:6057: sbreng ba ni rgyal ba kun dang dbyer med mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:6058: par sbyor ba'i dngos grub bde ba chen po'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:6059: shes sbyin par byed pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6060: de ltar yang thabs zhags las /
NK064(ngu)001:6061: sor mo nang du bsnol nas bkan //
NK064(ngu)001:6062: gung mdzub mthe bong mathe'u chung rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:6063: so sor rtse sprad phyir bkyed de //
NK064(ngu)001:6064: srin lag gshibs bsgreng dam tshig rgya //
NK064(ngu)001:6067: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sprad la //
NK064(ngu)001:6068: de bzhin h+aum dang l+aam du sbyar //
NK064(ngu)001:6069: h+aa dang p+aam yang de bzhin te //
NK064(ngu)001:6070: +aam dang t+aam du sbyar ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:6071: rgyab sbyar s+w+aa dang m+aam bsgreng ba //
NK064(ngu)001:6072: 'di ni yab kyi spyi rgya yin //
NK064(ngu)001:6073: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:6074: dang m+aum sbyar h+aum dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:6075: l+aam sbyar s+w+aa dang p+aam du sbyar //
NK064(ngu)001:6076: +aam dang m+aam sbyar h+aa t+aam bsgreng //
NK064(ngu)001:6077: yum gyi spyi rgya yin par bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:6079: gsum pa so so'i phyag rgya la lnga las /
NK064(ngu)001:6080: dang po rigs lnga'i phyag rgya las gtso bo yab yum ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6081: 'bru bzhi sbas nas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6082: bdag nyid gtso bo mi bskyod pa'i skur bsgom pa phyag rgya chen po /
NK064(ngu)001:6083: de'i ngang las lag g.yas pa'i h+aum ma gtogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6084: yig 'bru gzhan bzhi po khu tshur gyi rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:6085: sbas nas gung mo gyen du bsgreng ba'i rgyab thugs
NK064(ngu)001:6086: kar gtad de bkan pa ni bca' ba dam rgya
NK064(ngu)001:6087: / h+aum yig mthing ga gung mo bsgreng ba de'i rtse mo bsgom pa ni bsam pa chos rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6088: h+aum zhu ba las rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar bar gyur pa ni bsam pa dam rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6089: lag g.yon pa'i zla ba lnga nang du brtul bas
NK064(ngu)001:6090: yum gyi yig 'bru lnga sbas pa'i khu tshur gyis
NK064(ngu)001:6091: dril bu bzung ba gsil zhing yum la 'khril ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:6092: tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos kyi sems dapa'am pad+ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:6093: rigs kyi steng du bzhag pas dku la brten thabs
NK064(ngu)001:6094: su bca' ba ni bca' ba las rgya dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6095: de ltar bsgom pa ni bsam pa las rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6096: de nas phyag rgya g.yas su bcas pa mdun du
NK064(ngu)001:6097: bsgyur nas g.yon du yum gyi thugs kar se gol
NK064(ngu)001:6099: ngag tu h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces brjod cing dgrol ba ni brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6100: shes rab la thabs kyis rgyas 'debs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6101: yum gyi phyag rgya ni mi bskyod pa'i g.yon phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:6102: kyi 'phang du yum dbyings phyug ma bsgom pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:6103: phyag chen / lag g.yon gyi 'bru bzhi nang du
NK064(ngu)001:6104: sbas nas gung mo thugs kar bkan thabs su bsgreng
NK064(ngu)001:6105: ba ni bca' ba dam rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6106: m+aum mthing ga gung mo bsgreng ba'i rtse mor bsgom pa ni bsam pa chos rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6107: m+aum zhu ba las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra can
NK064(ngu)001:6108: 'od 'bar bar gyur pa ni bsam pa dam rgya
NK064(ngu)001:6109: / lag g.yas nyi ma la gnas pa'i 'bru lnga
NK064(ngu)001:6110: ma bcings pas yab kyi barla g.yas pa las kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6111: sems dpa'i steng du bzhag pa'i tshul gyis 'khril zhing
NK064(ngu)001:6112: dbu yab la cung zad btud de zhal 'dzum pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6113: mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal la blta ba'i tshul du
NK064(ngu)001:6114: bca' ba ni bca' ba las rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6115: de ltar bsgom pa ni bsam pa las rgya /
NK064(ngu)001:6116: de nas phyag rgya g.yon du bcas pa mdun du
NK064(ngu)001:6117: bsgyur nas g.yas su yab kyi thugs kar se gol
NK064(ngu)001:6118: gyi sgra dang bcas te m+aum d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai
NK064(ngu)001:6119: ces brjod cing dgrol ba ni brjod pa chos rgya
NK064(ngu)001:6120: ste thabs la shes rab kyis rgyas 'debs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6121: mdor na phyag rgya bdun po de'ang bzhir 'du ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6122: dam rgya dang las rgya gnyis la bca' ba dang bsam pa /
NK064(ngu)001:6123: chos rgya la bsam pa dang brjod pa gnyis gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:6124: su phye ba tsam du zad pas drug po dbye
NK064(ngu)001:6125: gzhi gsum du bsdus pa'i steng phyag rgya chen po
NK064(ngu)001:6126: bsnan pas bzhi'am / yang na lha sku sgyu ma lta bur gsal ba phyag chen /
NK064(ngu)001:6129: dgrol ba las rgya ste bzhi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6130: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK064(ngu)001:6131: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:6132: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:6134: de bzhin du rnam snang yab yum sogs rigs gzhan bzhi po'i phyag rgya yang /
NK064(ngu)001:6135: 'bru bzhi sbas nas sogs tshigs bcad brgyad de /
NK064(ngu)001:6136: bdag nyid rnam snang sogs rigs gang yin der gsal ba las /
NK064(ngu)001:6137: lag g.yas pa'i 'bru bzhi sbas nas rang rigs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6138: sor mo bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bcas
NK064(ngu)001:6139: shing / s+w+aa +aam h+aam bzhi rigs mthun gyi kha
NK064(ngu)001:6140: dog can sor mo bsgreng ba de'i rtse mor bsam
NK064(ngu)001:6141: pa las rang rang gi thugs phyag mtshan 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:6142: dang rin chen dang pad+ma dang ral gri rnams 'od
NK064(ngu)001:6144: g.yon zla brtul gyis yum gyi 'bru lnga sbas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6145: khu tshur gyis dril bu gsil zhing yum la 'khril
NK064(ngu)001:6146: ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos la brten pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:6147: // yang g.yon du rigs kyi yum gang yin gsal ba las /
NK064(ngu)001:6148: g.yon pa'i 'bru bzhi sbas nas rang rigs kyi sor
NK064(ngu)001:6149: mo bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bca' zhing
NK064(ngu)001:6150: / l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam bzhi rigs kyi kha dog
NK064(ngu)001:6151: can sor mo bsgreng ba de'i rtse mor bsam pa
NK064(ngu)001:6152: las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra can 'od 'bar bar
NK064(ngu)001:6153: / gyur cing / g.yas nyi ma 'bru lnga dang
NK064(ngu)001:6154: bcas pa ma bcings pas las te yab kyi barla
NK064(ngu)001:6155: g.yas pa'i steng du bzhag pas 'khril zhing yab la
NK064(ngu)001:6156: dbu btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis zhal la blta
NK064(ngu)001:6157: / gyur cing / ba ste / yab yum so
NK064(ngu)001:6158: so'i mthar sngags brjod cing thabs shes phan tshun rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:6160: gnyis pa sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6161: ut+pala klu shing sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6162: lag g.yas pa'i mthe bong ma gtogs pa'i sor mo
NK064(ngu)001:6163: gzhan bzhi la nyi dkyil re re'i steng du mdzub
NK064(ngu)001:6164: mo nas brtsams te thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi'i sa
NK064(ngu)001:6165: bon / k+sh+aim t+r+aam h+r+aim dz+rim dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6166: gsung gi sems dpa'i tshe mee th+l+him h+aum m+aum bzhi dgod /
NK064(ngu)001:6167: g.yon gyi sor rtse bzhi la zla dkyil re rer
NK064(ngu)001:6168: nang sems kyi yum bzhi'i sa bon h+aum t+r+aam h+r+ai
NK064(ngu)001:6169: +aam dang / phyi'i sems ma dzahh+aum bam hohbzhi bkod nas /
NK064(ngu)001:6170: sems dpa' sems ma gang yin gyi skur gsal ba
NK064(ngu)001:6171: las 'bru gsum sbas nas rang rigs kyi sor mo
NK064(ngu)001:6172: sbreng ba'i rtser sa bon so so yongs su gyur
NK064(ngu)001:6174: byams pa'i klu shing la sogs pa thugs phyag mtshan 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6175: de bzhin du sa snying gi rin chen myu gu /
NK064(ngu)001:6176: nam snying gi ral gri 'od 'bar ba /
NK064(ngu)001:6177: spyan ras gzigs kyi pad+ma dkar po /
NK064(ngu)001:6178: phyag rdor gyi rdo rje 'bar ba /
NK064(ngu)001:6179: sgrib sel gyi chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK064(ngu)001:6180: kun bzang gi rin chen snye ma ste yab brgyad dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6181: de dag gi yum sgeg mos gzugs mdzes gsal ba'i me long /
NK064(ngu)001:6182: m+aa les rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6184: n+airtisa gar mkhan mchog gi mtshan ma rnga yab nyid dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6185: de bzhin du push+pesa me tog gi phreng ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6186: bdug spos kyi mchod snod 'chang ba'i d+h+au pe ma /
NK064(ngu)001:6188: gan+d+he ma'i dri'i byug pa rnams 'od 'bar bar bsam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6189: la sogs zhes pa'i khongs nas sems dpa' brgyad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6190: g.yon zla brtul 'bru sbas kyis phyag mtshan dril bu
NK064(ngu)001:6191: bzung ba gsil zhing barla g.yon pa chos la brten
NK064(ngu)001:6192: thabs su bcas la tshul de dang yab kyi dbu
NK064(ngu)001:6193: rnams kyang yum la cung zad 'byo bar bsgom zhing
NK064(ngu)001:6194: / sems ma brgyad kyi lag g.yas nyi ma 'bru
NK064(ngu)001:6195: lnga ma bcings pas yab kyi barla g.yas las la
NK064(ngu)001:6196: brten pas 'khril zhing dbu rnams yab la cung zad
NK064(ngu)001:6197: 'dud pa'i tshul du bca' ba dang bsam pa'i mthar
NK064(ngu)001:6198: so so'i sngags dang bcas thabs shes phan tshun rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:6200: mdor na gong gi phyag rgya chen po sogs phyag
NK064(ngu)001:6201: rgya bdun ldan rigs lnga'i skabs bzhin du thabs shes
NK064(ngu)001:6202: gnyis med chos nyid dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:6203: // gsum pa sgo ba yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6204: sgo bzhi sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:6205: sgo bzhir gnas pa'i khro bo yab yum gyi phyag
NK064(ngu)001:6206: rgya ni sngar bzhin g.yas kyi sor mo bzhi la
NK064(ngu)001:6207: h+aum re dang g.yon gyi sor mor dzahh+aum bam hohbakoda
NK064(ngu)001:6208: nas lha so so'i skur gsal bas khu tshur las
NK064(ngu)001:6209: rang rigs kyi sor mo bsgreng ba'i rtser sa bon
NK064(ngu)001:6210: so so las / gshin rje gshed kyi n+ri mgo gdengs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6211: stobs chen gyi rdo rje rtse lnga gnon thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6212: rta mgrin thod dbyug sbrul chen pos dkris pa gnon thabs su 'dzin pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6213: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rdo rje rgya gram las kyi mtshan ma gnon thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6214: yum bzhir thod khrag tu gyur par bsam zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:6215: de ltar sgo bzhir gnas pa de dag kyang yab kyi g.yon rnams sdigs mdzub dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6216: yum gyi g.yas rnams rim par lcags kyu dang zhags
NK064(ngu)001:6217: pa dang s+pho ta ste lcags sgrog dang hohzhesa dgyes
NK064(ngu)001:6218: pa skyed byed dril bu 'dzin pas phan tshun dbu
NK064(ngu)001:6219: 'dud pa dang 'byo ba'i tshul gyis yab yum 'khril
NK064(ngu)001:6220: ba'ang gong du bshad ma thag pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:6221: bzhi pa thub drug gi phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6222: thub drug sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6223: thub pa drug gi phyag rgya ni gdul bya ma nges pa 'dul ba'i phyir sna tshogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:6224: 'on kyang rigs mdor bsdus na phyag rgya drug tu 'du ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6226: pi wam go cha gseg par sgrom //
NK064(ngu)001:6227: pusti me chur shes par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:6228: zhes pas k+r+aim trum sogs kyi sa bon las phyag
NK064(ngu)001:6229: mtshan de dag thugs kar 'dzin par bsam pa yin
NK064(ngu)001:6230: no // 'dir thub drug la thabs shes zung 'brel
NK064(ngu)001:6231: gyis mnyes par byed pa'i phyag rgya med dam snyam
NK064(ngu)001:6232: no // na / dmigs bcas rtags kyi yum med
NK064(ngu)001:6233: kyang 'dir ni dmigs med chos kyi dbyings kyi yum
NK064(ngu)001:6234: dang 'du 'bral med pas mnyes par byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:6235: lnga pa kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6236: kun bzang sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6237: byed pa po kun bzang phyag g.yas pa steng du
NK064(ngu)001:6238: bkod pa'i mnyam bzhag las ye shes lnga'i 'od zer
NK064(ngu)001:6239: 'phro ba / yum bya ba mo de las 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:6240: te phyag g.yon steng du bkod pa'i mnyam bzhag mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:6241: 'phro ba / cing / bzhugs thabs yab rdzogs pa rdor skyil dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6242: yum pad+mo'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6243: de las gzhan yang yum gyi phyag rgya'i bye brag
NK064(ngu)001:6244: ni chos nyid cir yang mi 'gag pas gcig tu
NK064(ngu)001:6245: ma nges par sna tshogs su snang ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6246: de yang ji ltar na de bzhin gshegs pa yab
NK064(ngu)001:6247: kun bzang ltar las ma 'gyur ba'i mnyam bzhag nyid
NK064(ngu)001:6248: dam / yang na rdo rje thal mo thugs kar sbyar ba nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:6250: rkang pa phyi ma gsum po phyag rgya spyi'i rnam grangs bsdu ba'i don du mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:6251: gdul bya'i dbang gis rigs so sor bsgrub na de
NK064(ngu)001:6252: dag gi phyag rgya rigs de dang de'i phyag mtshan
NK064(ngu)001:6253: gyi rnam par bstan pa sogs ma nges pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:6254: / yang na lha so so'i phyag rgya mi nus
NK064(ngu)001:6255: pas bsdus pa la dga' na de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:6256: rigs lnga so so'i phyag rgya'am spyi'i dam rgya sngar
NK064(ngu)001:6258: de'ang mi nus na rdo rje thal mo 'ba' zhig bcas pas kyang rung zhes bzhed do //
NK064(ngu)001:6259: gsum pa lta ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6260: phyag rgya chen po'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6261: rtog tshogs thams cad phyag rgya chen po snang stong
NK064(ngu)001:6262: dbyer med lha sku sgyu ma lta bu'i rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:6263: gsum gyi rol par snang ba'i tshogs mchog ni srid
NK064(ngu)001:6264: zhi'i mtha' 'gog byed thabs dang shes rab dbyer mi
NK064(ngu)001:6265: phyed pa ste / yul med rang gsal zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:6266: gi don zab mo de rtogs pa'i blo dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:6268: lus ma bskyod cing yan lag ma bsgul yang ci
NK064(ngu)001:6269: byas cir snang thams cad kun lha sku phyag rgya
NK064(ngu)001:6270: chen po'i ngang du gnas pa las mi 'da' bas
NK064(ngu)001:6271: lag pa bsgyur pa sogs bcos ma'i phyag rgya nges
NK064(ngu)001:6272: par 'ching dgos pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:6273: bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas la gnyis te //
NK064(ngu)001:6274: snang ba rnam 'byed la ji ltar bslab pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6279: bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6281: yan lag sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6282: yan lag gi bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6283: de yang yab kyi rtog pa'i gnas su yab bcu bdun thub drug dang bcas pas nyer gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:6284: yam gyi rtog pa'i gnas su yum bcu bdun 'god do //
NK064(ngu)001:6286: bdag nyid mi bskyod par gsal ba'i dbu la rnam snang /
NK064(ngu)001:6289: rkang pa g.yon la mtha' yas /
NK064(ngu)001:6291: mig rna ba sna lce bzhi'i g.yas kyi cha'i rtsa la rim par sa snying /
NK064(ngu)001:6300: lag mthil g.yas su gshin rje gshed //
NK064(ngu)001:6302: rkang mthil g.yon par rta mgrin /
NK064(ngu)001:6305: dpung pa'i sta zur la lha min /
NK064(ngu)001:6309: gsang gnas su dmyal pa'i thub pa rnams dgod do //
NK064(ngu)001:6310: de bzhin du yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma'i yan
NK064(ngu)001:6311: lag lnga la spyan ma dang bzang mo sogs yum
NK064(ngu)001:6312: lnga / mig sogs bzhi'i g.yas par sgeg sogs yul gyi lha mo bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6313: g.yon par d+h+au pe ma sogs dus kyi lha mo bzhi /
NK064(ngu)001:6314: rkang lag gi mthil rnams su sgo ma bzhi rnams go rim yab ltar dgod de /
NK064(ngu)001:6315: yab yum bsdoms pas yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu
NK064(ngu)001:6316: ni rags pa dang phyir gnas pa'i cha nas thabs
NK064(ngu)001:6318: de ltar thabs lha bzhi bcu po de rnams so
NK064(ngu)001:6319: so'i srog gi gor rang nyid 'dra ba'i yan lag
NK064(ngu)001:6320: gi lha ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan
NK064(ngu)001:6321: spangs pa tshon gang ba re re spros te bsgom
NK064(ngu)001:6323: nang na gnas pa'i cha nas shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6324: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa lha
NK064(ngu)001:6325: gnyis la bkod pa'i thabs lha bzhi bcu po re
NK064(ngu)001:6326: re la'ang sku gsung thugs byin rlabs kyi lha gsum
NK064(ngu)001:6327: gsum 'phro bas brgya nyi shur 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:6328: thabs kyi lha dang byin rlabs kyi lha bsdoms pa
NK064(ngu)001:6329: brgya drug cu po re re la'ang rang rang gi
NK064(ngu)001:6330: rigs kyi bdag pos gtso byas pa'i dbu rgyan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6331: lha lnga lnga ste brgyad bargya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6332: mdor na thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu /
NK064(ngu)001:6333: shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu /
NK064(ngu)001:6334: sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya nyi shu /
NK064(ngu)001:6335: dbu rgyan gyi lha brgyad brgya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6336: kun dril bas rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la yan
NK064(ngu)001:6337: lag dang lhag pa'i lha stong bsgom pa ni sangs
NK064(ngu)001:6338: rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6340: de ltar ldan pa'i sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6341: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor de dag gang la
NK064(ngu)001:6342: ji ltar ldan pa'i lha gtso mchog mi bskyod pa
NK064(ngu)001:6344: lha gzhan rnams la'ang rigs 'gre shes par bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:6345: khyad par gang rtsa lhar song ba'i yab yum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6346: rtog pa'i gnas su kun bzang yab yum 'god pa
NK064(ngu)001:6348: de ltar nges par byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:6350: rgyal mchog kun tu bzang po yab yum ste zung
NK064(ngu)001:6351: lnga la'ang sngar bkod pa ni de bzhin du brtsis
NK064(ngu)001:6353: sems dpa' brgyad dang sgo skyong bzhi ste yab yum zung bcu gnyis la stong tsho bcu gnyis /
NK064(ngu)001:6354: thub drug la yum med pas g.yas kyi cha la yab nyi shu rtsa gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6355: g.yon gyi cha la yum bcu bdun po rnams rkang
NK064(ngu)001:6356: lag gi lha gnas de dang de'i rtsa'i mdun rgyab
NK064(ngu)001:6357: dang / phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum rnams
NK064(ngu)001:6358: dbang rtsa'i phyi dang nang du 'god pa'i nges pas
NK064(ngu)001:6359: thub pa drug re re la'ang stong tshang bas stong
NK064(ngu)001:6360: dang / tsho drug / de dag gi steng du gtso bo mi bskyod pa'i stong tsho gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6361: mdor na stong tsho nyi shu rtsa bzhi po thams
NK064(ngu)001:6362: cad kyang 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar bar
NK064(ngu)001:6363: bsgoms pa ni nyi khri bzhi stong gi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:6364: la bslab pa'o // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6365: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab ces te /
NK064(ngu)001:6366: stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong po de la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:6367: te snang 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin las su rung
NK064(ngu)001:6368: bas snang ba thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6369: dkyil 'khor rab 'byams bsam gyis mi khyab par gsal
NK064(ngu)001:6370: ba ni bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor la
NK064(ngu)001:6371: bslab pa'o // gnyis pa des don byed tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6372: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6373: don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus
NK064(ngu)001:6374: pa'i zhing khams bsam yas pa rnams su 'dul byed
NK064(ngu)001:6375: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo de ltar spros pas gdul
NK064(ngu)001:6376: bya 'gro ba'i don rnams mos pa bzhin du 'dul
NK064(ngu)001:6378: der ma zad theg pa mtho ba gsang sngags dang byang sems /
NK064(ngu)001:6379: dman pa nyan rang ste yang dag pa'i grub mtha' la zhugs pa thams cad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6380: phyin ci log gi grub mtha' la zhugs pa mu stegs byed rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6381: gang la'ang ma zhugs pa'i skye bo bsam yas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6382: de dag kyang lha sogs zhi ba'i rigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6383: bdud srin sogs khro bo'i rigs kyi gdul bya'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:6384: chen po thams cad la so sor mos pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:6385: mthun par byas pa'i 'dul byed kyi sku'i bkod pa
NK064(ngu)001:6386: kun tu snang bar mdzad na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:6387: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor las g.yos pa mi mnga' zhing
NK064(ngu)001:6388: rtsol rtog dang bral bas don mdzad pa ni dper
NK064(ngu)001:6389: na zlos gar mkhan nyid dang 'dra ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6390: gar mkhan de yang lus gcig po de las ma
NK064(ngu)001:6391: g.yos bzhin du rnam 'gyur gyi bkod pa sna tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:6393: lnga pa phyag rgya'i rnam grangs bsdu ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6394: mdor na phyag rgya sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6395: mdor na lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag gi phyag rgya thams cad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6396: rnam pa 'di kho na'o zhes sam /
NK064(ngu)001:6397: grangs gcig tu nges zhes brjod du med de /
NK064(ngu)001:6399: lus kyi yan lag gi dbang du gnyis dang gsum
NK064(ngu)001:6400: gcig tu bsdoms te yan lag lnga po re re'ang
NK064(ngu)001:6401: rigs lnga yab yum bcu bcur rnam par 'phro bas
NK064(ngu)001:6403: rtog pa'i yan lag gi dbang du thabs shes gnyis bsdoms pa'i lha brgyad cu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6404: rdo rje gsum du byin gyis rlob pa'i lha brgya nyi shu /
NK064(ngu)001:6405: de dag las kyang rnam par 'phro ba dbu rgyan
NK064(ngu)001:6406: gyi lha brgyad brgya ste sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:6408: de bas na lus kyi yan lag bskyod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6409: rtog pa'i yan lag spro ba'ang lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK064(ngu)001:6410: kyi phyag rgya'i de bzhin nyid las mi 'da' bar
NK064(ngu)001:6412: de dag kyang mdor bsdu na yan lag bsgul zhing
NK064(ngu)001:6413: lus bskyod pa ci snang ci byas thams cad kun
NK064(ngu)001:6414: rang bzhin ji lta bar rtogs goms kyis lha sku
NK064(ngu)001:6415: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas pa las mi
NK064(ngu)001:6416: g.yo zhing / de ltar gnas pa'i dus nyid na'ang der 'dzin med pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:6417: mi gnas pa'ang ma yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:6418: gnas pa'ang min te mtha' dang bral ba'i chos nyid
NK064(ngu)001:6419: do zhes de skad du spyod yul yongs su dag
NK064(ngu)001:6420: pa'i rgyal mchog ston pa nyid kyis bshad ces sdud
NK064(ngu)001:6424: rgyud 'di la le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:6425: 'dis lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag thams cad phyag
NK064(ngu)001:6426: rgya'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs nas rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:6427: lta ba ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi phyag rgya spros
NK064(ngu)001:6428: nas bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6430: // le'u dgu pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6436: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa
NK064(ngu)001:6437: de nas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ston
NK064(ngu)001:6438: pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa chos thams cad dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:6439: med blang dor dang bral ba zag med bde ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:6440: ye shes la dgyes pa chen por longs spyod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6441: bdag nyid kun tu bzang pos sku gsung thugs ye
NK064(ngu)001:6442: shes rdo rje'i gsang ba gsum thob par byed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6443: thabs las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dkyil 'khor dbang
NK064(ngu)001:6444: sgrub ste las kyi rim pa gsum du bkod cing
NK064(ngu)001:6445: / de nyid ston pa'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:6446: la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:6447: / brjod do // gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6452: sngon du slob dpon gyis bsnyen pa bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6453: dkyil 'khor gyi las rim dngos so //
NK064(ngu)001:6455: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:6457: yid dang mthun pa'i gnas su ting nge 'dzin gsum
NK064(ngu)001:6458: gyis khog phub nas yi ge dang phyag mtshan dang
NK064(ngu)001:6459: lha sku ste rdo rje gsum gyi phyag rgya shin
NK064(ngu)001:6460: tu phra ba'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i sgo nas
NK064(ngu)001:6461: mtshan dus grangs gsum gang rung gi bsnyen pa rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:6463: 'di ni gzhan don gnyer ba'i slob dpon gyis nges
NK064(ngu)001:6464: par 'da' mi rung ba'i dam tshig gi mchog ste
NK064(ngu)001:6465: gtso bo yin pas 'bad par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6467: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6468: des khro bo dang mchog gi dkyil 'khor mtshon par bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6471: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6472: tshon dang bri ba rnam pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6473: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6474: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:6477: sa gzhi mnyam pa spyir bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6478: go ma ye btang ba bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6480: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyam la //
NK064(ngu)001:6482: skal ldan gzhug bya'i dkyil 'khor rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:6485: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor gsum du 'jug mi nus pa'i gang zag rnams /
NK064(ngu)001:6486: de las gzhan yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs te /
NK064(ngu)001:6487: der 'jug pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:6488: thog mar sa dang sar 'dzin gyi rtog pa rig
NK064(ngu)001:6489: pa'i dbyings su mnyam par bya ba'i phyir sa gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:6490: sa'i cho gas rab tu mnyam par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6492: gzhi dang rang mtshan bslang dbang dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6493: sbyang byin bsrung dang bzung ba ni //
NK064(ngu)001:6494: dang po nyid la nyid du bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:6496: sa der dkyil 'khor rung mi rung brtag pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:6497: spyir gnam sa bar gsum gyi dpyad de sa'i gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:6498: la brtag pa / bye brag tu sa rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag cing /
NK064(ngu)001:6499: brtags pas rung bar mthong na snang ba sa'i bdag po la rin 'jal ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6500: mi snang ba dkyil 'khor gyi lha la 'dod don
NK064(ngu)001:6501: gsol zhing sa bdag 'khor dang bcas par bden pa
NK064(ngu)001:6503: gzhi der dbang mchog gi phur bu gdab pas dbang du bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6504: lto 'phye ston gsum mgo shar du blta ba sogs
NK064(ngu)001:6505: g.yas bskor gyi gnas lugs shes pas lto ba'i thad
NK064(ngu)001:6506: nas brkos la / chu sa'i sgo nas pra brtag cing gter bcug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6507: stegs bu dbus bgas kyis mtho zhing shar dang byang
NK064(ngu)001:6508: yid tsam gzhol ba brtsigs pa la ba byung dang
NK064(ngu)001:6509: rdzas sum cus skyang nul bya ba rnams ni las
NK064(ngu)001:6511: gzhan yang zhi ba'i me dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6513: mtshan med stong nyid kyi ngang las mtshan bcas gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:6514: der gzhal yas khang bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams
NK064(ngu)001:6515: kyis sa'i nyes skyon sbyang ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6516: de nas slob dpon rdo rje'i 'gros kyis shar sgo
NK064(ngu)001:6517: nas zhugs te dbus su gnas pas bdag nyid gtso
NK064(ngu)001:6518: bo yab yum du bskyod pa'i sems sprin las 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:6519: rnams spro zhing / mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba rnams mchod nas /
NK064(ngu)001:6520: yum bzhi'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa'i phyogs kyi slob ma
NK064(ngu)001:6521: bzhis slob dpon la mchod cing gsol ba btab rjes
NK064(ngu)001:6522: / slob dpon gyis rgyal ba rnams bskul zhing byin bsdus nas /
NK064(ngu)001:6523: rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje'i snyems pas 'bar ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:6524: spyan dang rdo rje'i 'gros kyis sa gzhi rdo rje'i
NK064(ngu)001:6525: rang bzhin du byin gyis rlob cing /
NK064(ngu)001:6526: khro bcu'i phur bu gdab pa dang mtshon cha lnga'i ra bas sa bsrung bar bya ba rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:6527: bzung ba ni 'og tu mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:6528: de dag ni nub dang po'i bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6530: 'bru lnga sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6531: phung po lnga sku lngar dag byed 'bru lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:6532: dbang po lnga phrin las lngar dag byed spos lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:6533: yul lnga yon tan lngar dag byed rin chen lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:6534: rnam shes lnga ye shes lngar dag byed snying po lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6535: 'dod yon lnga gsung lngar dag byed sman lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6536: khams lnga rigs lngar dag byed bdud rtsi lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6537: rdzas sum cu po nyid rab tu mnyam par sbyar
NK064(ngu)001:6538: ba'i lde gus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la go ma
NK064(ngu)001:6540: 'di nyid t+ai ka rnams su gzhung gi 'gros ltar thig gis khongs su bsdus na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:6541: rdo rje las rim ltar 'dir las dang bya bas sbyang ba'i khongs su sdebs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:6542: dkyil 'khor khang pa rnying pa lta bur ni thig dang sbrel kyang legs par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:6543: gnyis pa tshad la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:6544: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6545: dkyil 'khor khru gang sogs rkang pa gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6546: yang na khru ni sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6547: gnas khang dang 'byor pa'i khyad par las chung 'bring
NK064(ngu)001:6548: che gsum du 'gyur bas dkyil 'khor logs rer khru
NK064(ngu)001:6549: gang gi tshad du bya ba'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6550: yang na de bzhi 'gyur lus gang gi tshad du bya ste chung tshad gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:6551: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad de khru bcu gnyis pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6552: yang na khru ni bcu drug gi tshad gnyis ni 'bring tshad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6553: khru nyi shu'am yang na nyi shu rtsa lngar bya ba gnyis ni che tshad do //
NK064(ngu)001:6554: de nas mchog gi dkyil 'khor lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi tshad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6555: yang na rgyang grags sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6556: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal zhan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6558: rab gsum gyi dgongs pa'i khyad par las chung 'bring che gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6559: bris dkyil las gzhan yang na rgyang grags gcig gi tshad du bsgom pa chung tshad de /
NK064(ngu)001:6561: sor mo nyi shu bzhi la khru //
NK064(ngu)001:6562: khru bzhi la ni gzhu gang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:6563: de dag lnga brgya dag la ni //
NK064(ngu)001:6564: rgyang grags de la dgon par 'dod //
NK064(ngu)001:6565: de brgyad dpag tshad ces bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6567: 'bring dpag tshad gcig gi tshad dam /
NK064(ngu)001:6568: yang na rab kyi tshad nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam
NK064(ngu)001:6569: yas par khyab pa'i sangs rgyas stong dang nyi khri
NK064(ngu)001:6570: bzhi stong dang bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:6571: sogs sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba bsgom pa'am
NK064(ngu)001:6572: / lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan zhes
NK064(ngu)001:6573: grags pa dkyil 'khor dngos su sprul nas ston pa
NK064(ngu)001:6575: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor sogs //
NK064(ngu)001:6576: rdo rje'i thig tshad dor tsam gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:6577: rgyang grags la sogs mtshan ma yi //
NK064(ngu)001:6578: dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gsal ldan pa //
NK064(ngu)001:6579: ting 'dzin lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan yin //
NK064(ngu)001:6581: sngon sangs rgyas gsang bas mtsho ma pham la thig
NK064(ngu)001:6582: btab nas many+dzu sh+r+ai sogs la rdo rje'i dbyings kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6583: dkyil 'khor dngos su bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6584: slob dpon pad+mas stag tshang du mkhar chen bza' la
NK064(ngu)001:6585: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha' dang mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:6586: par bstan nas dbang bskur ba lta bu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6587: gzhan du sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes grags pa de'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6588: gang dag lhag ting gi tshad 'dir smos pa ni skabs 'chol lo snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:6590: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyis mtshon nas lhag pa ting
NK064(ngu)001:6591: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i phyir 'brel bas
NK064(ngu)001:6594: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:6596: phur bu sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6599: spyir mi 'gyur ba'i don gyis thig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6600: de'i rgyur 'gying bskor gyi phur bu gnyis 'du bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:6602: ye thig gi rgyu pad+ma'i rgyas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6603: dam thig gi rgyu ras bal 'jam po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6605: gos rgyan bzang pos mdzes par brgyan pa'i mtshan ldan
NK064(ngu)001:6606: yid du 'ong ba'i grogs phyag rgya lo bcu drug
NK064(ngu)001:6610: sbom phra sgo yi nyi shu cha'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6612: tshon gyis kha dog so sor phye ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6613: ye shes kyi thig skud kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am lnga sgril dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6614: dam tshig gi thig skud kha dog dagu'am sum sgril lo //
NK064(ngu)001:6616: ye thig gdab pa'i srad bu ye shes lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6617: dam tshig gi thig skud sku gsung thugs kyi ngo
NK064(ngu)001:6618: bor byin gyis rlob pa'i cho ga rigs mthun gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6619: yig 'brur bskyed pa la mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba
NK064(ngu)001:6620: rnams sbyor ba'i byin bsdu zhing bstim pa la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:6623: thig g.yog rig ma dngos sam der mos pa la
NK064(ngu)001:6624: thig sna gtad de yab yum lhar gsal bar byas
NK064(ngu)001:6625: pas dam tshig gi thig sku gsung thugs kyi rang
NK064(ngu)001:6626: bzhin can du btab pa'i steng du ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6627: thig ni mkha' la btab pas sku gsung thugs re
NK064(ngu)001:6628: re'ang ye shes lnga lnga'i rang bzhin du rgyas gdab
NK064(ngu)001:6629: par bya ba'o // nyes pa spangs pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6630: dkyil 'khor gyi las la mkhas pas lag len dang
NK064(ngu)001:6631: ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon chen pos rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:6633: thig skud ma chad cing thig sna ma shor ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6636: thig la mi 'gom pa'i sgo nas gdab cing /
NK064(ngu)001:6637: gal te 'gom dgos na h+r+aih'i sgra dang 'degs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6638: rgyas thig mkha' la bteg pa'i 'og tu 'dzul nas
NK064(ngu)001:6639: las bya'o // bzhi pa tshon ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6640: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK064(ngu)001:6642: ma mthong sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6645: ye shes lngas 'gro ba kun la khyab kyang de'i
NK064(ngu)001:6646: don ma mthong ba'i rmongs pa rnams la rang gnas
NK064(ngu)001:6647: kyi don bstan par bya ba'i phyir tshon kha dog
NK064(ngu)001:6650: 'byor pa rab kyis rin chen sna lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6651: 'bring gis 'abru'am sman kha dog bsgyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6652: tha mas sa tshon kha dog lnga la bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6654: kha dog rgyas par na rigs re re'ang lnga lngar phye bas nyi shu rtsa lnga'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6655: yang na kha dog lnga yi grangs su bsdus kyang rung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:6657: sa bon phyag mtshan las rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thabs shes zung 'brel lnga'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6658: rgyas par na so so'i rigs chung dang bcas pas
NK064(ngu)001:6659: lha lnga bcu rnams bsgoms pa zhu ba las rin
NK064(ngu)001:6660: po che'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsam pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:6662: lag sor la dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod nas dang
NK064(ngu)001:6663: por slob dpon gyis 'gying phur btab pa'i shul du
NK064(ngu)001:6664: tshon sna lngas rkang rjes shar du blta bas g.yon
NK064(ngu)001:6665: pa'i khu tshur gyis dbang ldan nas brtsams te pany+tsa
NK064(ngu)001:6666: re kh+aa sgo tshad gcig gi tshad du bri bar
NK064(ngu)001:6667: bya zhing / pra brtag pa'i don du de la ka p+aa la bkab ste bzhag nas /
NK064(ngu)001:6668: slob bu rnams dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang
NK064(ngu)001:6669: gis 'dul ba'i cho ga ste de'i lugs bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:6670: bag dang ldan pas dgye bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6671: de ltar yang rnam snang sgyu d+r+wa las /
NK064(ngu)001:6672: tshon ni nang nas bkye bar bya //
NK064(ngu)001:6673: phyi rol nas ni tshon mi dgye //
NK064(ngu)001:6674: dang po byang shar nas brtsams te //
NK064(ngu)001:6675: thog mar slob dpon nyid kyis bkye //
NK064(ngu)001:6676: de nas slob mas bya bar bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:6679: tshon ha cang mthug pa'am srab pa /
NK064(ngu)001:6680: tshon thal shor ba sogs spyi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6686: mi gsal ba sogs 'dug na ngan pas bsal ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6688: lte ba rtsibs dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6689: dbus kyi lte ba zlum po'i mthar 'khor lo rtsibs
NK064(ngu)001:6690: bzhi rtsibs rten mu khyud dang ldan pa'i phyi rol
NK064(ngu)001:6692: dbyibs gru bzhi'i rnam pa sgo bzhi sgo khyud can
NK064(ngu)001:6693: rta babs snam bu brgyad pa phyi rol du pad
NK064(ngu)001:6694: rdor me'i khor yug dang ldan par bya ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:6695: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum ka'i thun mong ba
NK064(ngu)001:6696: ste / khyad par rgyas pa ltar na dbus kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6697: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i gnas
NK064(ngu)001:6698: lngar rtsibs bzhi pa'i 'khor lo chung ba mu khyud
NK064(ngu)001:6699: dang bcas pa re res mtshan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6700: rgyas 'bring gnyis la gru chad kyi phyir bar khyams dang ldan pa bri zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:6701: bsdus pa la ni khyams med pa'i phyir gru chad la sgo dod pa'i rnam pa can no //
NK064(ngu)001:6702: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6704: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas so sor rten tsaka li lta bu bris 'bur ram /
NK064(ngu)001:6705: med na tshon gyis bri ba'i rjes 'brel du sku phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6706: gsung tha ta'am h+aum m+aum sogs sa bon dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6707: thugs phyag mtshan nam rang mdog mtshungs pa'i thig le
NK064(ngu)001:6708: 'bri ba sogs mtshan ma gsum gang rung dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:6709: pa'i gzugs kyi rnam pa'ang ci nus dgod par bya'o
NK064(ngu)001:6710: // bdun pa rab gnas la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6711: nub gnyis pa'i las rim gzhung bshad kyi dbang du 'brel sdebs nas 'dir bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6712: skabs thob kyi las rim dkyil 'khor rab gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:6715: yan lag can gyi lhag gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:6717: khro bo mi 'chi thab sbyor bskyed bzlas zhu ba'i sgo nas thog mar las bum sgrub ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6718: gnas bya thams cad la bsangs gtor bya ba'i ched du'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6719: de dang rjes 'brel du rdor dril /
NK064(ngu)001:6720: thod chu sngar bshad pa'i thig tshon rab gnas rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:6726: rnam rgyal bum par dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo yongs
NK064(ngu)001:6727: rdzogs bskyed bzlas 'od zhus bum chu nus ldan du
NK064(ngu)001:6729: khrus dang sems bskyed nas gnang ba byin cing spro ba bskyed /
NK064(ngu)001:6730: bgegs dang sgrib pa phral ba sngon du 'gro bas
NK064(ngu)001:6731: slob ma lhar bskyed cing bskur rlob go bgo lus
NK064(ngu)001:6732: bsrung rnams byas la so shing dor /
NK064(ngu)001:6735: sku sha gsum byin zhing gegs brgyad bshad de /
NK064(ngu)001:6737: gal te ngan na sngags rgya dang mes sbyang ba rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:6740: sa bzung ba zhes gsungs pa de yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:6741: las thig rdzogs pa'am skya thig tsam gdab pa gang
NK064(ngu)001:6742: rung gi lha gnas nges par byas nas gzhal yas
NK064(ngu)001:6743: khang bsgoms rjes / lha gnas rnams su byang sems
NK064(ngu)001:6744: kyi thig le tshom bu dang bcas pa so so'i
NK064(ngu)001:6746: rang gtso bo yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:6747: 'khor gyi lha thams cad spros la dbang nas bstod
NK064(ngu)001:6748: pa'i bar byas rjes snyan gsan phab ste rol pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:6749: gzi byin gyis de nyid du thim par mos pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:6750: // gnyis pa dkyil 'khor rab gnas la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6751: las khrigs kyi sdebs bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6753: dang po la don dgu las /
NK064(ngu)001:6754: dang po sngon du bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6755: slob dpon gyis bum bsnyen bya zhing bum chu bsdu ba /
NK064(ngu)001:6757: gnas bya'i gzugs brnyan la ba byung bku zhing shing shun gyis 'phyi ba sogs byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:6758: zhi ba'i las gzhung bsrang ba rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:6759: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyis sbyang zhing bskyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6760: gsum pa spyan drang zhing bstim pa gnyis le'u 'di nas bshad pa ltar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:6761: bzhi pa thur mas spyan dbye ba sogs dbang po'i skyon bsal ba'i chos bdun dbul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:6762: lnga pa thun mong du ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:6763: gyi bum chus dbang bskur zhing sku gsung thugs byin
NK064(ngu)001:6764: gyis brlabs nas / khyad par dbu rgyan sogs rgyan chas nyi shu rtsa lngas mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6765: drug pa chu bdun gyis khrus gsol zhing ras kyis 'phyi ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6766: bdun pa mchod pa phyi nang lhag ting gsang mchod rnams 'di nas bshad pa ltar dbul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:6767: brgyad pa 'dod don ma rdzogs kyi bar brtan bzhugs gsol ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6768: dgu pa bskor ba dang smon lam gdab pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:6769: te rab gnas kyi cho ga las shes par bya'o
NK064(ngu)001:6770: // gnyis pa gzhung don bshad pa la drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6772: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:6773: rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:6774: de ltar sbyangs shing bskyed pa'i yon tan /
NK064(ngu)001:6775: ye shes pa drang zhing gzhug pa /
NK064(ngu)001:6778: bcos bu'i sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6779: bcos bu ste kha dog bsgyur ba'i ras la dbyibs
NK064(ngu)001:6780: ni bla re 'phan gdugs lda ldi sogs sna tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:6781: pa dang / rin po che'i rgyan phreng dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6782: btung ba dang bza' ba bro mchog ldan pas kyang yongs su bskor zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:6783: gzhan yang thun mong ma yin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan bkod dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6784: khrus chas sogs rab gnas kyi yo byad /
NK064(ngu)001:6785: thun mong du phyi nang gi mchod gtor sogs bkod legs par bshams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6787: lus ngag sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6788: rang gi lus ngag sems gsum dang gnas bya'i rten
NK064(ngu)001:6789: gyis mtshon pa'i phyi nang gi chos thams cad sems
NK064(ngu)001:6790: kyi snang ba las gzhan gang na'ang mi gnas shing
NK064(ngu)001:6791: cir yang mi dmigs pa'i ngang las med bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:6792: rang snang ba mi g.yor lta bu'i tshul du mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:6793: par sbyor bas yul chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu
NK064(ngu)001:6794: la yul can rig pa ni ro gcig tu 'dres
NK064(ngu)001:6795: pas yul med rang gsal nam mkha' ltar mtha' bral
NK064(ngu)001:6796: du bsgom zhing sh+au nya t+aa'i sngags kyis nga rgyal
NK064(ngu)001:6798: ting 'dzin rol mo sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6799: stong nyid kyi ngang las ting 'dzin gyi rtsal cir
NK064(ngu)001:6800: yang ma 'gags pa'i rol mo mtha' yas mchog dang
NK064(ngu)001:6801: ldan pas rang gi thugs ka nas spros pa'i sa
NK064(ngu)001:6802: bon las 'byung lnga rim brtsegs gzhal yas khang gdan
NK064(ngu)001:6804: der gzugs sku rnams stong nyid ye shes su gsal
NK064(ngu)001:6805: ba la bdag nyid lha yab yum sbyor ba'i byang
NK064(ngu)001:6806: sems tha ta sogs gsung yi ge'i 'khor lo'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6807: h+aum m+aum sogs snying po'i rnam par bton pa las skad cig gis bskyed pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6808: yang na yig 'bru rnams so so'i gdan la bkod
NK064(ngu)001:6809: de 'od zer spro bsdu bya'am ma byas kyang rung
NK064(ngu)001:6810: ste phyag rgya phra ba phyag mtshan las rags pa
NK064(ngu)001:6811: sku yongs su rdzogs pa'i lha gnas gsum du sku
NK064(ngu)001:6812: gsung thugs rdo rje'i lha dang ldan par bskyed cing
NK064(ngu)001:6813: byin gyis brlabs na dngos grub ya mtshan thun mong
NK064(ngu)001:6814: dang rmad po che mchog 'grub par 'gyur ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:6815: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6816: nam du'ang de las mi 'da' bar ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:6818: sa la sogs la sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6819: 'di ltar sa dang shing la sogs pa rgyu dman
NK064(ngu)001:6820: pa la sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:6821: byas pas kyang rnam grol 'bras bu'i rim pa gdul
NK064(ngu)001:6822: bya rang rang gi skal ba dang mthun pa thob
NK064(ngu)001:6823: par 'gyur na gzung 'dzin dag pa stong pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:6824: dang rol mo lta bu'i ye shes kyis sbyangs shing
NK064(ngu)001:6825: lhar bskyed pas 'dod pa'i 'bras bu thob pa smos
NK064(ngu)001:6826: ci dgos te / sems kyi de kho na nyid
NK064(ngu)001:6827: ye nas lha yin pa las gzhan pa'i lha sku
NK064(ngu)001:6828: btsal du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:6830: phyogs dus sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:6831: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK064(ngu)001:6832: pa'i bdag nyid chen po chos kyi sku cir yang
NK064(ngu)001:6833: mi dmigs pa thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spros bral gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6834: ngang la bzhugs pa las gzugs sku ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:6835: dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'dul ba'i mos pa ltar bzhengs
NK064(ngu)001:6836: pa thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:6837: gang du na rig pa rang snang dbyer med dam
NK064(ngu)001:6838: tshig gi dkyil 'khor la spyan drangs pa de nyid
NK064(ngu)001:6839: 'jug cing bstim pa'i mtshan nyid kyis dam ye mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:6840: par sbyor bas phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun nas don
NK064(ngu)001:6841: gnyis mthar phyin par gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:6842: sngon bsnyen pa'i smon lam gyi dbang gis 'gro don
NK064(ngu)001:6843: mdzad pa'i phrin las ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK064(ngu)001:6844: thugs rjes bzhengs nas byon pa dam tshig gi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:6845: 'khor la rab tu rdzogs par 'jug pa ni sangs
NK064(ngu)001:6846: rgyas thams cad 'di las 'da' bar mi mdzad pas
NK064(ngu)001:6847: nye bar 'brel bar gyur pa'i phyir dam tshig gi
NK064(ngu)001:6848: mchog ces bya'o // drug pa la gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:6849: dang po phyi nang gi mchod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6850: glu tshig sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste phyi'i mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang na bza' lhab lhub /
NK064(ngu)001:6851: nang sman gtor tshogs kyi yo byad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6852: ngag gi glu tshig lus kyi bro gar /
NK064(ngu)001:6853: rol mo ye shes sogs mchod pa'i sprin phung mtha' yas pa'i tshogs kyis rab tu mchod cing /
NK064(ngu)001:6854: rgyas 'debs ma sogs gsang yum bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6855: yid 'jo ba'i tshul can sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6856: phyi nang gi sems ma brgyad de lha mo bcu
NK064(ngu)001:6857: drug gis ji ltar 'dod pa'i skabs kyi las gang
NK064(ngu)001:6858: byed pa de bzhin du mchod do //
NK064(ngu)001:6859: gnyis pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6860: mchod pa'i phyag rgya sogs rkang pas dman pa'i tshigs bcad drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6861: yid sprul gyis ji ltar mchod pa las mi 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:6862: ba'i phyag rgya chen po ni rang sems kyi bkod
NK064(ngu)001:6863: pa yid bzhin gyi char 'bebs pa'i rin po che'i
NK064(ngu)001:6864: sprin tshogs ltar bsam mi khyab kyis mchod de /
NK064(ngu)001:6865: ji ltar na rang gi thugs ka nas sa bon
NK064(ngu)001:6866: so so spros pas snang grags thams cad mchod rdzas
NK064(ngu)001:6868: de yang b+h+r+aum las phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK064(ngu)001:6869: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnam par dag par
NK064(ngu)001:6870: rlob ste / de'i yon tan yang mnyen 'jam reg
NK064(ngu)001:6871: na bde ba dang ldan pa'i rang bzhin rgyu sna
NK064(ngu)001:6872: tshogs rin po che'i sa gzhi khod snyoms pa la
NK064(ngu)001:6873: mig mang ris su mdzes par bris shing rin po
NK064(ngu)001:6874: che'i phra tshom gyis spras pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6875: t+r+aam las ri dang ri bran thams cad 'dod rgu
NK064(ngu)001:6876: kun 'byung ba'i rin chen gyi phung po 'od 'bar
NK064(ngu)001:6878: a las rgya mtsho dang lteng ka sogs kha dog
NK064(ngu)001:6879: dang dbyibs legs pa'i rdzing bu ro bro ba'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:6880: bsil zhing dwangs pa sogs yan lag brgyad ldan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6882: b+h+r+aum las gnas khang thams cad rgyu rin chen las
NK064(ngu)001:6883: grub pa'i khang pa rgyan dang bkod pa sna tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:6885: t+r+aam las rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad rin po
NK064(ngu)001:6886: che'i rgyan dang dar gyi lda ldis sbrel ba'i lha'i
NK064(ngu)001:6887: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing rgyas pa'i tshal dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6888: h+r+aihls sgra thams cad snyan pa'i glu dbyangs dang 'phags
NK064(ngu)001:6889: pa mchod cing sems can la chos ston pa'i tshigs
NK064(ngu)001:6890: su bcad pa'i sgrar rang byung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6891: m+aam las gos thams cad bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs la sogs pa sna tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6892: t+r+aam las rgyan thams cad do shal dpung rgyan se
NK064(ngu)001:6893: mo do sogs rin po che'i rgyan gyi khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:6894: dang / a las longs spyod thams cad ro brgya
NK064(ngu)001:6895: ldan pa'i bza' ba dang bdud rtsi'i btung ba ro
NK064(ngu)001:6897: h+aum las 'gro ba kun kyang rang lus la ji
NK064(ngu)001:6898: ltar mdzes pa'i rgyan gyi khyad par gyis brgyan cing
NK064(ngu)001:6899: 'dod yon sna tshogs thogs pa'i lha dang lha mo
NK064(ngu)001:6900: zhing gi rdul snyed kyi grangs dang mnyam pas lus
NK064(ngu)001:6901: kyi bro gar dang ngag gi glu dbyangs la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:6902: pa bsam yas kyis phyogs bcu'i nam mkha'i mthar klas
NK064(ngu)001:6903: kyi khams thams cad yongs su bkang nas rgyal ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:6904: dkyil 'khor kun la re re zhing nas rgyas bar
NK064(ngu)001:6905: dbul te / ji ltar na skal ldan rnal 'byor
NK064(ngu)001:6906: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba'am gsal ba'i khyad
NK064(ngu)001:6907: par gyis dus rim gyis sam yang na cig car
NK064(ngu)001:6908: du spros te 'khor gsum mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings
NK064(ngu)001:6909: dang mnyam pa nyid du sbyor zhing snang srid thams
NK064(ngu)001:6910: cad gnyis med kyi ngo bor gnas su stob pa
NK064(ngu)001:6911: las mi 'da' ba mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por
NK064(ngu)001:6914: gsal ldan ma'am sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6915: las rgya shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gsal ldan ma yin na rang nyid kyis sam /
NK064(ngu)001:6916: mi ldan na yab kyis lhar bskyed cing mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs la /
NK064(ngu)001:6917: dper na 'phags pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis stong gsum 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:6918: rten gyi khams thams cad yungs 'brur gzhug cing chud
NK064(ngu)001:6919: pa'i tshul bzhin du yum gyi pad+ma'i sna rtse yungs
NK064(ngu)001:6920: 'bru tsam la rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK064(ngu)001:6921: cad tshang zhing ma 'dres par bkod pa la chos
NK064(ngu)001:6922: kyi dbyings nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs
NK064(ngu)001:6923: shing bstim pa thabs shes rol pa'i bde bas mchod
NK064(ngu)001:6924: do // des dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mnyes nas
NK064(ngu)001:6925: dngos grub ster bar 'gyur ba las mi 'da' ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:6926: dam tshig mchog gi bdud rtsi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6927: de ltar bde ba'i bdag nyid chen po yum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6928: mkha' dkyil mchod pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:6929: kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mnyes shing /
NK064(ngu)001:6930: de'i byin rlabs kyis srid gsum gyi 'gro ba thams
NK064(ngu)001:6931: cad la dga' ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:6933: der ma zad rnal 'byor pa rang nyid sgyu 'phrul
NK064(ngu)001:6934: d+r+wa ba ste thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i ting
NK064(ngu)001:6935: nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa yis 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:6936: phyogs bcu dus bzhir don gnyis mthar phyin par gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:6937: pa'i sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:6938: dang khams gsum gyi 'gro ba sems can rnams la
NK064(ngu)001:6939: thugs rjes gzigs pa'i ye shes mngon sum du gsal
NK064(ngu)001:6942: dbyibs dang kha dog sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6944: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6945: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:6946: zhes pas sa chog gi tshe mtshan ma ngan na zhi ba /
NK064(ngu)001:6947: rab gnas kyi tshe rgyas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:6948: dbang bskur ba'i gong du dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:6949: slob ma sta gon gyi tshe kun rmi ltas ngan na drag po bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:6950: de yang sbyin sreg rtsa bar /
NK064(ngu)001:6951: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6952: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6953: phur bu lha dus las rim dang //
NK064(ngu)001:6954: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:6957: spyir zhi rgyas gnyis bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:6958: dbang drag gnyis gnyan pa'i gnas su bya ba'am /
NK064(ngu)001:6959: bye brag zhi ba ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse //
NK064(ngu)001:6961: dbang chu bo 'dus pa'i sum mdo //
NK064(ngu)001:6964: las bzhi gang byed kyi sreg shing /
NK064(ngu)001:6969: gsum pa thab kyi rnam pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6970: 'khor lo rin chen pad+ma rgya gram bzhi'i lte ba
NK064(ngu)001:6971: la gnas pa'i thab khung dbyibs ni zhi bar zlum
NK064(ngu)001:6973: bzhi ka'ang rgyar khru gang dpangs su khru phyed pa bang rim gsum pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6974: kha dog ni dkar ser dmar mthing ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:6975: thabs so so'i dbus su mtshan ma ni zhi bar 'khor lo /
NK064(ngu)001:6977: dbang la pad+ma h+r+aih drag por rdo rje h+aum yig dang ldan par bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:6984: don gyi sems spyir bden pa dbyer med kyi lta
NK064(ngu)001:6985: ba rtogs shing byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pa
NK064(ngu)001:6986: / bye brag las so so'i kun slong stongs kyi sems ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6990: zhe sdang khros pa'i sems so //
NK064(ngu)001:6996: yul de dag gi ling+ga gnas yig dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:6997: bris te las dang mthun pa'i brub khung du gzhug
NK064(ngu)001:6998: go // bdun pa phur bu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:6999: rgyu dbyibs las dang mthun pa'i phur bu bzhi sogs la rim par grangs drug dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7003: rang rang gi brub khung gi kha khyer la bskor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7005: las sbyor gyi lha zhi khro gang la brten pa de'i gzhung yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:7006: sbyin sreg gi lha la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:7007: sbyin lha ni drang srong gi chas can ra skyes
NK064(ngu)001:7008: la gnas pa las bzhi gang yin gyi sku mdog
NK064(ngu)001:7011: zhi ba la rnam snang dang bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK064(ngu)001:7012: rgyas pa la rin 'byung dang rat+na /
NK064(ngu)001:7013: dbang la mtha' yas dang pad+ma /
NK064(ngu)001:7014: drag po la mi bskyod pa dang badz+ra he ru
NK064(ngu)001:7015: ka rnams kyis gtso byas pa'i zhi khro'i lha kun
NK064(ngu)001:7016: las gang yin gyi kha dog can du bskyed do
NK064(ngu)001:7018: zhi sogs rim bzhin lo dang zhag gi dbang du byas pa gnyis re ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7024: phyi rol du cha gsum btang /
NK064(ngu)001:7025: nang du las bzhi'i 'dug stangs kyis shis pa'i phyogs la kha bltas te /
NK064(ngu)001:7026: zhi khro gang byed kyi gzhung bsrang /
NK064(ngu)001:7027: las bzhi so so'i 'dzab kyi 'phro 'dus thugs dam bskul /
NK064(ngu)001:7028: de nas tshogs tha ma dang sbrel te ling+ga la dgug bstim dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7029: so so'i bskul sngon 'gros gtor thun dbab cing phur bu gdab /
NK064(ngu)001:7030: mtshon char dbab gris gtubs nas sreg rdzas dang bsres la bzhag go //
NK064(ngu)001:7031: sbyin sreg gi las rim dngos ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7032: dper na kha zas kyis lus kyi 'byung ba rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:7033: pas de la der brten gyi dbang po dang rnam
NK064(ngu)001:7034: shes rgyas par 'gyur ba ltar me'i sgo nas me
NK064(ngu)001:7035: lha tshim pas / de'i sgo nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshim par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7036: me lha'i rang bzhin ni mchod sbyin gsol ba'i zhal
NK064(ngu)001:7037: du gyur pa zhes grags pas na thog mar 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:7038: rten pa'i me lha mchod par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7039: me sbar la thab nang du t+r+aam h+r+aihh+aum bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:7040: las gang byed kyi me lha bskyed cing bskur rlob dbab /
NK064(ngu)001:7041: dad pa dang ni sogs kyis bos la bstim /
NK064(ngu)001:7042: mchod sreg gi rdzas dang dgang blugs phul la smon lam gdab /
NK064(ngu)001:7043: de nas me lha'i lto bar las bzhi gang byed kyi sreg lha bskyed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:7044: bskur rlob dbab drangs bstim pa la mchod nas /
NK064(ngu)001:7045: bza' btung ro bro ba'i tshogs kyi sreg rdzas dang
NK064(ngu)001:7046: dgang blugs rnams las gang byed kyi tshogs las bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:7047: so so'i skabs dang sbyar ba'i mchod pa rab tu
NK064(ngu)001:7048: sbyin nas bden pa dang smon lam brjod cing bstod
NK064(ngu)001:7049: par bya'o // tshul des thog mar zhi ba'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:7050: 'khor mchod nas slar khro dkyil du bsgyur te sreg
NK064(ngu)001:7051: blugs sngar ltar phul rjes las gang yin gyi bro
NK064(ngu)001:7052: par bya'o // bya'o // bcu gcig pa lhag ma'i las ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7053: tshogs lhag dang sreg rdzas lhag rnams bsdus te lhag chog bya zhing brtan ma bskyang /
NK064(ngu)001:7054: lhag chad bskang la sreg lha dang me lha ye shes pa gshegs /
NK064(ngu)001:7055: dam tshig pa bsdu ba sogs las kyi rjes rnams mtha' rgyas su bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7056: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7058: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7059: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7060: bgegs bskrad lhar slob dam tshig sbyin //
NK064(ngu)001:7061: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7062: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7063: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7064: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7065: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK064(ngu)001:7067: zhes chos bco brgyad po rigs bsdus na gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7068: slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7069: slob ma 'jug pa'i chos bcu drug go //
NK064(ngu)001:7072: de ltar dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub kyi las rim kun
NK064(ngu)001:7073: byas nas dbang gis phyug cing dbang don shes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7074: rdo rje slob dpon rang nyid slob ma 'jug pa
NK064(ngu)001:7076: slob ma la dbang ji tsam bskur ba de cho ga rgyas bsdus ci rigs pas blang ba'am /
NK064(ngu)001:7077: yang na rig pa'i me tog dor ba tsam gyis kyang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i go chod cing /
NK064(ngu)001:7078: gang ltar yang slob ma 'jug par gsol ba gdab
NK064(ngu)001:7079: pa dang bzod gsol gnang ba nong pa rnams te
NK064(ngu)001:7080: / slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:7082: de nas slob ma sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7083: slob dpon zhugs pa de nas chos bcu drug gis slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7084: thog mar slob mas khrus bya /
NK064(ngu)001:7085: gnyis pa gdong bcings te snyim pa me tog gis bkang la gsol ba gdab /
NK064(ngu)001:7086: gsum pa 'dod don dri lan byas nas slob dpon gyi drung du drang /
NK064(ngu)001:7087: bzhi pa dus gsum gyi rgyal ba la lus dbul /
NK064(ngu)001:7088: lnga pa slob bu'i tshe bsrungs la bgegs bskrad /
NK064(ngu)001:7089: drug pa sgrib pa phral nas lhar bskyed de go bgo lus bsrung bya /
NK064(ngu)001:7090: bdun pa rdo rje gsum gyi dam tshig byin /
NK064(ngu)001:7091: brgyad pa dam tshig de nyid tshig gis dbab /
NK064(ngu)001:7092: dgu pa khe nyen gyi sgo nas chu nan bya /
NK064(ngu)001:7093: bcu pa skrag pa dang dogs pa med pa'i brtul
NK064(ngu)001:7094: zhugs kyis rmad du byung ba'i dam tshig gzhung bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:7096: bcu gcig pa lha dang las 'brel brtag phyir me tog dor /
NK064(ngu)001:7097: bcu gnyis pa me tog de spyi bor bcings la
NK064(ngu)001:7098: 'og min nas yi dam gyi lha bkug pa sngar
NK064(ngu)001:7099: chu nan gyi lha dang gnyis med du bstim pa
NK064(ngu)001:7100: ni phyi'i lha dbab pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7103: nang gi lha dbab pa ni gsang mtshan 'dogs shing lha'i sgom thabs ston pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7104: bcu gsum pa lha bsgom pa la nan tan byed par gdams pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7105: skal pa mnyam pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7106: de ltar dkyil 'khor zhugs phyin chad sgo gsum rdo
NK064(ngu)001:7107: rje gsum du byin gyis brlabs pas yi dam gyi
NK064(ngu)001:7108: lha dang skal pa mnyam par gyur pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7109: ye shes de nyid don du gnyer nas bsgrubs na
NK064(ngu)001:7110: dus nye ba tshe 'dir mngon du 'byung ba'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:7111: thun gyi dngos grub ya mtshan chen po nyid 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:7112: zhing thob par nges pas lha bsgom pa la nan
NK064(ngu)001:7114: gzhan du lha'i sgom bzlas la dad pa med na
NK064(ngu)001:7115: rdo rje gsung gi dam tshig nyams par gyur pas
NK064(ngu)001:7116: na 'di phyir mi 'dod pa'i gnas su ltung ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7119: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad cing lha ngo bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:7120: de'ang brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes su sngar song ba'i nang
NK064(ngu)001:7121: gi lha dbab pa dang nan tan byed par gdams
NK064(ngu)001:7122: pa gnyis skabs 'dir blangs nas mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:7123: bcu drug pa slob mas yon dbul te /
NK064(ngu)001:7124: de dag ni slob bu 'jug pa'i chos so //
NK064(ngu)001:7125: bcu pa dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7126: bde ba chen po'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7127: thabs shes zung 'brel bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:7128: rgyas pa 'bri ba'am mi nus pas ni gtso bo
NK064(ngu)001:7129: stangs dpyal te yum gnyis sam /
NK064(ngu)001:7130: yang na rigs lnga yab yum tsam gyis te dad
NK064(ngu)001:7131: ldan gyi slob ma der rab tu zhugs na dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:7132: 'khor rgyas par zhugs pa dang 'dra bar 'dod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7133: don dbang dang dngos grub yid 'ong thob pas na
NK064(ngu)001:7134: sngar 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:7137: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:7138: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yis //
NK064(ngu)001:7139: bsod nams rtag pa gang yin pa //
NK064(ngu)001:7140: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7142: gnyis pa des khro bo dang mchog gi dkyil 'khor mtshon pa bstan pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:7145: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:7146: 'khor las rim yang khog zhi ba'i skabs su bshad
NK064(ngu)001:7147: pa de bzhin du don bcus ston na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:7148: mi 'dra ba'i khyad par 'ga' zhig yod de /
NK064(ngu)001:7149: 'dir yi ge 'jigs pas khro bo'i dkyil chog ltar shes par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7150: gnyis pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7151: shin tu phra la sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7152: ting nge 'dzin gyi gnad shin tu phra zhing zab
NK064(ngu)001:7153: pa la blo sbyangs pa'i rnal 'byor pas bsam yas
NK064(ngu)001:7154: lhun grub sogs lhag ting gi dkyil 'khor dag la'ang
NK064(ngu)001:7155: bshad ma thag pa de bzhin du rnam grangs bcur
NK064(ngu)001:7157: de la sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7158: chos thams cad mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'am ji bzhin pa'i don la mnyam par 'jog pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7160: rgyang grags sam dpag tshad nas ji srid mkha' khyab
NK064(ngu)001:7161: kyi bar rang gi rig pas ji tsam dpag nus
NK064(ngu)001:7162: pa de tsam du bsgom pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7164: rang rig dkyil 'khor du gsal ba las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7165: tshon ni rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mtshon pa'i rang gdangs ma 'dres pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7167: sems kyi chos nyid la sku dang ye shes kyi
NK064(ngu)001:7168: dkyil 'khor ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gsal ba ste
NK064(ngu)001:7169: / rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa la'ang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7171: snang grags rig gsum rdo rje gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du ma 'gags par dgod pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7172: brten pa lha bskyed pa'ang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:7173: rab gnas ni ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs
NK064(ngu)001:7174: te bstim nas mchod pas 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi
NK064(ngu)001:7175: dbyings su sems rab tu bzhugs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7177: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgyar 'bar ba'am /
NK064(ngu)001:7178: 'od gsal lam gtum mo'i mes mtshan rtog sreg cing bde chen ye shes rgyud la sbyin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7180: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:7181: zhugs nas rgyun chad med par nyams su len pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:7183: sngon 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:7184: gnyis pa dbang la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7186: snod dang mtshams par bskur tshul /
NK064(ngu)001:7187: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7189: de nas rigs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7190: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa de nas rigs kyi bur
NK064(ngu)001:7191: byas pa dkyil 'khor mthong bas skal ba mchog tu
NK064(ngu)001:7192: gyur pa des me tog phog pa'i lha dang sbyar
NK064(ngu)001:7194: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs la rgyal srid de rang gi 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7195: rdo rje'i rigs la ni rang gi lus dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7196: pad+ma'i rigs la bu dang chung ma /
NK064(ngu)001:7197: rin chen rigs la gser dngul sogs nor gyi dbyig /
NK064(ngu)001:7198: las rigs la rang la gang yod kyi dngos po'i nang nas rab tu gces shos de dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7199: rigs drug pa la rang gi yid du 'ong zhing
NK064(ngu)001:7200: bla ma'i thugs la gang 'thad kyi dngos po ste
NK064(ngu)001:7202: yang na ma phye bar rgyal srid sogs rang gang
NK064(ngu)001:7203: la gces shing yid du 'ong ba de nyid dbul
NK064(ngu)001:7204: lo // de ltar dbang phyug la 'dod pa'i longs
NK064(ngu)001:7205: spyod lngas mchod na rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:7206: kyang mchod par 'gyur ba yin pas nye ba da
NK064(ngu)001:7207: lta zhugs pa'i dkyil 'khor de nyid mchod pa lta
NK064(ngu)001:7209: sangs rgyas thams cad rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:7210: la zhugs nas gdul bya'i mchod pa len par mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:7211: pa'i phyir dang / des nyams chag sogs nyes pa
NK064(ngu)001:7212: thams cad byang zhing dag par 'gyur ba'i phyir te
NK064(ngu)001:7213: pa'i phyir dang / / 'jam dpal zhal lung las /
NK064(ngu)001:7215: nga ni 'di yi lus gnas te //
NK064(ngu)001:7216: sgrub po gzhan la mchod pa len //
NK064(ngu)001:7217: de mnyes de yi rang gi rgyud //
NK064(ngu)001:7218: las kyi sgrib pa dag byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:7221: dad brtson sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7222: thog mar slob dpon gyis slob ma'i rgyud brtags pas
NK064(ngu)001:7223: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang gsum bskur rung gi snod
NK064(ngu)001:7224: ldan du rab tu rtogs na blo'i theg tshad dang
NK064(ngu)001:7226: de'ang slob bu dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu sbyin zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:7227: rang bzhan gyi don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7228: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba
NK064(ngu)001:7229: zab mo'i dbang gsum snod kyi rim pa bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:7231: gal te mi theg pa la sbyin na bu'i rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:7232: chud zos par 'gyur bas slob dpon gyis lhag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7233: snying rjes slob bu'i rgyud chud ma zos par rjes
NK064(ngu)001:7236: gang du dad dang brtson 'grus dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7237: brtul zhugs gsum dang ldan pa la //
NK064(ngu)001:7238: sa bon 'jug dang nus skyed nas //
NK064(ngu)001:7239: bde ba'i dbang ni rim bzhin sbyin //
NK064(ngu)001:7243: de la mtshan ma dgod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7245: spyir gsang ba sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs la dkyil 'khor rnam pa bzhir dbang lnga bskur bar gsungs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7246: de yang phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan du phan dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:7247: nang lus dkyil 'khor du nus dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:7248: gsang ba b+ha gar gsang dbang dang sher dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:7249: de kho na nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor du bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba las /
NK064(ngu)001:7250: 'dir ni gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor yab yum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:7251: mkha' gsang mtshon byed 'bur du dod pa'am bris pas
NK064(ngu)001:7252: kyang rung ste / sor bzhi pa'i pad+ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7255: shin tu phra ba'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7256: dkyil 'khor khru gang ba sogs la ltos na shin
NK064(ngu)001:7257: tu phra zhing mtshon byed rtags kyis mtshon bya mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:7258: dbyings bde ba'i ye shes kyi rgyur mtshon pa'i dam
NK064(ngu)001:7260: slob dpon lha sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7261: phyag mnyam bzhag gi mthil du thugs bde ba'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:7262: shes skyed byed kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa yum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:7263: mkha' de nyid mtshon byed pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK064(ngu)001:7264: bzhi pa tshad dga' bzhi mtshon pa'i sor ni bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:7265: yi tshad du bya ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7266: de nas rdo rje'i tshad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7267: yang na thal mo sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7268: de las gzhan yang rdo rje'i tshad ji ltar na /
NK064(ngu)001:7269: thal mo ni brda ste slob dpon yab yum gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:7270: kyi dbang po rab tu bsnol nas yab lha sku
NK064(ngu)001:7271: phyag rgya chen por gsal ba'i phang du yum blangs
NK064(ngu)001:7272: nas ni bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rten gyi
NK064(ngu)001:7273: dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i rdo rje mtshon byed rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:7274: sngon po rtse lnga pa mdzub gang ba'i tshad du'ang
NK064(ngu)001:7275: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bzo bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7276: gnyis pa mtshan ma dgod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7277: sen zlum sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7278: gsang dkyil gnyis kyi pad+ma'i lte ba dang 'dab bzhir sen zlum tsam gyi nyi dkyil dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7279: rdo rje'i rwa lnga la de tsam gyi zla ba
NK064(ngu)001:7280: la sran ma tsa na ka'i 'bru tsam gyi pad+ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:7281: gdan re re'i steng du yungs 'bru tsam gyi yi
NK064(ngu)001:7282: ge rdo rje la yab kyi 'bru lnga dang pad+mara
NK064(ngu)001:7283: yum gyi 'bru lnga bkod pa las lha'i phyag rgya
NK064(ngu)001:7284: til 'bru tsam du bri ba ste gsal gdab bo
NK064(ngu)001:7285: // ji ltar na mtshon byed rtags la bkod pa
NK064(ngu)001:7286: ltar mtshon bya yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:7287: gsang gnyis la thabs shes bsnol ba'i sgo nas dgod
NK064(ngu)001:7288: // par bya'o // gsum pa sgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7293: cho ga lnga ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7296: phyag rgya gcig pa phra rags gnyis /
NK064(ngu)001:7297: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi cho ga lnga ni sngon
NK064(ngu)001:7298: du rdzogs pa ste brtan pa thob par byas shing
NK064(ngu)001:7300: dam tshig lta ba ting 'dzin dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7301: byang chub sems dang snying rje ste //
NK064(ngu)001:7302: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs bya //
NK064(ngu)001:7303: zhes pa ltar lam gyi yo byad lnga'am /
NK064(ngu)001:7308: sbyor sgrol te sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7309: yid skyob pa dang byin gyis rlob pa'i phyir sngags
NK064(ngu)001:7310: te yan lag gi lha dgu'i dbu rgyan rigs bdag
NK064(ngu)001:7311: gcig gis bsdus pa'i gnad kyis gcig tu brtsis pas
NK064(ngu)001:7314: snying gar ye shes sems bsgom snying gar nyi zla'i dkyil //
NK064(ngu)001:7315: dam tshig phyag rgya bzhag ste de steng yig 'bru bzhag /
NK064(ngu)001:7316: zlos tshe spro bsdus bzlas pa sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK064(ngu)001:7318: de dag rdzogs par gsal ba'i rnal 'byor pas rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:7319: ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par
NK064(ngu)001:7321: zhugs nas nyams len la rab tu brtson par byas na 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7324: mthar thug sku lnga 'grub pa'i dus so //
NK064(ngu)001:7326: zhag ni sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7327: dbang po dang brtson pa yang rab kyis zhag ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK064(ngu)001:7328: rab kyis zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig /
NK064(ngu)001:7329: 'bring gis zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK064(ngu)001:7330: thams cad kyang zla ba bcu drug ste lo gcig
NK064(ngu)001:7331: dang zla ba bzhi rnams kyis dbang po rtul na
NK064(ngu)001:7332: rnam smin nam / rno na tshe la dbang sgyur
NK064(ngu)001:7333: ba'i rigs kyi dam pa ste lam mchog yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:7334: rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang rig 'dzin 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK064(ngu)001:7335: rnam smin nam / // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7336: de tshe sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7337: mthong lam la gnyis las nus thob tshe dbang rig
NK064(ngu)001:7338: 'dzin thob pa de'i tshe lo brgya brgya na phyir
NK064(ngu)001:7339: bsnur ba lan bcu drug ste stong drug brgya tshun
NK064(ngu)001:7340: chad kyis rim gyis pa phyag chen dang lhun grub
NK064(ngu)001:7341: rig 'dzin brgyud nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu la
NK064(ngu)001:7342: sbyor zhing thod rgal ba tshe dbang nas lhun grub
NK064(ngu)001:7343: rig 'dzin nam / shin tu blo chen lam gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:7344: ma brgyud par mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga
NK064(ngu)001:7345: lhun gyis grub pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par
NK064(ngu)001:7346: rig 'dzin nam / byed de / rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:7347: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK064(ngu)001:7348: brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:7349: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK064(ngu)001:7351: ji ltar 'grub pa'i tshul ni 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7352: gsum pa bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis te 'grub tshul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7355: 'grub tshal du rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7356: de dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7358: ye shes thig le sogs rkang pas dman pa'i tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7359: lam mthar chags kyi dbang du lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7360: thod rgal gyi dbang du tshe dbang gi dgongs par
NK064(ngu)001:7361: rig pa'i ye shes spros bral thig le de nyid
NK064(ngu)001:7362: kyi ngang la mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus su sangs
NK064(ngu)001:7363: rgyas kyi ye shes spros pa dang bral ba'i thig
NK064(ngu)001:7364: le de nyid rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7365: dgongs pa'i ngo bo ni blo'i yul las 'das pas
NK064(ngu)001:7366: bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:7367: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir mchog ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7368: de tshe phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir mngon par rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:7369: pa byang chub pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:7370: kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa yon tan bsam
NK064(ngu)001:7371: gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7372: zhing der rgya gang du'ang ma chad pas 'di tsam
NK064(ngu)001:7373: zhes bsam pa'i yul dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK064(ngu)001:7374: gzhi tshad med kyi ye shes kyi 'khor lo la
NK064(ngu)001:7375: brten pa'i bkod pa mdzes pa'i rgyan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7376: 'dod yon gyi rol mo'i sprin tshogs rnam par 'khrigs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:7377: de ltar rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor che ba'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:7378: ma lus zad pa med pa'i rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK064(ngu)001:7379: bsam yas par snang ba kun kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:7380: skad cig dang po mnyam bzhag gi gzigs ngor rang
NK064(ngu)001:7381: rig mngon sum gyis mthong nas skad cig gnyis pa
NK064(ngu)001:7382: rjes thob la nye bar brnyes pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7383: de thob pa dang gsung lnga yang lhun gyis grub
NK064(ngu)001:7384: pas ris su ma chad pa rgya chen po'i gsung
NK064(ngu)001:7385: gi snang ba las gdul bya'i don lhun grub tu
NK064(ngu)001:7386: 'byung ba'ang gzhi lam 'bras bu'i ye shes gsum tshul
NK064(ngu)001:7387: gcig tu gyur pas mthun pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o
NK064(ngu)001:7388: // de'i phyir gzhan du grub pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:7389: rig pa'i ye shes la rang snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7391: dpag bsam sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7392: dper na lha'i gnas sogs su dpag bsam shing gis
NK064(ngu)001:7393: grib mar gnas pa rnams kyi re ba skong nus
NK064(ngu)001:7394: pa dang / yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK064(ngu)001:7395: ches mchod pa byed pa rnams kyi re ba skong
NK064(ngu)001:7396: pa dang / nus pa dang / der ma zad
NK064(ngu)001:7397: gzhan yang 'dod pa 'byung ba'i gnas su gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:7398: pa dang / nus pa dang / kun snang yang
NK064(ngu)001:7399: / don de dag rdzas grub tu yod nas de
NK064(ngu)001:7400: la spyod pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7401: gzhon nu me skyes kyi rin po che'i khang bzang
NK064(ngu)001:7402: ma skyes dgra'i khang pa dang barjesa kyang kho rang
NK064(ngu)001:7403: gi phyi bzhin 'brang ba ltar rang rang gi sems
NK064(ngu)001:7404: kyi snang ba bsod nams kyi mthu brtas shing brtan
NK064(ngu)001:7405: par gyur pa nyid de lta bur snang ba yin
NK064(ngu)001:7406: no // de bzhin du 'bras bu 'grub tshul kyang de dang 'dra ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7407: gzhi ji lta ba mngon du gyur pas spangs thob
NK064(ngu)001:7408: med par sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ngo
NK064(ngu)001:7409: mtshar ba'i cho 'phrul chen po ya mtshan rmad du
NK064(ngu)001:7410: byung ba brnyes pa'i yon tan gyi chos de yang
NK064(ngu)001:7411: / lam pa nyid kyis phar bgrod nas der slebs pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:7412: gzhan zhig na yod pa tshur bkug nas 'ongs pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7413: thabs rang gsal 'gags med bde ba chen po la
NK064(ngu)001:7414: goms pa rab tu brtan par gyur pa'i rang rig
NK064(ngu)001:7415: pa'i ye shes nyid shes rab stong pa nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:7416: dbyings su grol ba'i zung 'jug de lta bu'i ngang
NK064(ngu)001:7417: du ma btsal bar rang byung du snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7418: gnyis pa 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7419: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes shing don byed nus par bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:7420: gcig du bral gyi don rang byung kyi ye shes su bstan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:7421: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya la gzigs tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:7423: shes rab dbyings sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7424: shes rab chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:7425: dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po nyid thabs
NK064(ngu)001:7426: lam gyi phyag rgya chen po goms par gyur pas
NK064(ngu)001:7427: snang zhen gyi 'khrul pa sangs pa'i don 'bras bu'i
NK064(ngu)001:7428: yon tan rnams rang gsal ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7429: bral 'bras tsam las lam gyis gsar du bsgrubs pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7430: gzhi'i ye shes de nyid la ni 'bras bu rang
NK064(ngu)001:7431: snang ba'i ye shes rol pa tsam du zad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7432: phyir ro // de ltar na 'bras bu'i snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:7433: de dag yod pa'i mtshan mar mi 'gyur ram zhe
NK064(ngu)001:7434: phyir ro // na / ye shes la ye shes rol pa nyid kyang dngos por ma grub ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7435: sgyu ma ltar gsog gsob ya ma barla'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7436: ye shes ci 'dra bar sku yang de 'dra ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7437: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten du mngon sum
NK064(ngu)001:7438: du 'byung zhing 'gro ba sdug bsngal las skyob pa
NK064(ngu)001:7439: dang / chos sku'i ngang las longs sku rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:7440: ba'i byin rlabs kyis brda'i chos ston pa'ang ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:7441: la brjod pa de bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7442: rang rig sku'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas bzhugs pa
NK064(ngu)001:7443: la 'bras bu'i sku rol zhing de nyid kyang rang
NK064(ngu)001:7444: bzhin med pa sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7445: 'o na sku dang ye shes des don byed mi nus pa zhig gam snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:7447: don bya ba'i yul la don byed nus pa'i thugs
NK064(ngu)001:7448: rje'i gzi byin mnga' ba'i phrin las kyis sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:7449: ye shes kyi rol pa gang la gang 'tshams su
NK064(ngu)001:7450: bstan nas sgyu ma lta bu'i phrin las kyis don
NK064(ngu)001:7451: mdzad cing / de lta na'ang ngo bo gzhan du 'gyur ba ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7452: sku lnga dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:7453: can gang gis kyang mi shigs pa'i nus mthu mnga'
NK064(ngu)001:7454: bas btsan po ste che ba'i mchog dam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7456: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba //
NK064(ngu)001:7457: rdo rje btsan po dam tshig mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:7458: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub che //
NK064(ngu)001:7459: 'gro ba kun la rab snang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7462: gcig dang du ma sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7463: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gzhan snang gzugs sku'i rol pa tha dad du ston pas gcig gi mtha' dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7464: ji ltar bstan kyang rang bzhin chos nyid kyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:7465: las ma g.yos pas du ma'i mtha' dang bral zhing
NK064(ngu)001:7466: / de ltos kyi gnyis ka dang gnyis ka ma yin pa'i mu yang med de /
NK064(ngu)001:7467: gcig dang du ma ma grub pas de'i mtha' khegs pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7468: yod med rtag chad la sogs pa'i mtha' dang de ltos kyi dbus kyang grub pa med de /
NK064(ngu)001:7469: brjod med de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su gshegs pas mtshan nyid med pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7470: sangs rgyas kyis kyang gzigs bya gzigs byed las 'das pas mi gzigs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7472: ji ltar mtshan nyid sna tshogs pa //
NK064(ngu)001:7473: de dag byis pa'i spyod tshul te //
NK064(ngu)001:7474: gang zhig mtshan nyid kun med pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:7475: sangs rgyas rnams ni mi mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:7477: de lta na'ang rang byung ye shes kyi dgongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:7478: ni gnas bya'i yul dang gnas byed kyi yul can
NK064(ngu)001:7479: gnyis med par rang gsal ma 'gags par thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:7480: du snang ba'o // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7481: log par sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7483: 'gro ba'i log par rtog pa gzung 'dzin gyis rnam
NK064(ngu)001:7484: par brtags pa'i sgrib pa de dag ye nas rnam
NK064(ngu)001:7485: par dag pas chos dang chos nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:7486: 'brel zhing / sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes kyang
NK064(ngu)001:7487: chos thams cad kyi chos dbyings las mi gzhan pa'i
