NK064(ngu)001:7488: phyir yul dang yul can rang bzhin tha mi dad
NK064(ngu)001:7490: sangs rgyas rnams sngon byang chub kyi spyad pa spyod
NK064(ngu)001:7491: pa'i tshe thugs rje chen pos sems can yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:7492: sgrol bar dam bcas pas las dang thugs rjer 'brel
NK064(ngu)001:7493: ba'o // de ltar 'brel ba gsum gyis 'brel bas
NK064(ngu)001:7494: na thugs rjes gzigs pa'i tha snyad gdags su rung
NK064(ngu)001:7495: ba'o // ste / gdul bya 'gro ba'i snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:7496: dngos po ma grub pas cir yang mi dmigs par
NK064(ngu)001:7497: gzigs pa ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang
NK064(ngu)001:7498: ba'o // ste / / rigs drug gi 'jig rten
NK064(ngu)001:7499: dus snga phyi dang gnas mtho dman sogs snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:7500: thams cad ma lus pa sa ler gzigs pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:7501: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK064(ngu)001:7502: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:7503: med par gzigs pa ni dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:7504: shes zhes bya'o // de skad ces ston pas ched du brjod par mdzad do //
NK064(ngu)001:7507: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:7508: 'dis rdo rje gsum thob byed las kyi rim pa
NK064(ngu)001:7509: gsum du bkod pa'i don mchog tu gsang ba 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:7510: daka'i dam tshig gi le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7512: // le'u bcu pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7518: dkyil 'khor du 'jig cing snod dang 'tshams par dbang
NK064(ngu)001:7519: bskur tshul mdor bstan pa de nas ji ltar bskur
NK064(ngu)001:7520: ba'i rim pa ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK064(ngu)001:7521: pa chen po chos kyi rgyal po'i go 'phang skal
NK064(ngu)001:7522: ba dang 'tshams par sbyin pa zhes bya ba'i ting
NK064(ngu)001:7523: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas dbang bskur ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7524: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK064(ngu)001:7525: gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7529: dang po dbang bskur ba'i rim pa 'chad pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK064(ngu)001:7530: spyir gsang bdag sgro phug pa chen po'i gsung rgyun snga phyi gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:7531: snga ma'i bka' srol 'dzin pa rnams dbang thams cad la /
NK064(ngu)001:7534: bskur thabs gsum du bsdus nas gsung na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:7535: phyis don brgyad brgyad du bsdus nas gsungs pa'i lugs dbang btsan du byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:7537: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7538: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK064(ngu)001:7539: zhes pa ltar don brgyad kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:7540: dang po rgyu la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:7542: rlung sems rtsa dang thig ler dbang bco brgyad rang chas su ldan pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7544: gnas brten rtsa dang thig le la //
NK064(ngu)001:7545: bcu dbang lnga gsum dbang rnams ldan //
NK064(ngu)001:7546: zhes pas phan nus gnyis la rang rang gi bstim gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7547: zab dbang gsum gyi lhag pa'i bden pa gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:7549: phan nus gnyis la dbang rdzas rab gnas can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7550: zab dbang la byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyag rgya ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7551: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:7552: dad brtson brtul zhugs gsum ldan pa'i rim pas phan
NK064(ngu)001:7553: nus zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur rung ba'i slob bu
NK064(ngu)001:7554: rgyu'i rkyen / dbang gsum bskur nus pa'i mtshan ldan gyi slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen /
NK064(ngu)001:7555: rdzas sngags ting 'dzin sogs 'dzom pa'i nus pa can dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK064(ngu)001:7556: dbang snga ma snga mas go phye nas phyi ma phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag rkyen no //
NK064(ngu)001:7559: ngo bo snod kyi mtshan nyid kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:7560: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:7563: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:7565: dper na mtshon la ngar btags pa ltar dbang bskur
NK064(ngu)001:7566: bas thob bya rang gnas kyi don mngon du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:7567: pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes pa'am sa bon tsam
NK064(ngu)001:7568: thebs pa ste / khog gzhung las /
NK064(ngu)001:7569: rno la ngar btags nus pa bzhin //
NK064(ngu)001:7570: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK064(ngu)001:7574: de rjes nus dbang dang zab mo'i dbang gsum snod dang sbyar te rim par bskur zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:7575: khyad par phan dbang gi 'khrugs sdebs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7576: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK064(ngu)001:7577: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK064(ngu)001:7578: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK064(ngu)001:7579: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK064(ngu)001:7580: drug pa dbang bskur ba'i las rim ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7585: rang skal gyi sgrib pa gang dag nas nus pa
NK064(ngu)001:7586: gang skye ba'i tshul rjes mthun smon lam dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:7587: pa ste / dbang re re la'ang lnga lnga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7588: bdun pa ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7589: brgyad pa thob pa'i yon tan gnyis kyi 'og tu ston no //
NK064(ngu)001:7590: da ni gzhung gi dkyus nyid la 'jug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7591: de yang dbang bskur ba'i rim pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:7594: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'i rim pa dang gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:7596: dbu rgyan sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7597: slob bu lhar gsal ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:7598: rin 'byung gi rab gnas can gyi dbu rgyan bskon
NK064(ngu)001:7599: la spyi bor rigs lnga'i dbang rgya 'ching zhing dbang
NK064(ngu)001:7600: rdzas tshogs brgyad kyi shes pa la bstim pas don
NK064(ngu)001:7601: ye shes lnga'i ngo bor dag pa'i rtags rigs lngas
NK064(ngu)001:7603: de bzhin du mtha' yas dang rdor sems kyis brlabs
NK064(ngu)001:7604: pa'i dar dmar mthing gi cod pan mgo bo'i g.yas
NK064(ngu)001:7605: g.yon du 'phur zhing dpyangs pa rtsa ro rkyang gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:7606: la bstim pas yon tan thams cad rdzogs shing gdug
NK064(ngu)001:7608: rin 'byung gis brlabs pa'i phreng ba mgor bcings shing
NK064(ngu)001:7609: thig le so gnyis la bstim pas gzungs dang ting
NK064(ngu)001:7610: 'dzin sogs 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs par dang
NK064(ngu)001:7611: / don grub kyis brlabs pa'i go cha lus la
NK064(ngu)001:7612: bskon zhing lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khebs pa la bstim
NK064(ngu)001:7613: pas rgol bas mi tshugs par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7614: rdor sems kyis brlabs pa'i rgyal mtshan lag tu gtad
NK064(ngu)001:7615: cing gsang ba'i dbang po la bstim pas log lta
NK064(ngu)001:7616: can zil gyis gnon par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7617: lha rang rang gis brlabs pa'i phyag rgya spyi bo'am
NK064(ngu)001:7618: snying gar bzhag cing so so'i rtog tshogs la bstim
NK064(ngu)001:7619: pas rtog pa lha'i ngo bor dag par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7620: mi bskyod pas brlabs pa'i gdugs spyi bor bzhag cing
NK064(ngu)001:7621: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo la bstim pas
NK064(ngu)001:7622: nyon mongs shing gdung ba las skyob par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7623: rigs lnga 'dus kyis brlabs pa'i bum pa'i chus spyi
NK064(ngu)001:7624: bor bskur zhing rtsa gnas thig les gang ba la
NK064(ngu)001:7625: bstim pas nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag nas ye
NK064(ngu)001:7626: shes lnga'i dbang thob par dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7627: rnam snang gis brlabs pa'i bza' btung khar byin zhing
NK064(ngu)001:7628: lce la gnas pa'i ro 'bab ma la bstim pas
NK064(ngu)001:7629: ye shes kyi snang ba 'dod yon gyi rol mor
NK064(ngu)001:7631: 'bras bu lngas brlabs pa'i snying po lnga spyi mgrin
NK064(ngu)001:7632: snying dang lte ba'i g.yas g.yon lnga'am mgor bzhag cing
NK064(ngu)001:7633: khams lnga'i bcud dam rdzas lnga la bstim pas khams
NK064(ngu)001:7634: lnga rigs lnga'i ngo bor dag par bsam zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:7635: de ltar phyi dbang bcu bskur bas ni 'di phyir
NK064(ngu)001:7636: phan pa'i sa bon tsam 'jog pa las da lta
NK064(ngu)001:7637: nas don gnyis sgrub pa'i nus pa so sor bzhag
NK064(ngu)001:7638: pa med pa'i phyir na phan dbang zhes bya ste
NK064(ngu)001:7639: / phyi dkyil 'khor drang don gyi bskyed rim rnams
NK064(ngu)001:7640: mnyan du rung ba'i skal pa can du byas so
NK064(ngu)001:7641: / // gnyis pa nus dbang lnga po rigs bsdus na gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7642: bdag don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan sgom /
NK064(ngu)001:7643: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la phrin las dang 'chad dbang /
NK064(ngu)001:7644: gnyis ka'i don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la rdo
NK064(ngu)001:7645: rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:7647: nyan dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7649: slob dpon rigs drug pa yab yum du gsal ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7650: sbyor mtshams nas slob bu'i mtshungs ldan gyi gnas so
NK064(ngu)001:7651: sor b+h+r+aum yig dmar ser spros pa las gzhal yas
NK064(ngu)001:7652: khang sgom pa dbang lnga ka la sbyar te /
NK064(ngu)001:7653: slob bu'i nyan byed rna ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsar
NK064(ngu)001:7654: b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa sgo dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:7655: pa'i gzhal yas su sgra gsal ba'i thig le shin
NK064(ngu)001:7656: tu dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa de
NK064(ngu)001:7657: t+r+aam yig zung lnga gsung chos kyi phyag rgya'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:7658: mchog las rin chen 'byung gnas rigs chung gi sems
NK064(ngu)001:7659: dpa' sgo skyong dang bcas pa'i lha yab yum bco
NK064(ngu)001:7660: brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bskyed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:7661: bskur rlob dbab drang bstim brtan mchod nas /
NK064(ngu)001:7662: slob dpon gyi sbyor mtshams nas spros pa'i 'od kyis
NK064(ngu)001:7663: bskul bas lha thams cad rjes chags kyis zhu ba
NK064(ngu)001:7664: slob bur thim pa'i rkyen gyis slob bu'ang 'od du
NK064(ngu)001:7665: zhu ba las rin chen 'byung gnas kyi skur bskyed
NK064(ngu)001:7666: pa la / glegs bam rin 'byung gi rab gnas can lag tu gtad de /
NK064(ngu)001:7673: gsang mchog a ti yo ga'i rgyud gang yin pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7674: der ma zad gsang ba sngags kyi rgyud sde gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:7675: kri yog sogs kun la'ang nyan par dbang bas mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:7676: par bya zhes gnang ba sbyin zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:7677: nyan nas gsang ba'i don nyid bsam pas brtag cing
NK064(ngu)001:7678: dpyod pa las gzhan 'chad dbang ma thob kyi bar
NK064(ngu)001:7679: de srid du su la'ang smra bar bya ba min
NK064(ngu)001:7680: pas ma ston cig ces dam tshig bsgrags nas /
NK064(ngu)001:7681: dbang rdzas rna ba'i thig ler bstim pas bka' phyi
NK064(ngu)001:7682: nang thams cad nyan pa la dbang thob par gyur
NK064(ngu)001:7683: pa'o // de nas sgom dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7685: dran pa gsal bar byed pa'i rten snying rtsa'i 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:7686: lo'i gzhal yas su dran pa gsal ba'i thig le
NK064(ngu)001:7687: dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid me tog 'phog pa'i lha
NK064(ngu)001:7688: gang yin gyi yi ge zung lnga'i phreng ba'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:7689: mchog las rigs gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro
NK064(ngu)001:7690: thim pa sogs sngar ltar las slob bu yi dam
NK064(ngu)001:7691: gang yin du bskyed pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:7692: rang rigs kyis brlabs pa'i phreng ba lag tu gtad de /
NK064(ngu)001:7695: bu khyod dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po yin
NK064(ngu)001:7696: pas sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje lha
NK064(ngu)001:7697: sngags 'od gsal gyi don sgom pa las mi 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:7698: bar gzung ste / rgyal ba thams cad ni sgrub
NK064(ngu)001:7699: pas mnyes par 'gyur bas na des mchod la 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:7700: bu rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i go
NK064(ngu)001:7702: rdzas snying gi thig ler bstim pas rnam par grol
NK064(ngu)001:7703: ba'i lam mtha' dag sgom pa la dbang thob par
NK064(ngu)001:7704: gyur pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:7705: phrin las dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7707: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas
NK064(ngu)001:7708: su bya byed gsal ba'i rten gyi thig le dwangs
NK064(ngu)001:7709: pa'i ngo bo nyid h+aam zung lnga'i phyag rgya'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:7710: mchog las phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim
NK064(ngu)001:7711: pa sogs las slob bu don grub tu bskyed pa
NK064(ngu)001:7712: la / las rigs kyis brlabs pa'i rgya gram lag tu gtad de /
NK064(ngu)001:7715: bu khyod ni da phyin chad rdo rje las mkhan
NK064(ngu)001:7716: yin gyis zhi rgyas sogs las rnams ma lus kun
NK064(ngu)001:7718: de'i grogs pho nya mang po'i rol pa nang du
NK064(ngu)001:7719: 'du zhing phyir 'phro ba kun gyis khyod kyi gnas
NK064(ngu)001:7720: skabs dang mthar thug gi dgos pa'i don thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:7721: sgrub par byed pa yin zhes bsgrags nas /
NK064(ngu)001:7722: rdzas lag pa'i thig ler bstim pas gzhan don phrin las kun la dbang thob par gyur pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7723: de nas 'chad dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7725: smra byed lce'i 'dom rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su
NK064(ngu)001:7726: sgra gsal ba'i thig le dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid
NK064(ngu)001:7727: h+r+aihzunga lnga'i phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las gsung chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:7728: rigs snang mtha'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo gsal spro
NK064(ngu)001:7729: thim pa sogs las slob bu 'od dpag med du
NK064(ngu)001:7730: bskyed pa la / snang mthas brlabs pa'i dung dang 'khor lo phyag shing rnams lag tu gtad de /
NK064(ngu)001:7733: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos kyi bdud rtsi bla med
NK064(ngu)001:7734: kyis gdul bya dad ldan gyi skyes bu ngoms par
NK064(ngu)001:7735: byos shig / ji ltar na dbang po rab 'bring
NK064(ngu)001:7736: tha ma'i blo can la so so'i blo'i rim pa
NK064(ngu)001:7737: dang mthun par chos kyi gsang ba bsgrag par bya
NK064(ngu)001:7738: ba las gzhan du min te /
NK064(ngu)001:7739: don du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro zhes bsgrags nas
NK064(ngu)001:7740: rdzas lce'i thig ler bstim pas bstan pa mtha' dag
NK064(ngu)001:7741: 'chad pa la dbang thob par gyur ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7742: gsum pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7744: bskyod chen yan lag lngar 'khor lo gzhal yas khang
NK064(ngu)001:7745: cha lnga'i gnas su skyod byed gsal ba'i reg shes
NK064(ngu)001:7746: kyi thig le'i ngo bo nyid lag g.yas par h+aum
NK064(ngu)001:7750: g.yas par h+aa rnams zung lnga lnga las rigs lnga
NK064(ngu)001:7751: so so rigs chung dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor lnga
NK064(ngu)001:7752: dang / lus kyi steng 'og phyogs mtshams bcur khro
NK064(ngu)001:7753: bcu yab yum gyi phreng ba sgom pa sogs sngar
NK064(ngu)001:7754: ltar las slob bu kun tu bzang por bskyed pa
NK064(ngu)001:7755: dang / la / rigs drug pas brlabs pa'i rdor dril lag tu gtad de /
NK064(ngu)001:7758: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:7759: gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag nyid che ba'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:7760: ste / rgyud dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:7761: po khyod yin pas dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag po
NK064(ngu)001:7762: gyis la skal ba dang 'tshams par sbyin pa'i bya
NK064(ngu)001:7763: ba la spyod cig ces gnang ba sbyin nas /
NK064(ngu)001:7764: dbang rdzas yan lag lnga'i thig le la bstim pas
NK064(ngu)001:7765: rang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa la dbang
NK064(ngu)001:7767: de ltar nang dbang lnga bskur bas rang gzhan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:7768: don da lta nyid nas dngos su byed pa'i nus
NK064(ngu)001:7769: pa so sor bzhag pa'i phyir nus dbang zhes bya
NK064(ngu)001:7770: ste / dang po gnyis kyis snang byed kyi man
NK064(ngu)001:7771: ngag sogs nang dkyil nges don gyi bskyed rim dang
NK064(ngu)001:7772: thun mong ba'i rdzogs rim rjes mthun pa rnams nyan
NK064(ngu)001:7773: bsgom nus pa'i skal pa can du byas shing /
NK064(ngu)001:7774: lnga pas ni rdo rje slob dpon du mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7775: 'chad phrin gnyis de'i byed las su 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7776: gsum pa zab dbang bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7777: shes rab sogs tshigs bcad gcig gi steng du zab dbang gsum sbrags nas ston te /
NK064(ngu)001:7778: yum shes rab ma mtshan dang ldan pa lo nyi shu ma /
NK064(ngu)001:7780: bcu gnyis ma gsum rim par dbang gsum gyi rten du gyur pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7781: thabs yab ni gsang dbang la rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7782: gong ma gnyis la slob ma ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7783: yab yum lhar gsal bas thabs shes gnyis kyi mkha' gsang byin gyis rlob cing /
NK064(ngu)001:7784: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par
NK064(ngu)001:7785: zhugs pa las yab kyi byang chub kyi sems bde
NK064(ngu)001:7786: ba'i rang bzhin h+aum yig gi 'bru tshogs su gsal
NK064(ngu)001:7787: ba'i chu rgyun yab kyi rdo rje'i lam nas yum
NK064(ngu)001:7789: de nas bshad pa'i zur gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:7790: dang po gsang dbang gi dus su pad+mora bskyil ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7791: byang sems de nyid thabs shes gang yang rung ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7792: mkha' gsang gi rtse nas dngos su len cing /
NK064(ngu)001:7793: mi nus na yab kyi lces blangs pa las sam /
NK064(ngu)001:7794: me long gis blangs te bdud rtsi dang sbyar ba
NK064(ngu)001:7795: slob bu'i lce thog tu bzhag pas byang sems de
NK064(ngu)001:7796: nyid yungs 'bru tsam gyi rdo rje sems dpa' sha
NK064(ngu)001:7797: stag tu gsal ba snying gar babs te bstim zhing
NK064(ngu)001:7798: / des chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa chen bzhi la
NK064(ngu)001:7799: gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa bon gnyid dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:7800: pa sbyangs pas sems nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7801: rang bzhin don dam spros med kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK064(ngu)001:7802: / dbang sgyur ba'o // yang zur gnyis pa sher
NK064(ngu)001:7803: dbang gi dus su yas babs dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis
NK064(ngu)001:7804: phyin pa'i thig le pad+mora reg pa'i gnas su bskyil
NK064(ngu)001:7805: ba gsang rtse'i sna rtse gnyis nas nyi zla phan
NK064(ngu)001:7806: tshun du bstim zhing ro gcig tu 'dres pas sems
NK064(ngu)001:7807: nyid don dam 'od gsal du dwangs pa'i rtags snang
NK064(ngu)001:7808: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi ye shes su shar ba
NK064(ngu)001:7809: na de'i lhan cig skyes pa'i bde chen gyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:7811: yang zur gsum pa dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang
NK064(ngu)001:7812: gi dus su byang sems yum gyi pad+mora bskyil bas
NK064(ngu)001:7813: yas babs kyi dga' bzhi'i 'gros re re la'ang dga'
NK064(ngu)001:7814: ba bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug /
NK064(ngu)001:7815: de la nyi zla so sor brtsis pas mtshan so gnyis /
NK064(ngu)001:7816: zla ba'i dga' ba bcu drug po la'ang ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:7817: lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pas dpe byad brgyad cu
NK064(ngu)001:7818: rdzogs shing / mngon par shes pa drug kyang 'char ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7819: slar yang yum gyi rtsa kha ga mu kha'i rtse
NK064(ngu)001:7820: nas nyi zla gnyis 'dres de'i ldog pa'i thabs kyis
NK064(ngu)001:7822: mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu drug gi dang po bzhis tshogs lam /
NK064(ngu)001:7823: de nas re res sbyor mthong /
NK064(ngu)001:7824: de nas dgus sgom lam sa dgu rdzogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7825: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha'i rang bzhin lhan cig
NK064(ngu)001:7826: skyes dga' lhan skyes mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK064(ngu)001:7827: po ni snang stong gi mthas ma bsgribs par gsal
NK064(ngu)001:7829: mi shigs pa'i dwangs mas lus thams cad la khyab
NK064(ngu)001:7830: cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pas
NK064(ngu)001:7831: pad+ma can dang / rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:7832: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rab 'byams su rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:7833: bas yi ge 'khor lo'i sa rdzogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7834: 'khor 'das mnyam nyid bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor du dbang sgyur ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7835: de ltar gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas
NK064(ngu)001:7836: thun mong ma yin pa'i rdzogs rim la spyod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7837: skal ba can du byas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7838: gnyis pa dbang ma bskur ba'i skyon ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7839: slob dpon sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7840: dbang bskur ba po'i slob dpon sgo gsum gyis mnyes par ma byas shing /
NK064(ngu)001:7841: phan nus zab mo'i dbang rnams rgyud la thob par
NK064(ngu)001:7842: ma byas par gsang sngags kyi rgyud dang man ngag
NK064(ngu)001:7843: nyan 'chad sgrub pa la sogs pa'i bya ba rtsom
NK064(ngu)001:7844: pa rnams tshe 'dir bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:7845: med cing / phyi ma ngan 'gror ltung bas brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:7846: gsum pa dbang bskur ba'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:7847: dus 'di sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7848: dbang thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad bu khyod dus
NK064(ngu)001:7849: gsum gyi rgyal ba'i sras su gyur pa yin zhing
NK064(ngu)001:7850: / phyi mar ngan song du ltung ba'i las bsrabs
NK064(ngu)001:7851: shing zad par byas pas ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal thams
NK064(ngu)001:7853: 'dir yang tshe ring zhing bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan la /
NK064(ngu)001:7854: skye ba phyi mar phan dbang gis mtho ris lha mi'i rgyal po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7855: nus dbang gis thar pa'i lam ston pa'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7856: zab dbang gis rgyal ba kun gyi rigs kyi bdag
NK064(ngu)001:7857: po chen por 'gyur ro zhes brjod par mdzad do
NK064(ngu)001:7860: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:7861: 'dis snod dang 'tshams par dbang gsum sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7863: // le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa bsdebs nas tshogs sgrub bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7868: le'u bcu gcig pa'i de nas sogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7869: bcu gnyis pa'i de nas sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:7870: sngar le'u dgu par tshogs sgrub mdor bstan pa de
NK064(ngu)001:7871: nas le'u gnyis sdebs nas tshogs sgrub rgyas par ston
NK064(ngu)001:7872: pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos
NK064(ngu)001:7873: bsgrub bya zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i
NK064(ngu)001:7874: go 'phang mchog gi dngos grub la dbang sgyur ba
NK064(ngu)001:7875: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7876: snang spyod kyi yul thams cad ye shes kyi rol
NK064(ngu)001:7877: mo'i sprin rnam par spros te longs spyod mi zad
NK064(ngu)001:7878: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo bkod pa zhes bya ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:7879: ting nge 'dzin gnyis la snyoms par zhugs nas ched
NK064(ngu)001:7881: gnyis pa gzhung gnyis sdebs pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:7888: shes 'jug sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7889: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:7890: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin goms pas
NK064(ngu)001:7891: lta spyod zung 'brel du 'byor pa ni sgrub byed
NK064(ngu)001:7892: thabs kyi nges pa mi gtong ba'i gzungs kyang yin
NK064(ngu)001:7893: la / sa bon dang chu lud ltar 'bras bur smin byed kyi rgyu dang rkyen yang yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7894: de ltar rtogs goms gnyis 'bras bu 'byin nus kyi
NK064(ngu)001:7895: mthu can du gang gi tshe gyur pa na zag
NK064(ngu)001:7896: med slob pa'i lam rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7897: mi slob pa'i lam rgyal ba sku lnga'i go 'phang
NK064(ngu)001:7898: thob nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing kun tu grags par
NK064(ngu)001:7899: 'gyur ro // yang cig car ba ltar na shes
NK064(ngu)001:7900: 'jug gnyis dbyer med chig chod du rtogs goms zung
NK064(ngu)001:7901: du 'byor pas zag med lam gyi ye shes gcig
NK064(ngu)001:7903: de ltar rim gcig car gnyis ka'i lam mtshan nyid gsum gyis 'ching ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7905: lam gnyis ka yang mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar phyin par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:7910: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK064(ngu)001:7913: 'grub 'bras gzhan 'tshol gyi zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7917: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs so //
NK064(ngu)001:7919: rgyu gcig sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7920: ma rig log rtog gi sems las 'khor ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:7921: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor las myang 'das su snang ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:7922: de ltar 'khor 'das gnyis su snang zhing zhen pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:7923: chos ni rgyu gcig pa'i rtags kyi gzhal bya yin
NK064(ngu)001:7924: la / 'jal tshul snga ma snga mas gtan la
NK064(ngu)001:7925: phab pa'i grub mtha' zhen cha gtan tshigs phyi ma
NK064(ngu)001:7926: phyi ma'i gzhal byar byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:7930: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs bzhis bcal bas /
NK064(ngu)001:7931: rim pa ji lta bar rang bzhin skye med /
NK064(ngu)001:7934: de'ang yul yul can med par mngon sum du rtogs pa ni mtshan nyid blo bral te grub mtha'o //
NK064(ngu)001:7936: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sems nyid
NK064(ngu)001:7937: rang byung gi ye shes skye ba med pa'i dbyings
NK064(ngu)001:7938: su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7939: de ltar rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7940: dper na rgyal bu dwa'u dmangs su 'dzin pa'i sgro
NK064(ngu)001:7941: 'dogs dang rgyal bur nges pa'i tshad ma gnyis ngo
NK064(ngu)001:7942: bo rgyal bur gcig pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7944: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig pas //
NK064(ngu)001:7945: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK064(ngu)001:7946: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK064(ngu)001:7948: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs rol pa 'gags med
NK064(ngu)001:7949: lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te
NK064(ngu)001:7950: / mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon
NK064(ngu)001:7951: byed yi ge du mar ma 'gags par snang bas
NK064(ngu)001:7953: dper na mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7955: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yis //
NK064(ngu)001:7956: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK064(ngu)001:7957: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste //
NK064(ngu)001:7958: thabs dang ldan pas rgyas gdab bo //
NK064(ngu)001:7960: rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gags med gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:7961: dngos su rtogs pa'i mthus de gnyis ngo bo dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:7962: med du rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs la 'byung ba
NK064(ngu)001:7963: yin te / lhag pa don dam dkon bdun ngo
NK064(ngu)001:7964: bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pas de'i snang ldog
NK064(ngu)001:7965: snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK064(ngu)001:7967: dper na gser dang gser gyi ser po bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7969: de nyid dbyer med byin rlabs las /
NK064(ngu)001:7970: de nyid de yi byin rlabs te //
NK064(ngu)001:7971: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK064(ngu)001:7972: byin rlabs ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK064(ngu)001:7974: bden pa dbyer med de'ang blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:7975: blta bya'i yul dang lta byed kyi shes pa gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:7976: su med pa rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med
NK064(ngu)001:7977: rang gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7978: de nyid chos rgyal thams cad kyi gnas lugs yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:7979: rgyud dag pa rnams kyis ye shes kyi gzigs ngor de ltar gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:7980: dper na mig skyon med pas dung dkar po mthong
NK064(ngu)001:7981: ba nyid dung gi kha dog gi gnas lugs yin
NK064(ngu)001:7982: pa bzhin no // de'ang rgya mtsho las /
NK064(ngu)001:7983: rang byung rang shar sems 'di dag /
NK064(ngu)001:7984: gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK064(ngu)001:7985: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK064(ngu)001:7986: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK064(ngu)001:7989: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas kyis gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:7990: de'ang lung dang man ngag dang 'gal ba'ang ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:7991: la / lung dang man ngag gi tshig tsam la
NK064(ngu)001:7992: brten pa'ang ma yin par rang gi rig pas blo'i
NK064(ngu)001:7993: gting du yid ches pas mngon sum du rtogs pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:7995: de ltar rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan
NK064(ngu)001:7996: tshigs kyis chos thams cad gtan la phebs te gnas
NK064(ngu)001:7997: lugs ji lta ba bzhin rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK064(ngu)001:7998: du gsal bar rdzogs pas spong len med par phyam
NK064(ngu)001:7999: gcig sku dang ye shes kyi rol par dbang sgyur
NK064(ngu)001:8001: 'di las che ba'i grub mtha' gzhan med pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8002: 'di dag snga ma'i grub mtha' phyi ma'i gzhal byar byas pa ni rim gyis pa'i rtogs tshul te /
NK064(ngu)001:8003: cig car ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK064(ngu)001:8004: dngos po gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad bden pa dbyer med du rgyu gcig pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8005: de mtshon byed yig 'bru a u ma gsum 'dus pa'i tshul gyis mtshon nas /
NK064(ngu)001:8006: gnyis su med pa'i dbyangs de'i byin gyis brlabs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8007: mthus rdo rje gsum du ye nas sangs rgyas par
NK064(ngu)001:8008: rang rig mngon sum gyis thag chod cing blo'i spyod
NK064(ngu)001:8009: yul las rnam par grol ba ni grub mtha' ste
NK064(ngu)001:8011: rgyu ni bden gnyis cig car du //
NK064(ngu)001:8012: gcig pas gcig pa'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK064(ngu)001:8013: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK064(ngu)001:8014: chos kun rang bzhin rtogs pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:8015: skye med dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK064(ngu)001:8016: chos kun snang bar shes pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:8017: de lta bu yi rang bzhin te //
NK064(ngu)001:8018: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK064(ngu)001:8019: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK064(ngu)001:8020: rnal 'byor sa la slebs pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:8023: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK064(ngu)001:8025: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba lnga dang //
NK064(ngu)001:8026: nang bcud kyi sems can phung po lnga dang de
NK064(ngu)001:8027: dag rang rang gi rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyis bsdus
NK064(ngu)001:8028: pa rnams ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:8029: 'khor du sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:8030: snod bcud rgyud gsum po de rim pa ji lta bar de bzhin gshegs pa yum lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8032: ye shes lngar dag pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8033: gang ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin la sgrib pa
NK064(ngu)001:8034: mtha' dag gis gos ma myong bas khyab cing de
NK064(ngu)001:8035: nyid sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:8036: pas khyab ste / chos kyi sku bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:8038: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK064(ngu)001:8039: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal //
NK064(ngu)001:8041: gal te de nyid rtogs shing goms na sangs rgyas yin mod /
NK064(ngu)001:8042: gnas pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas su ji ltar 'gyur snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:8043: rtogs rung ma rtogs rung rang bzhin rnam dag ni sangs rgyas yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:8044: 'dus byas rnams rtogs rung ma rtogs rung mi rtag pa yin pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:8046: mnyam gnyis sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8047: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:8048: mnyam pa bzhis 'khor 'das gnyis med du rtog pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8049: de la mnyam pa bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8050: spros pa phyogs re tsam dang mtha' dag chod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8051: dbye bas rnam grangs dang rnam grangs ma yin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8052: don dam zhes phye ba gnyis ka'ang spros pa bkag
NK064(ngu)001:8053: pa'i stong nyid tsam du mnyam zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8054: snang du 'dra'ang don byed nus mi nus kyis yang
NK064(ngu)001:8055: dag dang log pa'i kun rdzob zhes btags pa gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8056: ka'ang bden pas stong pa tsam du mnyam pa gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8057: ni theg chen thun mong ba'i tshul yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:8058: khyad par sngags bla na med pa'i tshul las ni lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis gsungs te /
NK064(ngu)001:8059: med dgag dang ma yin dgag gi dbye bas rnam
NK064(ngu)001:8060: grangs dang rnam grangs ma yin pa'i stong nyid gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8061: ka'ang lhag pa'i don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK064(ngu)001:8062: du lhun gyis grub par mnyam zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8063: ma dag pa las snang log pa'i dang dag pa
NK064(ngu)001:8064: lhar snang yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis ka'ang lhag
NK064(ngu)001:8065: pa kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:8066: du mnyam pa'o // de ltar 'jal byed gtan tshigs
NK064(ngu)001:8067: rnams kyis btsal bas gzhal bya 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK064(ngu)001:8068: thams cad ro mnyam par rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:8069: du rtogs pa ni grub mtha' ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8070: de'i tshe dag ma dag gi phye ba'i zhing thams
NK064(ngu)001:8071: cad kyang kun tu bzang po'i zhing khams kyi rang
NK064(ngu)001:8072: bzhin du dbyer mi phyed cing /
NK064(ngu)001:8073: sgo gsum gyi byed spyod cing dang ci byas kyang
NK064(ngu)001:8074: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8075: lhun rdzogs su gyur nas cir snang ye shes su
NK064(ngu)001:8076: 'char ro // gang dag rtogs pa bzhi dang dag
NK064(ngu)001:8077: mnyam gyi gtan tshigs 'di rnams sngar le'u gsum par
NK064(ngu)001:8078: yang byung bas zlos so snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:8079: gnas tshul dang rtogs tshul gyi ldog pas zlos skyon med de /
NK064(ngu)001:8080: snga ma ni btags gzhi 'khor ba'i chos gtan la 'bebs pa'i ched du smos la /
NK064(ngu)001:8081: 'dir ni lta spyod sbrel ba'i phyir tshogs sgrub kyi sngon 'gror smos pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8083: dus bzhi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8084: de ltar gtan la phebs pa'i grub mtha'i 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:8085: de dag dus bzhi dang phyogs bcu ste yul dus
NK064(ngu)001:8086: gnas skabs gang nas btsal kyang rang gi sems nyid
NK064(ngu)001:8087: las logs su gyur pa'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rang
NK064(ngu)001:8088: mtshan pa zhig rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8090: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de ka rtogs na rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te /
NK064(ngu)001:8091: 'di ltar nang du sangs rgyas ma rtogs na gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:8092: phyi rol tu btsal kyang mi rnyed pas ma 'tshol
NK064(ngu)001:8094: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la /
NK064(ngu)001:8099: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8102: gnas yo thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8105: yan lag sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8106: sngags kyi yan lag lnga tshang zhing dam tshig ma nyams pas rgyud dag pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8107: sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad lnga dang ldan zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8108: de ting sogs cho ga lnga po rdzogs par shes
NK064(ngu)001:8109: pa'i rnal 'byor pa tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa
NK064(ngu)001:8110: gang yin gyi lha grangs dang mthun pa tshogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8111: dkyil 'khor gyis tshogs bsgrubs na nges par legs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8113: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8115: gnas dang sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:8116: rang dbang zhing bar chad mi 'byung ba'i gnas 'khor khang rim pa gsum ldan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8120: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad de nyer mkho'i longs
NK064(ngu)001:8121: spyod thams cad bsags pas ci bde bar spyad du
NK064(ngu)001:8122: yod pa dang / des mtshon te mthun rkyen rnams ma nyams par tshang zhing 'gal rkyen med la /
NK064(ngu)001:8123: sgrub pa'i blo ni gzhan rkyen gyis mi 'phrog pas mthar skyel ba'i zhe bcad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8124: lta sgom spyod gsum 'brel ba'i blo rab dang ldan pas /
NK064(ngu)001:8125: dang por sgrub pa la 'jug dus 'dod pa'i don
NK064(ngu)001:8126: ma grub kyi bar du bsgrub bo snyam pa'i dam
NK064(ngu)001:8127: nos pa bzhin du mthar skyel bar bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8128: de'i tshe brtson pa 'dor ba'i le lo dang sgyid
NK064(ngu)001:8129: lug gi snyoms las su lus pa rnams med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8130: sgo nas blo la the tshom med par bsgrubs byas
NK064(ngu)001:8131: na tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gang bsgrubs kyang thun mchog
NK064(ngu)001:8132: gi dngos grub thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:8134: 'bras chos lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje gsang
NK064(ngu)001:8135: mchog rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dam pa thob par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:8137: sgrub pa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8138: ji tsam bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs ni sum cu phrag drug sogs le'u dgu par bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8139: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i tshes grangs sogs ni bshad
NK064(ngu)001:8140: rgyud rgyas pa sogs rgyud gzhan las smos pa bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:8141: du bshad par bya zhes kha 'phangs te /
NK064(ngu)001:8143: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la bya //
NK064(ngu)001:8144: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK064(ngu)001:8147: snying po'i rgyud 'di rgyud ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:8148: rgyud la kha 'phangs pa'i phyir zer /
NK064(ngu)001:8149: de ltar na 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa dang mkha' 'gro
NK064(ngu)001:8150: ma kun spyod kyi rgyud sogs kyang rgyud ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:8151: par 'gyur te / rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:8153: rgyud du sbas pa 'dir bshad bya //
NK064(ngu)001:8154: zhes rgyud gzhan la kha 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8155: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8157: khro bo'i sgo nas bsgrub pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8159: bsnyen sgrub bzhi mdor bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8162: bsnyen pa dang ni sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8163: 'di'i skabs su spyir lam rim las /
NK064(ngu)001:8164: 'di yang lam sgrub sbyor ba yi //
NK064(ngu)001:8167: sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:8169: lam bgrod tshul rim gyis pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:8170: lta ba rtogs nas stong chen dang kun ting la gnas pa bsnyen pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8171: phyag rgya gcig spros ni nye bsnyen dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8172: tshogs sgrub ni sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8173: de 'bras mthong lam thob ma rag pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8175: byang chub sems rtogs 'grus pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:8176: bsnyen pa'i dam pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:8177: sems chas snying rje man chad do //
NK064(ngu)001:8178: phyag rgya gsal ba nye bsnyen pa //
NK064(ngu)001:8179: de phyir gcig dang spros pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8180: sgrub pa nyid ni bar chad med //
NK064(ngu)001:8181: dus kyi tshogs mthas sgrub chen len //
NK064(ngu)001:8184: bar chad med pa'i lam pa tshogs sgrub pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:8185: sngon 'gro shoms byed cing nub dang po 'go 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:8186: gyi bsnyen pa la 'jug pa dang bcas pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:8187: bsnyen pa dang / ji tsam bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs phyed tshun chad ni nye bsnyen te /
NK064(ngu)001:8188: de gnyis la 'od zer dkar po spros pas snod rung du byed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8189: nub tha ma ma gtogs pa'i phyed phan chad 'od
NK064(ngu)001:8190: zer dmar po'i 'phro 'du bsnol mas dngos grub bskul
NK064(ngu)001:8191: zhing bsdu bas bcud dag par byed pa ni sgrub
NK064(ngu)001:8192: pa dang / rtags mthong nas nub tha mar 'od
NK064(ngu)001:8193: zer mthing ga tshur bsdu bas rgyud dag par byed
NK064(ngu)001:8194: pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8195: zla gcig la dper byas na lam rim las /
NK064(ngu)001:8196: zla phyed phyed zhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK064(ngu)001:8198: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK064(ngu)001:8200: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK064(ngu)001:8201: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK064(ngu)001:8204: sgrub pa chen po'i dus der dngos grub yum gyi mkha' las blang pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:8205: phyag rgya btsal nas chas su 'jug pa ni bsnyen pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8206: yum rlob cing sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba sogs ni nye bsnyen dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8207: rol nas dbab bzung gi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8208: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blangs te ldog dgram gyi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8209: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8211: nye sgrub thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8215: nub dang po bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8217: mkha' dkyil sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8218: bskyed rim ltar na ting 'dzin gsum sngon du 'gro
NK064(ngu)001:8219: bas mkha' dkyil ltar dwangs pa'i dbyings kyi snang brnyan
NK064(ngu)001:8220: gzhal yas khang du pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la
NK064(ngu)001:8221: / rang byung ye shes kyis kun la dbang sgyur
NK064(ngu)001:8222: ba'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' stangs dpyal te
NK064(ngu)001:8223: / yab yum dang / rdzogs rim ltar na dbyings dang ye shes te /
NK064(ngu)001:8224: de ltar zung 'brel du bsgom par byas pas rgyal
NK064(ngu)001:8225: ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun kyang lhag ma ma
NK064(ngu)001:8226: lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:8227: rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8228: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa'ang dbyings ye zung 'jug tu 'du ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8229: de la spyir tshogs sgrub kyi sngon du zhi khro gang byed kyi bsnyen pa byed pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8231: nges rdzogs su bslab pa'i lugs yin pas /
NK064(ngu)001:8232: dang por lta ba gtan la phebs par byas nas
NK064(ngu)001:8233: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi la brtan pa thob
NK064(ngu)001:8235: 'dir don rtogs kyi rgya gcig tsam smos pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8236: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i bsdus don lta bu las sngon
NK064(ngu)001:8237: du bya ba'i bsnyen pa kho na 'chad byed du
NK064(ngu)001:8238: ma nges kyang / snying rje sgyu ma nas thod
NK064(ngu)001:8239: brgal du bgrod pa 'byung mi srid pas tshogs sgrub
NK064(ngu)001:8240: kyi sngon du rgya gcig 'gro bas khyab pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:8241: sa khongs 'dzin byed tsam du smos pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8247: lnga dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8249: lha yab yum brang sprad de so sor bsgom pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:8250: rnal 'byor pa spyis tshom bu spyir bsgom pa gang
NK064(ngu)001:8251: mos kyis gtso bo rigs kyi yab lnga dang yum
NK064(ngu)001:8252: lnga'i lha zhal sbyor du bzhugs pa la so so'i
NK064(ngu)001:8253: rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum zung bzhis bskor
NK064(ngu)001:8254: bas tshom bu lnga'i lha lnga bcu bkod pa la
NK064(ngu)001:8255: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcus bskor bas lha
NK064(ngu)001:8256: bdun cu'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i tshul du shoms
NK064(ngu)001:8257: kyi tshe bri zhing bsnyen pa'i dus su rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:8258: bsgom par bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8259: de bzhin sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8260: shar phyogs su de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8261: dbus su rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8262: nub tu pad+ma'i rigs rnams la so so'i rigs chung gi sems dpa' zung bzhis bskor ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8263: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor cha gsum
NK064(ngu)001:8264: gyi mthar khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bas
NK064(ngu)001:8265: lha zhe drug gi tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu
NK064(ngu)001:8266: gsum gyi lha rnams bri zhing bsgom mo //
NK064(ngu)001:8268: rigs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8269: rigs thams cad kyi rigs kyi bdag po ste rigs kyi gtso bo ni thugs rdo rjer 'du zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8270: de'i rgyu mtshan rgyal ba thams cad kyi thugs ye
NK064(ngu)001:8271: shes lnga gcig tu 'dus pa ni rang byung gi
NK064(ngu)001:8272: ye shes te / de nyid mtshon byed thugs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8273: mchog rdo rje mi bskyod pa yab yum la rang
NK064(ngu)001:8274: gi rigs chung gi sems dpa' zung bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8275: khro bo yab yum bzhis bskor bas lha bco brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:8276: kyi tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu gcig pa'i lha
NK064(ngu)001:8279: rnal 'byor pa pho mos lha so sor bsgom pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8280: tshom bu'i lha sgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK064(ngu)001:8282: rnal 'byor thabs dang sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8283: rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum rnams
NK064(ngu)001:8284: kyis rim pa ltar de bzhin gshegs pa rigs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8285: yab lnga dang rigs kyi yum lnga ru so sor
NK064(ngu)001:8286: bsgom zhing / de bzhin du 'khor gyi rnal 'byor pa pho rnams kyi sems dpa' dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8287: mo rnams kyis sems ma nyid du bsgoms nas lha
NK064(ngu)001:8288: so so'i sngags dang rang rang gi phyag rgya dang
NK064(ngu)001:8289: ting nge 'dzin de dang de yang dag par so
NK064(ngu)001:8290: so ma 'dres par gsal ba la bslab pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8294: lnga pa sgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK064(ngu)001:8296: rdo rje'i rigs sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8297: rdo rje'i rigs su rigs gzhan thams cad 'du bas
NK064(ngu)001:8298: tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor 'od 'phro gzi byin
NK064(ngu)001:8300: yo byad la chags med tshul gyis spyod pas 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:8301: gsum mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su bstim par bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:8302: ste / de'i 'bras bu ni lta spyod gnyis med
NK064(ngu)001:8303: du 'byor bar gyur nas thob pa'i mthong lam de
NK064(ngu)001:8304: lam gong ma phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la
NK064(ngu)001:8307: yang na sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8308: tshom bu gcig pa las gzhan yang na sku gsung
NK064(ngu)001:8309: thugs kyi tshom bu gsum du bsgrub par bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:8310: nyid de / sangs rgyas thams cad ma lus pa
NK064(ngu)001:8311: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du 'dus pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:8312: nyid de / / tshom bu gsum gyi lha'i ting
NK064(ngu)001:8313: 'dzin gsal zhing gzi byin 'bar ba'i 'od zer 'phro
NK064(ngu)001:8314: nyid de / / bas bsgoms nas / yo byad
NK064(ngu)001:8315: rnams gnyis med kyi blos mnyam pa'i dbyings kyi ngang
NK064(ngu)001:8316: du thim par spyad pas brnyes pa'i 'bras bu mthong
NK064(ngu)001:8317: nyid de / / bas bsgoms nas / lam gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8318: las / tshe dbang de rig 'dzin bzhi'i nang nas
NK064(ngu)001:8319: dngos grub mchog brnyes pa lhun grub rig 'dzin thob
NK064(ngu)001:8320: pa la sbyor bar 'gyur bas yon tan bdag don
NK064(ngu)001:8321: du rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus 'bar ba ste
NK064(ngu)001:8323: gzhan don du 'gro ba'i nyon mongs sdug bsngal sel
NK064(ngu)001:8324: bar byed pa'i phrin las kyis thams cad kyang rdo
NK064(ngu)001:8325: rje gsum mi phyed pa'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas
NK064(ngu)001:8328: sngags 'chang sogs rkang pa bdun te /
NK064(ngu)001:8329: sngags 'chang gang zhig dngos grub yang dag thob par
NK064(ngu)001:8330: 'dod pas ni rnal 'byor pa thabs dang shes rab
NK064(ngu)001:8331: grangs tshang ba tshogs pa thams cad kyis tshom bu'i
NK064(ngu)001:8332: dkyil 'khor cha lnga dang khro phreng rnams te lha
NK064(ngu)001:8333: bdun cu so sor bsgoms nas /
NK064(ngu)001:8334: yo byad la chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:8335: yon ma 'gags pa'i 'od zer rnam pa mang po
NK064(ngu)001:8336: 'phro zhing gnyis su med pa'i dbyings su bstim par
NK064(ngu)001:8337: byed pa'i bya bas brnyes pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam
NK064(ngu)001:8338: gnyis las tshe dbang des dngos grub mchog gi snying
NK064(ngu)001:8339: po sku lngar sbyor ba 'grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:8340: 'o na tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par gang snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:8341: rnam snang sogs rigs bzhi'i gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs
NK064(ngu)001:8342: gcig gis bsdus pas rigs tha dad kyi gtso bo
NK064(ngu)001:8343: gcig tu gyur pa ni dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8344: rang gi rigs chung gis bye brag tu bskor bas
NK064(ngu)001:8345: rigs tha mi dad kyi gtso bo rigs so sos
NK064(ngu)001:8347: gsum pa sgrub pa chen po la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8348: sgrub byed yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8349: de'i bsgrub bya dngos grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:8351: yo byad bzhi la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8352: +aa li k+aa li la spyad pa'i thabs so //
NK064(ngu)001:8354: gos rgyan sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8355: dar dang zhing lpags sogs lus la bgo ba'i gos dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8356: rin chen dang thod phreng sogs 'dogs pa'i rgyan gyi yo byad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8357: dri ro zhim pa'i bza' btung gi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8358: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs sbyar ba'i sgra tshig gi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8359: rigs so so'i rkang bro dang lag gar gyi 'du 'phro ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8360: yo byad bzhi'i tshogs gang dang gang spyod pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:8361: cad kyi sprin phung la rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8362: kyi rang bzhin h+aum gis mtshon nas rang snang gi
NK064(ngu)001:8363: longs spyod du shes pas chags zhen med par rab
NK064(ngu)001:8364: spyad na 'bras bu ngo mtshar 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:8365: thams cad mnyes pas phan yon rlabs po che thob
NK064(ngu)001:8369: de gnyis spyad kyang nyes pas mi gos par bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8373: yum gyi mkha' las dngos grub chen po blang ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8375: lha mo sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8379: sbyor thabs kyi sgyu rtsal shes mi shes sogs kyi sgo nas phye ba'i mi mo ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8382: tha ma rigs ngan mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8383: yang na rnal 'byor pa nus pa thob pas dang po gnyis dngos su dgug pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:8384: de ltar mi nus pas phyi ma ste mi'i bu mo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8385: gang ltar kyang rnal 'byor pa'i blo khyad kyis bzang ngan so sor dbye ste bzang po bsten pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:8386: yang na mi dbye bas gang rung bsten pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8388: yum gyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8389: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:8390: yab yum lhar bskyed cing mkha' gsang rdo rje dang
NK064(ngu)001:8391: pad+mara rlobs pa'i yum gyi pad+mara tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:8392: bskyed nas / de nyid du bde ba chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:8393: rang bzhin thugs kyi dkyil 'khor byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu)001:8394: bskyed nas / spro zhing / bde ba'i sgra dang
NK064(ngu)001:8395: 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas kyi sprin 'khrigs pa'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:8396: ma lus la mchod cing spyan drangs /
NK064(ngu)001:8397: de rnams dgyes par rol pas 'dod chags chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:8398: mes byang sems dkar dmar shin tu dwangs pa'i ngor
NK064(ngu)001:8399: bor zhu ba bdag gi spyi bo nas zhugs pad+ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:8400: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mchod pas thams cad rang
NK064(ngu)001:8401: rig gi ngo bor dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas
NK064(ngu)001:8402: bdag dang 'khor 'das dbyer med bde ba chen pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8405: sgrub pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8406: de ltar sgrub par byas pa'i mkha' gsang gi nyi
NK064(ngu)001:8407: zla gnyis 'dres ye shes lngar rang gsal bar byed
NK064(ngu)001:8408: pa'i snying po de pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor nas tshogs sgrub
NK064(ngu)001:8409: kyi nub tha ma'i tho rengs kyi dus su yab
NK064(ngu)001:8410: kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i lce yis blangs te ldog
NK064(ngu)001:8411: dgram gyi sbyor bas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8413: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8414: rdzu 'phrul gyis mkha' la bya ltar 'gro ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8415: lus kyi kha dog gsal zhing gzi byin 'bar ba'am
NK064(ngu)001:8416: sems kyi mngon shes gsal zhing ting 'dzin dang ye
NK064(ngu)001:8417: shes kyi 'od 'bar bas lam gong mar bgrod pa
NK064(ngu)001:8418: dang / tshe nyi zla dang mnyam pa la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8419: yid bzhin rin po che'i sprin ltar 'dod pa'i char
NK064(ngu)001:8420: 'bebs pa zag med slob pa'i lam rig 'dzin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:8421: sa dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu rigs bdag kun
NK064(ngu)001:8422: tu bzang po'i sa mchog thob par 'gyur te mchog
NK064(ngu)001:8424: gnyis pa k+aa li sgrol ba'i thabs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8425: zhing gyur sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8426: bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa ni mchog bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8427: mchog phran thugs rjes bzung bya'i zhing gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:8428: snga ma ni dngos grub kyi rdzas khyad par can gyi rgyu skye ba bdun pa'i mi yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:8429: phyi ma ni zhing bcu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8431: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK064(ngu)001:8432: dam nyams log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:8434: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK064(ngu)001:8435: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK064(ngu)001:8436: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK064(ngu)001:8438: yang na mchog zhing bcu las sku dgra gnyis gcig tu brtsis pa'i mi bdun dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8439: mchog phran ni ngan song gsum rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:8440: ji ltar sgrol ba'i thabs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8441: e gru gsum 'bar ba'i nang nyi zla'i steng du
NK064(ngu)001:8442: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pas bsgral
NK064(ngu)001:8444: de nas bsgral bya r+au tra ste bdag 'dzin gsum sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8445: sgrol byed slob dpon dpal chen po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8446: sgrol ging tak+ki r+aa dza'i nga rgyal la gnas pas
NK064(ngu)001:8447: gri 'jam dpal rnon por bskyed de lag gi 'du
NK064(ngu)001:8448: byed kyis khog pa phye bas ma rig pa'i rgya
NK064(ngu)001:8449: dral bar bsgom / de nas lag sor la dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:8450: bo 'bru lnga bkod pa des snying bzung bas yig
NK064(ngu)001:8451: 'bru'i 'od kyis rigs drug gi sa bon gnyid dang
NK064(ngu)001:8452: bcas pa sbyangs pa'i dwangs ma h+aum yig drug dang
NK064(ngu)001:8453: dral bar bsgom / / de'ang gcig tu gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:8454: slob dpon gyi shangs bug g.yon nas sku la bcug
NK064(ngu)001:8455: pas sgrib pa rnam par dag pa de nyid rdo
NK064(ngu)001:8456: rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkha' dbyings su thim nas
NK064(ngu)001:8457: gnas pa'i h+aum yig de thugs kyi phyag rgya rdo
NK064(ngu)001:8458: rje 'od 'bar bar gyur pa las rdo rje sems
NK064(ngu)001:8460: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro bas brjid pa'i gtsug
NK064(ngu)001:8461: tu 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtags rigs
NK064(ngu)001:8462: bdag bsgom zhing / de nyid rlung dkyil la gnas
NK064(ngu)001:8463: pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du bzhag nas
NK064(ngu)001:8464: phata kyis 'og min du 'phang ba'i las kyis sgrol
NK064(ngu)001:8465: ba'i thabs 'di ni ngo mtshar che ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8466: bsgral bya sdig can ngan 'gro las thar nas rnam
NK064(ngu)001:8467: par grol ba thob pa'i thabs khyad par can yin
NK064(ngu)001:8468: pa'i phyir ro // gsum pa nyes pas mi gos par bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8469: ye nas sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8470: chos thams cad ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid
NK064(ngu)001:8471: kyi gnas lugs rtogs pas ji ltar sgyu mar snang
NK064(ngu)001:8472: ba'i skyes bus mig yor du snang ba'i gang zag
NK064(ngu)001:8473: la sbyor sgrol byas pa'i tshul bzhin du sbyor ba
NK064(ngu)001:8474: dang sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang 'dzin zhen
NK064(ngu)001:8475: med pas rdul phra rab kyi cha tsam yang byas
NK064(ngu)001:8476: pa med de / ye shes rgyas pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:8477: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mkhan po dag /
NK064(ngu)001:8478: rang gis sprul pa'i sgyu ma la //
NK064(ngu)001:8479: dge dang mi dge 'du byed pa //
NK064(ngu)001:8480: nyes pa gang gis mi gos ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:8481: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par spyod //
NK064(ngu)001:8484: skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:8485: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK064(ngu)001:8487: gnyis pa bsgrub bya dngos grub la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8491: rnal 'byor sngags 'chang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8492: lam bskyed rdzogs kyi rnal 'byor yid skyob sngags kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8493: rang bzhin rang rig la 'chang bas bsgrub bya'i dngos
NK064(ngu)001:8494: grub ni / lta ba chos thams cad sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:8495: ye shes su mnyam rdzogs lhun gyis grub par rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:8496: pa de'i ngang la bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gnas
NK064(ngu)001:8497: grub ni / shing / spyod pa ci la'ang chags
NK064(ngu)001:8498: thogs dang zhen pa med par spyod pa'i thabs des
NK064(ngu)001:8499: chos thams cad ye nas dbyer med du rtogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:8500: ni dngos grub 'byung ba'i gazhi'am rgyu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8502: yan lag sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8503: rang snang gi yan lag lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8505: de dag gi rnam shes dang bcas pa kun gyi
NK064(ngu)001:8506: rnam pa ye shes lnga'i ngo bor smin pa mtshon
NK064(ngu)001:8507: byed yi ge du shes par bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8508: des mtshon bya rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rigs lnga yab kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:8509: yang na gdul bya'i dbang gis khro bo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8510: de bzhin du gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la
NK064(ngu)001:8511: sogs pa yul gyi rnam pa kun dbyings lnga'i ngo
NK064(ngu)001:8512: bor smin pa mtshon byed yi ge m+aum du shes
NK064(ngu)001:8513: par bya zhing / des mtshon bya rigs lnga yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:8514: yang na khro mo lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8515: gnyis pa khro bo'i sgo nas sgrub pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8516: khro bo khro mo'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste //
NK064(ngu)001:8517: khro bo yab lnga dang khro mo yum lnga'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:8518: chen po la 'khor pho nya gnas ma brgyad dang
NK064(ngu)001:8520: bka' nyan sgo ma bzhi'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8521: ci bgyi'i mngags gzhug dbang mo nyer brgyad la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:8522: pa'i khongs nas khro bcu yab yum ste bdun cu
NK064(ngu)001:8523: don brgyad kyi tshogs rnams kyi rnal 'byor dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:8524: pas bsgrubs na mchog thun gyi dngos grub dang las
NK064(ngu)001:8525: bzhi sogs 'dod pa'i 'bras bu rnams rdzogs par byed
NK064(ngu)001:8528: gsum dang lnga ru bsgom par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:8529: zhes pas sngar gyi rigs bzhi he ru ka rdo
NK064(ngu)001:8530: rje'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum bzhis barjesa
NK064(ngu)001:8531: pa'i lha don brgyad ni tshom bu gcig pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8532: yang rdo rje he ru ka rigs chung dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:8533: pa lte bar bkod nas shar nub kyi rtsibs la
NK064(ngu)001:8534: bud+d+ha dang pad+ma he ru ka so so'i rigs chung
NK064(ngu)001:8535: dang bcas pa bsnan pa'i go brgyad ni tshom bu
NK064(ngu)001:8536: gsum pa / de'i steng du lho byang gi rtsibs
NK064(ngu)001:8537: la rat+na dang karma he ru ka rigs chung dang
NK064(ngu)001:8538: bcas bsnan pa'i brgya bco brgyad ni tshom bu lnga
NK064(ngu)001:8539: gsum pa / pa'o // gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid gcig car ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8540: cho ga lhag gam sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8541: cho ga ste lam gyi rim pa rnams cig car
NK064(ngu)001:8542: ba'i gang zag gis rim gyis pa ltar bsgoms pas
NK064(ngu)001:8543: lhag gam ma bsgoms pas ma tshang na'ang chad lhag
NK064(ngu)001:8545: de'i nyes pa med pas dngos grub thob pa la mi sgrib ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8546: nam mkha' la rdul gyis mi gos pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:8547: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la'ang rim cig car gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:8548: dang po rim gyis pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8549: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras bu /
NK064(ngu)001:8550: tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs /
NK064(ngu)001:8551: mthar thug gi 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8557: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad la spyad pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8559: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8560: tshom bu'i lha zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:8561: rgya rang rig la thebs pas thams cad mngon rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:8562: lha dang lha mi'i dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing brtan
NK064(ngu)001:8563: pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pas chags zhen med par
NK064(ngu)001:8564: spyod ces 'og ma rnams la'ang sbyar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8565: de'i ngang las yan lag lnga la lha bkod de
NK064(ngu)001:8566: rkang lag gi bsgul bskyod bro gar las mi 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:8567: ba'i phyag rgya 'od zer sprul pa'i 'du 'phro sna
NK064(ngu)001:8568: tshogs dang bcas te spyad pa yis sa 'og dang
NK064(ngu)001:8570: steng gi nam mkhar thogs med du 'gro bas klu
NK064(ngu)001:8571: dang lha'i bu mo rnams dbang du byed par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:8574: snyan pa'i glu dang brjod pa'i tshig thams cad rang
NK064(ngu)001:8575: rig ye shes kyi sgra las mi 'da' ba'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:8576: rgyar spyad pa yis gsung gcig gis mtha' yas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8577: gdul byar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:8581: rin chen rus pa sogs kyi rgyan dang dar dang
NK064(ngu)001:8582: ko rlon sogs bgo ba'i chas gos rnams ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8583: las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgyar spyad pa yis gzi
NK064(ngu)001:8584: byin 'bar ba'i rgyal po rgol ba gang gis kyang
NK064(ngu)001:8585: thub pa med pa'i stobs dang ldan pa 'grub par
NK064(ngu)001:8588: sha chang sogs bza' dang btung ba rnams ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8589: las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgyar spyad pa yis 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:8590: rgur bsgyur ba'i yid bzhin gyi sku bzang po dang
NK064(ngu)001:8591: ro brgya ldan pa'i bdud rtsi zad pa med pas
NK064(ngu)001:8592: 'gro ba tshim par byed pa 'grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:8595: +aa li sbyor ba dang k+aa li sgrol ba'i brda tshig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8596: rang rig pa'i ye shes las mi 'da' ba'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:8597: rgyar spyad pa yis las thams cad dang mchog thun
NK064(ngu)001:8598: gyi dngos grub thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:8599: gnyis pa tshe dbang gi cha lugs ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8600: mi dang sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8603: gzugs kyi lha tshangs pa la sogs pa'i skye ba
NK064(ngu)001:8604: rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang gzhan las khyad par du
NK064(ngu)001:8605: gyur pa ste / skye ba la rang dbang 'byor
NK064(ngu)001:8606: bas gang la gang 'dul du skye bar snang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:8607: gyur pa ste / phyir ro // des na nus
NK064(ngu)001:8608: thob mthong lam gyi sa la gnas pas rgyu'i theg
NK064(ngu)001:8609: pa'i rab dga' dang mthong lam tsam du skal ba
NK064(ngu)001:8610: mnyam kyang dgongs pa rgyu'i mi g.yo ba'i sa la
NK064(ngu)001:8611: bzhugs pa'i byang sems dang mnyam par 'gyur ba yin
NK064(ngu)001:8612: gyur pa ste / phyir ro // no // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8613: pha rol sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8614: shes 'jug 'brel bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:8615: ni rgyu 'bras kyi sa lam thams cad yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:8616: rdzogs pa ste / de yang slob lam sa bcu'i
NK064(ngu)001:8617: ngo bo pha rol tu phyin pa bcu po gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8618: su med pa'i don mthar phyin pa la rdzogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:8619: rdzogs pa ste / ni / gang la yang yongs su mi 'dzin pas sbyin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8620: ci la'ang ma chags pas tshul khrims /
NK064(ngu)001:8621: gnyis med kyi don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8622: de'i ngang las mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan /
NK064(ngu)001:8623: de las dus thams cad du mi g.yel ba'i brtson 'grus /
NK064(ngu)001:8624: don phyin ci ma log par rang rig la gsal ba'i shes rab /
NK064(ngu)001:8625: de mngon du gyur pas smon lam /
NK064(ngu)001:8626: 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'tshol bas thabs /
NK064(ngu)001:8627: mi mthun phyogs kyis mi bardzi bas stobs /
NK064(ngu)001:8628: ye ji bzhin pa'i don mngon du rtogs pas ye shes te /
NK064(ngu)001:8629: de ltar phar phyin bcu po kun tu rdzogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:8630: na sa'i khyad par bcu'i bgrod pa'ang rdzogs par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:8631: te / 'di ltar mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings rang
NK064(ngu)001:8632: mtshan mthong bas sa dang po rab tu dga' ba
NK064(ngu)001:8633: te / / mthar lta'i dri ma dag pas gnyis pa dri ma med pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8634: sems nyid rang gsal bas 'gro ba'i don mi 'gog par byed pas gsum pa 'od byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8635: rang rig nyid thams cad du 'od gsal bas bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba /
NK064(ngu)001:8636: don gnyis dus gcig tu byed pas lnga pa sbyang dka' ba /
NK064(ngu)001:8637: sems nyid yul med du rang gsal bas drug pa mngon du gyur pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8638: mtha'i lta ba las ring du song bas bdun pa ring du song ba /
NK064(ngu)001:8639: g.yeng ba'i yul med pas brgyad pa mi g.yo ba /
NK064(ngu)001:8640: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes mnga' bas dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK064(ngu)001:8641: yon tan de dag kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas bcu pa chos kyi sprin rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8642: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum yang grub ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8643: rang rig cir yang mi dmigs pa 'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8644: nyid kun tu khyab cing snang bas thabs ma 'gags
NK064(ngu)001:8645: pa ste kun tu 'od kyi sa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8646: de las ma g.yos bzhin du ma chags mi dmigs
NK064(ngu)001:8647: pa'i shes rab kyis gos pa med pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8648: ni thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyi phyir mchog ste
NK064(ngu)001:8650: shes rab spros bral gyi ye shes mchog gi byin
NK064(ngu)001:8651: rlabs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rtsol
NK064(ngu)001:8652: ba med pa lhun gyis grub par ston nus pa
NK064(ngu)001:8653: mchog tu gyur pa'i ye shes ni 'khor lo tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:8656: thabs ni kun tu 'od yin shes rab pad+ma can //
NK064(ngu)001:8657: thabs dang shes rab mchog nyid 'khor lo tshogs chen te //
NK064(ngu)001:8659: de ltar mthong sgom mthar gsum gyis bsdus pas bcu ni rgyu'i sa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8660: spang bya spong ba dang gnyen po skye ba'i sa yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8661: sa mtshan nyid pa yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:8662: kun tu 'od sogs gsum ni mthar thug 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:8663: sangs rgyas kyis gcig gi ngo bo la sku gsum
NK064(ngu)001:8664: gyi chas phye nas btags pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8665: sa lam gyi khyad par de thams cad dus yun
NK064(ngu)001:8666: ring por sbyang mi dgos par myur du lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:8668: 'o na rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od dang mthar
NK064(ngu)001:8669: thug sa gsum gyi nang tshan kun tu 'od gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:8673: lam gyi rtsol bas ngal ba rnams //
NK064(ngu)001:8674: brod pa bskyed phyir kun tu 'od //
NK064(ngu)001:8675: rdo rje 'dzin stug bkod par bstan //
NK064(ngu)001:8676: mthar thug sa gsum cha las brjod //
NK064(ngu)001:8678: rang sa thob las ngo bo nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:8679: gcig par smra ba mun sprul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:8681: dbyig gi sgron ma las kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:8682: khyod kyi mthar phyin kun tu 'od //
NK064(ngu)001:8683: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:8685: +aar+ya de ba'i gsung mig sgron rang 'grel du drangs par kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:8686: rgyu yis bgrod pa'i kun tu 'od //
NK064(ngu)001:8687: thabs chen lam gyi chos sku ste //
NK064(ngu)001:8690: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK064(ngu)001:8691: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:8692: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:8693: rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi dmigs yul la ltos
NK064(ngu)001:8694: nas tha dad pa'i 'bras bu re thob na'ang mthar
NK064(ngu)001:8695: thug yang dag pa'i 'bras bu la ltos nas gcig
NK064(ngu)001:8696: tu gyur pas skyon med de /
NK064(ngu)001:8698: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK064(ngu)001:8699: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK064(ngu)001:8700: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:8701: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK064(ngu)001:8703: gnyis pa cig car ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8704: dkyil 'khor kun tu sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8706: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi'i char
NK064(ngu)001:8707: gtogs pa'i ye shes chig chod du rang rig la
NK064(ngu)001:8708: gsal ba'i blos rab tu sbyor bas na mthar thug
NK064(ngu)001:8709: gi 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi che ba'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:8710: thams cad kyang rtsol med du 'grub par 'gyur te
NK064(ngu)001:8712: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas pa //
NK064(ngu)001:8713: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:8715: gnyis pa gsung tshul la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8716: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8717: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:8719: rdo rje sogs te tshogs sgrub kyi don 'di rnams
NK064(ngu)001:8720: rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu
NK064(ngu)001:8724: de skad ces ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:8725: kyis 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched
NK064(ngu)001:8726: du gleng zhing ched du brjod pas snang spyod thams
NK064(ngu)001:8727: cad ye shes kyi rol mor 'char ba'i sprin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:8729: gsum pa mtshan nyid sdebs pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8731: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:8735: de dag snang la mi dmigs par spyad pas tshogs chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8736: de lta bu'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu gcig
NK064(ngu)001:8737: gsum lnga ba'i sgo nas tshogs sgrub pa'i le'u ste
NK064(ngu)001:8738: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8740: // le'u bcu gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8746: tshogs sgrub bstan pa de nas thabs grol gyi man
NK064(ngu)001:8747: ngag snying po ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:8748: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad kyi sku
NK064(ngu)001:8749: gsung thugs mi phyed pa'i rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK064(ngu)001:8750: cad rig pa'i ye shes rang snang ba las tha
NK064(ngu)001:8751: mi dad pas gcig tu 'dus nas gnas pa'i ston
NK064(ngu)001:8752: pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos 'khor 'das
NK064(ngu)001:8753: kyi chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen po
NK064(ngu)001:8754: rang byung gi ye shes su ma btsal bar lhun
NK064(ngu)001:8755: gyis grub pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig snod
NK064(ngu)001:8756: ma yin pa la shin tu gsang ba rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:8757: gsang pa'i snying po de kho na nyid mtshon byed
NK064(ngu)001:8758: thabs kyi sprin rnam par bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:8759: la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa 'di
NK064(ngu)001:8760: brjod do // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8764: man ngag gi ngo bo bshad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8765: de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:8766: yul gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8775: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba mtshon pa'i sgo /
NK064(ngu)001:8776: de gnyis ka'i tha snyad mtshon byed kyi sgo /
NK064(ngu)001:8777: mtshon bya don gyi khyad par 'byin tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:8779: ma rtogs pa dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8781: dang pa 'jig rten pa'i lta ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:8783: log par rtogs pa gnyis kyi /
NK064(ngu)001:8785: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i thabs la rmongs pa sor
NK064(ngu)001:8786: bzhag lha dang mi'i theg pa gnyis so zhes bzhed
NK064(ngu)001:8788: de lta na'ang man ngag lta phreng dang bi ma la'i 'grel chung las /
NK064(ngu)001:8789: phyal rgyang gnyis la bzhed pa ltar 'chad de /
NK064(ngu)001:8790: rten 'byung rgyu 'bras kyi chos yod med gang du'ang
NK064(ngu)001:8791: ma rtogs pas spong len mi byed pa'i kun tu
NK064(ngu)001:8792: rmongs pa ni phyal pa zhes bya zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8793: tshe snga phyi dang las 'bras yod pa tsam rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:8794: kyang phyi ma rgyang du bor te tshe 'di'i btsan
NK064(ngu)001:8795: phyug mthu stobs sogs 'jig rten pa'i rig pa bzo
NK064(ngu)001:8796: dang mo rtsis sogs la brten nas bsgrub pas na
NK064(ngu)001:8798: de la phyal ba ni ma rtogs pa dngos dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8799: rgyang 'phen pa ni zhar las byung ba'i ma rtogs pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8800: de gnyis ka grub mthas blo bsgyur ba'i lta ba
NK064(ngu)001:8801: ma yin kyang sems kyi gnas tshul bsdu ba'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:8802: de'i zla la bshad pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:8804: chad lta mur stug pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8807: chos nyid ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pas 'khrul
NK064(ngu)001:8808: gzhi byas nas tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:8810: tshe gcig gi chos thams cad rgyu med glo bur
NK064(ngu)001:8811: du skye zhing mtha' chad par smra bas snga phyi'i
NK064(ngu)001:8812: mur thug pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8813: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pas 'khrul gzhi byas nas
NK064(ngu)001:8814: bdag dang gtso bo'am dbang phyug sogs rtag pa gcig
NK064(ngu)001:8815: pu rang dbang can du 'dod pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8820: gcer bu pa dang bzhi'i steng du chad lta mur
NK064(ngu)001:8821: stug pa bsnan pas tarka sde lnga zhes grags shing
NK064(ngu)001:8822: / de thams cad bdag tu lta bar mthun te /
NK064(ngu)001:8823: mu stegs pa ni bdag rtag par 'dod la /
NK064(ngu)001:8824: mur stug pa ni bdag yod pa chad par 'dod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8825: rgyu mtshan des thams cad 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i thabs ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:8826: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin gyis bcings pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8828: ji srid bdag la mngon chags pa //
NK064(ngu)001:8831: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:8832: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:8833: dang po rgyu'i theg pa la'ang rnam par thar pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8834: sgo phyogs re tsam rtogs pa ni nyan thos dang
NK064(ngu)001:8836: snga mas gang zag gi bdag med dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8837: phyi mas de'i steng du chos bdag gzung ba rang
NK064(ngu)001:8838: bzhin med par rtogs pas phyed dang gnyis rtogs kyang
NK064(ngu)001:8839: 'dzin pa rang bzhin med par ma rtogs pa'i phyir
NK064(ngu)001:8840: ro // bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam thar gyi
NK064(ngu)001:8841: sgo la spyod kyang rdo rje'i theg pa'i don ma
NK064(ngu)001:8842: ro // rtogs pas / yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa ni dbu sems gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8843: sems tsam pas don dam par gzung 'dzin gnyis med dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8844: dbu ma pas don dam par spros pa dang bral bar 'dod pas bdag med gnyis rtogs kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:8845: chos thams cad ye nas dag mnyam chen por gnas pa'i don ma mthong ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:8846: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i theg pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:8847: dang po phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:8848: sgo gsum gyi bya bas rgyud 'dul ba gtso bor byed pa kri ya dang u pa ya /
NK064(ngu)001:8849: sems kyi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtso bor byed pas 'bras bu sgrub pa ni yo ga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8850: gnyis pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud la /
NK064(ngu)001:8851: phyi rgyud man chad thun mong gi yul du ma
NK064(ngu)001:8852: gyur pas gsang ba ni pha rgyud bskyed pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:8854: ma rgyud rdzogs pa a nu yo ga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8855: chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:8856: dag pa rang byung gi ye shes su gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8857: don a nu man chad kyi yul du ma gyur
NK064(ngu)001:8858: pas gsang ba ni gnyis med kyi rgyud a ti
NK064(ngu)001:8859: yo ga ste / ma h+aa yo ga la gsum du phye ba'i bskyed rdzogs gsum mo //
NK064(ngu)001:8860: de ltar a ti man chad kyi don de rnams ni mtshon bya sgo'i khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8862: yi ge sgra btags sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8863: mtshon bya de rnams tha snyad gang gis mtshon zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:8864: yi ge a las sgra'i nga ro dang ming gzhi
NK064(ngu)001:8865: gsal bar byed pa'i tha snyad kyis gtags pa dbyangs
NK064(ngu)001:8866: gsal gyi yi ge sil bu 'dus pa las don
NK064(ngu)001:8867: gyi ngo bo tsam ston pa ming 'byung zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8868: de du ma tshogs pa la brten nas don gyi khyad par gsal bar ston pa'i tshig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8869: tshig gi tshogs 'dus pa las gzhung so so'i lus grub cing /
NK064(ngu)001:8870: des rang rang gi brjod bya'i don rab tu mtshon te gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:8872: khong nas sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8873: spyir gzhung tshig so so'i khong nas rang rang gi brjod bya'i don gnas shing /
NK064(ngu)001:8874: khyad par mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud sems can
NK064(ngu)001:8875: kun gyi khong na gnas kyang rtogs dka' bas gab
NK064(ngu)001:8876: cing / mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud du
NK064(ngu)001:8877: gsang ba zab mo rnams skal med kyis mi go
NK064(ngu)001:8879: de ltar gab sbas kyi don gnyis po de 'byin
NK064(ngu)001:8880: par byed pa po ni rgyud don phyin ci ma
NK064(ngu)001:8881: log par ston pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs
NK064(ngu)001:8882: la gnas pa'i phyir des 'byin cing /
NK064(ngu)001:8884: rang gnas rang bzhin gyi rgyud ngo sprod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8885: yi ge'i rgyud 'chad pa'i man ngag gis 'khrugs pa
NK064(ngu)001:8886: sdeb cing gab pa mngon du phyung ba'i tshul gyis
NK064(ngu)001:8887: so // gnyis pa myong bar byed pa'i thabs la /
NK064(ngu)001:8888: gzhung gcig gi steng du bshad tshul gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:8889: shes rab grol lam gyi dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8890: thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8892: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8893: grol lam cig car ba ltar du bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8894: dang po la'ang mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK064(ngu)001:8895: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8898: rang rig pa ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:8899: dag pa rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor lhag pa
NK064(ngu)001:8900: bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba des
NK064(ngu)001:8901: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la ris med du
NK064(ngu)001:8902: ldan par khyab pa ni lta ba'i ngo bo ste
NK064(ngu)001:8903: / gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor de nyid gtan tshigs
NK064(ngu)001:8904: rnams kyis gtan la phab pas yul med rang gsal
NK064(ngu)001:8905: du rtogs pa ni grub mtha'o //
NK064(ngu)001:8906: de nas rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8907: dkyil 'khor la ni sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8908: ye nas rnam par dag pa chos nyid don gyi
NK064(ngu)001:8909: dkyil 'khor de la ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8910: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor stong pa chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:8912: don dam chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor de'i rang gdangs
NK064(ngu)001:8913: ma 'gags pa ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor snying
NK064(ngu)001:8914: rje chen po mkha' khyab tu bsgom pa ni snying
NK064(ngu)001:8916: de gnyis zung du 'jug pa mi 'gyur ba'i bde
NK064(ngu)001:8917: ba chen po cir yang ma 'gags pa las rang
NK064(ngu)001:8918: byung ba'i yi ge ar snang ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8919: de las a phra mo dang ka sogs kyi 'phro 'du la sems sbyang zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:8920: de thams cad kyang thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:8921: kyi ngo bo yi ge h+aum gi dkyil 'khor du
NK064(ngu)001:8922: bsdus la bsgom pa ni phra ba yig 'bru la
NK064(ngu)001:8923: bslab pa'o // de nyid rdo rje rtse lnga par
NK064(ngu)001:8924: gsal ba yongs su gyur pa las snang stong dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:8925: med kyi lha sku'i dkyil 'khor yan lag lhag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8926: lha dang bcas pa bsgom pa ni phyag rgya gcig
NK064(ngu)001:8928: des dkyil 'khor thams cad bsgoms par 'gyur bas na mchog ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8929: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun //
NK064(ngu)001:8930: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:8932: zung 'jug gi lha sku de tha dad du zhen
NK064(ngu)001:8933: pa'i blos rtogs dka' bas gsang ba'i don dang mtha'i
NK064(ngu)001:8934: spros pa dang bral bas thig le ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8935: de ltar spros bcas kyi dkyil 'khor 'char gzhir gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK064(ngu)001:8936: de'ang 'byung ba lnga ni shes rab kyi rang bzhin rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8937: chen po'i sgras brjod pa phung po lnga ni rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8938: de ltar rtog tshogs thams cad byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu)001:8939: su rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas lha rtog
NK064(ngu)001:8940: dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje'i tshogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:8941: 'di ltar mig sogs dbang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8944: mig gi rnam shes sogs rig pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8945: de ltar rtog tshogs kyis bsdus pa'i spyod yul rnams sems dpa' sems ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:8946: khro bo khro mo sogs lhar yongs su dag pas na kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8947: rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la yan lag gi
NK064(ngu)001:8948: lha bzhi bcu pa re bsgom pa ni thabs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8949: lha bzhi bcu'o // de rnams kyang rang gi sems
NK064(ngu)001:8950: nyid rnam par 'phrul pa'i bdag nyid chen po yan
NK064(ngu)001:8951: lag lhag pa'i lha thugs ye shes sems dpa' re
NK064(ngu)001:8952: re bsgoms pas shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu dang
NK064(ngu)001:8953: lha bzhi bcu'o // / thabs lha bzhi bcu po la sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8954: bzhi bcu pa tshan pa bzhi la ye shes lnga'i
NK064(ngu)001:8955: phyag rgya dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga res brgyan
NK064(ngu)001:8957: de ltar nyi khri bzhi stong po thams cad gsal
NK064(ngu)001:8958: zhing brtan pa ni snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:8959: ting nge 'dzin te spros bcas so //
NK064(ngu)001:8960: dwangs ma dkar dmar gyi snying po'i thig le dbab
NK064(ngu)001:8961: ldog gi sbyor bas lhan skyes kyi ye shes la
NK064(ngu)001:8963: des mtshon nas yo byad lnga yul dang yul can
NK064(ngu)001:8964: gnyis su med par mnyam par sbyor bas spyod bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:8965: ma chags pa bde ba'i ye shes kyi rol mo
NK064(ngu)001:8966: yis rtog tshogs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang
NK064(ngu)001:8967: gsal bas dgyes pa dang ldan pa'i lha nyid la
NK064(ngu)001:8968: nyid rol pa'i tshul du mchod pa mnyam rdzogs chen
NK064(ngu)001:8969: por dbul ba ni tshom bu tshogs sgrub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:8970: de nas 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8971: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8972: de ltar zag pa med pa'i ye shes dang bsod
NK064(ngu)001:8973: nams khyad par can gyi mthus gnas skabs kyi 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:8974: bu 'od gsal gyi lha skur mngon du gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:8975: mthong lam gnyis gang rung thob pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:8976: zung 'jug ye shes sgyu ma'i skur rang snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:8977: rgya chen dang mthar lam gyi sa brnyes pa la
NK064(ngu)001:8979: de'i dgongs pa ni spyod yul thams cad rang byung
NK064(ngu)001:8980: gi ye shes rang snang ba'i rol mo dag pa
NK064(ngu)001:8981: rab 'byams lha'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas par 'char zhing
NK064(ngu)001:8982: / snang stong mi phyed pa'i ye shes mchog thugs su chud la /
NK064(ngu)001:8983: de nyid rtogs dka' zhing spros pa'i yul las 'das
NK064(ngu)001:8984: pas gsang ba'i thig le ste mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:8985: dbyings so // zung 'jug de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo'am dngos gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:8986: de'i tshe na phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dbyings su mngon
NK064(ngu)001:8987: par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i rgyal ba thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:8988: kyi sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs te 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:8989: bu'i chos rnams ma lus pa rang gi rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:8990: las tha dad med par rtogs pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:8991: bdag nyid la yod pa de'i zhal bdag gis mthong
NK064(ngu)001:8992: bas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:8993: pa'i bdag nyid du dbang sgyur ba'i mchog nyid de
