NK064(ngu)001:8994: / slob lam gyi rtse mor phyin pas lam gyi nang nas dam pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:8995: de ltar man ngag lam rim gyis rgyab byas nas
NK064(ngu)001:8996: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:8997: / 'di la snga rabs pa rnams kyis bskyed rim zhes bshad na'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:8998: grol lam cig car ba la ltos nas de ltar gsungs pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:8999: rim pa gnyis kyi zlas phye ba'i bskyed rim ni ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:9001: de kho na la bslabs pas spyod pa'i nye rgyu
NK064(ngu)001:9002: tshogs sgrub kyis zag med mthong lam la sbyor ba
NK064(ngu)001:9005: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su cho ga gsum bskyed dang bzlas pa bya tshul sogs 'byung yang /
NK064(ngu)001:9006: de tsam gyis bskyed rim kho nar mi 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:9007: rdzogs rim gyis drangs pa'i lha'i gsal snang la bslab tshul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9008: thun mtshams kyi bya ba bzlas pa sogs sbyar te
NK064(ngu)001:9009: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu bslab pa'i ched yin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9010: phyir ro // 'on kyang bskyed rim ltar bslab pa'ang mtha' gcig tu ni mi 'gog ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9011: gang zag 'ga' zhig bskyed pa'i rim pas spros bcas kyi lha'i gsal snang ci rigs thob nas /
NK064(ngu)001:9012: tshogs kyi spyod pas thun mong gi dngos grub mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:9013: spyod bsgrubs te dngos dang sprul pa'i sgo nas phan
NK064(ngu)001:9014: 'dogs pa dang tshar gcod pa sogs kyis sems can
NK064(ngu)001:9016: rten des sangs rgyas byang sems rnams mnyes par byas
NK064(ngu)001:9017: pa'i mthus rdzogs rim pa la zhugs te zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:9018: gi sku sgrub pa ni yod par 'dod dgos so
NK064(ngu)001:9019: // des na lam gyi gnad ni 'di yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:9021: yan lag dbang po thams cad kun //
NK064(ngu)001:9022: rang bzhin yongs kyis dag pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:9023: ting 'dzin de bzhin gshegs pa lngar //
NK064(ngu)001:9024: ye nas ma bcos yongs kyis gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:9026: rang lus gdod nas phyag rgya che //
NK064(ngu)001:9027: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK064(ngu)001:9028: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar man ngag gi gnad gzigs
NK064(ngu)001:9029: pa'i dam pa gong ma rnams bskyed rim zhes gsung
NK064(ngu)001:9030: yang / de'i don 'chad pa'i tshe lhag pa kun
NK064(ngu)001:9031: rdzob 'di ltar snang ba kun rang bzhin gyis lha'i
NK064(ngu)001:9032: dkyil 'khor du yongs su grub pas /
NK064(ngu)001:9033: de ltar gsal btab cing goms pa na zung 'jug
NK064(ngu)001:9034: gi lha sku rang shar du 'byung bar bzhed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9035: phyir rdzogs rim gyi lha sku las 'os med do
NK064(ngu)001:9036: // ji ltar bsgom pa'i gnad kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:9037: lta ba gtan la phebs pa'i gang zag gis sgo gsum gyi bya ba btang nas /
NK064(ngu)001:9038: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gyis nyin mtshan sbrel
NK064(ngu)001:9039: te don dam 'od gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9040: ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK064(ngu)001:9041: zhi lhag zung du 'jug pa'i 'od gsal gyi ngang
NK064(ngu)001:9042: du sems thim ste 'gags pa na phyi nang gsang
NK064(ngu)001:9043: ba'i drod dang zad par gyi snang ba sogs stong
NK064(ngu)001:9044: gzugs kyi snang ba mtha' yas pa 'char la /
NK064(ngu)001:9045: de'i ngang las nyin snang dang mtshan mo rmi lam
NK064(ngu)001:9046: gyi snang ba thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shar
NK064(ngu)001:9047: nas 'gro ba rnams la dmigs med kyi snying rje
NK064(ngu)001:9048: rang gsal ma 'gags pa'i ngang du mnyam par 'jog
NK064(ngu)001:9049: pa snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor la bslabs pas
NK064(ngu)001:9050: / snang ba ris med las snying rje chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:9051: 'phen pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyi rkyen gyis zung
NK064(ngu)001:9052: 'jug gi lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9053: de las ches cher 'phel te snang ba thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:9054: zung 'jug gi lhar mngon sum du spro bar nus
NK064(ngu)001:9055: pa ni phyag rgya spros bcas so //
NK064(ngu)001:9056: de las nye rgyu'i spyod pa spros bcas tshogs sgrub bam /
NK064(ngu)001:9057: spros med rnal 'byor pho mo gtso bo yab yum
NK064(ngu)001:9058: tsam tshogs pa la brten pa'am shin tu spros med
NK064(ngu)001:9059: ni yab mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen nyid yum rnam
NK064(ngu)001:9060: kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa nyid dang kha sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:9061: gyi spyod pas zag med kyi lam la sbyor bar
NK064(ngu)001:9062: byed do // des na thog mar stong chen 'od
NK064(ngu)001:9063: gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i lam las brtsams pas
NK064(ngu)001:9064: lha sku'i snang ba rnams kyang zung 'jug gi lha
NK064(ngu)001:9065: sku phyag rgya chen por 'char ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:9066: mngon sum pa'i lam rdzogs pa'i rim pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9068: ko dra ba yi sa bon las //
NK064(ngu)001:9070: rnam rtog sa bon las byung ba'i //
NK064(ngu)001:9072: rnam par mi rtog las skyes pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:9075: gnyis pa cig car ba ltar bshad pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:9078: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9079: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas sku gsung
NK064(ngu)001:9080: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas te rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:9081: gyis rnam par dag pa yin gyi /
NK064(ngu)001:9082: phyis lam gyis 'bras bu gsar du bsgrubs pa ni ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:9083: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin de ltar yin kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:9084: yin pa tsam gyis phan mi thogs pas /
NK064(ngu)001:9085: gzhi de ltar yin pa lam gyis mngon du rtogs par bya dgos te /
NK064(ngu)001:9086: de yang ye nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor sems
NK064(ngu)001:9087: can thams cad la rang chas su ldan pa'i don
NK064(ngu)001:9088: rtogs nas / ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyis ye nas yin pa'i dkyil 'khor de la ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9089: de ltar yin par shes pa'i tshul gyis dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:9090: du gsal 'debs shing bsgom par byas nas rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:9091: gyi dkyil 'khor dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i ting nge
NK064(ngu)001:9092: 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor las byung ba ni thugs rang
NK064(ngu)001:9093: rig pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste
NK064(ngu)001:9094: / dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi mchog 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9095: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras gsum du snang yang don
NK064(ngu)001:9096: la gsang ba byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin thig
NK064(ngu)001:9097: le chen po'i dkyil 'khor spros bral gyi dbyings las
NK064(ngu)001:9098: gzhan du ma g.yos pas de tsam du zad do
NK064(ngu)001:9100: dang po dkyil 'khor ji ltar ldan par bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9101: 'byung ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9102: sngar ltar 'byung ba lnga yum lnga yin pa sogs
NK064(ngu)001:9103: rtog tshogs thams cad rang bzhin gyis lhar rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:9104: dag pas 'gro ba kun la de ltar ye nas
NK064(ngu)001:9105: rang chas su ldan pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:9106: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar bsgom tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9107: kun tu bzang po'i sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9108: de ltar chos thams cad kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas pa de la /
NK064(ngu)001:9109: de'i don legs par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa bdag
NK064(ngu)001:9110: nyid chen pos ye nas grub pa'i don de dang
NK064(ngu)001:9111: gnyis su med par rig pas lhag pa'i dgongs pa
NK064(ngu)001:9112: zab mo ste / thugs rang byung gi ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9113: gcig dang du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba las rol
NK064(ngu)001:9114: pa ma 'gags pa ye shes lngar 'char ba'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:9115: gyis lta zhing bsgom par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9116: gsum pa de ltar bsgom pa las cir 'gyur ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9117: snying po'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9118: chos thams cad kyi snying por gyur pa'i chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9119: dbyings thig le nyag gcig dang gnyis su med par
NK064(ngu)001:9121: don phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa'i rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:9122: rang byung ba ni byang chub kyi sems bde ba
NK064(ngu)001:9124: de nyid kyi rol mo sna tshogs par 'char ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:9125: sprin gyis ye shes la ye shes dgyes par rol
NK064(ngu)001:9126: pa'i tshul du mchod par dbul zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9127: de ltar gzhi lam 'bras gsum du bstan kyang rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems las ma g.yos te /
NK064(ngu)001:9128: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyi stobs kyis bsgrubs
NK064(ngu)001:9129: pa'i ye shes sgyu ma lta bur ma 'gags par
NK064(ngu)001:9130: rang snang ba'i rol mo'i dkyil 'khor rnam 'gyur mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:9131: yas par 'phrul yang mchog gsang ba'i thig le byang
NK064(ngu)001:9132: chub kyi sems de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:9134: de lta bu'i man ngag dang man ngag can gyi yon tan gang zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:9135: dbyings de nyid ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi ste man ngag gi don yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:9136: man ngag de dang ldan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9137: phyogs bcu dus bzhir tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:9138: ma lus pa bdag nyid las mi gzhan pa'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:9139: du sku'i zhal mthong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9140: gsung chos la dbang sgyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9141: yon tan phrin las mthar phyin pa'i mchog nyid du dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9142: thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i bslu med skyabs kyi dam par gyur pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:9143: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor la gnas sogs rkang pa gsum gyis de thob tshul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9144: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas sogs rkang pa
NK064(ngu)001:9145: lngas thugs rje chen po'i mdzad pa ji ltar 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:9146: tshul bstan pa'i yon tan rnams kyang 'dir sbrel ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:9147: bka' srol yod kyang yi ges 'jigs so //
NK064(ngu)001:9148: de ltar man ngag de la slob dpon chen po pad+mas lta ba'i phreng bar /
NK064(ngu)001:9149: rtogs pa bzhi'i lam gyis yid ches par bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9150: mtshan nyid gsum gyis don mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9151: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis don lhun gyis grub par bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9152: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i thabs bstan pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9153: don rnam pa bzhir phye nas gsungs pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:9154: phyi ma ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9155: dang po gsum ni sngar bshad pa la 'dus pas 'dir rgyas par ma spros so //
NK064(ngu)001:9156: gnyis pa thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9157: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag ltar bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9158: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9163: khyab brdal chen po'i man ngag go //
NK064(ngu)001:9165: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9166: snying khong stong gi dbus na rtsa'i dwangs ma rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:9167: 'dab brgyus pa ldang ba 'dra ba brgyad yod pa
NK064(ngu)001:9169: mdun gyi gsum chos nyid kyi rtsa ste skye ba med pa'i rang snang ba'i las byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9170: g.yas kyi gcig ye shes kyi rtsa ste ye shes 'char ba'i las byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9171: g.yon gyi gcig yon tan gyi rtsa ste mngon shes
NK064(ngu)001:9172: dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams snang ba'i las byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:9173: / rgyab kyi gsum rang rgyud kyi rtsa ste shes pa rnams rmongs shing 'joms pa'i las byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:9174: rtsa de dag gi sbubs na 'od bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9175: de'i khrod na sbyangs bya dang sbyong byed kyi sa bon rnam shes dang bcas pa rnams gnas te /
NK064(ngu)001:9176: chos nyid kyi rtsa la 'od zlum po dkar po /
NK064(ngu)001:9180: ye shes kyi rtsa la 'od gru bzhi ser po /
NK064(ngu)001:9184: yon tan gyi rtsa la 'od zla gam dmar po /
NK064(ngu)001:9186: sbyong byed +aah nyon mongs can gyi yid /
NK064(ngu)001:9187: rang rgyud kyi rtsa la 'od gru gsum dmar nag la /
NK064(ngu)001:9188: sgo lnga'i shes pa gnyid dang bcas pa gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:9189: 'dir chos nyid dang ye shes kyi rtsa'i 'od dkar
NK064(ngu)001:9190: po dang ser por byas pa ni dpe chung rang
NK064(ngu)001:9192: gsang thig las ni chos nyid ser po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9193: ye shes mthing gar bshad do //
NK064(ngu)001:9194: de ltar snying gi dkyil 'khor rtsa chen bzhi dang ldan pa de'i nang na /
NK064(ngu)001:9195: dwangs ma lnga'i dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9196: dbus su ye shes snying po'i thig le stong gsal
NK064(ngu)001:9197: 'gag med bde ba chen po'i ngo bor bzhugs te
NK064(ngu)001:9198: / nyi zla kha sbyor gyi rgyud las /
NK064(ngu)001:9199: tsit+ta rin chen gzhal yas na //
NK064(ngu)001:9200: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK064(ngu)001:9201: sku ni snang la rang bzhin med //
NK064(ngu)001:9202: cha phra 'od gsal snying por bzhugs //
NK064(ngu)001:9205: lus la ye shes chen por gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:9206: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spangs //
NK064(ngu)001:9207: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK064(ngu)001:9208: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9211: rtag tu snying la gnas pa yi //
NK064(ngu)001:9212: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK064(ngu)001:9213: de sgom byed pa'i skye bo la //
NK064(ngu)001:9214: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:9216: de la dwangs ma lnga ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9217: rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba
NK064(ngu)001:9218: sbom phra rta rnga bcu gshags tsam gyi nang na
NK064(ngu)001:9219: / khrag gi dwangs ma mtshal khu lta bu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9220: me'i dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9221: rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og na yod pa'i rlangs tsam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9222: nam mkha'i dwangs ma bar snang sang seng go 'byed pa'i tshul du yod de /
NK064(ngu)001:9223: lnga po'ang ye nas yum lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:9226: rtsa'i dwangs ma ni 'byung ba sa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9228: me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK064(ngu)001:9230: khrag gi dwangs ma ni chu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9246: ye shes snying po'i thig le ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9247: rig pa'i dwangs ma sems nyid 'od gsal ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9248: yum lnga 'dus pa bya ba mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9249: ye shes lnga 'dus rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9250: sku lnga 'dus pa bde chen gyi skur don gyis 'gyur zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9251: der ma zad dwangs ma drug po'ang gnyis gnyis ro
NK064(ngu)001:9252: gcig tu 'jug pas shin tu phra ba'i sgo gsum
NK064(ngu)001:9253: mam / rdo rje mi shigs pa gsum du'ang 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:9254: sa chu gnyis sku rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:9255: me rlung gnyis gsung rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:9256: mkha' sems gnyis thugs rdo rje ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9258: mi shigs ye shes thig le ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9259: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK064(ngu)001:9260: gcig dang du ma rnam spangs pa //
NK064(ngu)001:9261: sna tshogs snang la mtshon du med //
NK064(ngu)001:9263: de ltar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus na ye
NK064(ngu)001:9264: shes snying po'i dkyil 'khor dwangs shing 'od 'bar bar
NK064(ngu)001:9265: bzhugs la / de nyid ni ye nas bzhugs pa
NK064(ngu)001:9266: ltar lam pas thig le'i dkyil 'khor yungs 'bru tsam
NK064(ngu)001:9267: 'od lnga'i gong bu can gsal ba yul gyis mi
NK064(ngu)001:9269: dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying po dang drug ye
NK064(ngu)001:9270: shes drug gi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:9271: phyin ci ma log pa'i yongs grub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:9272: de la spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar
NK064(ngu)001:9273: sems gtad de bsgoms pas ye shes snying po'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:9274: 'khor ste thig le 'od 'bar ba las byung ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:9275: 'od kyis sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge bskul ba
NK064(ngu)001:9276: 'od du 'bar bas sbyang bya'i yi ge drug gnyid
NK064(ngu)001:9278: las dang bag chags thams cad mi dmigs pas 'khor ba chos nyid du grol zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9279: dwangs ma lnga'ang ye shes snying po la bsdus pas bde ba'i ye shes 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9280: de'ang rtsas bde ba'i rten byed /
NK064(ngu)001:9281: chus bde ba sdud cing rgyud rlan par byed /
NK064(ngu)001:9282: drod kyis bde ba smin par byed /
NK064(ngu)001:9284: nam mkhas khams gsum bde ba chen por yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:9285: grol bar byed pas bde ba'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK064(ngu)001:9286: bo ni dmigs med mtha' bral thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:9288: de ltar nam mkha'i gzugs su skyes pa de nyid
NK064(ngu)001:9289: thig le byang chub kyi sems yin te chos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9290: sku'o // zhes pas rlung sems kyi dwangs ma thams
NK064(ngu)001:9291: cad thugs kyi dkyil 'khor der rdzogs pa'i tshe snang
NK064(ngu)001:9292: cha 'od lnga dang stong cha chos kyi skur ro
NK064(ngu)001:9293: gcig tu 'dres pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9294: sku gnyis mngon du gyur nas 'tshang rgya ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:9295: 'di ni dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9296: rnal 'byor pa 'chi ba'i dus su'ang dwangs ma dang rlung thams cad dbu mar 'du /
NK064(ngu)001:9297: dbu ma'i rlung dang dwangs ma'i shin tu dwangs ma
NK064(ngu)001:9298: rim bzhin 'dus pa las 'chi srid stong pa'i 'od
NK064(ngu)001:9300: de nub nas snang ba'i 'od gsal rigs lnga tshom
NK064(ngu)001:9301: bu'i snang ba nam mkha' khyab par 'char ba'ang 'di'i
NK064(ngu)001:9302: gnad kyis byung bar bzhed do //
NK064(ngu)001:9304: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9305: lte ba'i rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbus na
NK064(ngu)001:9306: dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le zhes bya ba a thung
NK064(ngu)001:9307: gi rnam par gnas pa ni chos kyi dbyings zab
NK064(ngu)001:9308: mo gsang ba shes rab kun tu bzang mo'i rang
NK064(ngu)001:9309: bzhin nyi ma'i thig le ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9310: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dbyings so //
NK064(ngu)001:9311: de'i rang bzhin ni shes rab dang thabs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9313: thig le de las byung ba 'byung ba lnga'i dwangs
NK064(ngu)001:9314: ma cha phra ba rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings ni
NK064(ngu)001:9315: shes rab ste rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9316: chen po rags pa mtshan nyid 'dzin pa ni thabs rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa ste yab lnga'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9317: de ltar thig le byang chub kyi sems thabs shes dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9318: de las byung ba'i rtog tshogs dbang po dang yul dang dus dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9319: yul so sor rig par byed pa'i rnam shes rnams
NK064(ngu)001:9320: sems dpa' dang 'joms byed yab yum sogs thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:9321: bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyi spyod yul du
NK064(ngu)001:9322: rnam par dag pas kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:9323: yin la / de dag thams cad kyang dbyings rang
NK064(ngu)001:9324: byung gi ye shes su rdzogs pas bdag nyid chen
NK064(ngu)001:9325: yin la / po ste / de dang kha sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:9326: snying ga'i 'khor lo la rgyal ba kun gyi lhag
NK064(ngu)001:9327: pa'i dgongs pa zab mo thugs stong pa nyid kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9328: ye shes kyi snang cha me long lta bu la
NK064(ngu)001:9329: sogs pa lnga ye nas lhun grub tu gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:9330: yin la / po ste / ste / des blta
NK064(ngu)001:9331: ba ni snying ga nas mar lte ba'i thig le
NK064(ngu)001:9332: la sems gtad de bsgoms pas snying ga'i thig le'i
NK064(ngu)001:9333: 'od dang dwangs ma'i drod mar song ba dbyings phyug
NK064(ngu)001:9334: lnga'i thig le la phog ste 'od du 'bar bas
NK064(ngu)001:9335: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su gsal bar gyur
NK064(ngu)001:9336: yin la / po ste / ste / / de'i
NK064(ngu)001:9337: drod slar yang yar song ste snying ga'i dwangs ma
NK064(ngu)001:9338: la thim pas dwangs ma'i bde drod ches cher 'bar
NK064(ngu)001:9339: ba na rags pa'i rlung gi rgyu ba 'gags pas
NK064(ngu)001:9340: thig le 'gro 'ong med par snying ga'i gnas las
NK064(ngu)001:9341: mi g.yo bar gnas pas bde ba chen po rang
NK064(ngu)001:9342: rig pa'i ye shes rang shar ba la blta bya
NK064(ngu)001:9343: lta byed med pa'i tshul gyis blta zhing nyams su
NK064(ngu)001:9344: len pa ni lte ba'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i man
NK064(ngu)001:9345: yin la / po ste / ste / / ngag go // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9346: snying po'i thig le sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9347: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:9348: 'gro ma rngams ma zhes bya ba yi ge am
NK064(ngu)001:9349: gi rnam par gnas pa la bza' btung gi bcud
NK064(ngu)001:9350: 'dus pas na snying po'i thig le ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9351: de snying ga'i dwangs ma chen po'i 'od dang drod
NK064(ngu)001:9352: yar song ste zhu ba'i dwangs ma snying gar mched
NK064(ngu)001:9353: / dbugs thig ler thim pas rlung dang rtog pa
NK064(ngu)001:9354: 'gags te 'khor lo gnyis bde ba dus gcig tu
NK064(ngu)001:9356: de ltar sbyar bas bde ba chen po la gnas
NK064(ngu)001:9357: pa'i rang gdangs ye shes lngar ma 'gags pa'i rol
NK064(ngu)001:9358: mo yis drod rlung rtsa gsum gcig tu 'dres te
NK064(ngu)001:9359: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mi
NK064(ngu)001:9360: g.yo bar rang gsal ba'i dgyes pa chen po la
NK064(ngu)001:9361: yul yul can gnyis med kyi ngang du mchod par
NK064(ngu)001:9363: mgrin pa'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK064(ngu)001:9365: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9366: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum
NK064(ngu)001:9367: cu rtsa gnyis kyi dbus na kun tu bzang po
NK064(ngu)001:9368: zla ba'i thig le ham gi rnam par gnas te
NK064(ngu)001:9369: / de'ang sngar mgrin pa'i thig le'i bde ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:9370: yul yul can gyi rtog pa zad pas zag pa
NK064(ngu)001:9371: med pa'i bde ba yin la /
NK064(ngu)001:9372: de nyid ma 'gags pa'i bsod nams kyi mthus thig le nyid rang bzhin med de /
NK064(ngu)001:9373: bde ba chen po'i ye shes sgyu ma lta bur rang snang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:9374: de las bde ba'i rol mo 'od kyi dkyil 'khor mtha' yas par spro ba'i mchog ces bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9375: mgrin pa'i thig le'i 'od kyis shin tu rtogs dka'
NK064(ngu)001:9376: bas gsang ba ste bde chen 'khor lo'i thig le
NK064(ngu)001:9377: la 'phog pas 'od du zhu nas spyi blugs su
NK064(ngu)001:9378: gyur pas bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin du gyur
NK064(ngu)001:9379: te / de nyid chos kyi dbyings dang ro gcig
NK064(ngu)001:9380: pas khams gsum thams cad so so ma yin pa
NK064(ngu)001:9381: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes nam
NK064(ngu)001:9382: mkha'i gzugs su skyes nas kun gyi dngos por bdag
NK064(ngu)001:9383: gyur pa zhes bya ba chos kyi skur gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:9384: de ni dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9385: te / dngos te / de ltar rnal 'byor pa
NK064(ngu)001:9386: bde ba chen po chos kyi skur gyur pa na
NK064(ngu)001:9387: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i rdzogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9388: sangs rgyas ma lus pa thams cad bdag nyid las
NK064(ngu)001:9389: gzhan du ma gyur pas sku'i zhal dus gcig la
NK064(ngu)001:9390: te / dngos te / mthong ba ste / de gsung la dbang sgyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9391: yon tan phrin las mchog nyid mthar phyin zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9392: thugs don dam pa'i ye shes su ro gcig tu
NK064(ngu)001:9393: gyur pa yin te spyi bo'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9394: man ngag go // de ltar 'khor lo bzhi'i rim pa mdor bsdu na /
NK064(ngu)001:9395: snying ga'i 'khor lo sgom pa las byung ba'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:9396: shes spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ni chos
NK064(ngu)001:9397: kyi sku dang / lte ba'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9398: ye shes rtog tshogs zhe gnyis lhar dag pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:9400: mgrin pa'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes ni longs sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9401: spyi bo'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes ni bde ba chen po'i sku ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9402: de'ang dwangs ma'i dwangs ma rnams 'khor lo bzhi'i lte
NK064(ngu)001:9403: ba'i dwangs ma g.yo byed dang bral ba'i 'od gsal
NK064(ngu)001:9404: la tshur thim pas bde gsal rnam par mi rtog
NK064(ngu)001:9405: pa'i ye shes chen po gcig dang du ma med
NK064(ngu)001:9406: pa'i chos nyid mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i 'od gsal
NK064(ngu)001:9408: gnyis pa 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9409: thabs nyid shes rab tu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9410: shes rab nyid thabs su dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9411: thabs shes dbyer med du sbyor ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9413: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9414: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems dkyil 'khor bde ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:9415: ye shes kyi ro dang bcas pa yab yum gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:9416: la rang chas su ldan pa de nyid rtogs par
NK064(ngu)001:9417: byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i lung rigs man ngag
NK064(ngu)001:9418: gsum gyis gtan la phab nas /
NK064(ngu)001:9419: yab yum lha'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa la skye
NK064(ngu)001:9420: mched rlob pa ni yan lag gi lha yab la
NK064(ngu)001:9421: yab dang yum la yum gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom zhing
NK064(ngu)001:9422: / mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara rlobs te snyoms
NK064(ngu)001:9423: 'jug gi brda bzhis bskul nas yab thabs kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:9424: 'khor dang yum shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis phyag
NK064(ngu)001:9425: rgya bzhis gnyis med du rol pa'i rjes chags kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9426: rkyen gyis rlung bskyod pas dmar cha 'bar ba des
NK064(ngu)001:9427: dkar cha zhu ba yas 'bab kyi dga' bzhi'i 'gros
NK064(ngu)001:9428: kyis phyin pa'i rim gyi zla ba rdo rje'i bum
NK064(ngu)001:9429: par 'dzag med du bzung ste gang ba las bde
NK064(ngu)001:9431: de nyid gnyis med kyi ye shes su gsal la mi rtog pas thugs kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK064(ngu)001:9432: de ltar myong ba'i tshe khams lnga'i bcud kun rdzob
NK064(ngu)001:9433: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas na
NK064(ngu)001:9435: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9436: de'i tshe yum gyi gsang ba pad+ma'i ze'u 'brur thig
NK064(ngu)001:9437: le nyi ma byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor snang
NK064(ngu)001:9439: de nyid thabs kyis zin na rtog tshogs sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:9440: ye shes su 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir dbyings
NK064(ngu)001:9442: yum gyi 'byung ba'i dwangs ma cha phra ba ni shes rab rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9443: chen po ste rags pa rigs kyi yab de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:9444: gshegs pa lngar gsal ba ste lhun gyis grub cing
NK064(ngu)001:9445: / byang chub sems kyi bde bas rtog tshogs thams
NK064(ngu)001:9446: cad ni sku dang ye shes kyi rdo rje dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:9448: de'ang dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams lhar yongs
NK064(ngu)001:9449: su dag pas spyod yul kun tu bzang po'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:9450: 'khor la sems lnga mthar phyin pa'i lhan skyes bde
NK064(ngu)001:9451: ba'i ye shes zag pa med pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK064(ngu)001:9452: po skyes pa de nyams su myong bas lhag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9453: thugs kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo bde ba chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:9454: ro ye shes lngar 'char ba las blta bya lta
NK064(ngu)001:9455: byed med pa'i tshul gyis blta zhing rang gsal ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:9457: snying po'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9458: yab yum gyi rtsa thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9459: snying po nyi zla'i dwangs ma thig le dus gcig
NK064(ngu)001:9460: tu mnyam par sbyor bas dngos po lhan cig skyes
NK064(ngu)001:9461: pa bde ba'i ye shes nyams su myong nas /
NK064(ngu)001:9462: slar yang dga' bzhi lugs ldog gi 'gros kyis myong
NK064(ngu)001:9463: ba'i bde ba mchog tu gsang ba'i rol mo yis
NK064(ngu)001:9464: rtog tshogs rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9465: su rnam par grol bas rab tu dgyes par gyur
NK064(ngu)001:9466: pa'i dkyil 'khor la bde stong gnyis su med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9468: de ltar tshogs drug gi rten gyi dwangs ma thams
NK064(ngu)001:9469: cad dbab bzung ldog pa'i thabs kyis tshogs brgyad rtog
NK064(ngu)001:9470: pa'i dngos po thams cad lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9471: su rang gsal bas zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9472: kyi ro ma 'gags par myong ba bsod nams kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9473: tshogs kyis bde ba'i ye shes sgyu ma lta bur
NK064(ngu)001:9474: snang la 'dzin med du spyod pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:9475: pa dang / 'dod chags bde stong gi ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9476: su rang snang ba'i rol mos rtog tshogs sku dang
NK064(ngu)001:9477: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab pas mtha'
NK064(ngu)001:9478: yas pa'i mchog tu rang gsal zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9479: nyi zla gnyis med kyi ye shes nyams su myong dka' bas gsang ba'i thig le ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9480: de nyid 'bras chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dbyings so //
NK064(ngu)001:9481: de ltar bsgoms pa'i yon tan kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:9482: bde ba chen po'i ye shes de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9483: de thob pa'i tshe phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9484: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung yon tan phrin
NK064(ngu)001:9485: las thugs te 'bras chos nyi shu rtsa lnga ma
NK064(ngu)001:9486: lus pa mngon du byas shing bdag nyid kyi zhal
NK064(ngu)001:9487: mthong ba med pa'i tshul gyis mthong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9488: 'dzag med kyi bde bas dbang po'i sdug bsngal bcom
NK064(ngu)001:9489: ste 'dod chags bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK064(ngu)001:9490: shes su dbang bsgyur bas na lam gyi nang nas
NK064(ngu)001:9491: mchog nyid dang / thabs kyi nang nas dam pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9492: bde myur gyi lam rmad du byung ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9493: de ltar 'og sgo thig le'i rnal 'byor nyams su
NK064(ngu)001:9494: blangs pa'i tshe gnas skabs la ltos pa'i dga' ba
NK064(ngu)001:9495: bzhi ni / snyoms par zhugs pas dang por thig le gnas nas g.yos pa ni dga' ba /
NK064(ngu)001:9496: bde ba nyams su myong ba ni mchog dga' /
NK064(ngu)001:9497: bde ba'i ngo bor sems 'gags pas stong par grol ba ni dga' bral /
NK064(ngu)001:9498: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po bde stong dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:9499: nyams su myong ba ni lhan skyes kyis dga' ba
NK064(ngu)001:9500: ste / lugs 'byung lugs ldog gi 'gros kyis dga'
NK064(ngu)001:9501: ba bzhi bzhi lus kyi gnas bzhi dang yang sbyar
NK064(ngu)001:9502: ste / la bshad do // de re re la'ang dga' ba'i dga' ba sogs bcu drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9504: gnas ni ye shes bcu drug po //
NK064(ngu)001:9505: tshogs sbyor la sogs dang po nas //
NK064(ngu)001:9506: mthar phyin sangs rgyas sa nyid de //
NK064(ngu)001:9507: gnas bzhi de bzhin dbye ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:9508: gnyis pa'i gnyis pa rab dga' sogs //
NK064(ngu)001:9509: pha rol phyin dang sa mtshan nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:9510: mtshungs phyir rdzogs par bshad pa yin //
NK064(ngu)001:9511: zhes pas dga' ba'i dga' ba bzhi tshogs lam sogs
NK064(ngu)001:9512: sngar dbang gi dus sbyar ba ltar las yas 'bab
NK064(ngu)001:9514: mas brtan la 'bras bu'i sa lam khyad par gyi sa gsum dang bcas pa rdzogs tshul sbyar zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9515: de'i tshe pha rol tu phyin pa bcu yang rdzogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9516: byang sems rtsa gnas thams cad du khyab par gtong ba sbyin pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9517: 'dzag med du sdom pa tshul khrims /
NK064(ngu)001:9518: thabs la mi skrag pa bzod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9520: de'i ngang las mi g.yo ba bsam gtan /
NK064(ngu)001:9521: rtog tshogs bde chen du shar ba shes rab /
NK064(ngu)001:9522: spyad kyang nyon mongs pas mi gos pa thabs /
NK064(ngu)001:9523: rnam rtog dus gcig la 'joms pas stobs /
NK064(ngu)001:9524: 'bras bu la smon pas smon lam /
NK064(ngu)001:9525: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes myong ba ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9526: gsum pa mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9527: dkyil 'khor la gnas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9528: thabs grol lam gyi dkyil 'khor la goms pa mthar
NK064(ngu)001:9529: phyin pa'i mthus gzhi gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor de
NK064(ngu)001:9530: nyid mngon du rtogs pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa rang
NK064(ngu)001:9531: bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor rang rig
NK064(ngu)001:9532: la lhun gyis grub par snang ba'i tshe ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9533: kyi rang bzhin rig pa'i rgyan du phyogs bcu dus
NK064(ngu)001:9534: bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams
NK064(ngu)001:9535: cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su thogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9536: 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad kyis mdzes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9537: de ltar spangs rtogs rdzogs pa 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:9538: rang snang gi sku gsum dbyer mi phyed par mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:9539: par sbyor ba las gdul bya 'dul byed thugs rje'i
NK064(ngu)001:9540: dkyil 'khor btsal ba med par yongs te swa yam
NK064(ngu)001:9541: b+hu'i sgra las rang byung gis 'byung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9542: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i gdul bya'i zhing khams
NK064(ngu)001:9543: kun tu gzhan snang gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor gang la
NK064(ngu)001:9544: gang gis 'dul zhing skyob pa'i mgon po sgyu ma
NK064(ngu)001:9545: lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du snang bas med snang sgyu
NK064(ngu)001:9546: ma lta bu'i 'khor ba las sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK064(ngu)001:9547: sems can rnams rang gnas su sgrol ba'i phrin las
NK064(ngu)001:9548: kyis don mdzad pa ltar snang yang /
NK064(ngu)001:9549: snang dus nyid nas bsgral bya sems can dang sgrol
NK064(ngu)001:9550: byed sprul pa gnyis ka rang mtshan pa med par
NK064(ngu)001:9551: sgyu ma'i skyes bus sgyu ma'i skye bo mang po
NK064(ngu)001:9552: sgyu ma'i sdug bsngal las bton nas sgyu ma'i bde
NK064(ngu)001:9553: ba la 'god pa'i tshul gyis 'dul byed sprul pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9554: dkyil 'khor gyis 'dul ba'i spyod pa ston par mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:9555: do // gnyis pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9556: ye shes rdzogs pa'i sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9557: chos thams cad ye nas rnam par dag pa rang
NK064(ngu)001:9558: byung gi ye shes chen por lhun gyis rdzogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:9559: rang bzhin gzhi'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa la ji
NK064(ngu)001:9561: de ltar gnas pa'i don dge ba'i bshes gnyen las
NK064(ngu)001:9562: thos shing bsam pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs par byas
NK064(ngu)001:9563: nas sgom pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs don goms par
NK064(ngu)001:9564: byas te / gnas lugs kyi don la blo mnyam
NK064(ngu)001:9565: par sbyor ba'i thabs kyis yin lugs ji lta ba
NK064(ngu)001:9566: ltar mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu rang byung
NK064(ngu)001:9567: ba sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:9568: bas gdul bya'i don la thugs rje chen po kun
NK064(ngu)001:9569: nas ngam pa'i phrin las lhun gyis grub par snang
NK064(ngu)001:9570: byas te / ngo // tshul 'di ni dus gsum
NK064(ngu)001:9571: gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9572: lam yin pas bla na med pa'i byang chub don
NK064(ngu)001:9573: du gnyer ba rnams kyis 'da' bar mi mdzad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9574: dam tshig mchog tu bstan to //
NK064(ngu)001:9575: gnyis pa de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9576: sgrub pa po gang zag gi che ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9577: sgrub thabs lam gyi che ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9579: gang zhig sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9580: sgrub pa po gang zhig rgyud 'di la mos par
NK064(ngu)001:9581: gyur pa tsam yang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:9582: bcur bzhugs pa thams cad kyis phyogs dang dus kun
NK064(ngu)001:9583: nas gzigs te / rnam pa thams cad du gsang
NK064(ngu)001:9584: ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus rgyud la bsnyen te thob
NK064(ngu)001:9585: par byed pa'i nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:9586: nas gzigs te / te / dper na sangs rgyas
NK064(ngu)001:9587: kyi nye ba'i sras nyan rang sogs ma yin par
NK064(ngu)001:9588: dgongs pa mthun par skyes pa thabs la mkhas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9589: byang chub sems dpa' rnams yin pa bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:9591: lam kun gyi 'bras bu yin pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9592: rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9593: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9594: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9596: skal pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9597: dus bskal pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phran
NK064(ngu)001:9598: kyi zhing gi rdul phran gyi grangs dang mnyam pa
NK064(ngu)001:9599: de snyed du rgyu'i theg par shin tu blo sbyangs
NK064(ngu)001:9600: pa la rab tu gnas shing brtson pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9601: gsang sngags phyi nang gi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK064(ngu)001:9602: bsnyen cing sgrub pa de thams cad kyis don du
NK064(ngu)001:9603: gnyer bya'i 'bras bu 'tshang rgya ba la lam gsang
NK064(ngu)001:9604: chen bla na med pa'i theg pa 'di kho na
NK064(ngu)001:9605: la rag las pa yin te gzhan med do //
NK064(ngu)001:9607: 'jig rten sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9608: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i zhing na sngar 'das pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9609: da ltar byung nas don mdzad pa'i rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:9610: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyang lam 'di la
NK064(ngu)001:9611: bsnyen pa ste brten nas 'bras bu sku lnga lhun
NK064(ngu)001:9612: gyis rdzogs te / rgyal ba kun gyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9614: 'byung dang sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9615: de ltar 'byung bzhin pa dang ma 'ongs pa na
NK064(ngu)001:9616: 'byung 'gyur gyi rnal 'byor pa thams cad kun kyang
NK064(ngu)001:9617: lam 'di yis 'bras bu lhun gyis grub par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:9619: 'di ni sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9620: rgyud 'di ni gsang chen nges pa'i don rmad du
NK064(ngu)001:9621: byung ba ste 'bras bu'i ngo bo ye nas sangs
NK064(ngu)001:9622: rgyas pa'i don lam du byas pas bsgrub bya gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:9623: nas sgrub mi dgos par 'grub pa'i nye lam du
NK064(ngu)001:9624: gyur pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9625: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK064(ngu)001:9626: thams cad la dgongs pa'i zhe phugs 'di las bzang
NK064(ngu)001:9627: ba'i lam gsang ba'i nges don gzhan zhig med nges
NK064(ngu)001:9628: yin pas btsal kyang gzhan gyis rnyed pa lta zhog
NK064(ngu)001:9629: rgyal bas kyang mi brnyes so ste mi rnyed do
NK064(ngu)001:9630: // gsum pa yul gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9631: snod dang ldan la sbyin pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9632: snod min la mi sbyin par bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9634: kun gyi sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9635: sangs rgyas kun gyi bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya chen
NK064(ngu)001:9636: po mchog tu gyur pa'i man ngag 'di ni thos
NK064(ngu)001:9637: bsam sgom gsum la blo rab tu sbyangs pa'i shes
NK064(ngu)001:9638: rab rnam pa gsum gyi mig dang ldan pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:9639: kyis ma nub par bzung la /
NK064(ngu)001:9640: skal ldan gyi slob ma zab don la mi skrag pas snod dang ldan cing /
NK064(ngu)001:9641: ngang tshul dge zhing bzang la dad pa brtan pas
NK064(ngu)001:9642: chos phyir lus dang longs spyod thams cad gtong nus
NK064(ngu)001:9643: pa rtag tu ngu lta bu de la yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:9646: gzhan du sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9647: de las gzhan du snod min la nam yang sbyin par mi bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9648: nyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9650: rmongs pa la 'phyar bas gsang ma thub par gal
NK064(ngu)001:9651: te sbyin na bka'i chad pas 'chi ba'i dus min
NK064(ngu)001:9652: par glo bur du ni srog zad nas tshe'i dus
NK064(ngu)001:9653: byed cing / shi ma thag tsha dmyal gyi mes bsreg pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9654: grang dmyal gyi chus sbrebs par byed pa'i sdug bsngal
NK064(ngu)001:9655: la yun ring gnas te nyam thag par 'gyur ro
NK064(ngu)001:9658: de skad ces ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK064(ngu)001:9659: kyis 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched
NK064(ngu)001:9663: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:9664: 'dis theg pa 'og ma rnams la shin tu gsang
NK064(ngu)001:9665: ba'i don tshe 'di nyid la grol ba'i thabs nye
NK064(ngu)001:9666: bar bstan pa'i man ngag zab cing snying por dril
NK064(ngu)001:9667: ba'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9669: // le'u bcu bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9675: lam thabs grol gyi man ngag snying po bstan pa
NK064(ngu)001:9676: de nas rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9677: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po
NK064(ngu)001:9678: rigs drug pas nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:9679: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:9680: la dgyes pa chen po'i glu drug po 'di blangs
NK064(ngu)001:9681: so // gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9682: 'bras chos nyer lnga so sor bstod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9685: dang po sku lnga la bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9687: ni ye shes lnga'i yi ges glu'i 'go 'dren par byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9689: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad rang rig
NK064(ngu)001:9690: pa'i ye shes gcig la lhun gyis rdzogs pas sku
NK064(ngu)001:9691: gsum snang ba'i go 'byed pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9692: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9693: rig pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dbyings thig le
NK064(ngu)001:9694: chen po'i klong du grol ba ni chos kyi sku'o
NK064(ngu)001:9695: // bsod nams kyi tshogs las grub pa'i sku mtshan
NK064(ngu)001:9696: dpe'i dkyil 'khor dag pa'i gdul bya la snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:9697: // ni longs sku'o // gang la gang 'dul gyi
NK064(ngu)001:9698: sku yi bkod pa sna tshogs par ston pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:9699: // ni longs sku'o // sprul pa'i sku'o // snang
NK064(ngu)001:9700: stong dbyer mi phyed pa'i thig ler sku gsum po
NK064(ngu)001:9701: kun ro gcig tu rdzogs pa ni rdo rje'i sku'o
NK064(ngu)001:9702: // ni longs sku'o // sprul pa'i sku'o // // hohzhesa pa de la mnyes pa'i don no //
NK064(ngu)001:9703: gnyis pa gsung lnga la bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9704: rdo rje bsod nams sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9706: 'gro ba sgrol ba la thogs pa med pa rdo
NK064(ngu)001:9707: rje'i tshig gis gdul bya'i bsod nams dang mthun par
NK064(ngu)001:9708: ston pa brjod pa tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:9709: brjod med thig le chen po'i rang bzhin brjod pa
NK064(ngu)001:9710: thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa ni skye med don
NK064(ngu)001:9711: gyi gsung ngo // sgra thams cad rang rig pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9712: rdo rjer lhun gyis grub pas rig pa ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:9713: gsung gi dkyil 'khor cir yang ma 'gags par ldan
NK064(ngu)001:9714: pas brda sprod pa ni rig pa byin rlabs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9715: gyi gsung ngo // gsung ngo // don tha dad
NK064(ngu)001:9716: pa tshig gcig tu mi phyed par 'bab pas rdo
NK064(ngu)001:9717: rje'i sgra chen po ste rjod byed kyi tshig gcig
NK064(ngu)001:9718: gis brjod bya'i don mtha' yas pa go bar byed
NK064(ngu)001:9719: pa ni tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:9720: sku'i brdas thogs pa med par gdul bya'i blo la
NK064(ngu)001:9721: don 'jal bas dbang bsgyur ba ni rdo rje rgyal
NK064(ngu)001:9722: po ste dgongs pa brda'i gsung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:9723: sgra thams cad grags stong dbyer mi phyed pa thig
NK064(ngu)001:9724: le chen por grol ba ni rdo rje'i gsung ngo
NK064(ngu)001:9726: gsum pa thugs lnga la bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9729: me long ye shes ni ye shes gzhan gsum po 'char gzhi'i rten byed pas sku dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9730: sor rtog ye shes ni shes bya thams cad ma 'dres par gzigs nas chos ston pas gsung dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9731: chos dbyings ye shes ni snying por gyur pas thugs kyi thugs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9732: de gsum rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid chen po de la
NK064(ngu)001:9733: yon tan ma lus pa'i 'byung gnas mnyam nyid dang
NK064(ngu)001:9734: / gdul bya 'dul ba'i phrin las bya grub ye shes kyang kun tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9735: de ltar ye nas ye shes lngar lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:9736: ye shes re re la'ang lnga lnga 'dus pa'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:9737: rang byung gi ye shes chen po gcig gi ngo
NK064(ngu)001:9738: bor 'dus pa'i thig le che hohzhesa mnyes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9739: bzhi pa yon tan lnga la bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9741: ni yon tan lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9742: mtha' dbus gang du'ang mi dmigs shing cir yang ma
NK064(ngu)001:9743: 'gags pa'i sgyu 'phrul ris med kun khyab mnyam pa
NK064(ngu)001:9744: chen po chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:9745: zhing khams kyi yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:9746: rgya tshad kyis gzhal ba'i yul rang snang gi bkod
NK064(ngu)001:9747: pa dang bcas pa mtha' yas par kun nas snang
NK064(ngu)001:9748: ba ni gzhal yas khang gi yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:9749: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kyang gsal zhing
NK064(ngu)001:9750: dag pa'i 'od zer sna tshogs pa spro ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:9752: 'dod yon gyi lha mo re re yang mtha' yas
NK064(ngu)001:9753: pa phyogs bcu kun nas ma btsal bar lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:9754: grub cing / dbang po so so la thim pas
NK064(ngu)001:9755: dgyes dgur spyod pa ni longs spyod kyi yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:9756: grub cing / no // mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs
NK064(ngu)001:9757: yon tan sna tshogs pa thugs la mnga' bas seng
NK064(ngu)001:9758: ge la sogs pa lngas btegs pa'i khri'i steng du
NK064(ngu)001:9759: grub cing / no // / khu ba dag pa sku zla ba /
NK064(ngu)001:9760: rdul dag pa gsung nyi ma /
NK064(ngu)001:9761: rlung dag pas skyon gyis gos pa med pa thugs pad+ma'i gdan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9762: re ba skong bas rin chen sna tshogs pa'i khri
NK064(ngu)001:9763: rkang ste khyad par du 'phags pa gdan khri'i yon
NK064(ngu)001:9765: lnga pa phrin las lnga la bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9767: ni phrin las lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9768: don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul phra
NK064(ngu)001:9769: mo snyed kyi zhing khams dag pa dang ma dag
NK064(ngu)001:9770: pa kun tu / byed pa'i thabs rgyal ba rnams
NK064(ngu)001:9771: kyis gdul bya'i don rnams thogs pa med par mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:9772: pa'i phrin las rdul phran gyi grangs de snyed du
NK064(ngu)001:9778: don de dag byed pa'i mkhan po ni zhi ba
NK064(ngu)001:9779: dang khro bo sogs gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul
NK064(ngu)001:9780: pa yang rdul phran gyi grangs dang mnyam pa bsam
NK064(ngu)001:9783: sprul pa de dag gis zhing de dag tu skad
NK064(ngu)001:9784: cig yud tsam la 'bad rtsol med par phrin las
NK064(ngu)001:9785: bzhis don mdzad pa ni lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin
NK064(ngu)001:9787: gnyis pa spyir bstod pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:9790: phyogs bcu dus bzhi dang rang snang rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:9791: 'khor thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin ni sku
NK064(ngu)001:9792: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9793: de dag gi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK064(ngu)001:9794: thams cad sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs rgyal ba
NK064(ngu)001:9795: drug pa'i bdag nyid chen por 'du zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9796: khyab byed rigs drug pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:9797: phrin las lnga char gyis kyang khyab bya rgyal ba
NK064(ngu)001:9798: thams cad la kun tu khyab bo //
NK064(ngu)001:9799: de'i phyir mtsho gcig tu gangs lnga'i gzugs brnyan 'char ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9800: gangs gcig mtsho lngar 'char ba'i dpes sku gsung thugs
NK064(ngu)001:9801: yon tan phrin las kyi snang tshul kun gcig gi
NK064(ngu)001:9803: gcig kun tu 'char bas na gcig dang du ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:9804: mtha' las grol ba thig le chen po'i rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:9806: de skad ces rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen pos ched du bsgrags so //
NK064(ngu)001:9809: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:9810: 'dis mnyes pa chen po'i glus nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9812: // le'u bco lnga pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9816: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad tshul mdor bstan /
NK064(ngu)001:9817: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9819: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9820: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas khro bo'i
NK064(ngu)001:9821: dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK064(ngu)001:9822: thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang
NK064(ngu)001:9823: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:9824: ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa nyid kyis rang snang
NK064(ngu)001:9825: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor las ma g.yos par
NK064(ngu)001:9826: 'dul byed sprul pa sku'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ji
NK064(ngu)001:9827: ltar 'tshams pa mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK064(ngu)001:9829: mnyam nyid ngang gi khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK064(ngu)001:9830: khro bas longs spyod rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK064(ngu)001:9831: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK064(ngu)001:9833: sbyir khro bo la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9834: bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab ni ngang gis khro ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9835: des rnam rtog gi mtshan ma 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9836: rang rig pa'i ye shes ni rtogs pa ngang gis khro ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9837: des 'khor ba'i sa bon drung nas 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9838: thugs rje ni shugs kyis khro ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9839: des 'gro ba skyob pa na 'bad rtsol med par mi mthun phyogs 'joms pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9840: phrin las phyag rgya'i khro bo ni gdul bya'i dbang gis khro bor ston pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9841: ji ltar 'tshams par 'byung bas gdul bya nam yang mi 'dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9842: de ltar bzhi las 'dir ni phyi ma phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9844: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK064(ngu)001:9845: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK064(ngu)001:9846: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK064(ngu)001:9847: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK064(ngu)001:9851: gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs /
NK064(ngu)001:9854: rgyu gang gis gol ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9855: gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9857: de ci'i phyir nas rmongs pas zhes pa'i bar te /
NK064(ngu)001:9858: de ltar 'dul byed khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par
NK064(ngu)001:9859: 'du mdzad pa de dgos ched ci'i phyir zhe na
NK064(ngu)001:9861: gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i ched du'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9862: de su zhig snyam pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:9863: spyir srid pa'i rtsa ba bdag tu rmongs pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:9864: rig pa'i rnam par rtog pas nga dang bdag tu
NK064(ngu)001:9865: zhen pa dang / chos thams cad blos sgro btags tsam las bden par grub pa ma yin kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:9866: phyin ci log gis gzung yul la bdag gir mngon par zhen pas 'khor bar 'khyams shing gdung la /
NK064(ngu)001:9867: de las nges par 'byin byed yang dag pa'i lam
NK064(ngu)001:9868: dang bral ba dag ni srid par 'du byed pa
NK064(ngu)001:9869: yin la / de'i steng du khyad par r+au dra
NK064(ngu)001:9870: ni gab pa'i gsang ba gnas lugs de bzhin nyid
NK064(ngu)001:9871: ma rtogs par sbas pa'i gsang ba sbyor sgrol sogs
NK064(ngu)001:9872: spyod pa barlang po la mngon par 'chel nas byol
NK064(ngu)001:9874: de yang rgyu las dge sdig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9875: 'bras bu bde sdug gi 'brel ba la rmongs pa'i dbang gis /
NK064(ngu)001:9876: de ltar spyod pa rnams r+au trar gol ba'i rgyu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9877: dper na sngon bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su byung ba'i dge slong thar pa nag po de /
NK064(ngu)001:9878: gol gzhi thub dka' gzhon nus /
NK064(ngu)001:9879: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK064(ngu)001:9880: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:9881: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK064(ngu)001:9883: zhes gsungs pa la sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas gol ba bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:9884: gnyis pa gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9885: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9886: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la 'tshe ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:9889: yi dwags su skyes tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:9892: srid par skye ba'i sa bon mi dge ba'i las
NK064(ngu)001:9893: rtsub mos 'phangs nas bar do med par mtshams med
NK064(ngu)001:9894: pa'i rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal ba mnar med par
NK064(ngu)001:9896: de nyid du rab tu tsha bas bsregs pa'i sdug bsngal drag pos yun ring gdungs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9897: 'di bas shin tu grang yang ci ma rung snyam
NK064(ngu)001:9898: pa'i mod la kha ba dang bu yug sogs kyis
NK064(ngu)001:9899: rab tu sbrebs pas grang ba dang lus pad+ma ltar
NK064(ngu)001:9900: cher gas pa'i sdug bsngal drag po dag gis rab
NK064(ngu)001:9902: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal rab tu tsha ba la sogs pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9903: tsha ba nas yang sos kyi bar brgyad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9904: shin tu grang ba pad+ma ltar cher gas pa la
NK064(ngu)001:9905: sogs pa ste chu bur can gyi bar brgyad po
NK064(ngu)001:9906: dag tu tsha grang gi dmyal ba phan tshun zung
NK064(ngu)001:9907: re re zhing skye res kyis 'jig rten gyi khams
NK064(ngu)001:9908: de 'jig pa'i dus su 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:9909: dang gzhan du brgyud nas 'pho zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9911: 'jig rten gyi khams gcig chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:9912: po re re la bar bskal nyi shu nyi shu
NK064(ngu)001:9913: ste bsdoms pas bar bskal brgyad cu la bskal chen
NK064(ngu)001:9914: du byas pa'i bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu
NK064(ngu)001:9915: gnyis su tsha grang gi sdug bsngal myong ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:9917: de nas rnam par sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9918: de nas dmyal bar skye ba'i las kyi rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:9919: smin pa de myong stobs kyis zad pa dang yi
NK064(ngu)001:9921: ltogs pa dang skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu nyen pa spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9922: phyi rol gyi 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams kyang yid
NK064(ngu)001:9923: du mi 'ong ba chu rnag tu mthong ba lta
NK064(ngu)001:9924: bu phyi'i sgrib pa can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9925: bza' btung cung zad rnyed pa zos pa na gdug
NK064(ngu)001:9926: cing rtsub pa'i dngos po me sogs sna tshogs su
NK064(ngu)001:9927: 'gyur bas nang khrol sreg pa sogs me lce'i 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:9928: lo can dang / zas skom sogs mthong ba spyod
NK064(ngu)001:9929: 'dod pas drung du bsnyegs pa'i tshe yod pa rjes
NK064(ngu)001:9931: lus shin tu rid cing skam pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9932: lto ba ri bo tsam la rkang lag 'jag ma
NK064(ngu)001:9933: dang kha khab mig lta bu sogs lus dang yan
NK064(ngu)001:9934: lag dang dbang po rnams mi 'tshams par nyams thag
NK064(ngu)001:9935: par gyur pa de lta bur bskal pa chen po
NK064(ngu)001:9936: drug tu 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing skyes so
NK064(ngu)001:9937: // gnyis pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK064(ngu)001:9938: de nas las kyi sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9939: de nas yi dwags su skye ba'i las kyi sgrib
NK064(ngu)001:9940: pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa de yang khad
NK064(ngu)001:9942: sngon gyi dus su sngags lam las gol te khro
NK064(ngu)001:9943: bo dang phra men gyi lha rang rgyud du bsgoms
NK064(ngu)001:9944: nas drag sngags bzlas shing las barlang por spyad pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9945: srid pas r+au dra'i rgyud du mtshams sbyar nas /
NK064(ngu)001:9946: yi dwags kyi 'gro bas bsdus pa'i srin po chen
NK064(ngu)001:9947: po bya'i gshog pa can lus rab tu 'jigs shing
NK064(ngu)001:9948: / sems gdug pa khro zhing gtum po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9949: las kyi rdzu 'phrul lus gcig la mgo bo brgya yod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9950: de yang mgo brnyan mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9951: lus mi gcig pa brgya la mgo bo gcig las med pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9952: stag seng sogs kyi lus sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9953: lus gcig la yan lag mang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9954: yan lag rigs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9955: de dag gi mda' dang mdung thung sogs gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thogs pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9956: gsod byed kyi 'khor dred mo 'phar ba bya gcan sogs rab tu mang po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9957: 'jigs pa'i sbrul gzugs sdom sdig sogs sna tshogs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9958: 'jigs pa'i sgra ra la ra la sogs sna tshogs sgrog pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9961: mi zhim pa'i dri dang kha rlangs kyis nad gtong zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:9962: lus can thams cad skyi bung zhes dngangs par byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9963: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag gis phyogs kun khebs pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9964: grang ba dang tsha ba'i dbugs kyis phyogs bcu kun tu stong khams thams cad 'khrug par byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9965: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa las gyur pa'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhis 'debs par byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:9966: sems myos shing dran pa nyams par byed pa'i byed las kyi mthus klu'i ris dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9967: lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9969: gzugs khams las tshangs pa'i ris sogs bsam gtan dang po'i gnas gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9970: 'od gsal gyi bar gnyis pa'i gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9971: dge rgyas kyi bar gsum pa'i gsum dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9972: 'bras bu che ba'i bar bzhi pa'i gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:9973: gnas rim bcu gnyis pa man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK064(ngu)001:9974: gnyis pa gang gis ji ltar 'dul pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9975: gdul byar gzigs nas 'dul ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9979: r+au dra des sngon dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten cing
NK064(ngu)001:9980: sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa'i stobs kyis 'brel bas
NK064(ngu)001:9981: thams cad mkhyen pas 'dul ba'i dus la bab par
NK064(ngu)001:9982: gzigs nas thugs rje dang phrin las kyis 'dul bar
NK064(ngu)001:9983: gyur to // gnyis pa la bcu gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:9985: che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9987: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9988: byin gyis rlobs kyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9990: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9991: phrin las rmad du byung ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9993: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:9995: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK064(ngu)001:9997: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:9998: gdul bya bstan pa de nas 'dul byed ston pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:9999: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje gsum
NK064(ngu)001:10000: gyi dkyil 'khor bkod pa'i zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK064(ngu)001:10001: ba las / don bya ba'i yul 'jig rten drug
NK064(ngu)001:10002: gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyi bdag po dregs
NK064(ngu)001:10003: pa can r+au dra 'dul ba'i nga rgyal chen pos
NK064(ngu)001:10004: zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi brjid ston pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:10005: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK064(ngu)001:10006: dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i bdag po rigs drug
NK064(ngu)001:10007: pa bcom ldan 'das dregs pa 'dul ba'i thabs la
NK064(ngu)001:10008: dgyes pa chen po khro bo'i rgyal po che mchog
NK064(ngu)001:10009: he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam
NK064(ngu)001:10010: par 'phro ba'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i ting
NK064(ngu)001:10011: nge 'dzin la dgongs pa snyoms par zhugs pa ste
NK064(ngu)001:10013: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK064(ngu)001:10014: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba yi //
NK064(ngu)001:10015: nga rgyal chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:10019: de bzhin nyid kyi sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10020: chos nyid de bzhin nyid skye med kyi dbyings nas
NK064(ngu)001:10021: yum khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon du phyungs
NK064(ngu)001:10022: te / hi hi zhes yab la dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis bskul bas /
NK064(ngu)001:10023: thabs shes kyi mkha' gsang rin chen dang pad+ma bde
NK064(ngu)001:10024: bas rgyas par mdzad nas yab yum gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:10025: par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas pad+mara nor bu thim nas
NK064(ngu)001:10029: rgyu gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi sprin spros pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:10030: rkyen de'i tshe h+aum h+aum h+aum rdo rje gsum gyi bdag nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:10031: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la ni
NK064(ngu)001:10032: rdo rje khro bo sna tshogs 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:10034: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK064(ngu)001:10035: sgo gsum bkas shing gtor cig ces thugs bskul ba'i tshig sbyar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10036: de skad ces brjod pas yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams
NK064(ngu)001:10037: nas khro bo 'chol ba'i sprin spro ba'i rkyen byed
NK064(ngu)001:10040: gang du spro na 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa go mtshams med par khyab par /
NK064(ngu)001:10041: gang spro na khro bo 'chol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs /
NK064(ngu)001:10042: che chung stong gsum gyi 'jig rten tsam la grangs
NK064(ngu)001:10043: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi rdul phra mo snyed tsam
NK064(ngu)001:10044: 'thon pas stong khams gang bar gyur nas gdug pa
NK064(ngu)001:10045: can rnams bag 'khums par byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10048: de ltar khro bo'i sprin spros pa des 'jig rten
NK064(ngu)001:10049: drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad kyi sa rnam pa
NK064(ngu)001:10050: drug tu g.yos / rab tu g.yos /
NK064(ngu)001:10052: zin pa'i sgra thams cad drag por 'ur 'ur /
NK064(ngu)001:10055: ma zin pa'i sgra rnams kyang rang 'khrol du chem chem /
NK064(ngu)001:10058: ri gling sogs dum bur shig shig /
NK064(ngu)001:10064: de ltar phyi rol du ltas g.yos pa dang 'ur
NK064(ngu)001:10065: ba sogs sde tshan lnga po re re la'ang chung
NK064(ngu)001:10066: 'bring che gsum ste bco lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10067: nang du lam pa'i sems la tshogs sbyor gyi rnal
NK064(ngu)001:10068: 'byor lngar g.yo thob goms pa'i nyams gsum bogs 'thon
NK064(ngu)001:10071: de ltar ltas chen po bco lnga dang khro bo'i
NK064(ngu)001:10072: sprin tshogs mi bzad pa'i chos kun tu snang ba
NK064(ngu)001:10073: de'i tshe 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong gsum
NK064(ngu)001:10074: gyi khams thams cad na gnas pa'i gtso bo /
NK064(ngu)001:10075: so so'i gnas su dbang che ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10076: 'phrul dang gzi brjid che ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10077: nus mthu che ba'i ris dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10081: dregs pa can thams cad 'jigs shing skrag nas lus sar 'gyel zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:10083: sems myos nas dran pa nyams te brgyal /
NK064(ngu)001:10085: kun tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:10088: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po che mchog nyid /
NK064(ngu)001:10089: 'jigs byed chen po shin tu rngam pa'i sku gdug
NK064(ngu)001:10090: pa can rnams skyi bung zhes byed pa'i gzi byin
NK064(ngu)001:10091: 'bar ba chen po'i me 'od 'phro ba khrag 'thung
NK064(ngu)001:10092: smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba'i rnam pa can /
NK064(ngu)001:10093: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed ltar
NK064(ngu)001:10094: mtha' yas pas mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa de
NK064(ngu)001:10095: nyid la gong du spros pa'i khro bo'i sprin las
NK064(ngu)001:10096: rdo rje'i rigs kyi khro tshogs thams cad 'dus te
NK064(ngu)001:10097: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi bdag nyid badz+ra
NK064(ngu)001:10098: he ru ka / rnam thar gyi dbu gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:10100: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i rtags zhabs bzhi par gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:10101: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang chen por bzhugs par dgyes nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10102: mkha' rlung gi dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i khrag gi
NK064(ngu)001:10103: rgya mtshor chags pa zhing chen gyi sa gzhi'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:10104: na keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng /
NK064(ngu)001:10105: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba chen po'i klong /
NK064(ngu)001:10106: gzhal yas khang gi dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i dkyil na dbang phyug lha chen po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10107: dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa chen po r+au
NK064(ngu)001:10108: dra pho mo ste khyo shug byi chings su bsnol
NK064(ngu)001:10109: ba'i gdan la zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum du bzhugs
NK064(ngu)001:10110: so // 'dir zhabs g.yon brkyang du bzhed pa'ang snang mod /
NK064(ngu)001:10112: +aa l+ai d+ha p+aa da zhes g.yas brkyang gi skad dod yod do //
NK064(ngu)001:10113: de bzhin du bde gshegs rigs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10116: las kyi rigs kyi khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin
NK064(ngu)001:10117: phung de dag so sor 'dus pa las me long
NK064(ngu)001:10118: lta bu la sogs pa ye shes bzhi'i bdag nyid
NK064(ngu)001:10119: rigs bzhi'i he ru kar gyur pa'ang /
NK064(ngu)001:10120: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po zhes sbyar te /
NK064(ngu)001:10121: bud+d+ha he ru kar gyur te 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i shar phyogs su dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10122: rin po cher gyur te lho phyogs su dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10123: pad+mara gyur te nub phyogs su dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10124: kun tu las su gyur te byang phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu)001:10125: khrag 'thung de dag kun kyang 'jigs byed chen po'i cha lugs dur khrod kyi chas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10126: h+aum phata sogs rngam pa'i nga ro dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10127: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis /
NK064(ngu)001:10131: lhor gshin rje la sogs te gdug pa can thams
NK064(ngu)001:10132: cad bsdus pa khyo shug gi gdan la g.yas brkyang
NK064(ngu)001:10133: gis bzhugs so // btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo
NK064(ngu)001:10134: rigs lnga'i tshogs rnams kyang rigs so so'i he ru
NK064(ngu)001:10135: ka'i sku la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK064(ngu)001:10137: de nas dregs pa sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10138: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang bas dregs pa can
NK064(ngu)001:10139: gdan du byas pa de nas dregs pa chen po
NK064(ngu)001:10140: r+au dra la sogs pa pho rgyud rnams kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:10141: khro zhing gtum pa'i sems kyis dgra zlar mthong ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10142: lus gdan du gnas kyang gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen po sna tshogs bstan nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10143: 'khor bcas mgrin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ros mi
NK064(ngu)001:10144: snyan barlang po'i gtum tshig gis 'di skad du smras
NK064(ngu)001:10145: pa / nged rnams gdan du bcings pa las thong thong /
NK064(ngu)001:10146: khyed cag snying rje'i bdag po ma yin nam /
NK064(ngu)001:10147: ci bdag cag la de ltar tho 'tshams par byed dam /
NK064(ngu)001:10149: shin tu gdug pa'i sems kyis khros nas da dung rngam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:10150: de nas gdug pa can de dag gi gnyen por
NK064(ngu)001:10151: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po rigs lnga'i he
NK064(ngu)001:10152: ru ka nyid sgrol byed rdo rje srin po dbu
NK064(ngu)001:10153: dgu phyag bco brgyad zhabs brgyad du gnas par sprul
NK064(ngu)001:10154: nas / thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pa
NK064(ngu)001:10155: nyid kyis r+au dra'i ngor shin tu khros pa ltar
NK064(ngu)001:10156: snang nas rngam pa'i skad kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:10157: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes de dag gi sgo gsum bsdus shig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10158: ha ha ha zhes dug gsum zhal du gsol bar dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10159: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi zhes sha khrag rus gsum zo zhig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10160: sngags de skad ces brjod pas dbang phyug chen po
NK064(ngu)001:10161: la sogs pa gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag
NK064(ngu)001:10162: gi bdag 'dzin gcod phyir don snying dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10163: yul 'dzin gyi sgo dgag phyir dbang po kun phyung /
NK064(ngu)001:10164: mngon zhen dgag phyir nang khrol kun drangs /
NK064(ngu)001:10165: las ngan gyi bag chags gcod phyir yan lag kun dum bur bcad cing gtubs nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10166: dug gsum dag par mdzad pa'i phyir du gti mug sha kun zos /
NK064(ngu)001:10168: zhe sdang rus pa kun 'chos so //
NK064(ngu)001:10171: pho rgyud bsgral te btul ba de nas mo rgyud sbyor bas 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:10172: h+aum h+aum h+aum ni lus ngag yid gsum bsdus shig pa'i bskul tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:10173: b+h+yo ni ma mo rnams kyi snying po dang bod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10176: dzahdza dgug pa'i sa bon no //
NK064(ngu)001:10177: de skad ces brjod pas phyogs bcu'i snod kyi 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:10178: rten gyi khams nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa dang bcas
NK064(ngu)001:10179: pa kun ma lus par yungs 'bru gcig tsam du
NK064(ngu)001:10180: chud par dbang 'byor ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen pos bsdus
NK064(ngu)001:10181: so // de nas bcud kyi sems can 'byung po
NK064(ngu)001:10182: phal pa'i rigs ma lus pa'i rgyal po ni lha
NK064(ngu)001:10183: dang lha min gyi blon po chen po rnams yin
NK064(ngu)001:10184: so // la / de'i yang rgyal po ni dregs
NK064(ngu)001:10185: pa chen po srin po la sogs pa dbang phyug
NK064(ngu)001:10186: chen po pho rgyud nyi shu rtsa brgyad po yin
NK064(ngu)001:10187: so // la / pas / de rnams so so'i
NK064(ngu)001:10188: chung ma ni 'byung po mo rgyud phal pa'i rigs
NK064(ngu)001:10189: thams cad kyi rje mo ste blon po chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:10190: so // la / pas / chung ma / de
NK064(ngu)001:10191: tsho'i yang rje mor gyur pa dbang phyug ma nyi
NK064(ngu)001:10193: khyo'i ming chung mar grags pas /
NK064(ngu)001:10194: srin po da sha g+r+ai ba'i chung ma srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10196: lha chen drag po'i 'khrug mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10197: brgya byin gyi dbang mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10199: gdod drug gi gzhon nu mo dang drug ni shar gyi ma mo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10201: nyi ma'i bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10202: zla ba'i zhi ba mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10203: be con gyi be con mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10204: srin po khrag mig gi srin mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10205: lha za byed kyi za ba mo dang drug ni lho'i ma mo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10206: dga' byed dbang phyug gi dga' ba mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10207: stobs bzang gi ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10208: b+h+rim gi ri ti'i gcig pur spyod ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10210: nor srung gi grub mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10211: rlung lha'i rlung mo dang drug ni nub kyi ma mo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10212: lha gsod byed kyi gsod byed mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10214: sa bdag phag chen gyi phag mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10215: gshin rje'i rgan byed mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10216: tshogs bdag gi sna chen mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10217: klu'i chu lha mo dang drug ni byang gi ma mo'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10218: lha nag po chen po'i nag mo chen mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10219: ra gdong chen po'i ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10220: srin po bum rna'i bum rna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10221: gsus po che'i gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo dang bzhi ni sgo ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10222: de la sogs pa ma mo'i tshogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10225: nang gi las byed g.yog dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10226: de'i yang g.yog dang bcas pa 'khor zhing gi rdul
NK064(ngu)001:10227: snyed ltar mtha' yas pa thams cad kyang bsdus so
NK064(ngu)001:10229: de nas bcom ldan 'das sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10230: mo rgyud rnams bsdus pa de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK064(ngu)001:10231: dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo
NK064(ngu)001:10232: rje srin por snang ba des ma mo rnams 'dul
NK064(ngu)001:10233: ba'i thabs kyis / slar yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed
NK064(ngu)001:10234: chen po lnga ka yongs su rdzogs par ma mo
NK064(ngu)001:10235: rnams la snang bar byas nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10236: de dag kun kyang dgyes pa chen pos rol pa
NK064(ngu)001:10237: las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin 'byung ba zhes
NK064(ngu)001:10238: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NK064(ngu)001:10239: / sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las sngags 'di phyung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:10241: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje /
NK064(ngu)001:10242: pra be sha rab tu zhugs pa ste gsang ba'i pad+mara ro //
NK064(ngu)001:10243: a la la hohdagyesa pas ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10246: de skad ces brjod pas 'byung mo'i rgyal mo rnams
NK064(ngu)001:10247: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang ba la shin tu
NK064(ngu)001:10249: rang rang gi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor sdud pa ste 'dzum zhing rgyas par gyur nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10250: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul
NK064(ngu)001:10251: du dbang mo rnams bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen
NK064(ngu)001:10252: po he ru ka rigs lnga'i sku la 'khril te
NK064(ngu)001:10253: / 'di ltar dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje he ru ka'i sku brgyad du snang ba la /
NK064(ngu)001:10254: phyogs kyi gtso mo srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo sogs bzhi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10255: sgo skyong nag mo chen mo sogs bzhi ste brgyad po rnams so sor 'khril to //
NK064(ngu)001:10256: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs bzhi po lnga lngar snang ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10257: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la tshangs ma sogs shar phyogs kyi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK064(ngu)001:10258: rin po che'i sku la bdud rtsi mo sogs lho'i ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK064(ngu)001:10259: pad+ma'i sku la khrag gis myos ma sogs nub kyi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK064(ngu)001:10260: ku na tu las kyi sku la mi mo sogs byang gi ma mo lnga rnams 'khril to //
NK064(ngu)001:10261: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po rigs
NK064(ngu)001:10262: lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis h+aum zhes
NK064(ngu)001:10263: brjod pas dbang mo rnams kyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK064(ngu)001:10264: tshogs rigs lnga'i rdo rje la bsdus nas sku'i stod
NK064(ngu)001:10265: smad shin tu bcum pas rol par gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:10266: bcu gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10269: sgo ma rnams spro ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10273: gnyis med du rol pa de nas dgyes te ha
NK064(ngu)001:10274: zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgras sbyor mtshams nas yab yum
NK064(ngu)001:10275: gyi byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK064(ngu)001:10276: zhi ba'i las kyis dag par byed pa dkar mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10277: dbang gis sdud pa rkun mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10278: zhi bas spang blang 'byed pa med pa'i dbyings su sbyar ba rmongs mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10279: drag pos mi mthun pa 'joms pa thal byed ma'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10280: rgyas pas yon tan gyis gang ba sbom mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10281: drag pos zhe gcod pa gtum mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10282: las thams cad pas gang yang 'grub pa sme sha can gyi tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10283: rgyas pas 'phel ba'i las sgrub pa ma tshogs ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:10284: tshogs rnams zhing dbyug dang thod khrag sogs rang rang
NK064(ngu)001:10286: ngo mtshar ba'i gzugs rgyan dang bcas pas dbang mo'i mkha' nas phyir 'thon to //
NK064(ngu)001:10287: gnas ma brgyad po re re yang nyi shu rtsa
NK064(ngu)001:10288: brgyad du 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba
NK064(ngu)001:10289: chen po'i 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan dang gru chad bzhir
NK064(ngu)001:10290: shar lho'i phyogs nas g.yas bskor gyis 'khor bar 'jigs
NK064(ngu)001:10291: pa'i gzugs rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas nas
NK064(ngu)001:10294: gnas ma 'thon pa de nas shin tu dgyes nas
NK064(ngu)001:10295: he zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgra dang sems sprin las
NK064(ngu)001:10296: / rtog pa zil gyis gnon pa seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10297: de bzhin du dpa' zhing brtul phod pa stag gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10298: thabs la mkhas pas phung po'i bdud 'joms pa wa gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10299: mel tshe mkhas shing lha'i bu'i bdud 'joms pa khyi gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10300: mig rno zhing shes bya la thogs pa med pa bzhad gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10301: dbugs bral la spyod cing 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms pa kang+ka'i gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10302: nyon mongs pa zad par byed pa khwa gdong /
NK064(ngu)001:10303: gdul bya phra ba'ang mi 'dor ba 'ug gdong ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10304: de ltar phra men chen mo re re'ang nyer brgyad kyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams /
NK064(ngu)001:10305: lag gnyis gyen du bsnol bas ro bzung ba sogs
NK064(ngu)001:10306: rang rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du bcas
NK064(ngu)001:10308: 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:10309: 'khor lo'i phyi rol gser khyams la shar phyogs nas
NK064(ngu)001:10310: 'khor bar phyogs bzhir mche ba can dang mtshams bzhir
NK064(ngu)001:10311: gshog pa can bzhi rngams pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod do
NK064(ngu)001:10314: yul ma 'thon pa de nas shin tu dgyes pas
NK064(ngu)001:10315: phrin las bzhi'i snang bas phyogs bcu'i zhing khams ma
NK064(ngu)001:10316: lus par khyab nas phata ces brjod pa'i bzhad sgra
NK064(ngu)001:10318: byams pas mi gtong bar 'dzin pa rdo rje sring 'gro rta gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10319: snying rjes 'ching ba rdo rje gdong mo phag gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10320: dga' bas sdom pa rdo rje 'jig rten seng gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10321: btang snyoms kyis myos par byed pa rdo rje ro
NK064(ngu)001:10322: langs spyang gdong ma'i tshogs rnams lcags kyu sogs rang
NK064(ngu)001:10323: rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du bcas nas
NK064(ngu)001:10325: 'thon nas kyang nyer brgyad po rigs bsdus te 'bar
NK064(ngu)001:10326: ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhir shin tu
NK064(ngu)001:10327: rngam pa'i gzugs kyis gnas so //
NK064(ngu)001:10328: gang dag sras mo nyi shu po spro ba'i yum
NK064(ngu)001:10329: 'dir dbang mo dang sgrub thabs su rigs kyi yum
NK064(ngu)001:10330: lngas byas pa gnyis 'gal lo zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:10331: 'dir sngon byung dregs pa 'dul ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10332: sgrub thabs kyi dus rjes 'jug nyams len gyi dbang du yin pas 'gal ba med do //
NK064(ngu)001:10335: dkyil 'khor 'god pa'i mdzad pa rdzogs pa de nas
NK064(ngu)001:10336: yab yum dgyes par rol pa'i sprin las phyogs bcu
NK064(ngu)001:10337: nas phata ces bsgrags pas thams cad rngams shing khros
NK064(ngu)001:10338: nas ma mo thams cad kyang sngon gang nas 'ongs
NK064(ngu)001:10339: pa'i rang rang gi gnas ga la ba der yud
NK064(ngu)001:10340: tsam la rdzu 'phrul gyis phyin par bakye'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10341: gsum pa de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10342: dbang bskur te gnas spar nas snang 'byed kyi ting 'dzin thob pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10343: 'bangs su dam bcas nas lus gdan du phul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:10344: 'khor phul te gus pas mchod par dam bcas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10345: dbang mo rnams las nod pa la dbang bskur nas mu ran la bkod tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:10347: de nas bcom ldan 'das sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10348: sbyor sgrol gyi phrin las rmad du byung ba bstan
NK064(ngu)001:10349: pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po
NK064(ngu)001:10350: dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga po de dag
NK064(ngu)001:10351: kun badz+ra he ru kar bsdus pa nyid rang byung
NK064(ngu)001:10352: gi thugs rje chen po gso bar byed pas bdud
NK064(ngu)001:10353: rtsi 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK064(ngu)001:10354: snyoms par zhugs nas sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:10355: mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las dbang bskur ba'i dam
NK064(ngu)001:10356: rdzas sngags dang bcas pa 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:10357: sngar zhal du bstabs pa'i dbang phyug chen po la
NK064(ngu)001:10358: sogs pa de rnams thams cad bcom ldan 'das khro
NK064(ngu)001:10359: bo chen po de dag gi lto ba na gnas
NK064(ngu)001:10360: pa dpal chen po'i bsnams te gshang lam nas bton
NK064(ngu)001:10361: te mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud pa
NK064(ngu)001:10362: las / slar yang bsnams nas u tsush+ma kro d+ha
NK064(ngu)001:10363: zhes pa khro mo rme ba brtsegs pa dang dam
NK064(ngu)001:10364: rdzas bdud rtsi phyungs nas badz+ra ma h+aa a mri
NK064(ngu)001:10365: ta mchog ster rdo rje bdud rtsi chen po /
NK064(ngu)001:10366: ma h+aa kro d+ha khro bo chen po /
NK064(ngu)001:10367: am am am zhes brjod pas lan gsum dam rdzas bdud rtsi lcer bzhag cing dbang bskur /
NK064(ngu)001:10368: rme ba brtsegs pas 'dam kun 'thungs te gsos pas
NK064(ngu)001:10369: dregs pa can de dag dran pa slar rnyed nas
NK064(ngu)001:10370: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob
NK064(ngu)001:10371: pas 'bar ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs bsam
NK064(ngu)001:10372: yas lhun grub kyi zhal mngon sum du mthong ste
NK064(ngu)001:10373: / khro bo de dag thams cad kyang dbu dgu brgya pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10376: sku gzi byin mtha' yas pa 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par mthong ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:10377: ye shes kyi cho 'phrul gyis sprul pa'i r+au dra btul ba de'i dus su /
NK064(ngu)001:10378: gdul bar bya ba'i yul 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:10379: bcu'i srid pa gsum po kun tu gnas shing dbang
NK064(ngu)001:10380: sgyur ba'i dregs pa'i dbang phyug chen po thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:10381: gang la gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:10382: sgo sna tshogs su snang ba'i rol ba bsam gyis
NK064(ngu)001:10383: mi khyab par rang rang gi zhing so sor snang
NK064(ngu)001:10384: ba'i snga phyi med pa dus gcig tu btul lo
NK064(ngu)001:10385: // 'o na skabs 'dir bstan gyi gdul bya sprul pa yin par gang gis shes snyam na /
NK064(ngu)001:10387: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis tshul du bstan par rig par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10388: de la dgos pa dang dgongs pa ci yod ce na /
NK064(ngu)001:10389: rang rgyud pa'i gol sa dgag pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10390: che ba'i mthu'i tshad bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10391: nang du bdud bzhi btul ba'i rtags phyi rol du bstan par 'brel to //
NK064(ngu)001:10393: ji skad bshad pa'i mthu 'di dag rang rgyud pa la yod pa ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:10394: sprul pa ba yin par som nyi mi bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10396: de ltar na gong du bdag tu rmongs pa'i zhes sogs kyis gnod do zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:10398: phyis 'jig rten du cha lugs dang mthu cha 'dra
NK064(ngu)001:10399: ba'i r+au dra rang mtshan pa 'byung ba rnams rgyu
NK064(ngu)001:10400: de lta bus bskyed par ston pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10402: gnyen po mchog rnams nyes pas mi gos par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:10403: rgyal bas sor mo'i phreng ba can sprul nas btul ba bzhin thabs kyi che ba dbyung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10404: sngags lam pa'i gol sa dgag pa'i ched du thabs la mkhas pa'i cho 'phrul rmad du byung ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10406: de nas de dag sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10407: gnas spar ba de nas dregs pa can de dag skrag pas lus shin tu 'dar zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:10408: sems bred pas rab tu dpa' zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK064(ngu)001:10409: bdag cag khyed kyi 'bangs su mchi /
NK064(ngu)001:10411: gal te 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na /
NK064(ngu)001:10412: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo dang lus ni dum bu brgyar 'gas shing /
