NK064(ngu)001:10413: snying yang tshal par 'gas shing dum bur gtub par gyur cig /
NK064(ngu)001:10414: lus kyang rul zhing myags la dmod tshig gi mes 'tshig nas thal bar brlag pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10415: tshe phyi mar yang rdo rje'i dmyal bar lhungs nas 'o dod 'bod par shog /
NK064(ngu)001:10416: de skad ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor nas
NK064(ngu)001:10417: rang rang gi lus khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:10418: gyi gdan du phul nas bzhag go //
NK064(ngu)001:10421: dregs pa can thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu yang smras pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10422: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang chung ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10424: sring mo rnams kyang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor chen por 'bul bas bzhes su gsol /
NK064(ngu)001:10425: gang gis na dregs pa can 'joms pa'i dpa' bo
NK064(ngu)001:10426: lha chen po rnams kyi yang rje bor gyur pa
NK064(ngu)001:10427: dpal he ru kas bzhes su gsol /
NK064(ngu)001:10429: mchod par dam bca' ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10430: bdag cag so sor 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:10431: 'di ltar zhal mthong ba'i khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:10432: 'khor chen po 'di'i ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10433: rnal 'byor pa yang rang gi gtsug gi nor bu
NK064(ngu)001:10434: 'od 'bar ba bkur ba ltar sems la g.yo sgyu
NK064(ngu)001:10435: med cing mchog tu gus pa dang ldan pa'i sems
NK064(ngu)001:10436: kyi blos blangs nas rnam pa thams cad du spyi
NK064(ngu)001:10437: bo'i gtsug tu bzhag ste bkur sti dang rim gro
NK064(ngu)001:10438: phun sum tshogs par bgyi bas /
NK064(ngu)001:10439: dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan 'chang ba de'i dgos pa'i las ci yin yang rung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10440: 'dod pa'i re ba ma lus pa rdzogs par bdag cag rnams kyis sgrub bo //
NK064(ngu)001:10441: gal te dpa' bo he ru ka'i spyan snga 'dir
NK064(ngu)001:10442: bdag cag rnams kyis yal gam bcas pa'i tha tshig
NK064(ngu)001:10443: smras pa 'di bzhin du ma bsgrubs na /
NK064(ngu)001:10444: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo tshal par bkas shing /
NK064(ngu)001:10445: lus dmod pa'i mtshon gyis gtubs te snying yang dum bur 'thor nas rul bar mchi'o zhes smras so //
NK064(ngu)001:10448: bro bor ba de nas dregs pa can de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10451: bu mo'i tshogs thams cad sngar bkye ba las slar
NK064(ngu)001:10452: yang dkyil 'khor gyi drung du yud tsam gyis 'ongs
NK064(ngu)001:10453: nas / de dag thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu smras pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10454: bdag cag dbang mo 'khor gyi tshogs dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:10455: thams cad kun g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba'i dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:10456: bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi bar bgyi na dpa'
NK064(ngu)001:10457: bo chen pos bdag cag rnams la /
NK064(ngu)001:10458: phrin las rnam pa bzhi las 'di dang 'di gyis
NK064(ngu)001:10459: shig ces las gang byed kyi bka'i bsgo ba skal
NK064(ngu)001:10460: ba dang mthun pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol zhes
NK064(ngu)001:10461: smras so // ci bgyi zhus pa de nas bcom
NK064(ngu)001:10462: ldan dgyes pa chen pos de rnams kyi lag tu
NK064(ngu)001:10464: rdo rje mi'i srin mo sogs rang rang dang mthun pa'i ming gi dbang bskur te /
NK064(ngu)001:10465: dkyil 'khor chen po'i gser khyams kyi phyi rol du
NK064(ngu)001:10466: khrag khyams la so so'i las bskos pa'i phyogs kyi
NK064(ngu)001:10467: rim pa ji lta bar bkod do //
NK064(ngu)001:10470: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:10471: 'dis khro bo rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:10472: dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste
NK064(ngu)001:10474: le'u bcu drug pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10480: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas gsung
NK064(ngu)001:10481: sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das
NK064(ngu)001:10482: dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:10483: chen po sngar bstan pa 'di dag gsang sngags kyi
NK064(ngu)001:10484: dam tshig gis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:10485: de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo khrag 'thung chen po
NK064(ngu)001:10486: rigs lnga rang rang gi btsun mo dang bcas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10487: tshogs de dag gi sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:10488: mi phyed pa'i rdo rje'i bdag nyid rang byung gi
NK064(ngu)001:10489: ye shes rang shar ba'i sngags kyi nga ro rngam
NK064(ngu)001:10490: pa las lhag ting gsung gi dkyil 'khor gsang sngags
NK064(ngu)001:10492: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:10495: dang po gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi skabs 'dir khro
NK064(ngu)001:10496: bo'i phrin las bsgom rim gyi sdebs cung zad brjod
NK064(ngu)001:10497: par bya ste / de la sngon 'gro /
NK064(ngu)001:10499: rjes kyi rim pa dang gsum gyi /
NK064(ngu)001:10500: sngon 'gro la chos bdun zhi ba dang 'dra ba
NK064(ngu)001:10501: las khyad par khro bo'i mtshams gcod la khro bcu
NK064(ngu)001:10503: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:10504: dang po khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10505: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK064(ngu)001:10507: ting nge 'dzin gyi dgos ched bstan pa'i sgo nas so //
NK064(ngu)001:10508: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10509: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10510: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10511: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK064(ngu)001:10513: sgrub thabs ltar de ting dang kun snang sngon du 'gro bas /
NK064(ngu)001:10515: rang rig h+aum las cho ga gsum gyis rgyu'i he ru ka smug nag cir yang 'gyur bar bskyed /
NK064(ngu)001:10517: rgyu'i he ru ka'i thugs ka nas sa bon spros
NK064(ngu)001:10518: te gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang
NK064(ngu)001:10519: gdan dang bcas pa bsgoms la /
NK064(ngu)001:10520: le'u bcu bdun pa ltar tshig gis gsal gdab /
NK064(ngu)001:10521: de nas bdag nyid ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10522: phyir bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya
NK064(ngu)001:10523: ba bdag sras kyi cho ga ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10524: le'u bco lnga pa ltar ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha sum cu bskyed /
NK064(ngu)001:10525: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:10526: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba
NK064(ngu)001:10527: gzhan sras kyi cho ga ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10528: bdag gtso bo'i thugs ka nas 'thon te bskul bas /
NK064(ngu)001:10529: lha tshogs rnams las thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10530: 'od zer spros pas bdag gi lus rtog sbyangs te
NK064(ngu)001:10531: 'od kyi gong bur gyur pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:10532: slar yang rdo rje gsum gyi 'od zer bstim pas
NK064(ngu)001:10533: yi ge 'bru gsum du gyur pa rim bzhin h+aum
NK064(ngu)001:10534: la bsdus pa de nyid zla ba la gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:10536: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la g.yas su bskor nas gtso bo'i thugs kar thim /
NK064(ngu)001:10537: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba sku'i dbyibs brgyud
NK064(ngu)001:10538: yum gyi mkhar son pa'i rkyen gyis gtso bo yab
NK064(ngu)001:10539: yum yang bde ba chen po'i ngo bor zhu zhing
NK064(ngu)001:10540: / h+aum ha he phata ces pas 'khor rnams kyang
NK064(ngu)001:10541: dbus kyi thig ler bsdus nas 'od kyi gong bur
NK064(ngu)001:10542: bsam pa ni bdag don chos sku'i ting nge 'dzin
NK064(ngu)001:10543: gyis snang ba'i zhen pa sbyong ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10544: de nas h+aum h+aum zhes pa'i sgra gdangs yid la
NK064(ngu)001:10545: dran pa tsam gyis 'od phung de h+aum yig zung
NK064(ngu)001:10546: du gyur pa las cho ga gsum gyis gtso bo
NK064(ngu)001:10547: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum bskyed nas dbang bskur
NK064(ngu)001:10549: de nas mkha' gsang brlab pa sogs byas te yum
NK064(ngu)001:10550: gyi mkhar byang chub kyi sems lha'i sa bon yig
NK064(ngu)001:10552: le'u 'dir bshad pa'i sngags kyis bskyed nas ngo mtshar
NK064(ngu)001:10553: tshogs kyi lha sum cu yum gyi mkha' las phata
NK064(ngu)001:10555: spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te gtso
NK064(ngu)001:10556: bo rang la bstim zhing 'khor rnams so so'i gnas
NK064(ngu)001:10557: su bkod / dbang mo nyer brgyad po gtso bo'i
NK064(ngu)001:10558: thugs ka nas b+h+yo nyer brgyad so so'i gnas su
NK064(ngu)001:10559: su bkod / spros pa las / ma nu rak+sha
NK064(ngu)001:10560: s+ai b+h+yo sogs bskyed sngags kyis khrag khyams su bskyed
NK064(ngu)001:10561: su bkod / spros pa las / cing / le'u
NK064(ngu)001:10562: bcu bdun pa bzhin du tshig gi gsal gdab pa
NK064(ngu)001:10563: rnams ni gzhan don gzugs sku'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:10565: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10566: spyan drang ba nas brtsams te dzapa bzla ba'i bar sa bcad drug dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10567: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la'ang tshogs mchod sogs
NK064(ngu)001:10568: sa bcad lnga ste sgrub thabs ltar shes par bya'o
NK064(ngu)001:10570: gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:10571: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10572: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba sogs las kyi rim pa'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:10573: dang po la gsum ste rigs lnga yab yum bcu'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10574: khro mo nyi shu'i rtsa bskyed las sngags dang bcas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10575: dbang mo rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:10578: sngar gyi dpe rgyun rnams su bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sngags thog mar 'byung yang /
NK064(ngu)001:10579: rgya dper badz+ra he ru ka nyid dang por yod
NK064(ngu)001:10580: ces gsung zhing thar lo 'gyur du'ang de ltar 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:10581: ngo // de la sngags kyi 'go 'dren rnams ni
NK064(ngu)001:10582: ye shes lnga'am rdo rje gsum gyi bdag nyid rab
NK064(ngu)001:10585: sarba ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK064(ngu)001:10588: karma las te yab lnga'i rigs so so'i mtshan /
NK064(ngu)001:10589: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka zhes pa ni spyi'i mtshan sngags bod pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10592: he ni he la ste spyod cing rtsen pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10593: ru ni ru d+hi ra ste khrag /
NK064(ngu)001:10594: ka ni bdag po'i sgra ste khrag la rol ba'i don gyis khrag 'thung ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:10595: de dag gi snying po bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:10596: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha
NK064(ngu)001:10597: pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata ces pa ni las
NK064(ngu)001:10599: ma h+aa tsan+da ni gtum po chen po /
NK064(ngu)001:10600: sarba dush+ta ni gdug pa can thams cad /
NK064(ngu)001:10601: an+ta ka ni mthar byed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10605: h+aum gsum gyi dang po rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:10606: gnyis pa thugs bskul ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:10607: gsum pa ni bsdigs par mdzod /
NK064(ngu)001:10608: phata ni bkas par gyis zhes las la bskul ba'i sngags te /
NK064(ngu)001:10609: rab sngags rdo rje sogs rigs gang yin gyi dpal khrag 'thung chen po zhes bos nas /
NK064(ngu)001:10610: gtum po chen po gdug pa can thams cad mthar byed pas bsnun cig /
NK064(ngu)001:10616: badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na pad+ma rnams sngar dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10617: sarba a mo g+ha thams cad don yod pa ste rigs kyi mtshan no //
NK064(ngu)001:10618: mah+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai rnams ni khro mo dbang phyug ma chen mo /
NK064(ngu)001:10619: thog mtha'i dang phata sngar bzhin /
NK064(ngu)001:10621: khyad par du d+h+aa ra 'chang ba /
NK064(ngu)001:10623: sarba dush+tana gdug pa can thams cad la /
NK064(ngu)001:10624: ma h+aa s+aur+ya nyi ma chen mo /
NK064(ngu)001:10626: h+r+ai sh+ru ta sa ma ta kun tu rgod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10636: badz+ra rnams ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10637: mjug gi ha brgyad ni rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:10638: bye brag goo r+ai dkar mo'am mdzod ldan ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10639: tsoo r+ai chom rkun ma'am rkun mo /
NK064(ngu)001:10640: pra mo he rab rmongs ma'am rmongs mo //
NK064(ngu)001:10641: be ta l+ai ro langs ma'am thal byed ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10644: g+hasma r+ai sme sha can nam drod mo /
NK064(ngu)001:10645: sma sha n+ai dur khrod ma'am ma tshogs ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10649: mjug gi he brgyad rtsa ba'i sa bon /
NK064(ngu)001:10650: sing+ha mu kh+ai seng gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10651: b+h+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai stag gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10652: sh+r+ai g+aa la mu kh+ai wa gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10653: sh+aa na mu kh+ai khyi gdong ma'am spyang gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10654: grid+d+ha mu kh+ai bya rgod gdong ma'am bzhad gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10655: kang+ga mu kh+ai kang+ga'i gdong ma'am dur bya'i gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10656: k+aa ka mu khi kh+aa gdong ma'am bya rog gdong ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10657: u l+au ka mu kh+ai 'ug gdong ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10661: +aar+ya te dza te nga 'phags ma sring 'gro ma'am ring 'gro ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10662: a mu ke gdong mo'am don yod ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10664: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu thal bar byed ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10665: mjug gi dzahh+aum bam hohbzhi ni sa bon no //
NK064(ngu)001:10666: gsum pa dbang mo'i rtsa sngags ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10668: bzhi tshad gcig ste nyer brgyad ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10669: ma mo'i tshogs kyi don dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10671: 'bod pa dang bskul ba'ang yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:10673: b+ha gi n+ai sring mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10674: b+har+y+aa chung ma la 'jug pa'i sgra bsdus pa'am /
NK064(ngu)001:10676: 'jigs par byed pa'i don la bshad pa ltar na 'jigs byed ma zhes bod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10677: bskyed sngags ni ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo sogs bshad rgyud me long las gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:10678: gnyis pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10680: me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba'i tshig sngags /
NK064(ngu)001:10681: drin lan du mchod cing brtan pa'i sngags so //
NK064(ngu)001:10683: ru lu ru lu h+aum zhes pa snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags te /
NK064(ngu)001:10684: spyir ru ni ru dza'i sgra las 'jig par gyis /
NK064(ngu)001:10685: lu ni lu nya'i sgras gcod pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10687: sngags kyi lha bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig cing chod
NK064(ngu)001:10688: la bsdigs par mdzod ces pas gdul bya gdug pa
NK064(ngu)001:10689: can gyi ngor chos kyi sku las 'jigs byed chen
NK064(ngu)001:10690: por bzhengs par mdzod ces bskul ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10691: khyad par ba ni ru lu'i bye brag bcu las spyan drang bar shes pa'i skabs te /
NK064(ngu)001:10692: sngon las kyi srin po'i dam tshig gi gdug pa'i glu dpal chen pos byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10693: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa pa ni spyan drang ba'i sngags te /
NK064(ngu)001:10694: e h+ye hi tshur sbyon tshur sbyon /
NK064(ngu)001:10696: dzahh+aum bam hohtshad med bzhis 'gro don la bskul ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10697: ram ni dam ye gnyis me ri 'dab 'byor tsam du bzhugs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10699: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum ni me tog dor ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10701: badz+ra kro d+ha rdo rje khro bo /
NK064(ngu)001:10704: khro la sogs ni dngos grub bskul ba ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10706: gdul bya khro la 'dul byed khros par snang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:10707: rgyud zhi bar mdzad pa thugs rje ngang gis khro
NK064(ngu)001:10708: bar bstan nas 'gro ba'i dpal mgon 'jigs byed chen
NK064(ngu)001:10709: po rngams pa'i tshogs khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:10710: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i byin rlabs
NK064(ngu)001:10711: gzhan las ches che ba'i rmad po che ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10712: de nyid dus da lta nyid du 'dir ni bdag la stsol bar mdzod cig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10713: badz+ra kro d+ha gsum ni sngar ltar dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10714: sa ma ya dam tshig gam dus la /
NK064(ngu)001:10715: s+t+wam khyod ces bod pa'am bab bo //
NK064(ngu)001:10717: hohmanyesa par mdzod ces pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10718: mchog ster rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig khyod /
NK064(ngu)001:10720: dam tshig gis dgyes par mdzod ces so //
NK064(ngu)001:10722: a li sogs te a ba b+h+ram sha'i skad yin ces gsung /
NK064(ngu)001:10723: de la a li ni chang ste btung ba /
NK064(ngu)001:10724: u li ni sha ste bza' ba /
NK064(ngu)001:10725: t+aa li ta pa li 'bru 'bras sogs dam tshig gi rdzas sna tshogs /
NK064(ngu)001:10726: damsh+t+aa zhal mche ba bgrad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10728: roo dri khro ba'am drag po /
NK064(ngu)001:10730: rdo rje khro bo mche ba bgrad pa'i zhal du stob bo zhes pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10734: 'khor gyi rnal 'byor ma rnams la stob pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10735: h+aum ha he phata ni dam ye gnyis med du gyur nas gsal zhing brtan par byas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10738: de skad ces gsung gsang sngags brjod pa'i mthu byin
NK064(ngu)001:10739: gyis 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba thams
NK064(ngu)001:10740: cad kyi lus snang ba'i rtog tshogs thams cad tshig
NK064(ngu)001:10741: / ngag grags pa'i rtog tshogs rab tu 'tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:10742: sems sgrib pa'i rtog tshogs kun tu tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:10743: de ltar tshig pas snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'bar /
NK064(ngu)001:10744: grags pa sngags kyi dkyil 'khor du rab tu 'bar /
NK064(ngu)001:10745: dran rig thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du kun tu 'bar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:10746: de'i tshe nam mkha'i gar khyab thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyi skus gang /
NK064(ngu)001:10747: gsung gis khyab par rab tu gang /
NK064(ngu)001:10748: thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyis kun tu khyab cing gang bar gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:10751: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:10752: 'dis khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i lhag ting gsung gi dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10754: // le'u bcu bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10760: gsung gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas lhag pa
NK064(ngu)001:10761: sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom
NK064(ngu)001:10762: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i sprin gsang
NK064(ngu)001:10763: sngags dang bcas pa de dag gis bskyed pa'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:10764: 'khor gyi rnam pa gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir ched
NK064(ngu)001:10766: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:10773: ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10776: 'bar ba'i 'khor lo sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10777: 'og gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i lte ba la
NK064(ngu)001:10778: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza
NK064(ngu)001:10779: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus su ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:10780: lnga'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:10781: / de'i phyir bden bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan cing /
NK064(ngu)001:10782: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pas dbyibs gru bzhi pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10783: rnam thar bzhi'i sgo bzhi sgo khyud can bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10784: bden gnyis mtshon pa'i 'bar ba'i bar khyams nang ma gser khyams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10785: phyi ma khrag khyams gnyis kyis mdzes shing /
NK064(ngu)001:10786: thod pa skam rlon rnying gsum gyi rtsig pa phyi ma rim pa lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10788: thams cad kyang rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar zhing gnam lcags kyi gzer bus btab pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10789: rtsig steng thod pa sna tshogs kyi pha gu 'phyar
NK064(ngu)001:10790: ba las rgyu ma dang snying gi mgul 'khor dang
NK064(ngu)001:10791: / bre phul gyi snam bur sbrul sbram dang thod phreng gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK064(ngu)001:10794: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i 'gram du 'dod pa'i snam bu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10795: sgo phyi ma la rgyu 'bras kyi rta bab sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis bkra ba /
NK064(ngu)001:10796: steng zhing lpags kyi thog phubs nyi ma dang zla
NK064(ngu)001:10797: ba'i mthongs dkar dang bcas pa'i dbus phyur bu lha
NK064(ngu)001:10798: chen gyi thod pas phub pa'i rtse mor tsit+ta'i tog
NK064(ngu)001:10799: gis brjid pa / phyi rol du r+au dra longs
NK064(ngu)001:10800: spyod dang bcas pa dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod
NK064(ngu)001:10801: brgyad kyis yongs su bskor zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:10802: 'bar ba'i me dpung me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba'i klong
NK064(ngu)001:10803: nas khro chung mang po 'phro zhing 'khrug pas mdzes
NK064(ngu)001:10805: khyu mchog sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10806: dbus kyi lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du /
NK064(ngu)001:10807: gti mug gnas su dag pa'i rtags su shar rtsibs la khyu mchog dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10808: nga rgyal dag pa lhor ma he dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10809: 'dod chags dag pa nub tu gzig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10810: phrag dog dag pa byang du stag dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10811: zhe sdang dag pa dbus su gtum pa dom rnams
NK064(ngu)001:10812: zung gi spar bas ni dregs pa zil gnon gyi
NK064(ngu)001:10813: gdan dbus su dbang phyug dang lha chen po drag
NK064(ngu)001:10814: po / la sogs pas shar du dri za /
NK064(ngu)001:10817: byang du gnod sbyin rnams pho mo kha bub gan
NK064(ngu)001:10818: rkyal du bsnol ba'i sog sbrag dang nu sbrag nas
NK064(ngu)001:10819: las la nan tur du bstan pa'i phyir bzung ba'o
NK064(ngu)001:10820: // 'khor gyi gnas yul sgo skyong rnams la nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan /
NK064(ngu)001:10821: dbang mo rnams la zhing skam po'i gdan re re'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10822: gnyis pa brten pa lha la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:10823: gtso bo rigs lnga'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10832: smug nag sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:10833: dug lnga gnas su dag cing phrin las lnga'i mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:10834: pa mtshon pa'i brdar rigs so so'i kha dog la
NK064(ngu)001:10835: / de dag kyang rigs mi 'gyur zhing las bzhi'i
NK064(ngu)001:10836: phrin las kyi gzhi dang mthar phyin pa drag pos
NK064(ngu)001:10837: mdzad pa'i phyir thams cad la nag po'i sgras smos
NK064(ngu)001:10838: / te / bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sku mdog smug nag /
NK064(ngu)001:10839: badz+ra he ru ka'i sngo nag /
NK064(ngu)001:10840: rat+na he ru ka'i ser nag dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10841: pad+ma he ru ka'i dmar nag /
NK064(ngu)001:10842: karma he ru ka'i ljang nag ste sku mdog rtsa zhal dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10843: g.yas zhal ni rat+na he ru ka'i sngon po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10845: g.yon zhal ni bud+d+ha dang pad+ma gnyis ser po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10847: gdug pa can gyi ngor shin tu 'jigs pa'i sku che zhing yan lag rags pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10850: thams cad kyang rnam thar gsum mtshon pa'i dbu gsum /
NK064(ngu)001:10851: ye shes drug gis 'gro don mdzad pa'i phyir phyag
NK064(ngu)001:10852: drug rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10853: phyir zhabs bzhi g.yas brkang ba'i dor stabs su bgrad
NK064(ngu)001:10855: ko rlon sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10856: bgo ba ko rlon gyi gos ni sna tshogs pa gyon pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10857: stobs bcus gti mug bcom pa'i brdar glang chen gyi ko rlon dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10858: byang chub sems kyis 'dod chags bcom pa'i brdar zhing lpags kyis stod g.yogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:10859: dpa' brtul drag po'i las kyis zhe sdang bcom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:10860: brdar stag lpags kyi sham thabs grol ba ste bgo
NK064(ngu)001:10862: klu rgyal rigs dkar pos skra chings /
NK064(ngu)001:10863: rje rigs ser pos snyan cha /
NK064(ngu)001:10864: bram ze'i rigs dmar pos se mo do dang mgur chu /
NK064(ngu)001:10865: dmangs rigs ljang khus ska rags dang do shal /
NK064(ngu)001:10866: gdol pa nag pos gdu bu ste thams cad kyang gdug pa sbrul gyi rnam pa can dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10867: thod phreng ni skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan /
NK064(ngu)001:10868: 'dzag pa'i mgo rlon lnga bcu'i do shal /
NK064(ngu)001:10869: tshal bus dpung rgyan te gdags pa'i rgyan gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:10870: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK064(ngu)001:10871: smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK064(ngu)001:10872: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris rnams ni byug pa'i rtsi gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10873: de dag ni dur khrod kyi chas brgyad do //
NK064(ngu)001:10874: snyan gong g.yas g.yon nas nyi zla'i 'od zer spro ba ni gsal ba'i chas gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:10875: gsung ni 'brug ltar chems pa'i rngams pa'i sgra chen drag po shin tu 'jigs par sgrogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10878: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten khor yug dang bcas pa
NK064(ngu)001:10879: ni badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag g.yon gyi tha mas
NK064(ngu)001:10881: rdo rje rtse dgu pa ni badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas dang po'i phyag mtshan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10882: rtse lnga pa dang dung chen gang ba ni thams cad kyi phyag bar pa gnyis dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10883: ral gri ni karma he ru ka'i g.yas dang po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10884: sgrub thabs su bshad rgyud brgyad pa ltar rgya gram bshad do //
NK064(ngu)001:10885: dgra s+t+wa ni rat+na'i g.yon tha ma /
NK064(ngu)001:10886: thong gshol ni karma'i g.yon tha ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10887: de la sogs pa rang rang gi lag cha sna tshogs pa 'dzin pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10888: phyag g.yas kyi dang po bud+d+ha'i 'khor lo /
NK064(ngu)001:10891: thams cad kyi g.yon dang po dril bu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10893: bud+d+ha'i g.yon tha ma tri sh+aul dang pad+ma'i rnge'u chung rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:10894: 'di dag ni bshad rgyud brgyad pa ltar sgrub thabs
NK064(ngu)001:10895: kyi phyag rgya gar mchod dang mthun par byas pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:10898: rang rang gi rigs kyi btsun mo 'jigs pa'i tshogs
NK064(ngu)001:10899: lnga ga sku mdog yab dang mthun pa gzig sham
NK064(ngu)001:10900: can / zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyi g.yas dril bus
NK064(ngu)001:10901: yab la 'khyud cing g.yon dung dmar zhal du stob
NK064(ngu)001:10902: can / pa / stong pa nyid dang snying rje
NK064(ngu)001:10903: zung du 'jug pa'i brdar yab dang gnyis su med
NK064(ngu)001:10904: can / pa / par 'khril ba'o // gnyis pa 'khor gyi bkod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10905: gnas dang sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10906: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ni 'khor ba bskyed pa'i gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10907: de'i yul brgyad gnas su dag par na goo r+ai ma sogs la gnas ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10908: sing+ha ma sogs la yul ma brgyad ces btags la /
NK064(ngu)001:10909: de dag gi phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10910: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK064(ngu)001:10912: sing+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK064(ngu)001:10914: sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10915: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK064(ngu)001:10917: so so'i sku mdog phyag mtshan dang mgo brnyan rnams kyang gar mchod kyis gsal bar bstan no //
NK064(ngu)001:10918: de ltar khro mo nyi shu'i 'khor gyi bkod pas rab tu mdzes shing /
NK064(ngu)001:10919: gzhan yang slas te chung ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10920: byi mo ste mdza' mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10921: bran mo ste las byed po'i cha nas btags pa
NK064(ngu)001:10922: dbang phyug ma'i tshogs grangs bcu tshan gnyis dang ya
NK064(ngu)001:10923: brgyad de nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis mdzes par bskor
NK064(ngu)001:10924: ba / de dag kyang rang rang gi stan zhing skam po re dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10925: sku mdog dang lag cha ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10926: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK064(ngu)001:10928: bdag gi las skal ci bgyis zhes zhu zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:10929: rdzu 'phrul ni thogs pa med par yud tsam gyis
NK064(ngu)001:10930: chas te so so'i las dang mthun pa'i phyogs su
NK064(ngu)001:10931: gnas so // de ltar khrag 'thung nga brgyad ni
NK064(ngu)001:10932: dkyil 'khor spros pa las bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor te
NK064(ngu)001:10933: gnas so // / 'bring po la de'i steng du khro bcu yab yum bsnan pas don brgyad /
NK064(ngu)001:10934: rgyas pa la de'i yang steng du khrag 'thung rigs
NK064(ngu)001:10935: lnga la rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum zung
NK064(ngu)001:10936: bzhis bskor ba'i bzhi bcu bsnan pas brgya bco brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:10937: do // yang 'phros don rnam grangs spros pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10939: yan lag bkod pa lnga bcu brgyad //
NK064(ngu)001:10940: cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang //
NK064(ngu)001:10941: dgu bcu'i lha rnams yan lag ldan //
NK064(ngu)001:10942: zhes pas badz+ra he ru ka'i yan lag lnga la khrag 'thung yab lnga dang yum la yum lnga /
NK064(ngu)001:10943: yab kyi dbang rten gyi nang rtsar goo r+ai ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu)001:10944: phyi rtsar sim ha ma brgyad /
NK064(ngu)001:10946: sgal tshigs la dbang mo nyer brgyad de thabs lha nga brgyad /
NK064(ngu)001:10947: de rnams la ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10948: sku gsung thugs kyi lha rnams re re bsgoms pas
NK064(ngu)001:10949: nga brgyad pa cha lnga la nyis brgya dang dgu
NK064(ngu)001:10950: bcu / de las shes rab kyi lha nga brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:10951: phri ba'i lhag nyis brgya so gnyis po re re
NK064(ngu)001:10952: la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste stong chig
NK064(ngu)001:10953: brgya drug cu 'byung ba nyis brgya dgu bcu la
NK064(ngu)001:10954: bsnan pas stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu ste gtso bo
NK064(ngu)001:10955: yab yum la tshang bar bsgom mo //
NK064(ngu)001:10956: des mtshon nas khrag 'thung rigs bzhi'i zung re re dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10957: gnas yul sgo dbang gi lha zhe brgyad la yum med pas /
NK064(ngu)001:10959: rkang lag g.yas kyi mdun rgyab la yab lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:10961: rkang lag g.yon gyi mdun rgyab la yum lnga bkod de /
NK064(ngu)001:10962: mdor na stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu cha nga gsum
NK064(ngu)001:10963: la bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:10964: 'khor 'byung zhing / bsam yas lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor ni zhi ba ltar ro //
NK064(ngu)001:10967: de skad ces brjod pa'i mthus 'jig rten drug gi
NK064(ngu)001:10968: phyogs bcu thams cad du 'bar ba chen po khro
NK064(ngu)001:10969: bo'i dkyil 'khor gyis kun tu khyab cing gsal bar
NK064(ngu)001:10970: gyur to // gsum pa mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:10972: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las //
NK064(ngu)001:10973: 'dis khro bo'i lhag ting sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:10975: // le'u bco brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10981: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:10982: gyi mchod pa ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK064(ngu)001:10983: pa chen pos dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams mnyes
NK064(ngu)001:10984: par byed pa rmad du byung ba'i mchod pa chen
NK064(ngu)001:10986: gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10989: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:10996: de la sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:10997: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la brten
NK064(ngu)001:10998: nas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa de la de
NK064(ngu)001:10999: bzhin gshegs rnams mchod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11000: mkha' 'gro rnams la sbyin pa gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:11001: de dag gi nang nas kyang khyad par du gyur pa'i mchog dam pa ni 'di yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:11002: thog mar rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11003: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin goms pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11004: thabs kyis gzung 'dzin gyi zhen rtog chos nyid skye
NK064(ngu)001:11005: med kyi dbyings su bsgral te rtogs pas bdag bsgral
NK064(ngu)001:11006: ba'o // de nas thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11007: bsgral bya sgrol byed gnyis med du rtogs pa'i blo yi gdengs kyis zin pa ni shes rab ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11008: de'i ngang las rgyu 'bras kyi don la rmongs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11009: blo ngan zhing bcur gyur pa'i sems can srid pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11010: 'jig rten 'og mar brgyud pa 'di dag snying re
NK064(ngu)001:11011: rje zhes thabs snying rje chen po'i sgo nas bsgral
NK064(ngu)001:11012: bya'i rnam shes gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11013: sems chos kyi dbyings der bsgral bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11015: 'khril ba'i sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11016: yab yum gnyis su med par 'khril bas bde ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11017: mchod rdzas chen po nyi zla byang chub kyi sems
NK064(ngu)001:11018: mnyam par sbyor bas rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid bde
NK064(ngu)001:11019: ba'i rol mos mnyes shing tshim par byas nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11020: byang chub sems kyi rdul phra rab mkha' khyab tu
NK064(ngu)001:11021: spros pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes pa
NK064(ngu)001:11022: dang / sems can thams cad kyang tshim ste bde
NK064(ngu)001:11023: chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ro mnyam par
NK064(ngu)001:11024: dang / byas pa'o // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11025: mnyam pa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11026: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du
NK064(ngu)001:11027: rtogs pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas chen po bdud
NK064(ngu)001:11028: rtsi lnga po 'di dag bdag dam tshig gi 'khor
NK064(ngu)001:11029: lo dang ye shes lha'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med du
NK064(ngu)001:11030: mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'khor gsum yongs dag gi mchod
NK064(ngu)001:11031: par dbul lo // bzhi pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11032: bza' dang sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11033: sha zan sogs bza' ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11034: shing thog sogs bca' ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11035: ja chang sogs btung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11036: srab 'jam yang ba'i bgo ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11037: gzhan yang lha dang mi'i longs spyod 'dod pa'i yon
NK064(ngu)001:11038: tan dang ldan pa'i snang ba thams cad lha dang
NK064(ngu)001:11039: lha mor rnam par dag pas 'bul tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11040: mchod yul ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la
NK064(ngu)001:11041: ni mchod rdzas 'dod yon lha mo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:11042: med bde ba chen por ro gcig tu thim pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11044: gnyis pa mchod pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11048: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11049: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir 'gro ba'i don la gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:11050: pa yi bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi che ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11051: yon tan rmad po che rnams kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:11052: rang rig rtogs pa las gzhan zhig logs nas btsal
NK064(ngu)001:11053: du yod pa'am tshur 'ongs pa ma yin na gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:11054: 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub lha srin la sogs pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11055: mthu las byung ba'i yon tan 'grub pa ni lta
NK064(ngu)001:11058: rnal 'byor sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11059: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig lta ba rtogs shing ting
NK064(ngu)001:11060: nge 'dzin las su rung ba rnams kyis lha sku
NK064(ngu)001:11061: phyag rgya chen po rang rig la mngon du rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:11062: par 'gyur zhing / de nyid yul gyis mi 'phrog
NK064(ngu)001:11063: par gsal ba la brtan pa thob nas 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:11064: 'grub bam mi 'grub snyam pa'i yid gnyis dang the
NK064(ngu)001:11065: tshom med par gyur pa na rang bzhin 'bras bu'i
NK064(ngu)001:11066: dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub chen po 'byung bar 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11067: par 'gyur zhing / ro // gsum pa de gsungs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11069: de skad ces brjod pa'i mthus mnyes pa chen pos
NK064(ngu)001:11070: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du mchod
NK064(ngu)001:11071: pa'i sprin gyi rol mo'i khyab par gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:11074: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:11075: 'dis rgyal ba rnams mchod cing ma mo dang mkha'
NK064(ngu)001:11076: 'gror sbyin pa'i thabs thun mong du ma grags pas
NK064(ngu)001:11077: mchog dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:11079: // // le'u bcu dgu pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11085: khyad par gyi mchod sbyin bstan pa de nas dam
NK064(ngu)001:11086: tshig gi rim pa ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das
NK064(ngu)001:11087: dgyes pa chen pos sngags 'chang rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:11088: log par mi ltung zhing 'bras bu myur du 'grub
NK064(ngu)001:11089: pas lam la 'bad pa don yod par bya ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11090: phyir / bla na med pa'i dam tshig chen po 'di dag ched du brjod do //
NK064(ngu)001:11091: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11095: dam tshig gi che ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11096: rnam grangs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11097: mnyam pa'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11098: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11099: dam tshig gi rang bzhin dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11100: dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11101: de ma nyams pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:11104: 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus pa'i che ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11106: bla med theg par sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11107: gang zag gang zhig rtogs goms kyi gdengs dang ldan
NK064(ngu)001:11108: pas mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig la gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:11109: ni bla na med pa'i theg par rab tu nges
NK064(ngu)001:11110: pa ste / nyams su lon na nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11111: des bskyed pa'i las rnams kun la spyad kyang sgyu
NK064(ngu)001:11112: ma mkhan gyis sgyu ma'i longs spyod la spyod pa
NK064(ngu)001:11113: ltar byas par snang yang de la 'dzin zhen med
NK064(ngu)001:11114: pas / de'i sgrib pa dang bag chags mi gsog pa'i steng du tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:11115: spyod pa de'i ngo bo la so byang phyi rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:11116: rnams kyi tshul khrims dang sdom pa thams cad kyang
NK064(ngu)001:11117: phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11120: ji ltar 'dus shing dag tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11122: bla med mchog gi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11123: gsang sngags bla na med pa rdo rje'i theg pa
NK064(ngu)001:11124: mchog gi dam tshig 'di'i nang du 'gro ba 'dul
NK064(ngu)001:11125: ba'i dbang gis rnam par bzhag pa'i nyan thos kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11126: tshul khrims ji snyed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11127: byang sems dang gsang sngags phyi nang gi bsrung bya
NK064(ngu)001:11128: ji snyed pa'i sdom pa bsam yas yod pa ma
NK064(ngu)001:11129: lus pa'i yon tan kun yar ldan gyi tshul du
NK064(ngu)001:11130: 'dir 'dus shing / nyes pa phra mos kyang gos pa med pas rnam par dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11131: de la ji snyed pa'i sdom pa kun rigs bsdus na /
NK064(ngu)001:11134: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa gsum du 'du la /
NK064(ngu)001:11135: de gsum yang rnam pa 'gal ba ltar snang yang /
NK064(ngu)001:11136: ngo bo tshang ba dang gnas 'gyur ba'i sgo nas
NK064(ngu)001:11137: so byang gnyis sngags sdom du 'dus shing rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:11138: dag pa ste / ji ltar na /
NK064(ngu)001:11139: so byang gnyis la mnyam pa chen po'i thabs kyis
NK064(ngu)001:11140: ma zin pa'i tha mal snang zhen gyi ldog cha
NK064(ngu)001:11141: re yod pa rtsa gtong gis so thar gyi gzhan
NK064(ngu)001:11142: gnod gzhi bcas las ldog pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11143: byang sdom gyi gzhan phan la zhugs pa'i ldog cha
NK064(ngu)001:11144: gnyis po de sngags sdom gyi mnyam pa chen po'i
NK064(ngu)001:11145: ngang nas gzhan don rtsol med du mdzad pa'i thabs
NK064(ngu)001:11146: mkhas kyi nang du tshang zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:11147: rdzas gong 'phel gyi tshul gyis sngags kyi sdom rdzas su gnas 'gyur ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11149: theg chen dam tshig la gnas na //
NK064(ngu)001:11151: bsrung ba med par thub pas na //
NK064(ngu)001:11152: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11157: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11159: mi tshangs par spyod pa spong ba ji ltar 'dus shing dag pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11161: yod med sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11162: don dam par chos thams cad yod pa rtag pa dang med pa chad pa'i mtha' dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11163: de gnyis ka dang bral ba'i dbu ma tsam du'ang mi dmigs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11164: kun rdzob tu sgyu ma'i skyes bus mig yor gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11165: sems can bsad pa'i lta bu'i tshul du snang yang
NK064(ngu)001:11166: / snang dus nyid nas bcad bya'i srog bden par
NK064(ngu)001:11167: grub pa med pas srog gcod mkhan dang bcad do
NK064(ngu)001:11168: ba'i 'du shes kyang ma grub pas don la bcad
NK064(ngu)001:11169: / du med de / srog dang de ldan gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11170: skyes bur 'dzin pa ni log rtog 'khrul ngo tsam
NK064(ngu)001:11171: / du med de / yin pa'i phyir / de
NK064(ngu)001:11172: ltar rtogs nas zhing bcu'i srog bcad kyang nyes pas
NK064(ngu)001:11173: / du med de / yin pa'i phyir / mi
NK064(ngu)001:11174: gos shing / tshogs rdzogs pas na srog gcod spong
NK064(ngu)001:11175: ba'i sdom pa'i ngo bo dang yon tan yar ldan
NK064(ngu)001:11176: / du med de / yin pa'i phyir / mi
NK064(ngu)001:11177: gos shing / du 'dus so // gnyis pa ni
NK064(ngu)001:11178: / du med de / yin pa'i phyir / mi
NK064(ngu)001:11179: gos shing / du 'dus so // / bden pa
NK064(ngu)001:11181: chos thams cad don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11182: bden pa gnyis ka'i tshul la bdag dang gzhan zhes
NK064(ngu)001:11183: dbyer med pas don dam par ma dmigs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11184: tha snyad kun rdzob tu'ang 'phrul dag'i lha rnams rang gis sprul pa'i longs spyod len pa ltar /
NK064(ngu)001:11185: ma byin par len dus nyid nas rang snang gi
NK064(ngu)001:11186: rdzas la rang snang gis len pa'i tshul gyi blangs
NK064(ngu)001:11187: te spyad kyang don la tha dad min pas /
NK064(ngu)001:11189: des bdag gir bzung ba'i rdzas ma byin par len rgyu zhig gud na med pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:11191: ci blangs kyang thams cad bdag nyid las mi 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:11192: bar gnyis med kyi dbyings su ro gcig tu rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:11193: pa'i phyir / de ltar bdag gzhan gyi rgyud dbyer
NK064(ngu)001:11194: med du shes pas 'jungs pa las blangs nas bkren
NK064(ngu)001:11195: pa la ster ba sogs byas na nyes pas mi
NK064(ngu)001:11196: gos shing tshogs rdzogs pas ma byin len spong ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11197: sdom pa'i ngo bo dang yon tan yar ldan du
NK064(ngu)001:11198: pa'i phyir / 'dus so // gsum pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11199: chos rnams sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11200: chos rnams thams cad ji ltar snang ba de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:11201: du yod pa ma yin pas sgyu ma lta bu
NK064(ngu)001:11202: ste rdzun tsam du zad la /
NK064(ngu)001:11203: de ltar brjod bya'i don ma grub bzhin du rjod
NK064(ngu)001:11204: byed kyi ming dang tshig tu sgro btags nas de
NK064(ngu)001:11206: de'i phyir yul shes bya dang brjod bya thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:11207: bden par ma grub pas rdzun pa nyid la ni
NK064(ngu)001:11208: / shes byed dang rjod byed rdzun pa nyid spyod pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11209: chos gang la'ang bden pa gnyis ma grub na /
NK064(ngu)001:11210: de la ltos pa'i rdzun pa'ang ma grub pas rdzun
NK064(ngu)001:11211: zhes bya ba'i chos ni ming tsam btags pa tsam
NK064(ngu)001:11212: du'ang yod pa ma yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11213: de ltar shes pas rdzun smras kyang nyes pas mi gos shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11214: ji ltar phan pa de ltar smras pas tshogs rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:11215: pa'i phyir na rdzun smra ba spong ba'i sdom pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11216: ngo bo dang yon tan yar ldan du 'dus so
NK064(ngu)001:11218: ma chags sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11219: chos thams cad la yul sems gnyis med du gsal ba ni ma chags pa'i ye shes te /
NK064(ngu)001:11220: de la gnyis su zhen cing chags pa'i dus na /
NK064(ngu)001:11221: gnyis med du shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11222: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11223: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang ldan pas 'khrig
NK064(ngu)001:11224: pa'i 'dod chags la spyod pa ltar snang ba'i dus
NK064(ngu)001:11225: nyid na yang tha mal gyi chags pa'i dri ma
NK064(ngu)001:11226: rdul tsam yang med pa ni 'dzag med kyi tshul
NK064(ngu)001:11227: khrims tshangs par spyod pa thams cad kyi mchog gam
NK064(ngu)001:11228: rgyal po ste / chos thams cad shin tu rnam
NK064(ngu)001:11229: par dag pa bde stong zung 'jug rang rig gi
NK064(ngu)001:11230: ngo bor grol ba ni chags pa chen po bde
NK064(ngu)001:11231: chen gyi ye shes yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11232: de ltar shes nas spyad na nyes pas mi gos shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11233: 'dzag med kyi ye shes grub pa sogs tshogs rdzogs
NK064(ngu)001:11234: pa'i phyir mi tshangs spyod spong pa'i sdom pa'i ngo
NK064(ngu)001:11235: bo dang yon tan yar ldan du 'dus so //
NK064(ngu)001:11236: gnyis pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdor bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11239: de gnyis kyi nges tshig bshad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11241: bla med sogs rkang pa drug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11242: 'di la dam tshig gsal bkra las /
NK064(ngu)001:11243: byang sems rnam gnyis slob dpon drug /
NK064(ngu)001:11244: mched bzhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:11245: gsang bcu rtsa bar shes par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:11246: zhes pa ltar rtsa ba'i dam tshig la lnga las /
NK064(ngu)001:11247: bla med mi spong ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11248: yul bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems lhag pa don dam dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11249: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis so //
NK064(ngu)001:11250: de mi spang ba'i tshul ni lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med du rtogs nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11251: sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' bar byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11253: yul kun gyis dam par bkur zhing bka' drin cung zad thob pa spyi'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11254: rab byung gi mkhan po lta bu 'dren pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11255: dam tshig 'bogs shing dbang bskur ba po dam tshig dbang gi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11256: bshags yul du gyur pa nyams chags skong ba'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11257: chos 'chad pa'i slob dpon lta bu shes rgyud 'grol ba'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11258: man ngag ston cing lung 'bogs pa po man ngag lung gi slob dpon te /
NK064(ngu)001:11260: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK064(ngu)001:11261: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK064(ngu)001:11262: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /
NK064(ngu)001:11266: man ngag nod pa gsum ni lhag par yang bkur ba'i yul gyi bla ma'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11267: bkur lugs ni sgo gsum g.yo zol med pas ci mnyes sgrub pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11268: sngags rgya rgyun mi bcad pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11269: yul sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11271: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11272: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:11273: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK064(ngu)001:11275: de dag brtson pa rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam /
NK064(ngu)001:11276: nyin zhag gcig gi nang du thun drug gam bzhi'i rnal 'byor du bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:11277: 'bring gis zla ba re la dus tshigs drug gam /
NK064(ngu)001:11280: tha mas kyang zla dus dang lo dus kyi mchod pa rgyun mi bcad par 'bad par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11282: yul spyi'i mched sems can thams cad /
NK064(ngu)001:11283: ring ba'i mched bstan la bzhugs so cog /
NK064(ngu)001:11284: nye ba'i mched sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa /
NK064(ngu)001:11285: 'dres pa'i mched bla ma gcig gis bsdus pa pha gcig pa'i spun dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11286: de'i shugs kyis dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus pa ma gcig gi spun rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:11287: de rnams las khyad par phyi ma gsum ni yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa'i mched dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11288: de'i nang nas kyang 'dres pa'i mched ni lhag par yang byams par bya ba'i yul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:11289: de dag la byams lugs kyi rtag tu mi 'bral
NK064(ngu)001:11290: zhing phan 'dogs pa'i lhag bsam gyis brtse gdung rgyun
NK064(ngu)001:11294: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11295: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11298: ji ltar gsang ba'i tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11299: spyir gsang sngags kyi tshig don rnams phyir gyur pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11300: snod ma yin pa la gsang bar bya ba yin mod /
NK064(ngu)001:11303: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11304: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK064(ngu)001:11305: zhes gsungs pa rnams ni shin tu gsang bar bya ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11306: de la spyir gsang bzhi ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11308: lta zab spyod pa barlang po dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11309: lha'i ming gzugs dang grub rtags gsang //
NK064(ngu)001:11310: zhes pa'i lta zab ni theg dman sogs blo 'phangs dma' ba rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11311: spyod pa ni ma 'dres pa thams cad la gsang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:11312: yi dam gyi lha sngags dang grub rtags ni ma 'dres pa la bstan na dam tshig nyams shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11313: 'dres par bstan na'ang dngos grub nyams par gsungs pas thams cad du gsang bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11315: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK064(ngu)001:11316: bar du gsang la bsgrub par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:11317: zhes pas sgrub pa'i bar de srid du gsang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:11318: gsang bar 'os pa ni rdzas dang spyod pa mthong thos su mi rung ba rnams so //
NK064(ngu)001:11320: slob dpon dang mched kyis gsang bar gdams pa rnams gzhan du smra bar mi bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11321: de ltar lnga po 'di la ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11322: ljon shing gi rtsa ba ltar yon tan gyi rten
NK064(ngu)001:11323: gzhi yin pas rtsa ba lnga zhes gsungs pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:11324: te / de'ang byang sems dang sngags rgya gnyis sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11325: gzhan gsum bsrung ba'i dam tshig gi mchog ste rtsa ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11326: yang rtsa ba gsum du bsdu na /
NK064(ngu)001:11327: bla ma dang mched la bsrung ba sku'i dam tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:11330: byang sems kyang thugs kyi dam tshig tu bsdus na bade'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11331: de ltar yang bde 'dus zhi rgyud las /
NK064(ngu)001:11332: byang chub sems gsum bsgom pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:11333: rdo rje thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK064(ngu)001:11335: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11337: mi dor ba lnga bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11340: gti mug sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11342: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK064(ngu)001:11343: zhes pas spyir yang log gnyis las /
NK064(ngu)001:11344: yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11345: chos thams cad mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i tshe /
NK064(ngu)001:11346: lta ba la phyogs ris dang spyod pa la blang
NK064(ngu)001:11347: dor gyis 'byed pa med pa ni gti mug dang
NK064(ngu)001:11348: / de ma rtogs pa la dmigs med kyi snying rje chen po'i 'dod chags dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11349: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'i zhe sdang dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11350: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba shongs su mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11351: gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen rtog mnyam nyid kyi klong du mi shong ba'i phrag dog ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11352: rtogs goms kyis sbyor bas mi spang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:11354: dug lnga rang mtshan pa rnams te /
NK064(ngu)001:11355: de dag ci'i phyir mi spang zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:11356: log pa'i dug lnga chos can /
NK064(ngu)001:11358: chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong pas spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11359: thabs kyis zin na spyad kyang mi 'ching bar rnam par grol ba'i lam yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11360: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11361: de bas na mi spang ba la dgos pa yod de /
NK064(ngu)001:11362: dngos po'i zhen pa ldog pa dang 'ching byed kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11363: las la spyad pas grol ba 'di 'dra ngo mtshar
NK064(ngu)001:11364: che snyam du thabs kyi lam zab mo la nges
NK064(ngu)001:11366: chos nyid zab mo rtogs pa la blo myur ba'i dgos pa rnams yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11367: gnyis pa mi dor ba lnga ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11368: dkar rtsi sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11369: dkar rtsi byang sems dkar po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11370: dmar rtsi byang sems dmar po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11372: sha chen dag pa'i snod de dwangs ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11373: dri chu rnams ni gtsang rme'i rtog pa sbyong ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11374: nad lnga sel zhing thun mong gi yon tan lnga 'byung ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11375: rigs lnga ye shes lnga sgrub pa'i dam rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:11376: mi dor bar dang du blang bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11378: dag pa'i snod bcud ces 'byung ba ni ma dag pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11379: rgya dper chu'i skad dod dza lam zhes yod cing /
NK064(ngu)001:11381: dkar dang dmar dang dri dang ni //
NK064(ngu)001:11382: sha chen dag pa yi ni snod //
NK064(ngu)001:11383: chu nyid kyang ni dor mi bya //
NK064(ngu)001:11385: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11386: yan lag sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11387: de ltar mi spang mi dor ba ni rtsa ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11388: grogs sam thabs su gyur pas na yan lag bcu
NK064(ngu)001:11389: yi dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11390: ye nas dag pa gsum dang mnyam pa bzhir gnas pa'i don rtogs pas spyad par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11392: bsrung zhing sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11393: sngar bshad bsrung zhing sgrub pa'i dam tshig rnam pa lnga ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:11394: ljon shing gi rtsa ba ltar bsrung na dngos grub
NK064(ngu)001:11395: 'byung zhing nyams na re zhig byang chub kyi rigs
NK064(ngu)001:11396: kyang med par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11397: mi spong mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:11398: ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi grogs su dgos pas
NK064(ngu)001:11399: yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11400: de dag kyang nyams na 'bras bu myur du 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:11401: ba la gegs byed pas ra ba mtshams kyi 'obs
NK064(ngu)001:11403: gsum pa mnyam pa'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11404: mnyam la sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11405: chos thams cad bden gsum ris med du mnyam pa
NK064(ngu)001:11406: la shes 'jug gi lam zab mos mnyam par sbyor
NK064(ngu)001:11407: ba yi don de las mi 'da' bas mnyam pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11408: dam tshig ste / de'i ngang la gnas na 'bras
NK064(ngu)001:11409: bu mnyam rdzogs chen po kun tu bzang po dbye
NK064(ngu)001:11410: ba med pa'i sa thob par 'gyur bas bsrung bar
NK064(ngu)001:11411: dam tshig ste / bya zhing / gal te de'i
NK064(ngu)001:11412: 'gal zla mnyam pa las 'das te tha dad du
NK064(ngu)001:11413: rtog na 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin
NK064(ngu)001:11414: dam tshig ste / bya zhing / no // bzhi pa dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11417: yan lag nyams pa'i skyon no //
NK064(ngu)001:11419: rtsa ba nyams pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11420: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i bslab sdom 'chal ba
NK064(ngu)001:11421: dag dam tshig gso ba'i thabs la dus nye bar
NK064(ngu)001:11422: mi brtson pa rnams dang skad cig tsam yang mi
NK064(ngu)001:11423: 'grogs shing yud tsam du'ang gtam smra bar ma byed
NK064(ngu)001:11425: nyams pa dang 'grogs par gyur pa'i nyes pa brjod kyis mi lang ste zlas nyams zhes bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11427: ji ltar 'o ma rul ba dag /
NK064(ngu)001:11428: rul bas 'o ma kun rul ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:11429: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK064(ngu)001:11430: rnal 'byor can kun ma rungs byed //
NK064(ngu)001:11433: rtsa ba'i dam tshig sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11434: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams par gyur na char phab
NK064(ngu)001:11435: pas than pa 'byung ba lta bu tshe 'dir yang
NK064(ngu)001:11436: las gang sgrub pa thams cad kyang 'bras bu phyin
NK064(ngu)001:11437: ci log par 'gyur ba sogs mi 'dod pa sna
NK064(ngu)001:11438: tshogs 'byung zhing / phyi mar yang yid du mi
NK064(ngu)001:11439: 'ong ba sna tshogs pa'i 'bras bu rdo rje'i dmyal
NK064(ngu)001:11440: ba sogs ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:11441: bzhin du khab len gyis lcags ltar rang dbang med
NK064(ngu)001:11444: yan lag sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11445: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na bsgrubs
NK064(ngu)001:11446: pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub med cing phyi mar ngan
NK064(ngu)001:11447: song gsum gyi gnas su ltung bar 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11448: lnga pa dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11449: dam tshig rnams ni sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:11450: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11451: rang bzhin ni sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa
NK064(ngu)001:11452: rdo rje chen po'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:11453: 'di ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag
NK064(ngu)001:11454: nyid chos kun gyi srog dang bslab pa thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:11456: drug pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11460: rtsa ba'i dam tshig sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11462: phyi ma rtsa ba yan lag las //
NK064(ngu)001:11463: lnga bcu'i brgya dang drug cu dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11464: nyis brgya'i bsrung bya ma lus pa //
NK064(ngu)001:11465: bka' lung gnyis kyi rjes su bsnyeg /
NK064(ngu)001:11466: ces pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig la brgya drug cu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11467: yan lag gi dam tshig la nyis brgyar phye bas sum brgya drug cu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11468: de yang rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po la ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11469: gcig ste re re la'ang thabs shes gnyis gnyis su phye bas bcu dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11470: yang rtsa ba lnga po re re la'ang bcu phrag
NK064(ngu)001:11471: gsum ste sum cu rer phye bas chig brgya lnga
NK064(ngu)001:11472: bcu ste / de sngar gyi bcu dang sdom pas brgya drug cu'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11475: dang po nyid las thabs spyod dang //
NK064(ngu)001:11476: shes rab nyid kyis nyis 'gyur yin //
NK064(ngu)001:11477: re re'ang bsrung bya sum cu ste //
NK064(ngu)001:11479: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis te bcu
NK064(ngu)001:11480: po re re la dbye tshul gti mug lta bu
NK064(ngu)001:11481: gcig la'ang nang tshan bcu phrag gnyis su ste nyi
NK064(ngu)001:11482: shu nyi shur dbye bas nyis bargya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11483: de ltar rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK064(ngu)001:11484: sum brgya drug cu so so'i don shes par 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:11485: na phra rgyas su blta bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11487: dam tshig 'di ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11488: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK064(ngu)001:11489: ni gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas rmad po
NK064(ngu)001:11490: che yin te / des don bya ba'i yul 'jig
NK064(ngu)001:11491: rten drug gi phyogs bcu na srid pa gsum gyis
NK064(ngu)001:11492: bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ji snyed cig yod pa de
NK064(ngu)001:11493: rnams so so'i rnam par rtog pa 'dul ba'i gnyen
NK064(ngu)001:11494: por dam tshig gi rnam grangs kyang bsam gyis mi
NK064(ngu)001:11495: khyab pa de snyed cig spros nas don mdzad do
NK064(ngu)001:11496: che yin te / // bdun pa ma nyams pa'i yon tan bstan pa la drug las /
NK064(ngu)001:11497: dang po 'bras bu thob cing tshad med pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11498: gzhan yang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11499: mnyam pa'i dam tshig las gzhan yang rtsa ba dang
NK064(ngu)001:11500: yan lag gi dam tshig rnams bsrungs pa'i 'bras bu
NK064(ngu)001:11501: rgyal mchog rigs kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po
NK064(ngu)001:11502: nyid kyi go 'phang thob par 'gyur te /
NK064(ngu)001:11503: de'i ngo bo ji ltar zhe na /
NK064(ngu)001:11504: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK064(ngu)001:11505: pa rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i ngo
NK064(ngu)001:11506: bor lhun gyis grub pas ched du sgrub pa med
NK064(ngu)001:11507: par 'bras bu'i mchog dam pa kun bzang gi yon
NK064(ngu)001:11509: de la sogs pa'i yon tan bsam brjod las 'das pas na mtha' yas pa'i mchog go //
NK064(ngu)001:11510: gnyis pa 'jig rten gyi gtso bos bstod cing bkur ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11511: rgyal ba'i sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11512: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog gsang sngags 'dzin cing dam tshig
NK064(ngu)001:11513: la gnas pa de lha chen po la sogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:11514: 'jig rten gyi gtso bo rnams dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11515: de'i 'khor ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad kyis
NK064(ngu)001:11516: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ltar bkur gnas dam par mthong
NK064(ngu)001:11517: bar 'gyur ro // gsum pa 'phags pas byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11518: dam pa sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11519: dam pa mchog rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11520: dam pa sar gnas kyi byang chub sems dpa' yis
NK064(ngu)001:11521: rim pa ji lta bar rang gi sras kyi thu
NK064(ngu)001:11522: bo dang / spun du dgongs pas thugs rje'i byin
NK064(ngu)001:11523: gyis rlob pa myur ba nyid du 'jug par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11524: bo dang / ro // bzhi pa rgyal ba'i spyod yul thob pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11525: bde gshegs sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11526: dam tshig dang ldan pa de ni bde bar gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:11527: pa nyid kyi spyod yul rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa
NK064(ngu)001:11529: ltung gnas kyi 'jigs pa dang bag tsha ba thams
NK064(ngu)001:11530: cad med pa spyod yul yongs dag kun tu bzang
NK064(ngu)001:11531: po'i zhing khams chen por sbyor bar 'gyur ro //
NK064(ngu)001:11532: lnga pa 'og ma'i 'dul sdom rdzogs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11533: ji bzhin sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11534: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid mngon du byed pa bla med kyi dam tshig dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11535: de'i nang du gdul bya rnams blo dang 'tshams par
NK064(ngu)001:11536: 'dul ba'i thabs nyan rang byang sems kyi kri yog
NK064(ngu)001:11537: sogs theg pa ji snyed pa de dag gi sdom
NK064(ngu)001:11538: pa bsam yas pa thams cad kyang 'dir yar ldan
NK064(ngu)001:11540: dgag bya ma lus pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11541: yon tan thams cad ma btsal bar rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11542: drug pa nyams kyang bskang ba'i thabs yod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11543: nyams na sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11544: gal te gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams par gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11545: na nyan thos kyi pham pa 'chab bcas byung ba
NK064(ngu)001:11546: ltar gsor mi rung ba ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:11547: skong ba'i thabs khyad par can gyi cho gas bskang bas sngar bzhin sor chud cing /
NK064(ngu)001:11548: dam tshig gi yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11549: de la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa'i mchog
NK064(ngu)001:11550: rdo rje'i theg pa 'di la mnga' ba yin no
NK064(ngu)001:11553: de skad ces brjod pas dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni de bzhin gshegs pa nyid yin pas na /
NK064(ngu)001:11554: de'i rang bzhin las rgyal ba de bzhin gshegs pa
NK064(ngu)001:11555: nyid kyang 'da' bar mi mdzad na gzhan lta ci
NK064(ngu)001:11556: smos te / de'i phyir gdul bya rnams la bla
NK064(ngu)001:11557: na med pa'i dam tshig bstan nas 'dul bar gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11558: smos te / to // gsum pa mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11560: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:11561: 'dis rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gi rnam bzhag bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11563: // le'u nyi shu pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11569: dam tshig bstan pa de nas dam tshig can gyis
NK064(ngu)001:11570: phrin las bya ba ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs
NK064(ngu)001:11571: pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos ye nas
NK064(ngu)001:11572: sems nyid phrin las bzhi'i rang bzhin du lhun gyis
NK064(ngu)001:11573: grub pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig de nyid
NK064(ngu)001:11574: cho ga bzhis bskul bas mngon du snang bar byin
NK064(ngu)001:11575: gyis rlob pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK064(ngu)001:11576: snyoms par zhugs nas phrin las kyi don ched du
NK064(ngu)001:11578: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11582: rdzas hom lug rgyud kyi sgo nas las bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11584: bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11585: las bzhi'i gnas gzungs thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11586: don stongs kyi sems bstan pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11587: dang po la'ang las rnam pa bzhi las /
NK064(ngu)001:11588: thog mar drag po'i phrin las la lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11592: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:11593: lu gu rgyud kyi bro'i las yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11595: bdud rtsi lnga sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11596: bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga ste zag rdzas sam /
NK064(ngu)001:11602: gzhan yang mi la rkang rjes kyi sa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11603: mi ma yin pa la gnas rten gyi sa sogs
NK064(ngu)001:11604: la rgyu byas pa'i ling+ga pho mo gang yin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11605: mtshan ma can dpral bar rus /
NK064(ngu)001:11606: snying gar srog gang yin ming du bcas pa rnams
NK064(ngu)001:11607: gro shog la bris te gnas so sor glan pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:11608: / yang na gro shog rang la ling+ga bris pa'i lte bar bla dwags /
NK064(ngu)001:11609: 'doms su che ge mo m+aa ra ya phata kyi spu gri bri /
NK064(ngu)001:11611: sngar gyi rdzas rnams byugs te /
NK064(ngu)001:11612: thod pa mtshan ngan gyi nang du mgo lho nub
NK064(ngu)001:11613: tu bstan nas bcug pa dkyil 'khor gyi byang phyogs
NK064(ngu)001:11614: su brub khung gru gsum du gzhug par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11616: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:11618: sngags 'chang rnams drag po'i las dang mthun pa'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis /
NK064(ngu)001:11619: e ram sogs brjod pas phyi snod kyi 'jig rten
NK064(ngu)001:11620: gru gsum e yig gi rnam pa can mthing nag
NK064(ngu)001:11621: me 'bar ba'i dbus su sngags kyi rkyen gyis nang
NK064(ngu)001:11622: bcud kyi sems can thams cad khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11623: lha tshogs lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor drag
NK064(ngu)001:11624: po'i las la mchog tu shis pa badz+ra he ru
NK064(ngu)001:11626: thams cad kyang sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs can du bzhengs par bsam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11628: bkug nas sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11629: ba hu'i sngags kyis las la gzud /
NK064(ngu)001:11631: bsgrub bya bkug nas gnyis med du bstim la /
NK064(ngu)001:11632: lcags sam shing nag po las byas pa'i rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:11633: phur bu rgya mdud dbal zur gsum pa gsum sras
NK064(ngu)001:11634: mchog badz+ra k+ai la yar bskyed nas byin gyis brlabs
NK064(ngu)001:11635: te / phur bskul dang sder mo'i sngags las kyi
NK064(ngu)001:11636: spu gri btags pas dpral ba sogs gnas gsum du
NK064(ngu)001:11638: mtshon cha'i char dbab pas lus ngag rdul phran bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:11639: du byas par bsams nas ling ro cha gsum du
NK064(ngu)001:11640: bcad la / cha gcig badz+ra he ru kas gtso
NK064(ngu)001:11641: byas pa'i khrag 'thung gi tshogs la dbul te stob
NK064(ngu)001:11642: bcad la / pa bya / cha gcig sbyin sreg gi sreg rdzas dang bsre /
NK064(ngu)001:11643: cha gcig bro gdan la bro ra'i dbus su spungs
NK064(ngu)001:11644: nas bro brdungs rjes mi ma yin gdug pa can
NK064(ngu)001:11645: gnas pa'i sar dong gru gsum par bcug ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11646: dur g.yam la ro sol gyis rdo rje rgya gram bris pas bkab la mnan par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11648: 'bar ba sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11649: drag po'i me lha'i lto bar badz+ra he ru kas
NK064(ngu)001:11650: gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK064(ngu)001:11651: pa'i lha tshogs gtum chen rngams pa'i cha byad can
NK064(ngu)001:11652: la / stongs kyi sems rab tu khros pa'i yid
NK064(ngu)001:11653: kyis sreg blugs kyi mchod sbyin byas na tshogs gnyis
NK064(ngu)001:11654: las grub pa sangs rgyas bsod nams brgya'i mtshan gyis
NK064(ngu)001:11655: brgyan pa'i sku yang 'jig na bsgral bya'i sems can
NK064(ngu)001:11658: e yi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11659: e b+h+rum zhes brjod pas phyi snod drag po'i dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:11660: 'khor e dbyibs gru gsum pa'i rnam pa can mthing
NK064(ngu)001:11661: nag 'bar ba'i dbus su sngags kyi rkyen gyis bcud
NK064(ngu)001:11662: thams cad khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i lha tshogs lnga bcu
NK064(ngu)001:11663: rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor gtso mchog badz+ra he ru
NK064(ngu)001:11665: ling ro dbus su spungs pa'i mthar sgrub pa po
NK064(ngu)001:11666: mched lcam kun bro ra gru gsum du bcas la
NK064(ngu)001:11667: / lag g.yas steng du byas te bsnol ba'i mathe'u
NK064(ngu)001:11668: chung rnams lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas
NK064(ngu)001:11670: zhe sdang rdo rje sogs kyi tshig dang sum+b+ha'i sngags kyis bskul zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:11671: phyag rgya de ltar bcings par gyur pa las mig
NK064(ngu)001:11672: dang lus bskyod nas bro brdungs pas rdo rje'i rigs
NK064(ngu)001:11673: kyi khro tshogs dpag med phyogs bcur g.yos pas bsgrub
NK064(ngu)001:11674: bya rdul du brlag par bsams la /
NK064(ngu)001:11675: che ge mo m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK064(ngu)001:11677: phyag rgya sprugs te bshig pas gzas po de nyid
NK064(ngu)001:11678: dran pa myos nas snying gas te lus kyang thul
NK064(ngu)001:11679: gyis 'tshig nas ming gi tha mar byed par 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11680: ro // de bzhin du dbang sogs las lhag ma gzhan gsum spyir des khog phub pa la /
NK064(ngu)001:11681: khyad par gyi sgos chos rnams bshad par bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11682: de la ling+ga bca' ba ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11683: rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la /
NK064(ngu)001:11684: bsgrub bya gang yin gyi ling+ga mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11685: de'ang dbang la gang dbang du bya bar 'dod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11686: rgyas pa la 'jig rten na tshe dang bsod nams
NK064(ngu)001:11687: rgyas pa sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan 'byung ba'i yid
NK064(ngu)001:11688: bzhin gyi gter du brtag pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11689: zhi ba la ma rungs pa gtum rngam 'khrug pa'i ngo bor brtag ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11690: de rnams las gang yin gyi brub khung du bcug nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11693: zhi bar shar du bzhag go //
NK064(ngu)001:11694: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11695: dbang la wam gi rnam pa'i dkyil 'khor dmar po zla gam /
NK064(ngu)001:11696: rgyas pa la ma yi rnam pa'i gru bzhi ser po /
NK064(ngu)001:11697: zhi ba la ya yi rnam pa'i zlum po dkar po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11698: thams cad kyang yangs shing me 'od 'phro ba can
NK064(ngu)001:11699: gyi nang du khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i lha tshogs lnga
NK064(ngu)001:11700: bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor las gang la shis
NK064(ngu)001:11701: pa'i mchog dbang la pad+ma he ru ka /
NK064(ngu)001:11702: rgyas par rat+na he ru ka /
NK064(ngu)001:11703: zhi bar bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:11704: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang las dang mthun pa'i kha dog can du bskyed do //
NK064(ngu)001:11705: de nas bsgrub bya'i las ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11706: sngar bzhin bsgrub bya dgug bstim gyi bar du byas te /
NK064(ngu)001:11707: dbang la zangs sam shing dmar po las dbal zla
NK064(ngu)001:11708: gam can rdo rjee chags pa ste pad+ma k+ai la
NK064(ngu)001:11709: yar bskyed pa'i phur bu lnga dbang po lnga dang
NK064(ngu)001:11710: / rgyas par gser ram shing ser po las dbal
NK064(ngu)001:11711: gru bzhi par byas pa nga rgyal dga' 'phro ste
NK064(ngu)001:11712: rat+na he ru kar bskyed pa'i phur bu bzhi yan
NK064(ngu)001:11713: / lag bzhi dang / zhi par dngul lam shing
NK064(ngu)001:11714: dkar po las dbal zlum por byas pa lhan ner
NK064(ngu)001:11715: gsal ba ste bud+d+ha k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur
NK064(ngu)001:11716: bu drug gis yan lag lnga dang snying la gdab
NK064(ngu)001:11717: / lag bzhi dang / par bya ste / phur
NK064(ngu)001:11718: bu thams cad kyang mgo bo rgya mdud can byin
NK064(ngu)001:11719: / lag bzhi dang / par bya ste / gyis brlabs te / phur bskul dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11720: sder mo'i sngags las so so'i spu gri'i sham bu can gyis gdab cing /
NK064(ngu)001:11722: ling ro cha gcig chags pa'i tshogs dang 'bar ba
NK064(ngu)001:11723: lhan ne sogs las dang mthun pa'i lha la stob
NK064(ngu)001:11724: par bya / cha gcig las gang yin gyi bsreg rdzas la bsre /
NK064(ngu)001:11725: cha gcig la bro gdan bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11726: de nas mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11727: las so so'i me lha'i lto bar 'das pa'i lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed de /
NK064(ngu)001:11728: de'ang dbang la lha tshogs 'od 'bar ba gzi brjid
NK064(ngu)001:11729: che zhing sku lhun po chen po lta bu pad
NK064(ngu)001:11730: rigs gtso bor byas pa la stongs kyi sems chags
NK064(ngu)001:11731: pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i gsung rdo rje
NK064(ngu)001:11732: pad+ma gar dbang yang dbang du 'gyur na gzhan lta
NK064(ngu)001:11734: rgyas par rin chen rigs gtso bor byas pa'i lha
NK064(ngu)001:11735: tshogs 'od 'bar ba sprul pa'i 'du 'phro can gzi
NK064(ngu)001:11736: brjid chen po la stongs kyi sems dga' zhing spro
NK064(ngu)001:11737: ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pas tshe dang bsod
NK064(ngu)001:11738: nams 'phel ba sogs yon tan tshad med nam mkha'i
NK064(ngu)001:11739: mtha' dang mnyam pa thob pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11740: zhi bar bud+d+hasa gtso byas pa'i lha tshogs dwangs shing
NK064(ngu)001:11741: gsal ba'i gzi brjid mchog tu 'bar zhing 'od zer
NK064(ngu)001:11742: 'tsher ba la stongs kyi sems zhi zhing dang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:11743: yid kyis mchod sbyin byas na ma rungs pa gtum
NK064(ngu)001:11744: chen rngam pa'ang zhi ba'i sems su lhan ner 'gyur
NK064(ngu)001:11745: ba'o // de nas lug rgyud yon tan dang bcas pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11746: sngar bzhin wam b+h+rum sogs kyis yi ge gsum gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11747: rnam pa'i dkyil 'khor me 'bar ba'i nang du las
NK064(ngu)001:11748: dang mthun pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba tshogs kyi dkyil
NK064(ngu)001:11749: 'khor bskyed la / ling ro spungs pa'i mthar mched
NK064(ngu)001:11750: rnams lag g.yas steng du byas nas bsnol ba'i dbang
NK064(ngu)001:11751: 'khor bskyed la / la srin lag / rgyas par gung mo /
NK064(ngu)001:11752: zhi bar mdzub mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing
NK064(ngu)001:11753: bsdams nas bro ra las dbyibs dang mthun pa bcas
NK064(ngu)001:11755: 'dod chags rdo rje sogs las so so'i tshig dang sum+b+ha'i sngags kyis bskul la bro brdungs /
NK064(ngu)001:11756: de'i tshe rigs so so'i khro tshogs dpag med spros pas las gang yin 'grub par bsams nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11757: las so so'i spu gri'i sngags brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs te bshig la /
NK064(ngu)001:11758: ling ro de dbang la rang gi mal 'og /
NK064(ngu)001:11760: zhi bar lam gyi dkyil rnams su las mthun gyi brub khung brus par mnan no //
NK064(ngu)001:11761: de dag gi yon tan kyang /
NK064(ngu)001:11762: dbang gis 'gro ba thams cad 'gugs par 'gyur ba la lta ci smos te /
NK064(ngu)001:11763: phyag na rdo rje'ang rang gi phyi bzhin du 'brang
NK064(ngu)001:11764: ba sogs yid la ci 'dod pa de bzhin du
NK064(ngu)001:11766: rgyas par gzi brjid 'bar ba'i rnam 'phrul chen po
NK064(ngu)001:11767: rigs kyi khro bo spro ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK064(ngu)001:11768: yon tan tshe dang bsod nams sogs 'dod dgu 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:11769: ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor bus nam mkha'i khams thams
NK064(ngu)001:11771: zhi bas pha rol ma rungs pa'i sems me ltar
NK064(ngu)001:11772: 'bar ba'ang lhan ner zhi ba'i byin rlabs kyis khyab
NK064(ngu)001:11773: par sdig pa dang gdug sems thams cad cung zad
NK064(ngu)001:11774: kyang yid la mi 'gyur bas g.yo ba med par
NK064(ngu)001:11775: byed pa'o // gnyis pa lhag ma'i las la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11779: slas dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11780: de ltar las bzhi gang yang rung ba byas pa'i rjes la /
NK064(ngu)001:11784: lhag gtor rnams kha phrus bran nas gtor mar bsre zhing so sor mchod de /
NK064(ngu)001:11785: dpal chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran du gnas pa slas te lha chen po'i chung ma dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11786: byi mo ste mdza' mo dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11787: g.yog byed pas bran mo'i tshogs te dbang phyug ma
NK064(ngu)001:11788: nyi shu rtsa brgyad po lhag ma'i mchod spyin 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:11790: cho ga bzhin du sbyin te za lam bdun cu'i sar bskyal zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:11791: sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar rang rang gi khas
NK064(ngu)001:11792: blangs pa'i dam tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags nas phrin
NK064(ngu)001:11793: las bzhi gang dang gang 'dod pa'i las de dang
NK064(ngu)001:11794: de byed par bka' bsgo bar bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11796: dam bsgrag cing las la bskul ba /
NK064(ngu)001:11797: las de ma bsgrubs pa'i skyon /
NK064(ngu)001:11798: las bsgrubs pa'i yon tan no //
NK064(ngu)001:11800: sngon tshe sogs rkang pa dgu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11801: sngon r+au dra 'dul ba'i tshe dpal chen po he
NK064(ngu)001:11802: ru ka gdul bya dang mthun par shin tu gdug
NK064(ngu)001:11803: cing gtum bag can du bzhengs te /
NK064(ngu)001:11804: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi dregs pa can
NK064(ngu)001:11805: ma lus pa rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'i dbang phyug
NK064(ngu)001:11806: dang byin rlabs khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir rmad
NK064(ngu)001:11807: po che mnga' bas lha chen po la sogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:11808: thams cad dbang du bsdus nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11809: de dag gi 'khor na gnas pa'i ma mo rnams
NK064(ngu)001:11810: longs spyod pa'i phyir dbang phyug dang slas su dbang
NK064(ngu)001:11812: zhi rgyas dbang drag so so'i las rnams skal ba
NK064(ngu)001:11813: bzhin bskos pa de nyid sngon ji ltar dam bcas
NK064(ngu)001:11814: shing khas blangs pa rnams skad cig kyang ma thogs
NK064(ngu)001:11815: par myur ba nyid du las kyi 'bras bu mngon
NK064(ngu)001:11816: par phyung bar mdzod cig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11818: dam bcas sogs rkang pa bcu gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11819: rang gi dam bcas pa bzhin du las ma byas
NK064(ngu)001:11820: na sngon ji ltar rang gis dam bcas shing mna'
NK064(ngu)001:11821: bor ba'i sdom bcas kyi mtshams de las 'da' bar
NK064(ngu)001:11822: 'gyur la / gal te dam tshig de las 'da'
NK064(ngu)001:11823: bar gyur na ni khyed cag rnams kyi mgo lus
NK064(ngu)001:11824: dang snying yang tshal pa bdun du yak+sha khro bos
NK064(ngu)001:11826: de bas na de 'dra'i nyen la ma bdo bar
NK064(ngu)001:11827: rnal 'byor sngags 'chang bdag gis las ji ltar bcol
NK064(ngu)001:11828: ba bzhin du sgrub par byos shig /
NK064(ngu)001:11829: gal te las de mngon du ma byas na rang
NK064(ngu)001:11830: rang gis mna' bor zhing khas blangs pa'i dmod pa
NK064(ngu)001:11831: bzhin rul myags 'tshig nas mthur du bltas te rdo
NK064(ngu)001:11834: rnal 'byor sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11835: de bas na rnal 'byor pa dam pa gnas par
NK064(ngu)001:11836: gyur pa'i las gang dang gang 'dod pa rnams yongs
NK064(ngu)001:11837: su rdzogs par bya ba dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11838: rnal 'byor pa de'i 'khor rnams kyang rang gi bu
NK064(ngu)001:11839: gcig pu la mas gdungs pa bzhin du skyongs shig
NK064(ngu)001:11840: dang / de'i mthus khyed cag phra men ma rnams
NK064(ngu)001:11841: kyang dngos grub rnam pa gnyis thob par 'gyur ba
NK064(ngu)001:11842: dang / de'i phyir / rnal 'byor pas ji ltar
NK064(ngu)001:11843: bcol ba'i las rnams mngon sum du grub par byos
NK064(ngu)001:11845: gsum pa bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11850: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang tshogs kyi sgrub pa'i dus
NK064(ngu)001:11851: su phrin las bzhi'i bya thabs kyi gtso bo ni
NK064(ngu)001:11852: bro gar glu tshig 'di yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:11853: hom dang rdzas sogs kyi sgo nas las bzhi'i phrin las gang dang gang bgyis kyang rung ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11854: las zin rjes 'dis mtha' bsdus na las byas pa gsor mi rung bar 'gyur ba yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11856: zhes pa khro bo'i sgrub thabs kyi //
NK064(ngu)001:11857: las rnams kun la brjod par bya //
NK064(ngu)001:11858: nges par gtso bo 'di yin te //
NK064(ngu)001:11859: rnam pa gzhan du gdul dkar 'gyur //
NK064(ngu)001:11862: khrag 'thung yab yum gyis las bzhi ka 'grub pa /
NK064(ngu)001:11863: phyogs kyi khro mos dbang rgyas /
NK064(ngu)001:11864: mtshams kyi khro mos zhi drag /
NK064(ngu)001:11865: phyogs kyi phra men mas drag po /
NK064(ngu)001:11866: mtshams kyi phra men mas kyang drag po /
NK064(ngu)001:11867: dbang phyug mas pho nya dang mngags gzhug gi las thams cad 'grub pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11869: khrag 'thung sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11870: khrag 'thung chen po badz+ra he ru ka la sogs
NK064(ngu)001:11871: pa rigs lnga'i he ru ka yab yum gyi rkang
NK064(ngu)001:11872: pa'i bro lag pa'i gar zhal gyi glu tshig gi
NK064(ngu)001:11874: zhi rgyas sogs las thams cad dang mchog thun gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11875: dngos grub thams cad ci dang ci thob par 'dod
NK064(ngu)001:11876: pa ltar las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:11879: mdzod ldan sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11880: goo r+ai'i sgra las mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs pa'i khongs nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11883: be t+aa li rnams kyi bro gar glu tshig chen
NK064(ngu)001:11884: mos ni 'gro ba dbang du 'du bar 'dod na
NK064(ngu)001:11886: tshe dang bsod nams sogs 'phel zhing rgyas par 'dod na 'phel zhing rgyas par byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:11888: sbos mo sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11889: puk+ka s+ai'i sgra las sbos mo chen mo la sogs pa'i khongs nas /
NK064(ngu)001:11892: tsan+da l+ai rnams kyi bro gar glu tshig chen mos
NK064(ngu)001:11893: ni mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams lhan ner zhi bar
NK064(ngu)001:11894: 'dod na zhi zhing lhan ner byed la /
NK064(ngu)001:11895: drag pos dran pa nyams te sems rmugs shing mi gsal bar 'dod na rmugs par byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:11897: seng gdong sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11898: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa mche ba can
NK064(ngu)001:11899: bzhi'i bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni gdug pa
NK064(ngu)001:11900: can thams cad kun gyi srog lus la za bar
NK064(ngu)001:11901: byed cing / rdul phran gyi cha tsam yang med par brlag par byed do //
NK064(ngu)001:11903: bzhad gdong sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11904: grid+d+ha'i sgra las bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs pa
NK064(ngu)001:11905: gshog pa can bzhi'i bro gar glu tshig chen mos
NK064(ngu)001:11906: ni gdug pa can thams cad kyi mthu rtsal ma
NK064(ngu)001:11907: lus pa'am rang gnas las 'byin pa ste bskrad par
NK064(ngu)001:11908: byed cing / de dag kun la yod pa'i phun
NK064(ngu)001:11909: sum tshogs pa rnams rab tu nyams par byed do
NK064(ngu)001:11910: byed cing / // 'di'i 'byin pa zhes pa'i rgya dper /
NK064(ngu)001:11911: +aa kar+sha zhes yod pas 'gugs pa'i don de dbang gi las su 'gyur ram snyam mo //
NK064(ngu)001:11913: slas dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11914: slas dang byi mo bran mo ste dbang phyug ma'i
NK064(ngu)001:11915: tshogs kyi bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni dgra
