NK064(ngu)001:11916: la rbad cing mngags gzhug gi las la gtang bar
NK064(ngu)001:11917: bya ba ste / 'gal byed thams cad brlag par byed pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11918: mthun pa'i phyogs rnams sgrub pa pho nya'i las thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK064(ngu)001:11919: bzhi pa las bzhi'i gnas gzungs thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11920: ljon pa sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11921: shing ljon pa can ni zhi ba'i gnas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11922: lcug phran gyi tshal ni rgyas pa'i dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11923: sdong gcig ni dbang gi dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11924: mes reg ste nags tshal 'tshig pa'i gnas su drag po'i las shis pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11925: las so so'i gzungs ma yang /
NK064(ngu)001:11926: zhi ba'i gzungs ma shing ljon pa chos mtshungs pa
NK064(ngu)001:11927: ni dung can ma'i rigs dkar mo bzhin lus mdzes
NK064(ngu)001:11929: rgyas pa'i gzungs ma ni lcug phran gyi tshal lta
NK064(ngu)001:11930: bu ste ba glang can gyi rigs sha rgyas shing
NK064(ngu)001:11932: dbang ni gzungs ma shing sdong po gcig pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:11933: chos mthun pa ni pad+ma can gyi rigs bzhin lus
NK064(ngu)001:11934: mdzes shing spun zla dang bu tsha med pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11935: drag po'i gzungs ma ljon shing mes reg pa lta
NK064(ngu)001:11936: bu ni ri mo can gyi rigs mdog nag cing
NK064(ngu)001:11937: ngag gtum pa la sogs pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11938: lnga pa don stongs kyi sems bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11939: dang bas sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11940: de la don gyi sems ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11941: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi gnas lugs rtogs shing /
NK064(ngu)001:11942: tshad med pa bzhi'i rgyu las byung ba'i byang chub
NK064(ngu)001:11943: kyi sems dang ldan pa ni las bzhi ka la
NK064(ngu)001:11944: khyab byed du dgos pa rgyu'i sems zhes bya ste
NK064(ngu)001:11946: rang rig sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK064(ngu)001:11947: thams cad rang dbang sgyur bdag phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:11948: sgrub pa'i gtso bor 'di gsungs so //
NK064(ngu)001:11951: mthun pa'i grogs byed pas rkyen gyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11952: las so so kun nas slong ba'i bsam pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11953: de'ang zhi ba la zhi zhing dang bas /
NK064(ngu)001:11954: rgyas pa la dga' zhing spro bas /
NK064(ngu)001:11955: dbang la chags shing zhen pas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11956: drag po la zhe sdang khros pa'i sems dang ldan pas k+aa li thabs te /
NK064(ngu)001:11957: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa rab tu bsgrub par bya'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11960: de skad ces brjod pas gdul bya rang bzhin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:11961: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de sems can rnams la
NK064(ngu)001:11962: / 'dul byed rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i de
NK064(ngu)001:11963: bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis phrin las rnam bzhis rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:11964: dag par spyod pas 'dul bar gyur to //
NK064(ngu)001:11967: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:11968: 'dis ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las bzhi
NK064(ngu)001:11969: mngon du snang bar byed pas byin gyis brlab pa
NK064(ngu)001:11970: zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11972: // le'u nyer gcig pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11978: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bstan pa de nas
NK064(ngu)001:11979: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i phyir bcom
NK064(ngu)001:11980: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po khrag 'thung nga brgyad
NK064(ngu)001:11981: 'dus pa'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis zhal shin tu
NK064(ngu)001:11982: rngam pa'i mdangs kyis rang snang gi 'khor lor dgyes
NK064(ngu)001:11983: pa'i glu drug po 'di blangs so //
NK064(ngu)001:11984: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:11985: 'bras chos lnga so sor bstod pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:11986: rten brten pa spyir bstod pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11988: dang po sku la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11991: 'go 'dren gyi h+aum rnams ni khro bo'i snang glu ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11992: glu rnams re re'ang sku lnga ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:11993: de la dpal chen po'i sku ni /
NK064(ngu)001:11994: dregs pa can rnams 'dul bas gtum po chen po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:11995: dus kyi mtha'i bskal pa 'jig pa'i me chen ltar
NK064(ngu)001:11996: 'bar ba'i sku las ye shes kyi 'od zer nyi
NK064(ngu)001:11997: ma 'bum dus gcig la shar ba ltar gyi gzi
NK064(ngu)001:11998: brjid chen pos thams cad zil gyis gnon pa /
NK064(ngu)001:11999: mi sdug pa'i khro gnyer rnam par 'gyur ba ni
NK064(ngu)001:12000: glog stong dus gcig la 'gyu ba bzhin 'khyug pas
NK064(ngu)001:12002: gdug pa can tshar gcod pa'i mche ba ni t+aik+sha'i
NK064(ngu)001:12003: sgra las zangs yag ste rnon po gtsigs pas ma
NK064(ngu)001:12004: rungs pa thams cad chom chom du za bar byed
NK064(ngu)001:12006: mjug gi hohrnamasa ni dgyes pa'i gad rgyang ngo //
NK064(ngu)001:12007: gnyis pa gsung la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12009: 'jigs rung khros shing rngam pa'i gsung gi nga ro
NK064(ngu)001:12010: ni 'brug stong dus gcig la ldir ba ltar sgra'i
NK064(ngu)001:12011: gtum chen gyi drag shul ri rab 'bum dus gcig
NK064(ngu)001:12012: la bsnyil ba'i skad dang mnyam pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12015: a la la zhes rdo rje'i gad rgyangs chen po
NK064(ngu)001:12016: rgod pas sa gsum g.yo ba dbugs kyi shugs las
NK064(ngu)001:12017: spyugs pa'i 'thor byed kyi rlung chen pos gdug pa
NK064(ngu)001:12019: dus mtha'i rlung chen pos gtor ba ltar byed pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12020: gsum pa thugs la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12021: khro bo shes rab sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:12022: ye shes chen pos ma rig pa'i tshogs la ngam
NK064(ngu)001:12023: ngam shugs kyis khros pa'i khro bo yang dag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12024: shes rab kyis gdul bya'i mun pa sel bar mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:12026: thugs ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyis shes bya'i yul
NK064(ngu)001:12027: kun dus gcig tu rang gsal ma 'gags par mkhyen
NK064(ngu)001:12028: cing / 'bar ba'i ye shes des gdul bya'i log rtog kun tu 'joms par mdzad pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12029: de yang ye shes lnga dang ji lta ji snyed
NK064(ngu)001:12030: mkhyen pa'i ye shes sogs sna tshogs pa'i ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:12031: rnam pa tha dad du gsal ba kun kyang rang
NK064(ngu)001:12032: byung gi ye shes thig le chen po gcig gi
NK064(ngu)001:12034: bzhi pa yon tan la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12035: khro bo'i rgyal po sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:12036: gdug pa can 'dul ba khro bo'i mdzad pas gdul bya la dbang sgyur ba'i rgyal po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12037: yon tan 'byung ba'i sprin chen po las 'phros pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12038: 'dul byed khro bo'i dkyil 'khoor gyi thugs rje'i char
NK064(ngu)001:12039: chen po 'bebs pas gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul
NK064(ngu)001:12040: pa'i dkyil 'khor zad pa med pa dgos 'dod yid
NK064(ngu)001:12041: bzhin du 'byung ba rin po che'i gter dang 'dra
NK064(ngu)001:12042: bas don mdzad pa sna tshogs su snang ba'i phyag
NK064(ngu)001:12043: rgya chen po'i skur khros pa thams cad ye shes
NK064(ngu)001:12044: chen po'i khro bor ro gcig pa'i thig le chen
NK064(ngu)001:12045: por gnas pa'o // lnga pa phrin las la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12047: bdud bzhi po kun gyi rang bzhin ma spangs par
NK064(ngu)001:12048: dbang du byed pa ni bdag nyid chen po dpal
NK064(ngu)001:12049: he ru ka'o // de'ang bdud bzhi'i dpung mthar byed
NK064(ngu)001:12050: kyi bdud de sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12052: bdud dang gshin rje sogs 'jigs pa'i tshogs rnams kyang
NK064(ngu)001:12053: bsdigs shing 'jigs par byed pas 'jigs byed chen po
NK064(ngu)001:12054: che btsan 'gran zla dang bral ba'i khrag 'thung gi
NK064(ngu)001:12055: tshogs thams cad kyang ngo bo chos sku spros bral
NK064(ngu)001:12056: thig le chen por ro gcig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12057: gnyis pa rten brten pa spyir bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12058: rdo rje brag chen sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:12059: khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:12060: sku ni rdo rje'i brag chen po ltar skye shi
NK064(ngu)001:12061: dang 'pho 'gyur med pas sra ba po ste che
NK064(ngu)001:12062: ba'i yon tan kun gyi rten du gyur pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12063: gsung dang yon tan ni rdo rje'i chu bo lta
NK064(ngu)001:12064: bu ste gdul bya'i tshogs ma lus pa sdud pa
NK064(ngu)001:12065: dang bde ba chen pos rgyud brlan cing tshim par
NK064(ngu)001:12066: mdzad pa'o // thugs ni rdo rje me ste thugs
NK064(ngu)001:12067: rje'i ye shes kun tu 'bar ba chen pos mtshan
NK064(ngu)001:12068: ma'i rtog pa thams cad bsreg cing shes bya'i yul
NK064(ngu)001:12069: thams cad mngon sum du mkhyen pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12070: phrin las ni rdo rje'i rlung ste gdul bya la
NK064(ngu)001:12071: khyab cing g.yo bas 'dul bar mdzad cing khyad par
NK064(ngu)001:12072: gdug pa can rnams chos dbyings su 'thor bar byed
NK064(ngu)001:12073: pa'i rlung chen po ste brten pa la bstod pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:12074: // rten gzhal yas khang la bstod pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12075: rdo rje brag chen ni keng rus kyi ri rab zhing chen gyis gzhi sra ba dang bcas pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12076: rdo rje chu ni rak+ta'i rgya mtsho /
NK064(ngu)001:12077: rdo rje me ni ye shes kyi me /
NK064(ngu)001:12078: rdo rje rlung ni 'og gzhi rlung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12079: nam mkha' ni kun gyi go 'byed pa ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12080: 'byung lnga dag pa yum lnga'i mkha' klong ni gzhal yas khang gi rang bzhin no //
NK064(ngu)001:12081: de skad ces rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen pos ched du glu blangs so //
NK064(ngu)001:12084: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:12085: 'dis rang snang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12087: // le'u nyer gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12092: de nas bcom ldan 'das sogs te /
NK064(ngu)001:12093: rgyud don rdzogs par bstan pa de nas rgyud gdams shing gtad pa ston te /
NK064(ngu)001:12095: ston pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal kun tu bzang pos so //
NK064(ngu)001:12097: lhan cig pa'i 'khor rgyud yongs su dag pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12098: go phye ba'i 'khor ye ji bzhin pa'i de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:12099: gshegs pa nyid de phyi rabs kyi gang zag chos
NK064(ngu)001:12100: kyi mig can rnams la gtad /
NK064(ngu)001:12102: bstan pa gsang sngags rmad du byung ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'adi'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12104: rgyud 'di nyid 'gro ba'i phan bde'i gzhir mi nub
NK064(ngu)001:12105: par brtan par zung zhig ces pa'i 'di ched du
NK064(ngu)001:12106: brjod do // gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12109: rgyud rdzogs nas mdzad pa chos nyid du bzhugs tshul lo //
NK064(ngu)001:12111: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12112: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12113: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams pa /
NK064(ngu)001:12114: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12117: phyogs bcu sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:12118: kye kye zhes 'khor gnyis la bos nas /
NK064(ngu)001:12119: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK064(ngu)001:12120: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK064(ngu)001:12121: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12122: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas
NK064(ngu)001:12123: pa gzhi rang bzhin gyi rgyud yin pas de'i don
NK064(ngu)001:12124: rtogs par bya'o zhes gdams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12126: gzung 'dzin sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:12127: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems kyi
NK064(ngu)001:12128: spros pa la zhen pas blo mngon par 'chel zhing
NK064(ngu)001:12129: goms pa yi mthus rang gi rnam rtog zhags pa
NK064(ngu)001:12130: dang 'dra bas khams gsum rigs drug gi gnas so
NK064(ngu)001:12131: sor 'dzin cing sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag par gyur
NK064(ngu)001:12132: pas na / de las grol bar gdams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12134: sa rnams sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:12135: de las grol byed dbang po'i rim pas theg pa
NK064(ngu)001:12136: so so'i sa rnams dang lam gyi khyad par ma
NK064(ngu)001:12137: 'dres par bkod pa nyan rang byang sems dang phyi
NK064(ngu)001:12138: rgyud gsum gyi theg pa yang rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:12139: snying po 'dir 'gro ba'i lam stegs yin pas na
NK064(ngu)001:12140: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam 'di nyid nyams su blang
NK064(ngu)001:12141: bar gdams pa'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12142: ye shes sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK064(ngu)001:12143: de ltar lam mthar phyin pas spangs pa dang rtogs
NK064(ngu)001:12144: pa'i ye shes ngo mtshar ba brnyes nas sku gsung
NK064(ngu)001:12145: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i yon tan
NK064(ngu)001:12146: rab 'byams mnga' ba nyid kyis phrin las gsung chos
NK064(ngu)001:12147: kyi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba'ang
NK064(ngu)001:12148: gdul bya'i don du mi 'gyur ba ni gang cung
NK064(ngu)001:12149: zad cig kyang rnam pa thams cad du yongs su
NK064(ngu)001:12150: ma gsungs te gsung bar mi mdzad pas na /
NK064(ngu)001:12151: de nyid thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12152: mdor na gzhi lam 'bras gsum yang rang bzhin gyi
NK064(ngu)001:12153: rgyud du 'dus pas na ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12154: don de las nam yang mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'o
NK064(ngu)001:12155: // gnyis pa gtad pa la gsum te /
NK064(ngu)001:12156: lhan cig pa'i 'khor sdud pa po dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12157: go phye ba'i 'khor phyi rabs kyi gang zag dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12158: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams la gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12160: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la zhes sogs rkang pa lnga ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12161: phyogs dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la
NK064(ngu)001:12162: dgongs pa gsang ba'i snying po 'di las lhag pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12163: don gzhan cung zad kyang mi mnga' bas 'di'i brjod
NK064(ngu)001:12164: bya ni zab pa'i phyir yod pa sgro 'dogs dang
NK064(ngu)001:12165: med pa skur ba 'debs pa sogs mtha'i spros pa
NK064(ngu)001:12166: thams cad nye bar zhi ba'i rang bzhin te /
NK064(ngu)001:12168: zab pa nyid de sgro 'dogs dang //
NK064(ngu)001:12169: skur pa'i mtha' las grol ba nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:12171: de rjod byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud gsang ba'i
NK064(ngu)001:12172: snying po de kho na nyid nges pa zhes bya
NK064(ngu)001:12173: ba 'di nyid kyang sgro skur thams cad dang bral
NK064(ngu)001:12174: ba'o // de ltar ston pa'i bdag nyid kyis rang
NK064(ngu)001:12175: bzhin chos nyid de bzhin nyid nges pa'i dbyings rim
NK064(ngu)001:12176: nas phyung ba'i rgyud 'di zung zhig ces sdud pa
NK064(ngu)001:12179: gang zag chos mig can la gtad pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12180: nges par lung bstan pa'i sgo nas gtad pa'i 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12182: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12183: phyogs dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK064(ngu)001:12184: gsung gi phyag rgya gsang chen snying po yi ge'i
NK064(ngu)001:12185: rgyud 'di ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig
NK064(ngu)001:12186: rang gis tshul bzhin du rtogs nas gzhan la ma
NK064(ngu)001:12187: nor bar smra bar byed pa de nyid ni kun
NK064(ngu)001:12188: tu bzang po nga dang tha mi dad pa yin
NK064(ngu)001:12189: cing / phan nus zab mo'i dbang yang rang bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:12190: gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir rgyud 'di bzung la mi nub
NK064(ngu)001:12193: de ni sogs rkang pa gsum ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12194: rgyud 'di 'dzin cing ston pa'i gang zag de ni
NK064(ngu)001:12195: nges pa kho nar gzhan la ston pa rig pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12196: skyes bu dang / de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK064(ngu)001:12197: zhes sangs rgyas su lung bstan te //
NK064(ngu)001:12199: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK064(ngu)001:12200: rang snang rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK064(ngu)001:12201: rig 'dzin mchog de lhun grub pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12202: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK064(ngu)001:12203: sa sbyong sems dpas bskyed du med //
NK064(ngu)001:12204: bde gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK064(ngu)001:12205: rig pa'i skyes bur lung thob pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12207: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sras kyi dwangs ma yin te /
NK064(ngu)001:12208: de ni kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi gsang ba zab mo 'di las skyes pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK064(ngu)001:12209: sa rab ste sa thams cad kyi mchog rig pa
NK064(ngu)001:12210: 'dzin pa'am rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la gnas pa
NK064(ngu)001:12211: yin te / de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK064(ngu)001:12213: de bas na rang gis don phyin ci ma log
NK064(ngu)001:12214: par rtogs par byas nas snod ldan rnams la ston
NK064(ngu)001:12218: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK064(ngu)001:12219: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:12220: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:12221: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK064(ngu)001:12222: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa la //
NK064(ngu)001:12223: gsang ba'i snying po mchog tu gtad //
NK064(ngu)001:12224: ces ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams la bstan pa skyong zhing phyogs bcur spel bar gnyer gtad pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12225: gsum pa mdzad pa chos nyid du bzhugs tshul ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12227: rgyud don de skad ces brjod pas ston 'khor gyi
NK064(ngu)001:12228: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa dbyer med
NK064(ngu)001:12229: par gyur cing / rgyud kyi mdzad pa rdzogs pas
NK064(ngu)001:12230: dgyes nas dus bzhi tha dad du mi dmigs pa
NK064(ngu)001:12231: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su rnam par
NK064(ngu)001:12232: dag pa'i zhing khams snang zhing bkod pa thams cad
NK064(ngu)001:12233: ston pa nyid kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK064(ngu)001:12234: rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun gyis grub pa stug po
NK064(ngu)001:12235: bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du 'pho 'gyur med par bzhugs
NK064(ngu)001:12236: par gyur cing / so // gsum pa mtshan ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12238: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis yod pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:12239: 'dis tha ma rgyud rdzogs shing ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa la mnyes pa dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12240: gdams shing gtad pa'i sgo nas rgyud yongs su bzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12242: // gsum pa mjug gi don rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK064(ngu)001:12244: brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer med pa'i rang
NK064(ngu)001:12245: bzhin lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don ye
NK064(ngu)001:12246: nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs
NK064(ngu)001:12247: rgyas par ston pas na gzhan las khyad par du
NK064(ngu)001:12248: 'phags pa'i phyir / de rjod byed yi ge'i rgyud 'di la'ang 'phags pa zhes btags so //
NK064(ngu)001:12249: rtog pa ni dngos grub rnam pa gnyis sgrub pa'i thabs kyi rgyud thams cad la grags shing /
NK064(ngu)001:12250: de dag thams cad las rgyud 'di mchog tu gyur pas na rgyal po'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12251: de lta bu'i rgyud gyi rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bya ba /
NK064(ngu)001:12252: de'i le'u'i grangs ni stong phrag brgya ba ste 'bum
NK064(ngu)001:12253: phrag gcig bzhugs pa las phyungs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK064(ngu)001:12254: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi bdag nyid du bstan
NK064(ngu)001:12255: pa 'di ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:12256: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi rgyud thams cad kyi 'byung
NK064(ngu)001:12257: khungs sam 'phro gzhir gyur pas lung gi spyi 'grel
NK064(ngu)001:12258: / phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin
NK064(ngu)001:12259: gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi gsang ba las
NK064(ngu)001:12261: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK064(ngu)001:12262: pa zhes bya ba'i rgyud 'di las bstan pa dang
NK064(ngu)001:12263: theg pa thams cad ma lus par 'phros te chos
NK064(ngu)001:12264: kyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa bskor ba
NK064(ngu)001:12265: de dag gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug bgrod pa
NK064(ngu)001:12266: gcig pas kun gyi 'bras bu bla na med pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12267: mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud chen po rdzogs so zhes pa
NK064(ngu)001:12268: ni gtan la phab zin pa'i don dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12269: i ti zhes pa ni shin tu zab pa'i don no //
NK064(ngu)001:12270: glegs bam gyi mthar rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma la mi tra'i zhal snga nas dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12271: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12272: rma +aa tsar+ya rin chen mchog gis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12274: rgyud 'di la lo pan sdebs pa'i gzhi 'gyur gsum yod par grags shing /
NK064(ngu)001:12275: de'ang sangs rgyas gsang ba dang bee ro tsa na'i snga 'gyur /
NK064(ngu)001:12276: slob dpon chen po pad+ma dang gnyags kyi bar 'gyur /
NK064(ngu)001:12277: bi ma la dang rma gnyags thun mong gi phyi 'gyur rnams las 'dir phyi ma ste /
NK064(ngu)001:12278: lo pan de rnams kyis legs par bsgyur zhing 'chad
NK064(ngu)001:12279: nyan gyis gtan la phab nas dar rgyas su mdzad
NK064(ngu)001:12280: do // zab rgyas bde gsheg gsung rab ma lus pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12281: phul gyur dpal ldan gsang ba snying po lta'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12282: thar 'dod rnams kyi 'jug ngogs gzhan med pas //
NK064(ngu)001:12283: 'jig rten 'di na mtshungs med yin bzhin nor /
NK064(ngu)001:12285: 1 / de don ji bzhin 'chad la zla bral ba //
NK064(ngu)001:12286: dpal ldan zur ba'i bka' srol bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK064(ngu)001:12287: gter chen bla ma'i thugs mtshor 'khyil ba las //
NK064(ngu)001:12288: dad brtson rnga yab rtse mos bcud du blangs /
NK064(ngu)001:12290: 2 / shin tu rnyed dka' gsang chen rdo rje'i tshig /
NK064(ngu)001:12291: dbye bar dka' mo rang dang rje mthun par //
NK064(ngu)001:12292: rnam par phye 'di dpal ldan gsang ba'i bdag /
NK064(ngu)001:12293: dgongs pa mdzes byed legs bshad rgyan du rlom /
NK064(ngu)001:12295: 3 / sbrang bu'i bgrod pas nam mkha' mtha'i 'tshol ltar //
NK064(ngu)001:12296: gsang chen zab mo byis blo'i spyod yul min //
NK064(ngu)001:12297: de phyir blun blos 'dir nongs gyur pa'i tshogs //
NK064(ngu)001:12298: 'phags dang dam pa rnams kyis bzod par mdzod /
NK064(ngu)001:12300: 4 / skye bo phal cher grags pa'i rjes 'gro bas //
NK064(ngu)001:12301: 'phags dang mkhas gzhung rnams kyang phyogs gcig tu //
NK064(ngu)001:12302: len pa min na bdag gzhung lta ci smos //
NK064(ngu)001:12303: de phyir gzhan don 'gyur snyam spro ba med /
NK064(ngu)001:12305: 5 / 'on kyang dam pa'i gsung gis bskul ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:12306: rang gi blo la'ang goms pa skye ba'i slad //
NK064(ngu)001:12307: blo rmongs gyur kyang bla ma'i man ngag la //
NK064(ngu)001:12308: brten nas rnam par bshad la skyon yod min /
NK064(ngu)001:12310: 6 / 'di las rnam dkar dge ba gang thob pa //
NK064(ngu)001:12311: de yis mkha' mnyam lus can thams cad kun //
NK064(ngu)001:12312: rmad byung lam gyi dri ma yongs spyangs te //
NK064(ngu)001:12313: rang byung ye shes mngon du rtogs par shog 7 /
NK064(ngu)001:12314: phyogs lhung sgro skur bral ba'i blo gros mkhar //
NK064(ngu)001:12315: rnam par song ba'i legs bshad 'od brgya pa //
NK064(ngu)001:12316: shar ba yis ni mi shes rmongs pa'i mun //
NK064(ngu)001:12317: mthar byed bkra shis snang ba 'bar gyur cig 8 /
NK064(ngu)001:12318: dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi 'grel pa grol
NK064(ngu)001:12319: lam gtso bor ston pa gsang bdag dgongs rgyan zhes
NK064(ngu)001:12320: bya ba 'di ni dpal gdong chu bya'i lo le'u
NK064(ngu)001:12321: gsum pa yan chad tsam grub pa las /
NK064(ngu)001:12322: de man chad le lo'i dbang gis lus pa phyis
NK064(ngu)001:12323: rje bla ma dam pa'i sras kyi thu bo thugs
NK064(ngu)001:12324: rje dang mkhyen rab rmad du byung ba zhabs drung
NK064(ngu)001:12325: rin po che sku mched gzigs pa'i slad dang /
NK064(ngu)001:12326: blo gsar don gnyer can mang pos kyang bskul zhing /
NK064(ngu)001:12327: khyad par sngon goms kyi yon tan phul du byung
NK064(ngu)001:12328: bas spras pa dpal ri sprul pa'i sku ngag dbang
NK064(ngu)001:12330: mang thos spong ba la gzhol ba me rag chos
NK064(ngu)001:12331: rje pad+ma phrin las dbang phyug gnyis kyis nan tan
NK064(ngu)001:12332: chen po'i gsung gis nye bar bskul ba la brten
NK064(ngu)001:12333: nas / dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo
NK064(ngu)001:12334: bo tshad med pa'i thugs rje dang dri ma med
NK064(ngu)001:12335: pa'i ye shes la mnga' 'byor ba mtshan brjod par
NK064(ngu)001:12336: dka' ba gter chen chos kyi rgyal po gter bdag
NK064(ngu)001:12337: gling ba'i bka' drin gyis 'tsho ba smyos kyi dge
NK064(ngu)001:12338: slong rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais rnam gnon lcags 'brug gi
NK064(ngu)001:12339: nas / lo / ston ra khrums zla ba'i mar ngo'i tshes bcu /
NK064(ngu)001:12340: rgyal phur 'dzom pa'i 'grub sbyor bzang po la /
NK064(ngu)001:12341: yon tan rin po che'i 'byung gnas gangs ri'i khrod
NK064(ngu)001:12342: kyi pad+ma 'od 'og min o rgyan smin grol gling
NK064(ngu)001:12343: gi chos grwar sug bris su sbyar ba'o //
NK064(ngu)001:12344: 'dis kyang bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen po 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur cig //
NK064(ngu)001:12347: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying po'i khams //
NK064(ngu)001:12348: thabs rgyud lam gyis yongs sbyangs nas //
NK064(ngu)001:12349: 'bras rgyud sku bzhir mtshams sbyor ba'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12350: bla ma de la gus phyag 'tshal /
NK064(ngu)001:12352: 1 / 'og min zhing khams nyams dga' bar //
NK064(ngu)001:12353: khyab bdag ston pa kun bzang gis //
NK064(ngu)001:12354: gang gsungs rdo rje'i theg pa ni //
NK064(ngu)001:12355: gsang 'dzin rnams kyis bsdu ba mdzad /
NK064(ngu)001:12357: 2 / mkha' spyod grub pa'i zhing rnams su //
NK064(ngu)001:12358: 'phel grib med par bzhugs pa nyid //
NK064(ngu)001:12359: rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga sogs kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:12360: zhing 'dir mngon du mdzad pa gang /
NK064(ngu)001:12362: 3 / 'phags yul pan grub dgongs pa'i mtshor //
NK064(ngu)001:12364: rma gnyags bee ro la sogs kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:12365: bsgyur bshad gangs can gdung sel mdzad /
NK064(ngu)001:12367: 4 / de nas gnubs nyang zur la sogs //
NK064(ngu)001:12368: skyes mchog rim par byon rnams kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:12369: bshad sgrub phrin las nyi ma yis //
NK064(ngu)001:12370: gsang chen ring lugs kun gsal mdzad /
NK064(ngu)001:12373: thun mong min las gzhan dag tu //
NK064(ngu)001:12374: chos dkon gyur tshe bla ma'i drin //
NK064(ngu)001:12375: gzhal du med las rnyed 'di mtshar /
NK064(ngu)001:12377: 6 / de phyir sde snod rgyud kun mchog /
NK064(ngu)001:12378: mchog gsang gsang ba snying po'i rgyud //
NK064(ngu)001:12379: rgyud don ji bzhin 'grel byed gzhung //
NK064(ngu)001:12380: gzhung lugs kun gyi snying po gang /
NK064(ngu)001:12382: 7 / ngaga gi dabnga phyug grub pa'i lha //
NK064(ngu)001:12383: chosa dapala rgya mtsho'i rnam dpyod las //
NK064(ngu)001:12384: 'khrungs pa'i yid bzhin nor bu ni //
NK064(ngu)001:12385: gsang bdag dgongs pa'i rgyan du shar /
NK064(ngu)001:12387: 8 / gang de o rgyan mkhan po yi //
NK064(ngu)001:12388: ring lugs smin grol 'dus pa'i gling //
NK064(ngu)001:12389: bshad sgrub chos kyi rgyal mtshan gyi //
NK064(ngu)001:12390: rtse mor mchod pa nyid du byas /
NK064(ngu)001:12392: 9 / de las ji snyed chos kyi char //
NK064(ngu)001:12394: bris shing dag byed 'bum ram pa //
NK064(ngu)001:12395: o rgyan skal bzang zhes bya'o /
NK064(ngu)001:12397: 10 / brkos mkhan o rgyan rdo rje dang //
NK064(ngu)001:12398: rdo rje tshe brtan dge gnyen gyis //
NK064(ngu)001:12399: legs brkos smin grol gling zhes pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12400: chos grwar sna tshogs lo la bsgrubs /
NK064(ngu)001:12402: 11 / 'di las byung ba'i bsod nams kyis //
NK064(ngu)001:12403: chos dang srid kyi phun tshogs dpal //
NK064(ngu)001:12405: kun bzang go 'phang thob phyir bsngo /
NK064(ngu)001:12407: 12 / legs byas chu yi gter chen las //
NK064(ngu)001:12408: 'khrungs pa'i bsod nams nyi ma ni //
NK064(ngu)001:12409: phan bde'i snang ba mtha' yas pa'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12410: bkra shis kun tu gsal gyur cig 13 /
NK064(ngu)001:12411: ces gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde kun
NK064(ngu)001:12412: gyi rtse mo dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i 'grel pa
NK064(ngu)001:12413: gsang bdag dgongs pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba gnas lnga
NK064(ngu)001:12414: rig pa'i bshes gnyen mkhan chen lo ts+aa ba chos
NK064(ngu)001:12415: dpal rgya mtsho'i rnam dpyod las byung ba 'di nyid
NK064(ngu)001:12416: o rgyan smin grol gling gi rig 'dzin 'dus pa'i
NK064(ngu)001:12417: sde rjes 'brang dang bcas pa rnams thos bsam lhur
NK064(ngu)001:12418: byed pa'i mig rkyen du chu pho rta'i lo la
NK064(ngu)001:12419: par du brkos pa'i tshe 'gyur med rdo rjes smra
NK064(ngu)001:12421: mdo sngags chos tshul tshang la ma nor ba //
NK064(ngu)001:12422: mkhas shing grub brnyes rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i srol //
NK064(ngu)001:12423: thub bstan snying po gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i //
NK064(ngu)001:12424: bstan pa 'phel rgyas 'dzam gling khyab gyur cig /
NK064(ngu)001:12425: mkhan slob chos gsum ring lugs che //
NK064(ngu)001:12427: 'gro rgyud mchog gsum snang ba dang //
NK064(ngu)001:12428: mi 'bral dus gsum dge legs shog /
